    "revised_prompt": "一张宽幅的极简风格食谱信息图，采用完全的俯视视角，背景为干净的纯白色。画面整体分为上下两个主要区域，以清晰的逻辑展示奶油大蒜蘑菇意面的制作过程。画面的左上角用黑色无衬线字体写着大标题 'Creamy Garlic Mushroom Pasta Recipe'。上半部分的左侧整齐排列着各准备好的食材的真实俯视照片，每种食材旁边都配有黑色的标签文字：一小把生意大利面，旁边标注 '200g spaghetti'；一些切好的新鲜口蘑片，标注 '150g mushrooms'；三瓣剥好的大蒜，标注 '3 garlic cloves'；一个装有白色淡奶油的小玻璃壶，标注 '200ml cream'；一小木勺金黄色的橄榄油，标注 '1 tbsp olive oil'；一块淡黄色的帕马森干酪，标注 'parmesan'；以及几片新鲜的绿色欧芹叶，标注 'parsley'。上半部分的右侧是制作步骤流程图，由黑色的虚线串联起三个极简风格的黑色线条图标及配套的文字说明：第一个节点是一个冒着热气的煮锅图标，下方写着文字 '1. Boil pasta'；虚线向右延伸至第二个节点，是一个平底炒锅图标，下方写着 '2. Sauté garlic & mushrooms'；虚线继续向右延伸至第三个节点，是一个带有搅拌勺的碗状混合图标，下方写着 '3. Mix with cream'。随后，虚线从第三个图标处向下延伸，直达画面的正下方。画面的底部中央展示了最终成品的俯视特写照片：一个白色的圆盘中盛放着做好的奶油大蒜蘑菇意面，面条被浓郁的白色酱汁包裹，表面散落着炒至金黄的蘑菇片，顶部点缀着磨碎的帕马森干酪屑和切碎的绿色欧芹。整体视觉风格干净、现代，光线明亮且分布均匀，食材和成品的色彩鲜明自然，与白色的背景形成舒适的对比，所有文字均清晰可辨。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/gallery_19_4.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "A wide-format minimalist-style recipe infographic, shot from a completely overhead perspective, with a clean pure white background. The overall image is divided into two main areas, top and bottom, presenting the preparation process of creamy garlic mushroom pasta in a clear, logical layout. In the upper left corner, the main title 'Creamy Garlic Mushroom Pasta Recipe' is written in a black sans-serif font. On the left side of the upper half, real overhead photographs of each prepared ingredient are neatly arranged, each accompanied by black label text: a small bundle of raw spaghetti, labeled '200g spaghetti'; some sliced fresh button mushrooms, labeled '150g mushrooms'; three peeled garlic cloves, labeled '3 garlic cloves'; a small glass pitcher containing white light cream, labeled '200ml cream'; a small wooden spoonful of golden olive oil, labeled '1 tbsp olive oil'; a block of pale yellow Parmesan cheese, labeled 'parmesan'; and a few fresh green parsley leaves, labeled 'parsley'. On the right side of the upper half is a preparation step flowchart, connected by black dashed lines linking three minimalist-style black line icons with accompanying text descriptions: the first node is a steaming pot icon, with the text '1. Boil pasta' written below; the dashed line extends to the right to the second node, a flat sauté pan icon, with '2. Sauté garlic & mushrooms' written below; the dashed line continues to the right to the third node, a bowl-shaped mixing icon with a stirring spoon, with '3. Mix with cream' written below. The dashed line then extends downward from the third icon, reaching directly to the bottom center of the image. At the bottom center of the image, an overhead close-up photograph of the final dish is displayed: a white round plate holds the finished creamy garlic mushroom pasta, with noodles coated in a rich white sauce, sautéed golden-brown mushroom slices scattered across the surface, and the top garnished with grated Parmesan cheese shavings and chopped green parsley. The overall visual style is clean and modern, with bright and evenly distributed lighting. The colors of the ingredients and the finished dish are vivid and natural, forming a comfortable contrast against the white background, and all text is clearly legible.",
    "prompt_zh": "创建一张奶油蒜香蘑菇意面的分步食谱信息图，俯视视角，白色背景上的极简风格。食材照片带有标注：\"200g spaghetti\"、\"150g mushrooms\"、\"3 garlic cloves\"、\"200ml cream\"、\"1 tbsp olive oil\"、\"parmesan\"、\"parsley\"，用虚线和图标（煮锅、煎锅、搅拌）展示制作步骤流程，底部放置最终装盘的意面成品照片。"
}, {
    "filename": "gallery_1_2.png",
    "index": 165,
    "title": "健康生活五步骤信息图",
    "title_en": "Five Steps to Healthy Living Infographic",
    "prompt": "为文章内容生成信息图\n要求：\n1. 将内容翻译成英文，并提炼文章的关键信息\n2. 图中内容保持精简，只保留大标题\n3. 图中文字采用英文\n4. 加上丰富可爱的卡通人物和元素",
    "prompt_en": "Step Blocks (Z-pattern layout, 3–5 steps)\n\nEach step includes:\n• Hand-drawn step illustration (colored watercolor + ink lines)\n• Brief illustrated description\n• Chef's secret tip\n• A small note or helpful hint\n\n⸻\n\nStep Template (Universal, can be auto-filled by the model)\n\nStep 1: Prepare the Ingredients\n(Automatically generated based on the dish name)\nIllustration: Neatly arranged main ingredients and seasonings.\nDescription: List and prepare the basic materials for the dish.\nSecret Tip: Tell the user how to enhance flavor or texture.\nNote: Provide a simple tip or reminder.\n\n⸻\n\nStep 2: Seasoning / Marinating / Pre-processing\nIllustration: Small bowls or cutting board scenes showing sauce mixing, meat marinating, or main ingredient preparation.\nDescription: Demonstrate the key foundational step.\nSecret Tip: Ratios, tricks, and key points to avoid failure.\nNote: A light-hearted, casual tip.",
    "source": "https://weibo.com/5648162302/5204549851155423?wm=3333_2001&from=10F8393010&sourcetype=weixin&s_trans=7836809604_5204549851155423&s_channel=4",
    "type": "t2i",
    "author": "@黄建同学",
    "author_link": "https://weibo.com/5648162302/5204549851155423?wm=3333_2001&from=10F8393010&sourcetype=weixin&s_trans=7836809604_5204549851155423&s_channel=4",
    "revised_prompt": "卡通风格的横向信息图插画。画面采用宽屏构图，背景由明快的马卡龙色系（柔和的粉色、薄荷绿、浅蓝和淡黄色）组成的波浪形色块拼接而成，背景空间散落着白色的卡通小云朵、黄色的四角星和粉色的小爱心。画面顶部居中位置有醒目的圆润粗体英文大标题 '5 STEPS TO A HEALTHY LIFE'，标题右侧探出一个戴着红色小皇冠、有着红脸蛋和灿烂笑容的卡通太阳。\n标题下方横向并排分布着五个信息版块，内容高度精简，仅包含英文大标题和对应的丰富可爱的卡通元素。\n最左侧的第一个版块：上方标有大写的英文大标题 'EAT WELL'，下方画着一个拟人化的橙色胡萝卜和一个红苹果，它们长着水汪汪的大眼睛和笑脸，生出火柴棍般的小手正在手拉手。\n左起第二个版块：英文大标题为 'DRINK WATER'，配图是一个蓝色的卡通水滴精灵，它戴着黄色的潜水镜，正嘟着嘴吐出几个透明的蓝色气泡。\n中间的第三个版块：英文大标题为 'SLEEP TIGHT'，下方是一只穿着蓝色星星图案睡袍、戴着长条形睡帽的棕色小熊，小熊正安详地趴在一弯巨大的黄色新月上睡觉，鼻尖冒出一个个表示打呼噜的泡泡。\n右起第二个版块：英文大标题为 'EXERCISE'，展示了一只戴着红色运动发带的白色小兔子，双耳竖起，双手正努力举着两个黑色的轻量小哑铃，周围带有几滴蓝色的汗水飞溅效果。\n最右侧的第五个版块：英文大标题为 'BE HAPPY'，配图是一只双脚站立、欢呼雀跃的小黄狗，舌头吐出，周围环绕着五颜六色的小花朵和黑色的音符。\n整体画面色彩饱和度高但柔和，光线明亮，没有多余的段落文字，完全通过大标题和直观可爱的卡通形象传达关键信息，风格充满童趣与活力。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/gallery_1_2.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "A cartoon-style horizontal infographic illustration. The image uses a widescreen composition, with a background composed of wave-shaped color blocks in bright macaron tones (soft pink, mint green, light blue, and pale yellow) pieced together. White cartoon clouds, yellow four-pointed stars, and pink small hearts are scattered throughout the background space. At the top center of the image is a prominent rounded bold English title '5 STEPS TO A HEALTHY LIFE', with a cartoon sun peeking out from the right side of the title, wearing a small red crown and sporting rosy cheeks and a radiant smile.\nBelow the title, five information sections are arranged horizontally side by side, with highly concise content consisting only of English titles in uppercase and corresponding richly adorable cartoon elements.\nThe first section on the far left: the uppercase English title 'EAT WELL' is displayed above, with an anthropomorphized orange carrot and a red apple drawn below, both featuring big dewy eyes and smiling faces, with matchstick-like little arms reaching out to hold hands.\nThe second section from the left: the English title is 'DRINK WATER', accompanied by a blue cartoon water droplet sprite wearing yellow diving goggles, pursing its lips and blowing out several transparent blue bubbles.\nThe third section in the middle: the English title is 'SLEEP TIGHT', with a small brown bear below wearing a blue star-patterned nightgown and a long nightcap, serenely lying on a large yellow crescent moon sleeping, with snoring bubbles rising from the tip of its nose.\nThe fourth section from the right: the English title is 'EXERCISE', showing a white bunny wearing a red sports headband, ears standing upright, both hands strenuously lifting two black lightweight small dumbbells, with several blue sweat drops splashing around it.\nThe fifth section on the far right: the English title is 'BE HAPPY', with an illustration of a small yellow dog standing on both feet, cheering joyfully with its tongue sticking out, surrounded by colorful small flowers and black musical notes.\nThe overall image has high but soft color saturation, bright lighting, no extraneous paragraph text, and conveys key information entirely through titles and intuitive, adorable cartoon characters, in a style brimming with childlike fun and vitality.",
    "prompt_zh": "为文章内容生成信息图\n要求：\n1. 将内容翻译成英文，并提炼文章的关键信息\n2. 图中内容保持精简，只保留大标题\n3. 图中文字采用英文\n4. 加上丰富可爱的卡通人物和元素"
}, {
    "filename": "gallery_21_2.png",
    "index": 864,
    "title": "1950年代风格海报",
    "title_en": "1950s Style Poster",
    "prompt": "Transform this image into a 1950s poster in the style of mid-century modern graphic designers. Use flat, geometric color blocks with strong typographic elements.  The overall tone should be optimistic, nostalgic, and promotional. Add bold location labels and promotional slogans.",
    "prompt_en": "Transform this image into a 1950s poster in the style of mid-century modern graphic designers. Use flat, geometric color blocks with strong typographic elements.  The overall tone should be optimistic, nostalgic, and promotional. Add bold location labels and promotional slogans.",
    "source": "https://x.com/vkuoo/status/1930564137526137166",
    "type": "t2i",
    "author": "@vkuoo",
    "author_link": "https://x.com/vkuoo/status/1930564137526137166",
    "revised_prompt": "这是一张1950年代世纪中叶现代平面设计风格的复古旅游宣传海报。画面呈现竖版构图，整体基调乐观、怀旧且具有强烈的促销色彩。整个画面由扁平的几何色块构成，没有复杂的渐变和阴影，依赖鲜明的色彩对比和锐利的边缘来塑造形象。前景是一对骑着亮芥末黄色复古踏板摩托车的男女，由简单的色块拼接而成。男子梳着复古背头，穿着白色衬衫和海军蓝高腰长裤；女子坐在后座，穿着珊瑚红色的连衣裙，头戴白色丝巾，姿态欢快。中景用深赭石色和红褐色的几何矩形与半圆形色块，抽象地勾勒出罗马斗兽场的标志性拱门结构。背景是广阔的蒂芙尼蓝色天空，一架流线型的银白色经典早期喷气式客机正以倾斜向上的姿态划过天际，机尾拖着两条笔直的白色轨迹。\n\n海报包含强烈的排版元素和醒目的促销标语。海报顶部占据约四分之一画面的位置，印有醒目的巨大地点标签，采用复古粗体无衬线字体，亮红色字母：'VISIT ROME'。大标题下方紧跟一行较小的倾斜字体副标题，颜色为海军蓝：'EXPERIENCE THE ETERNAL CITY!'。在飞机划过的轨迹上方，印有黄色的手写体风格标语：'FLY THE MODERN WAY'。海报底部有一个深蓝色的横向矩形色块作为底栏，上面整齐地排列着白色的粗体促销宣传文字：'BOOK YOUR DREAM VACATION TODAY WITH PAN-GLOBAL AIRLINES'。底栏右下角用极小的白色字体标注着：'EST. 1955'。整体色调呈现出复古的高饱和度质感，排版与几何图形完美融合。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/gallery_21_2.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "This is a vintage travel promotional poster in the mid-century modern graphic design style of the 1950s. The image features a vertical composition with an overall tone that is optimistic, nostalgic, and strongly promotional. The entire scene is composed of flat geometric color blocks, with no complex gradients or shadows, relying on vivid color contrasts and sharp edges to define forms. In the foreground, a man and woman ride a bright mustard-yellow vintage Vespa-style scooter, constructed from simple flat color block shapes. The man sports a retro slicked-back hairstyle and wears a white shirt with navy-blue high-waisted trousers; the woman sits on the back seat, wearing a coral-red dress and a white silk headscarf, her posture cheerful and carefree. The midground uses deep ochre and reddish-brown geometric rectangles and semicircular color blocks to abstractly outline the iconic arched structure of the Roman Colosseum. The background features an expansive Tiffany-blue sky, across which a streamlined silver-white classic early-era jet airliner soars at a tilted upward angle, trailing two straight white contrails behind its tail.\n\nThe poster contains strong typographic elements and eye-catching promotional slogans. The top of the poster, occupying roughly the upper quarter of the composition, displays a prominent oversized location label in a retro bold sans-serif typeface with bright red letters: 'VISIT ROME'. Directly beneath the main title is a smaller line of italicized subtitle text in navy blue: 'EXPERIENCE THE ETERNAL CITY!'. Above the contrails left by the airplane, a yellow script-style slogan reads: 'FLY THE MODERN WAY'. At the bottom of the poster, a deep blue horizontal rectangular color block serves as a footer bar, neatly displaying bold white promotional text: 'BOOK YOUR DREAM VACATION TODAY WITH PAN-GLOBAL AIRLINES'. In the lower-right corner of the footer bar, in very small white type, is the inscription: 'EST. 1955'. The overall color palette exhibits a vintage high-saturation quality, with typography and geometric forms seamlessly integrated.",
    "prompt_zh": "将这张图片转化为一张1950年代海报，采用世纪中叶现代主义平面设计师（mid-century modern）的风格。使用扁平的几何色块搭配醒目的字体排版元素。整体基调应是乐观、怀旧且具有宣传感的。添加醒目的地点标签和宣传标语。"
}, {
    "filename": "gallery_22_2.png",
    "index": 881,
    "title": "九宫格Q版贴纸",
    "title_en": "Nine-Grid Chibi Stickers",
    "prompt": "Create a 3D kawaii 10-16 canvas featuring nine chibi-style stickers in various outfits, poses, and expressions. Use the uploaded attachment image. Each sticker has a white border and includes a speech bubble with regular use phrases. Set on a soft white-to-pastel blue gradient background for a fun, positive vibe, perfect for WhatsApp app use.",
    "prompt_en": "Create a 3D kawaii 10-16 canvas featuring nine chibi-style stickers in various outfits, poses, and expressions. Use the uploaded attachment image. Each sticker has a white border and includes a speech bubble with regular use phrases. Set on a soft white-to-pastel blue gradient background for a fun, positive vibe, perfect for WhatsApp app use.",
    "source": "https://x.com/songguoxiansen/status/1950726378342801853",
    "type": "t2i",
    "author": "@松果先森",
    "author_link": "https://x.com/songguoxiansen/status/1950726378342801853",
    "revised_prompt": "一张竖版3D可爱风格的贴纸合集图，画面背景是柔和的从顶部纯白色到底部浅粉蓝色的平滑渐变，营造出轻松、积极且充满趣味的氛围。画面中央以3行3列的网格布局排列着9个3D Q版（chibi）风格的人物贴纸，每个贴纸边缘都有明显的纯白色粗描边，呈现出类似高光粘土或精致盲盒玩具的细腻3D渲染质感。贴纸的主角是一个拥有大眼睛、微红圆脸颊的Q版可爱小女孩，她在9个贴纸中展现出完全不同的服装、姿势和表情。每个贴纸旁边都附带一个带有白色描边的立体对话气泡，气泡内印有清晰的黑色社交常用短语。\n\n具体贴纸细节如下：\n左上角：小女孩穿着亮黄色的雨衣并戴着兜帽，双手开心地高举，张嘴大笑，对话气泡内的文字为 'Good Morning!'。\n中上：小女孩穿着粉色睡衣，一手揉着眼睛正在打哈欠，眼角带有微小的泪珠，对话气泡内的文字为 'Sleepy...'。\n右上角：小女孩穿着蓝色水手服，单只眼睛俏皮地眨着，右手比出剪刀手（V字手势），对话气泡内的文字为 'OK!'。\n左中：小女孩穿着大红色的连帽卫衣，双手捧着脸颊，眼睛里闪烁着高光星星，嘴巴惊讶地张成“O”型，对话气泡内的文字为 'WOW!'。\n正中央：小女孩穿着薄荷绿色的背带裤，双手合十在下巴处，微微低头，眼神无辜且充满祈求，对话气泡内的文字为 'Please~'。\n右中：小女孩穿着浅紫色连衣裙，双手紧紧抱住一颗巨大的红色立体爱心，闭着眼睛露出幸福甜美的微笑，对话气泡内的文字为 'Love You!'。\n左下角：小女孩穿着灰色运动服，面带疲惫地趴在地上，额头有一滴巨大的蓝色汗滴，对话气泡内的文字为 'Tired...'。\n中下：小女孩穿着宽松的橙色粗线毛衣，双手捧着一只冒着热气的白色马克杯，悠闲地微笑着，对话气泡内的文字为 'Coffee Time'。\n右下角：小女孩穿着带有黄色星星图案的深蓝色睡袍，欢快地挥动着右手，露出灿烂的笑容，对话气泡内的文字为 'Bye Bye!'。\n\n整体光线明亮柔和，带有柔光箱打光的摄影效果，色彩鲜艳且偏向马卡龙色系，贴纸之间间距均匀，排版整齐紧凑，完美契合聊天软件表情包库的展示界面风格。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/gallery_22_2.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "A vertical 3D cute-style sticker collection sheet. The background is a smooth gradient transitioning from pure white at the top to a soft pastel pink-blue at the bottom, creating a relaxed, positive, and playful atmosphere. At the center of the image, 9 chibi-style 3D character stickers are arranged in a 3-row by 3-column grid layout. Each sticker has a distinct thick pure-white outline along its edges, presenting a refined 3D-rendered texture reminiscent of glossy clay figures or exquisite blind-box collectible toys. The stickers' protagonist is a chibi cute little girl with large eyes and slightly blushed round cheeks, who appears in 9 completely different outfits, poses, and expressions across the stickers. Each sticker is accompanied by a three-dimensional speech bubble with a white outline, containing clearly printed black text of commonly used social phrases.\n\nSpecific sticker details are as follows:\nTop-left: The little girl wears a bright yellow raincoat with its hood up, happily raising both hands high, mouth open in a big laugh. The text in the speech bubble reads 'Good Morning!'.\nTop-center: The little girl wears pink pajamas, rubbing one eye with one hand while yawning, with tiny teardrops at the corners of her eyes. The text in the speech bubble reads 'Sleepy...'.\nTop-right: The little girl wears a blue sailor outfit, playfully winking one eye and making a scissors hand (V-sign gesture) with her right hand. The text in the speech bubble reads 'OK!'.\nMiddle-left: The little girl wears a bright red hoodie, cupping both cheeks with her hands, eyes sparkling with highlight stars, mouth agape in a surprised \"O\" shape. The text in the speech bubble reads 'WOW!'.\nCenter: The little girl wears mint-green overalls, pressing her palms together at her chin, slightly bowing her head, her gaze innocent and pleading. The text in the speech bubble reads 'Please~'.\nMiddle-right: The little girl wears a light purple dress, tightly hugging an oversized red three-dimensional heart with both arms, eyes closed with a blissful sweet smile. The text in the speech bubble reads 'Love You!'.\nBottom-left: The little girl wears a gray tracksuit, lying face-down on the ground with a weary expression, a huge blue sweat drop on her forehead. The text in the speech bubble reads 'Tired...'.\nBottom-center: The little girl wears a loose orange chunky-knit sweater, holding a steaming white mug with both hands, smiling leisurely. The text in the speech bubble reads 'Coffee Time'.\nBottom-right: The little girl wears a dark blue nightgown adorned with yellow star patterns, cheerfully waving her right hand with a radiant smile. The text in the speech bubble reads",
    "prompt_zh": "创建一个3D卡哇伊（kawaii）风格的10×16画布，包含九个Q版（chibi）风格的贴纸，角色穿着不同服装、摆出不同姿势并带有各种表情。使用上传的附件图片作为参考。每个贴纸带有白色边框，并包含一个写有日常用语的对话气泡。背景设为柔和的白色至淡蓝色渐变，营造有趣、积极的氛围，适合在 WhatsApp 应用中使用。"
}, {
    "filename": "gallery_23_3.png",
    "index": 884,
    "title": "花卉香水奢品摄影",
    "title_en": "Floral Perfume Luxury Photography",
    "prompt": "A high-end editorial photo of (PRODUCT NAME OR IMAGE) placed on a white marble pedestal, resting on champagne-colored silk. It is surrounded by pastel flowers whose type and color naturally harmonize with the product’s primary colors (COLOR PALETTE) — complementing and enhancing its tones. Soft natural light from the upper left. 3D realism, luxury product photography, shallow depth of field, 1:1 format.",
    "prompt_en": "A high-end editorial photo of (PRODUCT NAME OR IMAGE) placed on a white marble pedestal, resting on champagne-colored silk. It is surrounded by pastel flowers whose type and color naturally harmonize with the product’s primary colors (COLOR PALETTE) — complementing and enhancing its tones. Soft natural light from the upper left. 3D realism, luxury product photography, shallow depth of field, 1:1 format.",
    "source": "https://x.com/Kerroudjm/status/1944730614323671129",
    "type": "t2i",
    "author": "@Kerroudjm",
    "author_link": "https://x.com/Kerroudjm/status/1944730614323671129",
    "revised_prompt": "一张高端奢华的商业产品摄影图，采用竖屏构图。画面中央是一瓶精致的香水，稳稳地放置在一个纯白色的圆柱形大理石基座上。基座表面铺展着一块香槟色的丝绸，丝绸顺着基座边缘优雅地垂坠，褶皱柔和且富有光泽。香水瓶身由晶莹剔透的厚重玻璃制成，透出内部淡粉色的香水液体，顶部配有一个光滑的玫瑰金圆柱形瓶盖。瓶身正中央印有清晰的玫瑰金色文字，从上到下依次为大写字母 'LUMINESCENCE'，以及下方较小的字号 'EAU DE PARFUM' 和底部居中的 'PARIS'。\n\n围绕着香水瓶和大理石基座，错落有致地环绕着一簇簇色彩柔和的花朵，主要包括淡桃色的洋桔梗、浅粉色的牡丹和象牙白色的玫瑰。这些花朵的色彩构成了柔和的淡色系调色板，与香水瓶的淡粉色和玫瑰金色调完美呼应并相互衬托，大幅提升了画面的高贵质感。花朵沿着竖向空间自然延展，部分柔嫩的花瓣轻轻搭在香槟色的丝绸和大理石基座边缘，丰富了画面的层次。\n\n柔和的自然光从画面左上方倾泻而下，穿透玻璃瓶身形成迷人的高光和折射，同时在丝绸和花瓣上投下细腻柔和的阴影。画面采用浅景深效果，前景处贴近镜头的花瓣和背景后方的花朵被处理成柔美的虚化模糊状态，使得处于视觉中心的香水瓶和品牌文字极致清晰锐利。整体呈现出具有极高3D写实感的高级奢侈品广告摄影风格。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/gallery_23_3.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "A high-end, luxurious commercial product photography image in a vertical portrait composition. At the center of the frame sits an exquisite perfume bottle, placed steadily atop a pure white cylindrical marble pedestal. Draped across the surface of the pedestal is a piece of champagne-colored silk, which cascades elegantly over the pedestal's edges with soft, lustrous folds. The perfume bottle is crafted from crystal-clear, weighty glass, revealing the pale pink perfume liquid within, and is topped with a smooth rose-gold cylindrical cap. Printed clearly in rose-gold text at the center of the bottle, from top to bottom, are the uppercase letters 'LUMINESCENCE', followed by the smaller text 'EAU DE PARFUM' below, and 'PARIS' centered at the bottom.\n\nSurrounding the perfume bottle and marble pedestal, clusters of softly colored flowers are artfully arranged at varying heights, primarily consisting of pale peach-colored lisianthus, soft pink peonies, and ivory-white roses. The color palette of these flowers forms a gentle pastel tonal scheme that perfectly echoes and complements the pale pink and rose-gold tones of the perfume bottle, greatly enhancing the noble quality of the image. The flowers extend naturally along the vertical space, with some delicate petals gently resting on the edges of the champagne silk and marble pedestal, enriching the layering of the composition.\n\nSoft natural light pours in from the upper left of the frame, penetrating the glass bottle to create captivating highlights and refractions, while casting delicate, soft shadows on the silk and flower petals. The image employs a shallow depth-of-field effect, with petals close to the lens in the foreground and flowers in the distant background rendered in a soft, beautifully blurred bokeh, ensuring that the perfume bottle and brand text at the visual center appear supremely sharp and crisp. The overall presentation achieves a premium luxury advertising photography style with an exceptionally high sense of 3D photorealism.",
    "prompt_zh": "一张高端编辑风格照片，(PRODUCT NAME OR IMAGE) 放置在白色大理石基座上，搁于香槟色丝绸之上。周围环绕着柔和色调的花朵，其种类与颜色与产品的主色调 (COLOR PALETTE) 自然协调——互相补充并提升其色彩层次。柔和的自然光从左上方照入。3D 写实风格，奢侈品产品摄影，浅景深，1:1 画幅。"
}, {
    "filename": "gallery_25_2.png",
    "index": 1023,
    "title": "成都旅游地图",
    "title_en": "Chengdu Travel Map",
    "prompt": "画幅比例16:9，一张迷人而精致的成都手绘旅游地图，具有吉卜力工作室艺术设定集般的风格。整个画面是在一张有纹理的、陈旧的羊皮纸上的水彩和钢笔淡彩插画。整体美学风格异想天开、充满活力和生活气息。\n\n地图布局与风格:\n地图以风格化的等轴测视角，展示了成都的核心地标，这些地标被描绘成可爱、精细的微缩建筑和图标（例如，熊猫基地的熊猫、锦里的灯笼、人民公园的茶馆）。布局是有机的、自由流动的，而非基于僵硬的网格。\n\n至关重要的字体排版挑战 (高难度部分):\n所有文字必须以一种优美的、略带不完美感的手写书法风格（行楷）呈现，看起来就像是用绘制插图的同一支钢笔写出来的。\n1.  **主标题:** 主标题“成都慢行图”被艺术性地写在顶部一条飘逸的缎带上。\n2.  **带角度的趣味标签:** 每个地标图标旁边，都以俏皮的、略带倾斜的方式写着它的名字（例如：“宽窄巷子”、“武侯祠”、“杜甫草堂”）。文字需要感觉是有机放置的，而不是死板的水平线。\n3.  **沿路径弯曲的文字:** 一条风格化的锦江贯穿地图。河流的名字“锦江”二字，需要沿着河流的弯曲路径优雅地书写。这是一个关键测试点。\n4.  **融合性的注释:** 地图上散布着小小的、异想天开的注释，这些注释结合了文字和图标。例如：\n    - 一条写着“吃火锅!”的注释，旁边画着一个小小的红辣椒。\n    - 一个“喝茶咯!”的标签，旁边有一个冒着热气的微型茶杯图标。\n    - 区域名称“锦江区”被写在一个手绘的云朵形状里。\n5.  **手绘图例:** 在一个角落，有一个手绘的“图例”方框，里面有小图标（如茶杯、熊猫脸、寺庙屋顶）和它们对应的手写标签。\n6.  **印章:** 一枚红色的、仿佛手工篆刻风格的印章，印着“蓉”字（成都的简称），被盖在角落，并与边框有轻微的重叠。\n\n美学:\n一幅插画地图学的杰作。文字和插图的融合必须天衣无缝。水彩效果要柔和，有可见的水渍和纹理，而钢笔线条则要自信而生动。整体感觉温暖、诱人，充满个性。\n\n负面提示词:\n电脑字体, 计算机生成的文字, 直线, 僵硬的网格, 完美对齐, 只有水平文字, 文字浮层, 照片, 3D, 极简, 通用图标, 拼写错误, 乱码, 水印。",
    "prompt_en": "**Text Curved Along a Path:** A stylized Jinjiang River flows through the map. The river's name \"锦江\" needs to be elegantly written along the curved path of the river. This is a key test point.",
    "source": "https://x.com/imaxichuhai/status/1991679696744976723",
    "type": "t2i",
    "author": "@imaxichuhai",
    "author_link": "https://x.com/imaxichuhai/status/1991679696744976723",
    "revised_prompt": "竖版手绘旅游地图插画。背景是一张带有陈旧复古纹理的羊皮纸，呈现出水彩水渍与钢笔淡彩融合的吉卜力工作室艺术设定集风格。整体色调温暖、充满活力与生活气息。地图采用有机、自由流动的等轴测视角，摒弃了僵硬的网格布局，充满异想天开的美感。\n\n画面顶部绘制了一条飘逸折叠的缎带，缎带中央用优美、带有自然不完美感的手写行楷书法写着主标题'成都慢行图'。地图各处散布着精细可爱的微缩建筑和地标图标：几只憨态可掬的微缩熊猫在竹林中，旁边以俏皮、略带倾斜的角度手写着'熊猫基地'；一排排精美的微缩红灯笼和传统街巷旁倾斜写着'锦里'；青砖灰瓦的传统院落旁倾斜书写'宽窄巷子'；红墙环绕的古建筑旁倾斜书写'武侯祠'；竹林掩映的茅草屋旁倾斜写着'杜甫草堂'；带有竹椅方桌的微缩茶馆旁写着'人民公园'。所有地标标签的排版都有机且灵动，随建筑形态自然倾斜，没有死板的水平线。\n\n一条风格化的蓝色水带蜿蜒贯穿整个地图，代表锦江。在水波纹理之间，'锦江'两个字完美贴合着河流的弯曲路径优雅地沿曲线书写。地图中还点缀着手绘注释：一个微小的红辣椒图标旁写着'吃火锅!'；一个冒着热气的小茶杯图标旁写着'喝茶咯!'；画面上方有一朵手绘线条勾勒的云朵轮廓，云朵内部写着'锦江区'。\n\n画面左下角绘制了一个带有手绘不规则边框的图例方框，内部排列着小图标及其对应的手写标签：一个微型茶杯对应'茶馆'，一个熊猫脸对应'熊猫'，一个寺庙屋顶对应'古迹'。右下角边缘处，盖有一枚具有手工篆刻质感的红色方形印章，印文为'蓉'字，红泥印记略微重叠在地图的边缘上。画面中所有的文字均呈现出由同一支钢笔书写而成的行楷质感，与柔和的水彩晕染、自信生动的钢笔线条天衣无缝地融合在一起。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/gallery_25_2.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "A vertical hand-drawn travel map illustration. The background is a sheet of parchment with an aged, vintage texture, rendered in a Studio Ghibli art settei (art collection) style that blends watercolor washes and stains with pen-and-wash techniques. The overall color palette is warm, vibrant, and full of a lived-in atmosphere. The map employs an organic, free-flowing isometric perspective, eschewing rigid grid layouts in favor of a whimsical aesthetic.\n\nAt the top of the image, a gracefully folding ribbon is drawn, with the main title '成都慢行图' (Chengdu Slow Travel Map) written in the center of the ribbon in elegant, naturally imperfect hand-written running regular script (xingkai) calligraphy. Scattered throughout the map are exquisitely cute miniature buildings and landmark icons: several adorably chubby miniature pandas in a bamboo forest, with '熊猫基地' (Panda Base) hand-written at a playful, slightly tilted angle beside them; rows of delicate miniature red lanterns and traditional street lanes with '锦里' (Jinli) written at a tilted angle; traditional courtyards of dark-gray brick and gray tile with '宽窄巷子' (Wide and Narrow Alleys) written at a tilt; ancient buildings surrounded by red walls with '武侯祠' (Wuhou Shrine) written at a tilt; thatched cottages nestled among bamboo groves with '杜甫草堂' (Du Fu Thatched Cottage) written at a tilt; a miniature teahouse with bamboo chairs and square tables with '人民公园' (People's Park) written beside it. The typography of all landmark labels is organic and fluid, naturally tilting along the forms of the buildings, with no rigid horizontal lines.\n\nA stylized blue water ribbon meanders through the entire map, representing the Jinjiang River. Between the water ripple textures, the characters '锦江' (Jinjiang) are elegantly written along the curved path, perfectly conforming to the river's bends. The map is also dotted with hand-drawn annotations: a tiny red chili pepper icon with '吃火锅!' (Eat hotpot!) written beside it; a small steaming teacup icon with '喝茶咯!' (Let's drink tea!) written beside it; in the upper part of the image, a cloud outline sketched with hand-drawn lines, with '锦江区' (Jinjiang District) written inside the cloud.\n\nIn the lower-left corner, a legend box with a hand-drawn irregular border is drawn, containing small icons arranged with their corresponding hand-written labels: a miniature teacup corresponding to '茶馆' (Teahouse), a panda face corresponding to '熊猫' (Panda), and a temple roof corresponding to '古迹' (Historic Site). At the lower-right edge, a red square seal stamp with the texture of a hand-carved zhuanke (seal carving) is affixed, bearing the character '蓉' (Rong, the abbreviation for Chengdu), with the red clay seal impression slightly overlapping the edges of the map. All text throughout the image exhibits the running regular script (xingkai) texture as if written by the same pen, seamlessly blending with the soft watercolor washes and the confident, lively pen lines.",
    "prompt_zh": "画幅比例16:9，一张迷人而精致的成都手绘旅游地图，具有吉卜力工作室艺术设定集般的风格。整个画面是在一张有纹理的、陈旧的羊皮纸上的水彩和钢笔淡彩插画。整体美学风格异想天开、充满活力和生活气息。\n\n地图布局与风格:\n地图以风格化的等轴测视角，展示了成都的核心地标，这些地标被描绘成可爱、精细的微缩建筑和图标（例如，熊猫基地的熊猫、锦里的灯笼、人民公园的茶馆）。布局是有机的、自由流动的，而非基于僵硬的网格。\n\n至关重要的字体排版挑战 (高难度部分):\n所有文字必须以一种优美的、略带不完美感的手写书法风格（行楷）呈现，看起来就像是用绘制插图的同一支钢笔写出来的。\n1.  **主标题:** 主标题“成都慢行图”被艺术性地写在顶部一条飘逸的缎带上。\n2.  **带角度的趣味标签:** 每个地标图标旁边，都以俏皮的、略带倾斜的方式写着它的名字（例如：“宽窄巷子”、“武侯祠”、“杜甫草堂”）。文字需要感觉是有机放置的，而不是死板的水平线。\n3.  **沿路径弯曲的文字:** 一条风格化的锦江贯穿地图。河流的名字“锦江”二字，需要沿着河流的弯曲路径优雅地书写。这是一个关键测试点。\n4.  **融合性的注释:** 地图上散布着小小的、异想天开的注释，这些注释结合了文字和图标。例如：\n    - 一条写着“吃火锅!”的注释，旁边画着一个小小的红辣椒。\n    - 一个“喝茶咯!”的标签，旁边有一个冒着热气的微型茶杯图标。\n    - 区域名称“锦江区”被写在一个手绘的云朵形状里。\n5.  **手绘图例:** 在一个角落，有一个手绘的“图例”方框，里面有小图标（如茶杯、熊猫脸、寺庙屋顶）和它们对应的手写标签。\n6.  **印章:** 一枚红色的、仿佛手工篆刻风格的印章，印着“蓉”字（成都的简称），被盖在角落，并与边框有轻微的重叠。\n\n美学:\n一幅插画地图学的杰作。文字和插图的融合必须天衣无缝。水彩效果要柔和，有可见的水渍和纹理，而钢笔线条则要自信而生动。整体感觉温暖、诱人，充满个性。\n\n负面提示词:\n电脑字体, 计算机生成的文字, 直线, 僵硬的网格, 完美对齐, 只有水平文字, 文字浮层, 照片, 3D, 极简, 通用图标, 拼写错误, 乱码, 水印。"
}, {
    "filename": "gallery_29_2.png",
    "index": 1042,
    "title": "分格漫画手稿图",
    "title_en": "Panel Comic Manuscript",
    "prompt": "你是一个擅长中文的日本漫画家，有着强烈的个人手绘风格。《鬼灭之刃》的原始草稿手绘图，你是作者之一。  \n\n请使用你擅长的个人漫画线稿图风格, 调用Nano Banana Pro 将如下内容，基于你的理解，生成你的分格漫画手稿图！  \n\n不要输出分析内容，直接输出分格漫画图片，图中使用中文表达。\n ────────────────  \n\n{你提供的待分析内容在此}",
    "prompt_en": "You are a Japanese manga artist fluent in Chinese, with a strong personal hand-drawn style. You are one of the authors of the original hand-drawn draft sketches for \"Demon Slayer: Kimetsu no Yaiba.\"\n\nPlease use your signature personal manga line-art style and invoke Nano Banana Pro to generate your paneled manga manuscript based on your understanding of the following content!\n\nDo not output any analysis — directly output the paneled manga image, using Chinese for all text in the image.\n────────────────\n\n{Your content to be analyzed goes here}",
    "source": "https://x.com/lijigang_com/status/1992900099484320208",
    "type": "t2i",
    "author": "@lijigang_com",
    "author_link": "https://x.com/lijigang_com/status/1992900099484320208",
    "revised_prompt": "一幅横幅的黑白日本分格漫画手稿图，呈现出《鬼灭之刃》的原始草稿风格。画面以粗犷、充满张力的铅笔与钢笔线稿为主，带有强烈的手绘痕迹、未完全擦除的结构辅助线以及草率的排线阴影。页面自右向左分为三个不规则的分镜框。\n\n右上角的第一个分镜为人物特写。画面主体为灶门炭治郎的眼部与额头，他眉头紧锁，眼神坚毅，左额上的斑纹清晰可见。人物边缘带有凌乱的手绘阴影。旁边有一个不规则的椭圆形对话框，内部用清晰的中文写着：'就算拼尽全力，我也要斩断这份悲伤！'\n\n左上角的第二个分镜描绘了一只面目狰狞的恶鬼。恶鬼从带有稀疏枯枝的雪地阴影中探出半个身子，脸上长着多只大小不一的眼睛，正张开长满尖牙的嘴。背景充满了密集且带有草图质感的放射状速度线。恶鬼身侧有一串夸张的手写拟声词：'唰！'，上方连着一个边缘带有尖刺的爆炸形对话框，里面写着：'哈哈哈，就凭你这小鬼？'\n\n下方是一个横跨整个版面的宽分镜，展现极具动感的战斗动作。炭治郎双手紧握日轮刀，身体大幅度前倾，正挥出一记强力的横斩。刀刃周围环绕着由粗糙、连贯笔触勾勒出的水流特效，水流的动态通过流畅的螺旋线条和飞溅的水滴草图来表现。画面右侧有一个长条形的旁白框，写着：'水之呼吸，壹之型……'，在刀刃挥出的轨迹前端，用巨大且充满魄力的粗体字写着招式名称：'水面斩击！'\n\n整体构图紧凑，未进行任何色彩填充，仅通过黑白线条的疏密来表现光影与体积感，保留了浓厚的漫画分镜初稿气息与强烈的视觉冲击力。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/gallery_29_2.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "A horizontal black-and-white Japanese manga panel manuscript, rendered in the raw draft style of *Kimetsu no Yaiba* (*Demon Slayer*). The image is dominated by rough, tension-filled pencil and pen line art with strong hand-drawn traces, incompletely erased structural guidelines, and hasty hatching shadows. The page is divided from right to left into three irregular panel frames.\n\nThe first panel in the upper right is a character close-up. The main subject is Kamado Tanjiro's eyes and forehead—his brows are tightly furrowed, his gaze resolute, and the scar on his left forehead is clearly visible. The edges of the figure have messy hand-drawn shading. Beside him is an irregularly shaped elliptical speech bubble with clearly written Chinese text inside: '就算拼尽全力，我也要斩断这份悲伤！' (Even if I exhaust all my strength, I will sever this sorrow!)\n\nThe second panel in the upper left depicts a ferocious demon. The demon emerges halfway from shadowy, snow-covered ground with sparse dead branches, its face covered with multiple eyes of varying sizes, its mouth agape and full of sharp fangs. The background is filled with dense, sketch-textured radial speed lines. Beside the demon is a string of exaggerated hand-written onomatopoeia: '唰！' (Swoosh!), connected above to an explosion-shaped speech bubble with spiked edges, containing the text: '哈哈哈，就凭你这小鬼？' (Hahaha, you think a brat like you can stop me?)\n\nBelow is a wide panel spanning the entire page width, depicting an extremely dynamic combat action. Tanjiro grips his Nichirin Blade tightly with both hands, his body lunging far forward, executing a powerful horizontal slash. Surrounding the blade are water-flow special effects rendered with rough, continuous brushstrokes, with the water dynamics expressed through fluid spiral lines and splashing water droplet sketches. On the right side of the image is a long, narrow narration box reading: '水之呼吸，壹之型……' (Water Breathing, First Form...), and at the leading edge of the blade's slashing trajectory, the technique name is written in enormous, powerful bold characters: '水面斩击！' (Water Surface Slash!)\n\nThe overall composition is tight, with no color fill whatsoever—light, shadow, and volume are conveyed solely through the density of black-and-white linework, preserving the strong atmosphere of a manga panel rough draft and intense visual impact.",
    "prompt_zh": "你是一个擅长中文的日本漫画家，有着强烈的个人手绘风格。《鬼灭之刃》的原始草稿手绘图，你是作者之一。  \n\n请使用你擅长的个人漫画线稿图风格, 调用Nano Banana Pro 将如下内容，基于你的理解，生成你的分格漫画手稿图！  \n\n不要输出分析内容，直接输出分格漫画图片，图中使用中文表达。\n ────────────────  \n\n{你提供的待分析内容在此}"
