    "prompt_en": "The character's facial expressions: joy, anger, sadness, happiness.",
    "source": "https://x.com/emakiscroll/status/1969959850676253016",
    "type": "t2i",
    "author": "@emakiscroll",
    "author_link": "https://x.com/emakiscroll/status/1969959850676253016",
    "revised_prompt": "一张动漫风格的角色表情差分设定图，采用竖屏构图。画面背景被均匀划分为从上到下的四个横向区块，分别展示同一个年轻女性角色的四种面部表情特写。该角色设定为拥有粉色长双马尾、用黑色蝴蝶结固定，眼瞳为清澈的碧绿色，身穿藏青色与白色相间的经典日系水手服，胸前系着红色领结。\n\n最上方的区块展示“喜悦”表情。背景为柔和的浅粉色，点缀着半透明的白色星星和樱花花瓣图案。角色嘴角微微上扬，露出温柔治愈的微笑，双眼微闭，长睫毛清晰可见，脸颊泛起淡淡的红晕。她双手轻轻交叠放在胸前。区块左上角带有标签文字'喜悦'和'Joy'。角色右侧有一个云朵状的对白气泡，里面写着文字：'能遇到你真是太好了。'\n\n第二个区块展示“愤怒”表情。背景为具有冲击力的暗红色，带有漫画风格的黑色放射状集中线，角色头部右上方有一个红色的愤怒符号（💢）。角色眉头紧锁形成倒八字，碧绿色的眼睛瞪大且眼神锐利，紧紧咬着牙，脸颊因为生气而微微鼓起。她双手交叉抱在胸前。区块左上角带有标签文字'愤怒'和'Anger'。角色左侧带有刺边形状的对白气泡，写着文字：'笨蛋！我绝对不会原谅你的！'\n\n第三个区块展示“悲伤”表情。背景为冷色调的灰蓝色，带有细长的雨滴和泪滴状装饰图案。角色眉头无力地下压呈八字眉，眼眶严重泛红且蓄满泪水，几颗晶莹的泪珠正沿着脸颊滑落至下巴，嘴唇微微颤抖并向下弯曲，神情委屈。区块左上角带有标签文字'悲伤'和'Sadness'。角色右侧带有边缘圆滑的对白气泡，写着文字：'为什么...为什么会变成这样...'\n\n最下方的区块展示“快乐”表情。背景为明亮活泼的橙黄色，点缀着白色的音乐符号和向外发散的阳光射线效果。角色正开怀大笑，嘴巴大幅度张开露出整齐洁白的牙齿，眼睛眯成两道弯弯的月牙状，充满生机与活力。她右手高高举起，比出一个充满活力的剪刀手（V字手势）。区块左上角带有标签文字'快乐'和'Happiness'。角色左侧带有爆炸框形状的对白气泡，写着文字：'哈哈哈哈！今天真是最棒的一天！'\n\n整张图片采用日系二次元赛璐璐平涂画风，线条清晰流畅，人物五官刻画精致，色彩明亮饱和，光影处理着重于突出面部肌肉的微小变化与眼神的情感传递，画面充满叙事感与角色魅力。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/gallery_2_4.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "An anime-style character expression variation reference sheet (hyoujou sabun settei) in vertical/portrait composition. The background of the image is evenly divided into four horizontal blocks from top to bottom, each displaying a facial expression close-up of the same young female character. The character is designed with long pink twin tails secured with black ribbon bows, clear emerald-green irises, wearing a classic Japanese sailor uniform (serafuku) in navy blue and white, with a red ribbon bow tied at the chest.\n\nThe uppermost block displays the \"Joy\" expression. The background is a soft light pink, accented with semi-transparent white stars and cherry blossom petal motifs. The character's lips are gently curved upward in a tender, healing smile, her eyes are softly closed with long eyelashes clearly visible, and a faint blush colors her cheeks. Her hands are lightly clasped together in front of her chest. The upper-left corner of the block bears the label text '喜悦' and 'Joy'. To the right of the character is a cloud-shaped speech bubble containing the text: '能遇到你真是太好了。' (I'm so glad I got to meet you.)\n\nThe second block displays the \"Anger\" expression. The background is an impactful dark red with manga-style black radial concentration lines, and a red anger symbol (💢) appears to the upper right of the character's head. The character's brows are tightly furrowed in an inverted V-shape, her emerald-green eyes are wide open with a sharp glare, her teeth are clenched tightly, and her cheeks are slightly puffed with anger. Her arms are crossed over her chest. The upper-left corner of the block bears the label text '愤怒' and 'Anger'. To the left of the character is a spiky-edged speech bubble containing the text: '笨蛋！我绝对不会原谅你的！' (Idiot! I will absolutely never forgive you!)\n\nThe third block displays the \"Sadness\" expression. The background is a cool-toned gray-blue, with slender raindrops and teardrop-shaped decorative motifs. The character's brows droop weakly in a downward V-shape (hapoji-mayu / 八字眉), her eye rims are severely reddened and brimming with tears, several glistening teardrops are sliding down her cheeks to her chin, her lips are slightly trembling and curved downward, and her expression is one of grievance. The upper-left corner of the block bears the label text '悲伤' and 'Sadness'. To the right of the character is a speech bubble with smooth, rounded edges containing the text: '为什么...为什么会变成这样...' (Why... why did it turn out like this...)\n\nThe bottommost block displays the \"Happiness\" expression. The background is a bright, lively orange-yellow, accented with white musical note symbols and outward-radiating sunray effects. The character is laughing heartily with her mouth wide open, revealing neat, white teeth, her eyes squeezed into two curved crescent-moon shapes, brimming with vitality and energy. Her right hand is raised high, flashing an energetic scissors hand (V-sign / peace sign). The upper-left corner of the block bears the label text '快乐' and 'Happiness'. To the left of the character is an explosion-shaped speech bubble (bakuhatsu-fuki).",
