    "title_en": "First-Person City Night Street Photography",
    "prompt": "draw what the red arrow sees \n/ \ndraw the real world view from the red circle in the direction of the arrow.",
    "prompt_en": "draw what the red arrow sees \n/ \ndraw the real world view from the red circle in the direction of the arrow.",
    "source": "https://x.com/tokumin/status/**1960583251460022626**",
    "type": "t2i",
    "author": "@tokumin",
    "author_link": "https://x.com/tokumin/status/**1960583251460022626**",
    "revised_prompt": "第一人称视角的真实世界都市夜景摄影照片，采用竖屏构图以突出街道的纵深感和两侧建筑的高耸感。画面展现了一段狭窄、繁华且潮湿的现代城市街道，视线沿着街道正中心向远方延伸。两侧是高耸入云的建筑群，遮挡了大部分夜空，建筑外墙布满了错综复杂的金属防火梯、生锈的管道和密集的空调外机，部分窗户透出暖黄色的灯光。街道两旁悬挂着繁杂的发光霓虹灯招牌：左侧前方突出的红色垂直招牌上清晰地用发光英文字母写着 'HOTEL'；右侧建筑外立面挂着一个亮蓝色的矩形招牌，上面写着白色的 'BAR'，紧挨着它的下方是一个黄色的方形小灯箱，上面写着黑色的字 'OPEN 24 HOURS'。在街道更深处的高楼上方，有一块巨大的电子广告牌，屏幕上显示着耀眼的青色发光文字 'NEON CITY'。地面是粗糙的黑色柏油马路，雨后的路面留有多处凹凸不平的积水，水坑像镜面一样完美倒影着上方招牌的红蓝光晕。马路正中央，一辆老式经典的黄色出租车正向街道深处行驶，尾灯亮起红光，车顶的黄色灯牌清晰地显示着黑色的 'TAXI' 字样。右侧人行道边缘，有两名身穿深色风衣、撑着黑色雨伞的行人，背对镜头，正朝着街道前方步行。视线的尽头，在街道两侧高楼形成的“峡谷”缝隙之间，一座巨型的针状钢铁电视塔在夜空和薄雾中若隐若现，塔尖闪烁着微弱的红色航空障碍灯。画面光线具有强烈的电影体积光效果，空气中弥漫着水雾，整体色调呈现出冷峻的青蓝色与浓烈的橙红色的强烈对比，画面极具沉浸感与写实感。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/gallery_3_1.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "A first-person perspective real-world urban nightscape photography shot, composed in vertical/portrait orientation to emphasize the depth of the street and the towering height of the buildings on both sides. The image depicts a narrow, bustling, and rain-slicked modern city street, with the line of sight extending from the center of the street toward the distant vanishing point. Soaring buildings on both sides block most of the night sky; their exterior walls are covered with intricate metal fire escapes, rusted pipes, and densely packed air conditioning units, with some windows emitting warm yellow light. The street is flanked by a dense array of glowing neon signs: on the left foreground, a protruding red vertical sign clearly reads 'HOTEL' in glowing English letters; on the right building façade hangs a bright blue rectangular sign with white text reading 'BAR', and directly beneath it is a small yellow square lightbox with black text reading 'OPEN 24 HOURS'. Further down the street, atop a high-rise, a massive electronic billboard displays dazzling cyan glowing text reading 'NEON CITY'. The ground is rough black asphalt; the rain-soaked surface has multiple uneven puddles that act like mirrors, perfectly reflecting the red and blue glows of the signs above. In the dead center of the road, a vintage classic yellow taxi is driving deeper into the street, its red tail lights glowing, with the yellow roof-mounted sign clearly displaying the black text 'TAXI'. On the right sidewalk edge, two pedestrians wearing dark trench coats and holding black umbrellas walk with their backs to the camera, heading further down the street. At the vanishing point, in the narrow \"canyon\" gap formed between the tall buildings on both sides, a massive needle-shaped steel television tower looms faintly through the night sky and thin mist, its spire blinking with a faint red aviation obstruction light. The lighting in the image has a strong cinematic volumetric light effect, with water mist permeating the air. The overall color palette presents a stark contrast between cool cyan-blue tones and intense orange-red tones, making the image highly immersive and photorealistic.",
    "prompt_zh": "画出红色箭头所看到的景象\n/\n画出从红色圆圈处沿箭头方向所见的真实世界视角。"
