    "title_en": "Kirby Sleeping & Blowing Bubbles Journal",
    "prompt": "梦境日记。粉红色的星之卡比睡在一颗星星上，嘴里吐出彩虹色的气泡。柔和的马卡龙色系，云朵和糖果的贴纸，闪粉笔画的细节，梦幻且甜美。",
    "prompt_en": "Dream Diary. A pink Kirby sleeping on a star, blowing rainbow-colored bubbles from its mouth. Soft macaron color palette, cloud and candy stickers, glitter pen details, dreamy and sweet.",
    "source": "https://x.com/songguoxiansen/status/1991795708308189668",
    "type": "t2i",
    "author": "@songguoxiansen",
    "author_link": "https://x.com/songguoxiansen/status/1991795708308189668",
    "revised_prompt": "一张手绘风格的手账日记跨页插画。画面中央是粉红色的星之卡比，它正闭着眼睛、神情安详地趴睡在一颗巨大的亮黄色五角星上，脸颊带有标志性的红晕。卡比微微张开的嘴里正吐出一连串大小不一的彩虹色半透明气泡，气泡表面折射出柔和的粉、黄、蓝、绿渐变光泽。整体画面采用柔和的马卡龙色系，背景是淡粉色、香草黄与婴儿蓝交织的水彩晕染底色。画面四周错落有致地装饰着多张带有白色描边质感的贴纸，包括软绵绵的笑脸云朵贴纸、粉白相间的螺旋棒棒糖贴纸以及透明糖纸包裹的彩色水果糖贴纸。在画面的左上角和右侧空白处，用可爱的深棕色手写体错落排版着日记内容，顶部标题为'梦境日记'，正文写着：'2024年5月20日 星期一 天气晴。昨晚做了一个好甜的梦，梦见自己飘浮在软绵绵的棉花糖云朵上，身边全都是闪闪发光的星星和五颜六色的糖果。真希望这个梦永远不要醒来~'。整个页面点缀着丰富的闪粉笔画细节，银色和金色的高光凝胶笔画出的十字星芒、波浪虚线边框以及散落的细碎圆点亮片遍布在卡比、星星和贴纸周围，营造出极其梦幻且甜美的童话氛围。横向构图使得各个元素丰满而不拥挤。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/gallery_42_4.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "A hand-drawn style bullet journal diary double-page spread illustration. At the center of the image is a pink Kirby, eyes closed with a serene expression, lying face-down asleep on a giant bright yellow five-pointed star, with his signature rosy blush on his cheeks. From Kirby's slightly open mouth floats a string of rainbow-colored, semi-transparent bubbles of varying sizes, their surfaces refracting soft gradients of pink, yellow, blue, and green. The overall palette employs soft macaron tones, with a watercolor wash background blending pale pink, vanilla yellow, and baby blue. Scattered artfully around the edges of the image are multiple stickers with a white-outlined texture, including soft smiling cloud stickers, pink-and-white spiral lollipop stickers, and colorful fruit candy stickers wrapped in transparent candy wrappers. In the upper-left corner and the blank space on the right side, diary entries are laid out in a cute dark brown handwritten font at staggered positions. The top heading reads 'Dream Diary,' and the body text reads: 'May 20, 2024, Monday, Sunny. Last night I had the sweetest dream—I dreamed I was floating on soft, fluffy marshmallow clouds, surrounded by glittering stars and colorful candies in every shade. I wish this dream would never end~'. The entire page is embellished with abundant glitter pen details—silver and gold highlight gel pen–drawn cross-shaped star sparkles, wavy dashed-line borders, and scattered tiny round sequin dots are spread all around Kirby, the star, and the stickers, creating an extremely dreamy and sweet fairy-tale atmosphere. The horizontal composition ensures all elements feel full yet uncluttered.",
    "prompt_zh": "梦境日记。粉红色的星之卡比睡在一颗星星上，嘴里吐出彩虹色的气泡。柔和的马卡龙色系，云朵和糖果的贴纸，闪粉笔画的细节，梦幻且甜美。"
