    "revised_prompt": "一张竖版数字插画形式的复杂流程图，背景是带有做旧网格纹理的泛黄羊皮纸。画面自上而下排列着大量颜色鲜艳、形状各异的流程节点和箭头，并配有夸张的美式卡通风格涂鸦。最上方是巨大的红色加粗标题：'HOW TO TOAST BREAD: THE ULTIMATE PROTOCOL'。下方是一个绿色椭圆形起始节点，写着 'START'。一条蓝色箭头向下指向一个黄色矩形，文字为 'LOCATE BREAD SUBSTANCE'，旁边画着一个用放大镜观察面包的涂鸦。箭头继续向下指向一个粉色菱形判定框：'IS BREAD ALIVE?'。左侧引出写着 'YES' 的红色箭头，指向一个橙色矩形：'BATTLE BREAD IN HAND-TO-HAND COMBAT'，旁边画着一片戴着红色拳击手套、表情愤怒的面包。下方连接菱形判定框 'WIN?'，'NO' 分支指向黑色墓碑形状的节点 'PERISH'；'YES' 分支则与主线汇合。主线菱形判定框右侧引出写着 'NO' 的绿色箭头，指向紫色矩形：'SLICE BREAD WITH LASER SWORD'，旁边画着一把发光的蓝色光剑切开面包。向下是一个青色矩形：'MEASURE THICKNESS TO NEAREST MICRON'，配有游标卡尺图案。接着是一个巨大的红色菱形：'CHOOSE YOUR TOASTER'。左侧分支写着 'NUCLEAR'，指向亮绿色发光的矩形 'REQUIRE PLUTONIUM CORE'，画着一个带有辐射标志和绿色烟雾的烤面包机。右侧分支写着 'CLASSIC'，指向蓝色矩形 'PLUG INTO 4TH DIMENSIONAL OUTLET'，画着一个扭曲的宇宙黑洞插座。两个分支向下汇合于黄色矩形：'INSERT SLICE INTO RECEPTACLE ALPHA'。紧接着是橙色菱形：'SET BROWNING LEVEL'。该节点引出三个分支：左侧 '1 (WARM BREATH)'，中间 '3 (GOLDEN GLORY)'，右侧 '6 (HELLFIRE)'。'HELLFIRE' 旁边画着猛烈的红色火焰。三个分支汇合至一个深蓝色矩形：'PUSH LEVER DOWN WITH EXACTLY 4.2 NEWTONS OF FORCE'，配有一个用机械臂按压拉杆的涂鸦。下方是一个紫色的循环椭圆：'PERFORM THE WAITING DANCE'，旁边画着一个跳舞的火柴人，带有沙漏符号。箭头向下指向一个爆炸形状的黄色节点：'POP!'。紧接下方是粉色矩形：'CATCH FLYING TOAST MIDAIR'，画着一片正从烤面包机中高高弹射飞出的面包。下方是青色菱形：'DID IT LAND ON THE FLOOR?'。'YES' 分支指向橙色矩形 'APPLY 5-SECOND RULE OVERRIDE'，接着向下指向 'BRUSH OFF LINT'，画着一片沾满毛球和灰尘的面包。'NO' 分支与前者汇合于绿色矩形：'PROCEED TO BUTTERING PHASE'。继续向下是黄色矩形：'SMEAR WITH HIMALAYAN YAK BUTTER'，旁边画着一头表情呆滞的卡通牦牛。最底端是一个巨大的金色、带有发光光环的椭圆形终点节点，内部写着大字：'CONSUME'。整个画面背景中填满了错综复杂的虚线辅助线、红色的警告标志以及随机散落的数学公式（如 'E=mc^2 * Toastiness' 和 'T > 300°C'），构图从上到下极度拥挤、夸张且充满科幻与荒诞感，色彩饱和度极高。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/gallery_44_4.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "A vertical-format digital illustration in the form of a complex flowchart, set against a yellowed parchment background with a distressed grid-line texture. Arranged from top to bottom are numerous brightly colored, variously shaped flowchart nodes and arrows, accompanied by exaggerated American cartoon-style doodles. At the very top is a huge red bold title: 'HOW TO TOAST BREAD: THE ULTIMATE PROTOCOL.' Below it is a green oval start node reading 'START.' A blue arrow points downward to a yellow rectangle with the text 'LOCATE BREAD SUBSTANCE,' alongside a doodle of someone examining bread with a magnifying glass. The arrow continues down to a pink diamond decision box: 'IS BREAD ALIVE?' A red arrow labeled 'YES' branches to the left, pointing to an orange rectangle: 'BATTLE BREAD IN HAND-TO-HAND COMBAT,' with a doodle of a slice of bread wearing red boxing gloves and looking furious. Below that connects a diamond decision box 'WIN?'; the 'NO' branch leads to a black tombstone-shaped node reading 'PERISH'; the 'YES' branch merges back into the main line. From the right side of the main-line diamond decision box, a green arrow labeled 'NO' points to a purple rectangle: 'SLICE BREAD WITH LASER SWORD,' with a doodle of a glowing blue lightsaber slicing through bread. Below is a cyan rectangle: 'MEASURE THICKNESS TO NEAREST MICRON,' accompanied by a vernier caliper illustration. Next comes a huge red diamond: 'CHOOSE YOUR TOASTER.' The left branch labeled 'NUCLEAR' leads to a glowing bright-green rectangle 'REQUIRE PLUTONIUM CORE,' depicting a toaster with a radiation symbol and green fumes. The right branch labeled 'CLASSIC' leads to a blue rectangle 'PLUG INTO 4TH DIMENSIONAL OUTLET,' depicting a twisted cosmic black-hole socket. Both branches converge downward into a yellow rectangle: 'INSERT SLICE INTO RECEPTACLE ALPHA.' Immediately following is an orange diamond: 'SET BRO",
