    "revised_prompt": "一张超写实的高档中式面馆商业美食海报，采用竖版构图与纯黑色背景，画面没有任何台座或支撑平台，所有元素均自由悬浮在空中。在画面正上方的视觉中心，悬浮着极具奢华感的标题，文字为'担担面 DAN DAN NOODLES'。中文字体采用极富表现力的手写毛笔字风格，呈现出厚重且立体的3D雕塑感黄金金属质感，表面有细腻的拉丝纹理，散发着温暖的金色光泽，在强烈的影棚光照下反射出逼真的高光，宛如悬浮在空中的纯金铸造笔触。\n\n在黄金主标题下方，垂直悬浮排列着担担面解构后的七个层次，所有图层均以45度俯视视角展示，具有统一的逼真光影效果。第一层是一堆鲜红色的干辣椒碎与金黄色的花椒粉。第二层是自然散落的浅黄色花生碎和鲜艳明亮的绿色葱花。第三层是盘绕堆叠的浅黄色手工碱水面，面条纹理清晰，根根分明。第四层是散落的黄色芽菜和翠绿的豌豆。第五层是一个透明玻璃碗，碗内盛满深红色的红油辣椒汤底，表面泛着油亮的光泽与清晰的反光，能够看到漂浮的辣椒颗粒。第一到第五层之间保持着均匀的正常间距。\n\n第六层是一处较大的空白过渡空间，间距是上方图层间距的两到三倍。该区域没有大型食材，仅有细微悬浮的油滴、缕缕上升的蒸汽以及飘落的细小食材碎屑，营造出充分的视觉分隔感与空间呼吸感。\n\n第七层位于最底部，是一碗盛装在传统深棕色陶瓷碗中的完整成品担担面。碗中完美融合了上方所有的食材，浅黄色的面条裹满油润明亮的红油，表面铺盖着花生碎、绿葱花、芽菜、豌豆和红辣椒碎。面条呈现出刚刚拌匀的诱人状态，油光锃亮并冒着微弱的热气。成品面碗的大小比例和视角与上方的解构食材完全一致，在其右下角还带有一抹明亮的星芒闪烁光效。\n\n画面中分布着带有优雅线条箭头的双语文字标签，分别指向对应的悬浮组件。第一层旁边的标签为'辣椒油&花椒粉 Chili Oil & Sichuan Pepper Powder'以及'麻辣风味 Numbing & Spicy Flavor'；第二层旁的标签为'花生碎&葱花 Crushed Peanuts & Scallions'；第三层旁的标签为'手工碱面 Handmade Noodles'；第四层旁的标签为'芽菜&豌豆 Yacai & Peas'和'丰富配料 Rich Toppings'；第五层旁的标签为'红油汤底 Spicy Red Broth'；最底层成品面旁的标签为'成品 Finished Dish'。\n\n整体画面采用戏剧性的工作室45度角打光，明锐的轮廓光精准勾勒出食材的精细纹理与玻璃碗的透明质感。空间中点缀着细腻的蒸汽特效与微小漂浮的油滴颗粒，营造出暗调情绪美学，展现出极具质感的奢华餐饮广告摄影风格。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/gallery_45_4.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "A hyper-realistic high-end Chinese noodle restaurant commercial food poster, using a vertical composition with a pure black background. The image has no pedestals or supporting platforms whatsoever; all elements float freely in mid-air. At the visual center of the top of the image, a luxurious-looking title floats, reading '担担面 DAN DAN NOODLES'. The Chinese characters are rendered in a highly expressive handwritten calligraphic brush style, presenting a heavy and three-dimensional 3D sculptural golden metallic texture with delicate brushed metal surface grain, emanating a warm golden luster, reflecting realistic highlights under intense studio lighting, as if pure gold-cast brushstrokes suspended in mid-air.\n\nBelow the golden main title, seven deconstructed layers of dan dan noodles are vertically suspended in sequence. All layers are displayed from a 45-degree overhead angle with unified realistic lighting and shadow effects. The first layer is a pile of bright red dried chili flakes and golden Sichuan pepper powder. The second layer consists of naturally scattered pale yellow crushed peanuts and vivid bright green scallion rings. The third layer is coiled and stacked pale yellow handmade alkaline noodles with clear texture, each strand distinctly visible. The fourth layer features scattered yellow ya cai (preserved mustard greens) and emerald green peas. The fifth layer is a transparent glass bowl filled with deep red chili oil soup base, its surface gleaming with an oily sheen and clear reflections, with visible floating chili particles. Layers one through five maintain even, normal spacing between them.\n\nThe sixth layer is a larger blank transitional space, with spacing two to three times that of the layers above. This area contains no large ingredients—only finely suspended oil droplets, wisps of rising steam, and tiny falling ingredient fragments, creating ample visual separation and spatial breathing room.\n\nThe seventh layer, positioned at the very bottom, is a complete finished bowl of dan dan noodles served in a traditional deep brown ceramic bowl. The bowl perfectly integrates all the ingredients from above: pale yellow noodles coated in glistening bright red chili oil, topped with crushed peanuts, green scallions, ya cai, peas, and red chili flakes. The noodles appear in an appetizing just-tossed state, glossy with oil and emitting faint wisps of steam. The size, proportion, and angle of the finished noodle bowl are completely consistent with the deconstructed ingredients above, with a bright starburst lens flare effect at its lower right corner.\n\nBilingual text labels with elegant lined arrows are distributed throughout the image, each pointing to its corresponding suspended component. The label beside the first layer reads 'Chili Oil & Sichuan Pepper Powder 辣椒油&花椒粉' and 'Numbing & Spicy Fl",
    "prompt_zh": "在画面构图的最顶部正中央，醒目地悬浮于食材分层之上的，是一个奢华的标题标签。文字内容为\"担担面 DAN DAN NOODLES\"，以富有表现力的手写中国毛笔书法（毛笔字）风格呈现。字体具有厚重的三维雕刻黄金金属质感（金属质感），带有拉丝表面处理、温暖的金色光泽，以及在戏剧性棚拍灯光下捕捉到的逼真金属反射效果。看起来如同锻造的金色笔触悬浮于空中。\n高端中式面馆美食海报，以解构分层方式展示担担面／麻辣四川"
