    "revised_prompt": "一张3D立体书插画，横向构图。画面中央是一本平铺展开的厚重精装书籍，书页上矗立着一个由多层纸张折叠展开形成的微缩立体场景。场景的主体是一座童话般的魔法森林蘑菇屋。蘑菇屋拥有一个巨大的淡粉色带白色波点的纸雕蘑菇伞盖，下方是带有明显纸张纹理的白色屋身，嵌着一扇半开的拱形木纹纸门和两扇透出暖黄色光芒的小圆窗。蘑菇屋周围错落有致地排列着多层立体的纸雕元素：一条由薄荷绿和纯白交替的石板小路蜿蜒通向屋门，道路两旁是层叠的粉彩薄荷绿纸质草丛、高低不一的松树剪影，以及几只躲在草丛后探出头的纸雕小兔子和半空中由细纸条支撑飞舞的蝴蝶。画面采用柔和的粉彩薄荷绿与淡粉色作为核心调色板，整体洋溢着充满童趣的手工质感。视角为轻微倾斜的俯视角度，完美展现了纸张层叠的深度、空间感和立体的机械结构细节。柔和的光线从侧面倾洒，在层层叠叠的粗糙纹理纸张之间投射出细腻真实的阴影，极大增强了三维立体效果。在翻开的左侧底部平铺书页上，用黑色复古衬线字体清晰地印着一行英文童话开篇语：'Once upon a time in the magical forest...'。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/gallery_46_2.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "A 3D pop-up book illustration in landscape composition. At the center of the image is a thick hardcover book lying flat and open, with a miniature pop-up scene formed by multiple layers of paper folding and unfolding rising from the pages. The main subject of the scene is a fairytale-like magical forest mushroom house. The mushroom house features a large pale pink paper-sculpted mushroom cap with white polka dots, beneath which is a white house body with visible paper texture, fitted with a half-open arched wood-grain paper door and two small round windows emitting warm yellow light. Around the mushroom house, multiple layers of paper-sculpted elements are arranged in varied heights: a winding cobblestone path in alternating mint green and pure white leads to the front door, flanked by layered pastel mint green paper bushes, pine tree silhouettes of varying heights, a few paper-sculpted little rabbits peeking out from behind the bushes, and butterflies supported in mid-air by thin paper strips as if fluttering. The image uses a soft pastel mint green and pale pink core color palette, exuding an overall handcrafted, whimsical charm. The viewing angle is a slightly tilted overhead perspective, perfectly showcasing the depth of layered paper, spatial dimension, and detailed mechanical structure of the pop-up. Soft light cascades from the side, casting delicate and realistic shadows between the layers of rough-textured paper, greatly enhancing the three-dimensional effect. On the flat left-side bottom page of the open book, a line of English fairytale opening text is clearly printed in black vintage serif font: 'Once upon a time in the magical forest...'.",
