    "title_en": "Black & White Pixel Animal Poster",
    "prompt": "A 16-bit pixel art poster showcasing all the black and white animals of nature. The composition uses a neat grid layout, reminiscent of a retro video game character selection screen or an encyclopedia page. Each animal is labeled with its English name in clear retro pixel font. The background is clean white or light gray, with vivid pixel details, exuding a retro aesthetic and high-quality production. --ar 16:9",
    "prompt_en": "A 16-bit pixel art poster showcasing all the black and white animals of nature. The composition uses a neat grid layout, reminiscent of a retro video game character selection screen or an encyclopedia page. Each animal is labeled with its English name in clear retro pixel font. The background is clean white or light gray, with vivid pixel details, exuding a retro aesthetic and high-quality production. --ar 16:9",
    "source": "https://twitter.com/Lessnoise365/status/1991791005319016642",
    "type": "t2i",
    "author": "@Lessnoise365",
    "author_link": "https://twitter.com/Lessnoise365/status/1991791005319016642",
    "revised_prompt": "一张16-bit像素艺术风格的海报。背景为干净清爽的浅灰色。画面采用横向构图和整齐的3行5列网格布局，整体视觉效果让人联想到复古电子游戏的角色选择界面或像素风百科全书图鉴。海报顶部居中有一行清晰的黑色复古像素字体标题 'BLACK AND WHITE ANIMALS'。\n\n画面主体由15个带有深灰色细像素边框的方形网格组成，每个网格内展示了一种自然界中的黑白动物。动物均由精细的高对比度像素块绘制，每个动物正下方配有清晰的黑色复古像素字体英文名称。\n\n第一行网格从左至右依次为：\n一只坐着啃食像素竹子的大熊猫，下方标注 'GIANT PANDA'；\n一匹侧身站立的斑马，身上像素条纹分明，下方标注 'ZEBRA'；\n一只直立的企鹅，黑背白腹，下方标注 'PENGUIN'；\n一头跃起的虎鲸，展现流线型的黑白身躯，下方标注 'ORCA'；\n一只翘起毛茸茸尾巴的臭鼬，背部有明显的白色条纹，下方标注 'SKUNK'。\n\n第二行网格从左至右依次为：\n一只带有黑白斑点的达尔马提亚狗，呈蹲坐姿态，下方标注 'DALMATIAN'；\n一只低头觅食的獾，面部带有标志性的黑白纵纹，下方标注 'BADGER'；\n一只立着长长黑白环状尾巴的环尾狐猴，下方标注 'RING-TAILED LEMUR'；\n一只侧身站立的马来貘，身体呈黑白分明的截断式配色，下方标注 'MALAYAN TAPIR'；\n一只站立的海鹦，黑白羽毛搭配特征性的三角形喙，下方标注 'PUFFIN'。\n\n第三行网格从左至右依次为：\n一头黑白花斑的荷斯坦奶牛，下方标注 'HOLSTEIN COW'；\n一只白头海雕，深色身体与纯白头部对比强烈，下方标注 'BALD EAGLE'；\n一只展翅的喜鹊，黑白羽毛错落有致，下方标注 'MAGPIE'；\n一只卧姿的白虎，白色皮毛上覆盖黑色像素条纹，下方标注 'WHITE TIGER'；\n一只展开黑白条纹翅膀的斑马燕尾蝶，下方标注 'ZEBRA SWALLOWTAIL'。\n\n整体画面展现了鲜艳且细腻的像素细节，像素块边缘锐利，没有任何现代的平滑模糊过渡效果。黑白两色在浅灰背景的衬托下显得极为纯粹，完美呈现了经典的复古像素美学与高质量的数字艺术制作水准。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/gallery_53_2.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "A 16-bit pixel art style poster. The background is a clean and crisp light gray. The image uses a landscape composition with a neat 3-row by 5-column grid layout, with an overall visual effect reminiscent of a retro video game character selection screen or a pixel-art encyclopedia compendium. Centered at the top of the poster is a clear line of black retro pixel font title reading 'BLACK AND WHITE ANIMALS'.\n\nThe main body of the image consists of 15 square grids with dark gray thin pixel borders, each grid showcasing one black-and-white animal found in nature. The animals are all rendered in finely detailed high-contrast pixel blocks, with a clear black retro pixel font English name directly below each animal.\n\nThe first row of grids from left to right: a giant panda sitting and munching on pixel bamboo, labeled 'GIANT PANDA' below; a zebra standing in profile with distinct pixel stripes, labeled 'ZEBRA'; an upright penguin with a black back and white belly, labeled 'PENGUIN'; a leaping orca displaying its streamlined black-and-white body, labeled 'ORCA'; a skunk with its fluffy tail raised and prominent white stripes along its back, labeled 'SKUNK'.\n\nThe second row of grids from left to right: a Dalmatian dog with black-and-white spots in a seated pose, labeled 'DALMATIAN'; a badger with its head lowered foraging, bearing its signature black-and-white facial stripes, labeled 'BADGER'; a ring-tailed lemur standing upright with its long black-and-white ringed tail raised, labeled 'RING-TAILED LEMUR'; a Malayan tapir standing in profile with its distinctly segmented black-and-white coloration, labeled 'MALAYAN TAPIR'; a puffin standing with black-and-white plumage and its characteristic triangular beak, labeled 'PUFFIN'.\n\nThe third row of grids from left to right: a black-and-white spotted Holstein cow, labeled 'HOLSTEIN COW'; a bald eagle with a dark body contrasting sharply against its pure white head, labeled 'BALD EAGLE'; a magpie with wings spread and black-and-white plumage in varied arrangement, labeled 'MAGPIE'; a white tiger in a reclining pose with black pixel stripes over white fur, labeled 'WHITE TIGER'; one with black-and-white striped wings spread open",
    "prompt_zh": "一张16-bit像素风格海报，展示自然界中所有黑白色的动物。构图采用整齐的网格布局，令人联想到复古电子游戏的角色选择界面或百科全书页面。每种动物下方用清晰的复古像素字体标注其英文名称。背景为干净的白色或浅灰色，像素细节生动鲜明，散发出复古美学与高品质制作感。--ar 16:9"
