    "revised_prompt_en": "A landscape-oriented, light-colored, minimalist-style infographic. The background is a pure pale yellow, with an overall soft and warm color tone and ample whitespace in the layout. At the top center of the image, there is a prominent black bold main title reading '一杯咖啡的旅程' (The Journey of a Cup of Coffee), immediately followed below by a smaller line of light gray subtitle text: '从种子到杯中的奇妙蜕变' (The Wondrous Transformation from Seed to Cup). In the central area of the image, four process steps are arranged horizontally from left to right, evenly spaced. Above each step is a dark yellow circular background block containing a white minimalist flat-style icon; below each icon are a black bold sub-heading and a gray explanatory paragraph, in that order. The steps are connected by gray minimalist rightward linear arrows ('→'), creating clear visual guidance. The first step on the far left features a plant icon with several leaves and coffee cherries inside the circle, with the sub-heading '1. 种植与采摘' (1. Planting & Harvesting), and the explanatory text: '在高海拔地区精心培育，手工采摘成熟的红色咖啡果实。' (Carefully cultivated in high-altitude regions, ripe red coffee cherries are hand-picked.) The second step features a large coffee bean and flame icon inside the circle, with the sub-heading '2. 处理与烘焙' (2. Processing & Roasting), and the explanatory text: '经过水洗或日晒处理后，在适宜温度下烘焙出独特的香气。' (After washed or natural processing, roasted at suitable temperatures to develop unique aromas.) The third step features a pour-over coffee kettle and dripper icon inside the circle, with the sub-heading '3. 研磨与萃取' (3. Grinding & Extraction), and the explanatory text: '将烘焙好的咖啡豆研磨成粉，用热水释放出浓郁的咖啡精华。' (Roasted coffee beans are ground into powder, and hot water is used to release the rich coffee essence.) The fourth step on the far right features a steaming coffee cup on a saucer icon inside the circle, with the sub-heading '4. 品鉴与享受' (4. Tasting & Enjoyment), and the explanatory text: '在宁静的时光里，细细品味每一滴咖啡带来的醇厚与温暖。' (In tranquil moments, savor the richness and warmth that every drop of coffee brings.) The overall composition is symmetrically balanced, with rounded and clean icon lines and no superfluous cluttered decorations, perfectly embodying modern minimalist design aesthetics.",
    "prompt_zh": "制作一张浅色极简风信息图，主题为《一杯咖啡的旅程》，包含四步流程、简洁图标、箭头流程、淡黄背景、清晰标题。"
