    "prompt": "一组具有[韦斯·安德森电影感的对称喜剧风三宫格写真。整体为高明度的暖色调，充满平和与松弛的情绪。统一使用圆润的无衬线字体添加字幕。画面中【水豚先生】与参考图一致，衣着为一条小小的浴巾和柠檬片眼罩。第一个宫格，对称构图：水豚先生舒适地泡在温泉里，头顶着毛巾，眼皮半阖，表情极度放松。几只小鸟和一只小乌龟安然地靠在它浮出水面的身体上，环境是露天温泉，周围是整齐的绿植和瓷砖，画面构图极度对称平衡，画面强调绝对的松弛感与和谐的共生。中文“不急，让水再泡一会儿”，英文“No rush. Let the water soak.”第二个宫格，俯拍视角：它面前的木质托盘上，一杯冰饮外壁凝结着诱人的水珠，旁边放着半本翻开的闲书，环境是从正上方拍摄，温泉水汽氤氲，构成完美的几何构图，画面强调细节的生活美感与清凉的视觉感受。中文“宇宙的尽头，是此刻的清凉”，英文“The universe ends here,inthiscool sip.”第三个宫格，全景：夜幕降临，水豚先生几乎要滑入水中睡去，只露出鼻孔和头顶的毛巾，小动物们也都在它身上安睡，周围亮起温暖的石灯，环境是深蓝色的夜空下，温泉被灯光照得暖融融，充满安宁的氛围，画面强调慢生活的终极幸福与温馨结局。中文“晚安，全宇宙的烦恼”，英文“Goodnight, universal worries.”",
    "prompt_en": "A set of three-panel photo series with a [Wes Anderson cinematic symmetrical comedy style. The overall tone is high-brightness warm colors, filled with a peaceful and relaxed mood. Uniform rounded sans-serif font is used for subtitles throughout. In the images, [Mr. Capybara] is consistent with the reference image, wearing a small bath towel and lemon slice eye mask. First panel, symmetrical composition: Mr. Capybara is comfortably soaking in a hot spring, with a towel on its head, eyelids half-closed, expression extremely relaxed. Several small birds and a little turtle rest peacefully on its body floating above the water surface. The setting is an open-air hot spring surrounded by neat greenery and tiles. The composition is extremely symmetrical and balanced, emphasizing absolute relaxation and harmonious coexistence. Chinese: \"不急，让水再泡一会儿\", English: \"No rush. Let the water soak.\" Second panel, top-down shot: On a wooden tray in front of it, an iced drink with enticing water droplets condensed on its exterior, beside a half-open leisure book. The setting is shot from directly above, with hot spring steam creating a hazy atmosphere, forming a perfect geometric composition. The image emphasizes the aesthetic beauty of life's details and a cool visual sensation. Chinese: \"宇宙的尽头，是此刻的清凉\", English: \"The universe ends here, in this cool sip.\" Third panel, wide shot: Night falls, Mr. Capybara has nearly slipped into the water to sleep, with only its nostrils and the towel on its head visible. The small animals are also sleeping soundly on it. Warm stone lanterns glow around them. The setting is a deep blue night sky, with the hot spring warmly illuminated by the lantern light, filled",
