    "author_link": "https://x.com/dotey/status/1920851135516082246",
    "revised_prompt": "一张包含上下三个宽屏宫格的电影截图拼接写真，整体呈现韦斯·安德森电影标志性的极度对称构图、高明度暖色调与复古色彩美学，氛围平和松弛。每个宫格的底部中央均配有圆润无衬线字体的中英双语字幕。\n\n第一个宫格位于画面上方，采用严格的中心对称构图。画面正中央，水豚先生舒适地泡在露天温泉里，头上顶着一条叠成方形的小小白色浴巾，眼睛部位戴着两片鲜黄色的柠檬片作为眼罩，眼皮半阖，神情极度放松。它的背部微微露出水面，两只圆润的小鸟和一只小乌龟正安然地停靠在它的背上。温泉池的边缘由复古的暖黄色与粉绿色马赛克瓷砖砌成，背景是修剪得极其平整对称的几何形状常绿灌木丛。画面底部居中带有白色字幕：'不急，让水再泡一会儿'，下方紧跟英文：'No rush. Let the water soak.'。\n\n第二个宫格位于画面中间，采用正上方90度垂直俯拍视角，呈现完美的几何切割构图。画面中心是一个漂浮在温泉水面上的方形浅色木质托盘。托盘内放置着一杯装满冰块与琥珀色液体的玻璃杯冰饮，杯子外壁凝结着细密诱人的水珠。冰饮旁边平放着半本翻开的纸质闲书，书页微微卷起。四周的温泉水面上升腾着氤氲的白色热气，水面波纹与托盘的直线边缘形成对比，视觉清凉且富有生活细节美感。画面底部居中带有白色字幕：'宇宙的尽头，是此刻的清凉'，下方紧跟英文：'The universe ends here,inthiscool sip.'。\n\n第三个宫格位于画面下方，为对称的全景视角。夜幕降临，背景是纯净的深蓝色夜空。水豚先生几乎完全滑入温泉水中，水面上仅仅露出它圆滚滚的鼻孔以及头顶的那块小浴巾。小鸟和小乌龟正安稳地趴在它露出水面的头顶毛巾上闭眼熟睡。温泉池的左右两侧对称伫立着两盏传统的日式石灯笼，灯笼内透出温暖明亮的橘黄色光芒，将原本深色的水面和升腾的水汽照得暖融融的，充满静谧安宁的睡前氛围。画面底部居中带有白色字幕：'晚安，全宇宙的烦恼'，下方紧跟英文：'Goodnight, universal worries.'。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/gallery_58_3.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "A composite film still arranged in three widescreen panels stacked vertically, exhibiting Wes Anderson's signature extreme symmetrical composition, high-brightness warm color palette, and vintage color aesthetics, with a serene and relaxed atmosphere. At the bottom center of each panel, bilingual Chinese-English subtitles are displayed in a rounded sans-serif typeface.\n\nThe first panel occupies the upper portion of the image, employing strict central symmetrical composition. At the very center of the frame, Mr. Capybara is comfortably soaking in an open-air hot spring, with a small white towel folded into a square perched atop his head. Over his eyes, he wears two slices of bright yellow lemon as eye masks, eyelids half-closed, expression supremely relaxed. His back slightly breaks the water's surface, and two plump little birds and a small turtle are calmly perched upon it. The edge of the hot spring pool is constructed of vintage warm yellow and pink-green mosaic tiles, and the background features immaculately trimmed, perfectly symmetrical geometric evergreen hedges. Centered at the bottom of the frame are white subtitles: '不急，让水再泡一会儿' (No rush. Let the water soak.), with the English line directly below: 'No rush. Let the water soak.'\n\nThe second panel occupies the middle portion of the image, shot from a direct 90-degree overhead bird's-eye perspective, presenting a perfectly geometric composition. At the center of the frame is a square light-colored wooden tray floating on the surface of the hot spring water. On the tray sits a glass filled with ice cubes and an amber-colored liquid, with fine, enticing water droplets condensed on the outer wall of the glass. Beside the iced drink lies a half-open paperback book laid flat, its pages slightly curled. Surrounding the tray, wisps of white steam rise from the hot spring water's surface, and the water ripples contrast with the straight edges of the tray, creating a visually refreshing scene rich in everyday aesthetic detail. Centered at the bottom of the frame are white subtitles: '宇宙的尽头，是此刻的清凉' (The universe ends here, in this cool sip.), with the English line directly below: 'The universe ends here, in this cool sip.'\n\nThe third panel occupies the lower portion of the image, in a symmetrical panoramic perspective. Night has fallen, and the background is a pure deep blue night sky. Mr. Capybara has slid almost entirely beneath the hot spring water, with only his round little nostrils and the small towel atop his head visible above the surface. The little birds and the small turtle are snugly nestled on the towel on his exposed head, eyes closed in sleep. On either side of the hot spring pool, two traditional Japanese stone lanterns stand symmetrically, emanating a warm, bright orange-yellow glow from within, illuminating the otherwise dark water surface and rising steam with a cozy warmth, suffused with a tranquil and peaceful bedtime atmosphere. Centered at the bottom of the frame are white subtitles: '晚安，全宇宙的烦恼' (Goodnight, troubles of the entire universe),",
    "prompt_zh": "一组具有[韦斯·安德森电影感的对称喜剧风三宫格写真。整体为高明度的暖色调，充满平和与松弛的情绪。统一使用圆润的无衬线字体添加字幕。画面中【水豚先生】与参考图一致，衣着为一条小小的浴巾和柠檬片眼罩。第一个宫格，对称构图：水豚先生舒适地泡在温泉里，头顶着毛巾，眼皮半阖，表情极度放松。几只小鸟和一只小乌龟安然地靠在它浮出水面的身体上，环境是露天温泉，周围是整齐的绿植和瓷砖，画面构图极度对称平衡，画面强调绝对的松弛感与和谐的共生。中文“不急，让水再泡一会儿”，英文“No rush. Let the water soak.”第二个宫格，俯拍视角：它面前的木质托盘上，一杯冰饮外壁凝结着诱人的水珠，旁边放着半本翻开的闲书，环境是从正上方拍摄，温泉水汽氤氲，构成完美的几何构图，画面强调细节的生活美感与清凉的视觉感受。中文“宇宙的尽头，是此刻的清凉”，英文“The universe ends here,inthiscool sip.”第三个宫格，全景：夜幕降临，水豚先生几乎要滑入水中睡去，只露出鼻孔和头顶的毛巾，小动物们也都在它身上安睡，周围亮起温暖的石灯，环境是深蓝色的夜空下，温泉被灯光照得暖融融，充满安宁的氛围，画面强调慢生活的终极幸福与温馨结局。中文“晚安，全宇宙的烦恼”，英文“Goodnight, universal worries.”"
