    "filename": "gallery_59_3.png",
    "index": 1902,
    "title": "废土竞技场电影分镜草图",
    "title_en": "Wasteland Arena Movie Storyboard Sketch",
    "prompt": "文生图：在一个巨大的、被摧毁的圆顶竞技场内的电影画面，有四个后世界末日幸存者。戏剧性的体块光穿透破碎的屋顶，在尘土飞扬的氛围中投射出强烈的耶稣光。地面上有碎石瓦砾，上方是扭曲的金属结构。土色调和棕褐色。超高细节，8K分辨率。\n分镜：以铅笔草图的形式呈现一组分镜头。",
    "prompt_en": "Text-to-image: A cinematic shot inside a massive, destroyed domed arena with four post-apocalyptic survivors. Dramatic chiaroscuro light penetrates through the shattered roof, casting intense god rays through the dusty atmosphere. Rubble and debris on the ground, twisted metal structures above. Earthy tones and sepia palette. Ultra-high detail, 8K resolution.\nStoryboard: Presented as a set of storyboard frames in pencil sketch style.",
    "source": "https://my.feishu.cn/docx/IKO3dWCeyobZ5CxWE18cV40xnth",
    "type": "t2i",
    "author": "@azed_ai",
    "author_link": "https://my.feishu.cn/docx/IKO3dWCeyobZ5CxWE18cV40xnth",
    "revised_prompt": "这是一张竖向排版的电影分镜图，采用超高细节的铅笔草图风格，整体呈现厚重的棕褐色与土色调。画面背景是一张带有轻微做旧纹理的棕褐色纸张，页面顶部居中写着手写体大写英文标题：'STORYBOARD: WASTELAND ARENA'。标题下方垂直排列着三个带有黑色粗线边框的矩形分镜画面，展示了一个巨大的、被摧毁的圆顶竞技场内的连续电影叙事镜头。第一个分镜框（顶部）是一个宏大的全景镜头，描绘了巨大的圆顶竞技场内部废墟。竞技场穹顶破裂出一个巨大的不规则洞口，上方边缘悬挂着断裂、错综复杂且扭曲的金属钢架结构。通过细腻的素描排线和留白，表现出戏剧性的体块光（耶稣光）从洞口倾泻而下，穿透尘土飞扬的空气，形成强烈的明暗对比。地面上堆积着巨大的混凝土碎块和瓦砾。在光柱底部的瓦砾堆中，站着四个极其渺小的人类幸存者剪影。该分镜框左下角标注着手写文字：'SCENE 1 - EXT. ARENA RUINS - DAY. WIDE SHOT.'。第二个分镜框（中部）是一个中景镜头，拉近展示这四个后世界末日幸存者。他们身穿破烂的废土风格披风，戴着防毒面具，背着沉重的拾荒背包，手中握着粗糙的金属武器。他们正站在高低不平的碎石废墟上仰望上方。强烈的顶光打在他们的肩膀和头部，铅笔的深色阴影勾勒出厚重的体积感，周围弥漫着清晰可见的尘埃颗粒。框左下角标注着：'SCENE 2 - MED SHOT. SURVIVORS ENTER THE LIGHT.'。第三个分镜框（底部）是一个低角度仰视镜头，前景是极其精细的碎石和一段生锈扭曲的金属工字钢特写。其中一名幸存者正抬腿跨过这块金属残骸，画面呈现出极强的透视感。背景上方是模糊的破碎圆顶轮廓和倾泻而下的强光。框左下角标注着：'SCENE 3 - LOW ANGLE. SEEKING A PATH.'。整张图片通过密集的铅笔交叉排线、精湛的素描阴影处理和棕褐色底纸的烘托，完美呈现了废土世界的苍凉氛围与电影级的镜头张力，细节丰富且极具立体感。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/gallery_59_3.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "This is a vertically formatted film storyboard illustration rendered in an ultra-detailed pencil sketch style, presenting an overall heavy sepia and earth-toned palette. The background is a sheet of sepia-toned paper with a subtle aged/distressed texture. At the top center of the page, a handwritten uppercase English title reads: 'STORYBOARD: WASTELAND ARENA'. Below the title, three rectangular storyboard frames with thick black-line borders are arranged vertically, depicting a continuous cinematic narrative sequence set inside a massive, destroyed domed arena. The first frame (top) is a grand establishing wide shot depicting the interior ruins of the enormous domed arena. The arena's dome has ruptured, revealing a large, irregular breach, with broken, intricate, and twisted metal steel truss structures dangling from its upper edges. Through delicate sketch hatching and reserved highlights, dramatic volumetric light (God rays) pours down through the breach, penetrating the dust-laden air and creating intense chiaroscuro contrast. The ground is heaped with massive concrete debris and rubble. At the base of the light shaft, amid the rubble, stand four extremely diminutive silhouettes of human survivors. In the lower-left corner of this frame, handwritten text reads: 'SCENE 1 - EXT. ARENA RUINS - DAY. WIDE SHOT.' The second frame (middle) is a medium shot, pulling closer to reveal the four post-apocalyptic survivors. They wear tattered wasteland-style cloaks, gas masks, heavy scavenging backpacks, and carry crude metal weapons. They stand on uneven rubble and debris, gazing upward. Strong top lighting strikes their shoulders and heads, with deep pencil shading delineating heavy volumetric form, and clearly visible dust particles permeate the surrounding air. The lower-left corner is annotated: 'SCENE 2 - MED SHOT. SURVIVORS ENTER THE LIGHT.' The third frame (bottom) is a low-angle upward shot, with the foreground featuring an extremely detailed close-up of rubble and a section of rusted, twisted metal I-beam. One of the survivors is lifting a leg to step over this metal wreckage, creating a strong sense of perspective. In the upper background, the blurred silhouette of the shattered dome and cascading intense light are visible. The lower-left corner is annotated: 'SCENE 3 - LOW ANGLE. SEEKING A PATH.' The entire image, through dense pencil cross-hatching, masterful sketch shading, and the warm enhancement of the sepia-toned base paper,",
    "prompt_zh": "文生图：在一个巨大的、被摧毁的圆顶竞技场内的电影画面，有四个后世界末日幸存者。戏剧性的体块光穿透破碎的屋顶，在尘土飞扬的氛围中投射出强烈的耶稣光。地面上有碎石瓦砾，上方是扭曲的金属结构。土色调和棕褐色。超高细节，8K分辨率。\n分镜：以铅笔草图的形式呈现一组分镜头。"
