    "title_en": "Oreo-Themed Miniature Shop",
    "prompt": "Tiny diorama shop for [BRAND]. Roof made of oversized [PRODUCT], big [BRAND] logo sign above the window, vendor handing a [PRODUCT] to a customer, ground covered with many [PRODUCT]. Hand-made polymer-clay look, studio macro photo, soft light, shallow depth of field, vertical 3:4",
    "prompt_en": "Tiny diorama shop for [BRAND]. Roof made of oversized [PRODUCT], big [BRAND] logo sign above the window, vendor handing a [PRODUCT] to a customer, ground covered with many [PRODUCT]. Hand-made polymer-clay look, studio macro photo, soft light, shallow depth of field, vertical 3:4",
    "source": "https://x.com/NanoBanana_labs/status/1966791308321910922",
    "type": "t2i",
    "author": "@NanoBanana_labs",
    "author_link": "https://x.com/NanoBanana_labs/status/1966791308321910922",
    "revised_prompt": "一张影棚微距摄影照片，展现了一个手工聚合物粘土质感的微缩立体模型。画面中央是一家小巧的奥利奥主题商店，整体呈现竖向构图。商店的屋顶由几块巨大的奥利奥夹心饼干交错搭建而成，饼干呈现深黑色，中间夹着厚实的白色奶油层，表面带有经典的压花纹理和清晰的英文字母 'OREO'，带有手工粘土圆润且微显指纹印记的真实触感。商店正面有一扇打开的木质售卖窗，窗户正上方悬挂着一块醒目的蓝色长方形招牌，招牌上用立体的白色粗体字写着大写的品牌名 'OREO'。在窗口处，一位身穿蓝色小围裙、头戴白色工作帽的粘土微缩店主探出上半身，手中正拿着一块小巧的奥利奥饼干递向窗外。店外站着一位顾客，是一个背着黄色双肩包、穿着红色休闲外套的微缩粘土小人，正微微仰头，伸出双手准备接过店主递来的饼干。商店周围的泥土地面上密集地散落着许多大小不一的奥利奥饼干，有些是完整的，有些被掰开露出了白色的夹心，铺满了整个前景和四周地面。画面采用柔和的影棚布光，光线均匀温和，凸显了聚合物粘土特有的哑光细腻质感。摄影采用了极浅的景深，焦点精准对焦在店主、顾客和招牌区域，而靠近镜头的前景饼干和背景边缘则呈现出强烈的平滑虚化效果，完美营造出微观世界的尺度感与梦幻氛围。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/gallery_5_2.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "A studio macro photography shot showcasing a handcrafted polymer clay-textured miniature diorama. At the center of the frame is a small Oreo-themed shop, presented in a vertical composition. The shop's roof is constructed from several oversized Oreo sandwich cookies stacked and interlocked together; the cookies are deep black with thick white cream filling layers in between, featuring the classic embossed pattern and clearly legible English lettering 'OREO' on their surfaces, with the authentic tactile quality of handmade clay—rounded forms with subtly visible fingerprint impressions. The shop's front features an open wooden serving window, and directly above the window hangs a prominent blue rectangular sign with the brand name 'OREO' in raised white bold uppercase lettering. At the window, a miniature clay shopkeeper wearing a small blue apron and a white work cap leans out from the upper body, holding a small Oreo cookie and extending it outward through the window. Outside the shop stands a customer—a miniature clay figure wearing a red casual jacket and carrying a yellow backpack—tilting their head slightly upward with both hands outstretched, ready to receive the cookie from the shopkeeper. The earthen ground surrounding the shop is densely scattered with numerous Oreo cookies of varying sizes; some are whole, while others have been split open to reveal the white cream filling, covering the entire foreground and surrounding ground area. The scene is lit with soft studio lighting, even and gentle, accentuating the characteristic matte and delicate texture of polymer clay. The photography employs an extremely shallow depth of field, with the focus precisely locked on the shopkeeper, customer, and signage area, while the foreground cookies closer to the lens and the background edges exhibit a strong, smooth bokeh effect, perfectly creating a sense of miniature-world scale and a dreamlike atmosphere.",
    "prompt_zh": "微缩立体模型店铺，品牌为[BRAND]。屋顶由超大尺寸的[PRODUCT]制成，橱窗上方挂着大大的[BRAND]标志招牌，店员正向顾客递出一份[PRODUCT]，地面上铺满了许多[PRODUCT]。手工聚合粘土质感，影棚微距摄影，柔和灯光，浅景深，竖版3:4。"
}, {
