    "revised_prompt": "这是一张具有极高写实度的街头摄影抓拍人像照片。画面采用竖版构图，视角位于人物胸部至眼睛的高度，利用长焦镜头的空间压缩感和极浅的景深，将中景处的女性主角作为画面的唯一清晰焦点。主角是一名年轻女性，肤色白皙，面部带有细腻自然的雀斑和真实的皮肤毛孔纹理。她位于画面中央略偏左的位置，可见胸部以上的身躯。她有着中棕色的头发，盘成凌乱的低发髻，脸庞周围垂落着几缕带有微湿都市质感的清晰发丝。她的身体向画面右侧倾斜（呈四分之三侧身），头部越过左肩回头，双眼直视镜头，眼神中透着柔和的强度，表情平静、放松且带有一丝微弱的严肃与好奇。她身穿一件米色哑光棉质风衣，领口敞开，露出经典的翻领，面料纹理在焦点内清晰可见；右肩隐约可见一条细细的金色链条包带反射出微光，耳垂上戴着一枚小巧的暖色调耳环。\n\n画面利用前后景的重度虚化来突出主角。前景左侧三分之一处被一个穿着灰蓝色外套的模糊中年男子身躯占据；前景右下角有一个深色头发的模糊人影；在主角右肩后方，隐约可见一位模糊的老年秃顶男子的头部和肩膀。背景是一条人群密集的繁忙大都市街道，所有背景元素均溶解在奶油般的平滑虚化中，没有任何清晰的细节或可读的标志。背景中可以辨认出黄色出租车的模糊轮廓以及点缀其间的暖橙色城市灯光光斑。\n\n光线与色调方面，画面沐浴在阴天到柔和日光的自然漫反射光线下，没有生硬的阴影，主角面部受光均匀，颧骨和鼻梁处带有柔和的高光。整体色调呈现电影级别的色彩科学，阴影和背景笼罩在一层青绿/灰绿色的雾霾感之中，与主角温暖自然的肤色形成对比。画面的虚化边缘带有轻微的猫眼光斑效果，亮部散景有微妙的光晕，并伴有细致的胶片颗粒感和柔和的暗角。前景人物带有一点自然的动态模糊效果，整体展现出高级时尚杂志般的街头纪实美感。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/gallery_67_1.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "This is a street photography candid portrait photograph with an extremely high degree of realism. The image is in vertical/portrait orientation, shot from a viewpoint at the subject's chest-to-eye level, utilizing the spatial compression of a telephoto lens and an extremely shallow depth of field to render the female subject in the middle ground as the sole sharp focal point of the frame. The subject is a young woman with fair skin, fine natural freckles, and realistic skin pore texture visible on her face. She is positioned slightly left of center in the frame, visible from the chest up. She has medium-brown hair pulled into a messy low bun, with a few strands of hair—carrying a slightly damp, urban texture—falling loosely around her face. Her body is angled toward the right side of the frame (in a three-quarter profile), with her head turned back over her left shoulder, both eyes looking directly into the lens. Her gaze conveys a soft intensity; her expression is calm, relaxed, with a faint hint of seriousness and curiosity. She wears a beige matte cotton trench coat with the collar open, revealing the classic lapels, the fabric texture clearly visible within the focal plane; on her right shoulder, a thin gold chain strap is faintly visible, catching a subtle glint of light, and a small warm-toned earring adorns her earlobe.\n\nThe image uses heavy bokeh in both the foreground and background to isolate the subject. The left third of the foreground is occupied by the blurred torso of a middle-aged man wearing a grey-blue coat; the lower-right foreground contains a blurred figure with dark hair; and behind the subject's right shoulder, the blurred head and shoulders of an elderly bald man are faintly discernible. The background is a bustling, crowd-dense metropolitan street, with all background elements dissolved into a creamy smooth bokeh, devoid of any sharp details or legible signage. Within the background, the blurred outline of a yellow taxi cab can be identified, along with warm orange urban light bokeh spots interspersed throughout.\n\nRegarding lighting and color grading, the scene is bathed in natural diffused light ranging from overcast to soft daylight, with no harsh shadows; the subject's face is evenly lit, with soft highlights on the cheekbones and bridge of the nose. The overall color palette exhibits cinematic-grade color science, with shadows and the background enveloped in a teal/grey-green haze, contrasting against the subject's warm, natural skin tones. The bokeh edges of the frame carry a subtle cat-eye bokeh effect, with delicate halation in the bright-area bokeh, accompanied by fine film grain texture and soft vignetting. The foreground figures exhibit a touch of natural motion blur, and the overall image conveys a high-fashion editorial street documentary aesthetic.",
    "prompt_zh": "核心意图：创建一张逼真写实的街头时尚抓拍肖像，采用极浅景深，画面中景处一位女性清晰对焦，周围行走的人群呈现为柔和的模糊/散景效果。保持精确的构图取景、主体位置、色彩分级和整体氛围。\n\n1）构图与取景（锁定）\n\n• 画幅比例：4:5竖版。\n\n• 机位高度：胸部至眼部水平（略高于主体肩线）。\n\n• 取景：中景主体位于画面略偏左居中位置，从上胸部到头顶清晰可见；包含肩部；背景大幅虚化。\n\n•"
