font: 'FRONT ELEVATION', 'SIDE ELEVATION', 'SECTIONAL VIEW', 'SEAT HEIGHT 420MM', 'OVERALL WIDTH 750MM', 'BACKREST ANGLE 105°', 'STEEL TUBING DIA 25MM'.\n\nIn the lower-right corner is a materials showcase panel, with three rectangular material swatch blocks arranged vertically. The first block displays a tobacco-brown leather texture, with the adjacent annotation text reading: 'MATERIAL 01: FULL GRAIN ANILINE LEATHER, TOBACCO BROWN'; the second block displays walnut wood grain material, annotated as: 'MATERIAL 02: SOLID",
