    "revised_prompt": "一张包含四张幻灯片卡片的涂鸦风格信息图表，采用2x2的网格布局排列，向高中生解释金融中的期货概念。整体画面呈现出一致的粗线条彩色铅笔手绘风格，色彩明快，线条粗犷带有明显的铅笔颗粒感。每张卡片都有一个柔和的纯色背景，外围被粗糙的黑色铅笔手绘边框包裹，并且每张卡片顶部都有居中、带下划线的黑色粗体手写体统一标题，排版类似一份精心设计的PPT演示文稿。\n\n左上角的卡片背景为淡黄色。顶部标题为 'What Are Futures?'。插图展示了左侧一个戴着草帽的农民涂鸦，右侧是一个戴着白色厨师帽的面包师涂鸦。农民头上有一个思想气泡，里面画着一株小麦、一个向下的红色箭头和一个美元符号；面包师头上也有一个思想气泡，画着一个可颂面包、一个向上的绿色箭头和美元符号。卡片下方的黑色手写文本写着：'Meet Farmer Bob and Baker Sue. Bob worries wheat prices will drop. Sue worries wheat prices will rise.'\n\n右上角的卡片背景为淡蓝色。顶部标题为 'The Contract'。画面正中央画着一份巨大的卷轴状纸质合同，合同上方画着一个闭合的金色挂锁图标，下方是一对正在握手的手。合同纸面上写着大号的 '$500' 和 '6 Months'。底部的文本内容为：'They sign a \"Futures Contract\". They agree to trade 100 sacks of wheat for $500 in 6 months. Price is locked!'\n\n左下角的卡片背景为淡粉色。顶部标题为 'Time Passes'。中心插图是一个翻开的日历，日历中间画着一个指针飞速旋转的钟表，代表时间流逝。日历周围画着一条剧烈波动的红色折线图，折线上下浮动，旁边用气泡标注着 '? $400 ?' 和 '? $600 ?'。底部的文字说明为：'6 months later... The market price of wheat changes. Maybe it is $400, maybe it is $600. It does not matter!'\n\n右下角的卡片背景为淡绿色。顶部标题为 'The Settlement'。插图中，农民和面包师满脸笑容地正在进行交易。农民抱着一个画有 '$500' 的钱袋，面包师抱着一个标有 'WHEAT' 的大麻袋。两人中间上方悬浮着一个巨大的绿色对勾和一个带有十字的盾牌图标，代表规避风险。底部的文字总结道：'They trade at the locked $500. Bob is safe from price drops. Sue is safe from price hikes. Risk managed!'\n\n整体风格生动幽默，图文并茂，手写的英文字体清晰易读，具有很强的故事性和教育功能。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/gallery_6_2.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "A doodle-style infographic containing four slide cards arranged in a 2×2 grid layout, explaining the concept of futures in finance to high school students. The overall image presents a consistent thick-lined colored-pencil hand-drawn style, with bright colors and bold lines carrying a distinct pencil-grain texture. Each card has a soft solid-color background, enclosed by a rough black pencil hand-drawn border, and each card features a centered, underlined, black bold handwritten-style unified title at the top, typeset similarly to a carefully designed PPT presentation slide.\n\nThe upper-left card has a pale yellow background. The top title reads 'What Are Futures?'. The illustration shows a doodle of a farmer wearing a straw hat on the left, and a doodle of a baker wearing a white chef's hat on the right. The farmer has a thought bubble above his head containing a wheat stalk, a downward red arrow, and a dollar sign; the baker also has a thought bubble, depicting a croissant, an upward green arrow, and a dollar sign. The black handwritten text at the bottom of the card reads: 'Meet Farmer Bob and Baker Sue. Bob worries wheat prices will drop. Sue worries wheat prices will rise.'\n\nThe upper-right card has a pale blue background. The top title reads 'The Contract'. Drawn in the center of the frame is a large scroll-shaped paper contract, with a closed golden padlock icon above the contract and a pair of shaking hands below it. Written on the contract surface in large text are '$500' and '6 Months'. The text at the bottom reads: 'They sign a \"Futures Contract\". They agree to trade 100 sacks of wheat for $500 in 6 months. Price is locked!'\n\nThe lower-left card has a pale pink background. The top title reads 'Time Passes'. The central illustration is an open calendar with a clock in the middle whose hands are spinning rapidly, representing the passage of time. Surrounding the calendar is a dramatically fluctuating red line chart, with the line moving up and down, and a bubble annotation beside it reading '? $400 ?",
    "prompt_zh": "请帮我生成多张16:9比例的涂鸦风格图片，用于向中学生解释\"期货\"的概念。图片应保持一致的粗线条彩色手绘铅笔风格，信息量丰富，文字使用英文，采用纯色背景，卡片周围带有轮廓边框，并包含统一的标题，类似于PowerPoint演示文稿的风格。"
