    "revised_prompt": "一张复古风格的古典建筑装饰纹理图集，采用竖版构图，背景呈现出做旧的泛黄羊皮纸质感。画面正上方居中印有优雅的复古衬线大写英文字体标题：'ARCHITECTURAL ORNAMENTS'。整个图集被划分为多个区块，展示了极具立体感和高精度的建筑材质与装饰构件。画面中央占据主导地位的是一个科林斯柱头（Corinthian capital）的正视图纹理，展现了繁复的茛苕叶（Acanthus leaves）雕刻细节，带有深邃的素描阴影和真实的石材风化质感，其下方印有一行小字标签：'FIG. 1: CORINTHIAN CAPITAL'。左上角展示了一块方形的巴洛克风格浮雕纹理切片，包含优美的曲线和扇形贝壳图案，下方标记：'FIG. 2: BAROQUE RELIEF'。右上角是一块矩形的无缝墙面纹理，呈现出带有岁月痕迹的粗糙花岗岩砖石交错排列，砖缝与石材孔隙清晰可见，下方标记：'FIG. 3: SEAMLESS STONE TEXTURE'。画面底部横向排列着两组无缝装饰边框纹理：上方一条是连续的藤蔓与花卉交织的石雕边框，下方一条是经典的希腊回纹（Greek key）几何装饰线条，边框下方居中标记有：'FIG. 4: FLORAL BORDER'。图集中散布着细微的褐色墨水飞溅和纸张褶皱痕迹。所有的建筑纹理均呈现出极高的清晰度、逼真的光影立体感与法线贴图般的深度细节，整体色调以暖棕色、石灰色和复古金褐色为主，呈现出古典、严谨且信息丰富的材质展示风格。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/gallery_77_3.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "A vintage-style classical architectural decorative texture collection plate, in portrait orientation, with a background presenting an aged, yellowed parchment texture. Centered at the very top of the image is an elegant vintage serif uppercase English title: 'ARCHITECTURAL ORNAMENTS'. The entire plate is divided into multiple sections, showcasing highly three-dimensional and high-precision architectural materials and decorative elements. Dominating the center of the image is a front-view texture of a Corinthian capital, displaying intricate Acanthus leaves carving details with deep sketch-like shading and realistic stone weathering texture; beneath it is a small-print label: 'FIG. 1: CORINTHIAN CAPITAL'. The upper left corner presents a square slice of Baroque-style relief texture, featuring graceful curves and fan-shaped shell motifs, labeled below: 'FIG. 2: BAROQUE RELIEF'. The upper right corner shows a rectangular seamless wall texture, depicting rough granite masonry in an interlocking bond pattern bearing traces of age, with clearly visible mortar joints and stone pores, labeled below: 'FIG. 3: SEAMLESS STONE TEXTURE'. Along the bottom of the image, two sets of seamless decorative border textures are arranged horizontally: the upper one is a continuous stone-carved border of intertwining vines and flowers; the lower one is a classic Greek key geometric ornamental line; centered beneath the borders is the label: 'FIG. 4: FLORAL BORDER'. Scattered throughout the plate are subtle brown ink splatter marks and paper crease traces. All architectural textures exhibit extremely high clarity, realistic light-and-shadow dimensionality, and normal-map-like depth detail. The overall color palette is dominated by warm browns, limestone grays, and vintage golden-browns, presenting a classical, rigorous, and information-rich material showcase style.",
