    "author": "@dotey",
    "author_link": "https://x.com/dotey/status/1992469131438719122?s=20",
    "revised_prompt": "传统中国水墨彩绘手卷风格的宽幅画作。底材呈现古旧绢本的泛黄底色与细微的织物肌理，整体色调为柔和的复古大地色系（如赭石、淡墨、花青）。画面采用散点透视构图与细腻的工笔技法，将现代都市景观与古典绘画形式相融合。\n画面中心俯瞰繁华的现代芝加哥河滨。视觉焦点是横跨河面的杜萨布尔桥（密歇根大道桥），这座巨大的钢制开启桥以传统细密的墨线勾勒出复杂的桁架和结构。桥面上车水马龙，拥挤着以传统笔触和色彩渲染的现代交通工具：包括多辆明黄色的出租车、带有局部色彩涂装的芝加哥交通管理局（CTA）公交车以及各色私家车，首尾相连排成长龙。\n桥下的芝加哥河水以传统网巾水纹描绘，水波荡漾。河面上穿梭着现代化的水上交通工具，包括带有平顶透明天棚的建筑观光游船（甲板上可见密密麻麻的小人）、水上出租车，以及几只单人和双人皮划艇，船身周围晕染出淡墨色的水痕。\n河岸两侧林立着以传统“界画”技法（运用界尺和毛笔绘制严谨直线）表现的摩天大楼。可见具有钟楼特征和繁复立面装饰的箭牌大厦（Wrigley Building），以及带有哥特式尖顶结构的论坛报大厦（Tribune Tower），大楼的窗棂、砖石纹理及建筑轮廓均被细致勾画。画面中远景处，可见横穿建筑群的高架铁路轨道，一列多节车厢的芝加哥“L”型列车正在轨道上行驶。\n桥边人行道与下方的河滨步道上，密布着数百个微缩人物，构成略显杂乱但生机勃勃的市井长卷。人物均着现代服饰（T恤、外套、牛仔裤等），以传统白描和淡彩绘制。步道上细节丰富：左侧有呈奔跑姿态的慢跑者；护栏旁聚集着手举微小长方形智能手机拍照的游客；桥头位置设有一个带条纹遮阳伞的现代街头热狗摊，摊面放有调料瓶，摊前排着由十多人组成的蜿蜒长队；步道台阶附近还有牵着宠物狗散步的行人。整个画面没有强烈的现代光影明暗，而是依赖线条的繁密与淡彩的晕染来塑造广阔而精密的叙事空间。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/gallery_79_3.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "A wide-format painting in the style of a traditional Chinese ink-and-color painted handscroll. The substrate presents the yellowed base tone and subtle woven textile texture of aged silk (juan-ben). The overall color palette consists of soft, vintage earth tones (such as burnt sienna/zhe-shi, pale ink, and indigo/hua-qing). The composition employs multi-point (scattered) perspective and meticulous gongbi brushwork technique, merging modern urban scenery with classical painting forms.\n\nThe center of the image presents a bird's-eye view of the bustling modern Chicago riverfront. The visual focal point is the DuSable Bridge (Michigan Avenue Bridge) spanning the river — this massive steel bascule bridge is delineated with traditionally fine, dense ink lines rendering its complex trusses and structural elements. The bridge deck is teeming with traffic, crowded with modern vehicles rendered in traditional brushwork and coloring: including multiple bright yellow taxicabs, Chicago Transit Authority (CTA) buses with partial color livery, and various private cars, all bumper-to-bumper in long queues.\n\nBeneath the bridge, the Chicago River water is depicted using traditional wang-jin (net-cap) water ripple patterning, with undulating waves. Modern watercraft navigate the river surface, including architectural sightseeing tour boats with flat-topped transparent canopies (with densely packed tiny figures visible on deck), water taxis, and several single and tandem kayaks, with pale ink wash water trails radiating around the hulls.\n\nLining both riverbanks are skyscrapers rendered in the traditional \"jiehua\" technique (using a straightedge and brush to draw precise straight lines). Visible are the Wrigley Building, recognizable by its clock tower features and elaborate façade ornamentation, as well as the Tribune Tower with its Gothic pinnacle structure — the window mullions, masonry textures, and architectural silhouettes of these buildings are all meticulously delineated. In the middle and far distance of the composition, elevated railway tracks can be seen running through the building clusters, with a multi-car Chicago \"L\" train traveling along the tracks.\n\nOn the sidewalks flanking the bridge and the riverwalk below, hundreds of miniature figures are densely packed, forming a slightly chaotic yet vibrant panoramic scroll of urban life. All figures wear modern attire (T-shirts, jackets, jeans, etc.) and are rendered in traditional baimiao (plain-line drawing) and light color washes. The riverwalk is rich in detail: on the left side are joggers in running poses; clustered against the railings are tourists holding up tiny rectangular smartphones to take photos; at the bridgehead is a modern street hot dog stand with a striped parasol, condiment bottles on the counter, and a winding queue of over a dozen people in front; near the riverwalk steps there are also pedestrians walking pet dogs. The entire painting eschews strong modern chiaroscuro light and shadow, instead relying on the density of linework and the gradation of light color washes to sculpt a vast and meticulously detailed narrative space.",
    "prompt_zh": "一幅气势恢宏、细节丰富的传统中国水墨彩绘手卷，绘于古旧绢本之上，完美地模仿了张择端名作《清明上河图》的艺术风格、笔法和散点透视。\n中心场景：俯瞰熙熙攘攘的现代芝加哥河滨。画面焦点是巨大的钢制开启桥（杜萨布尔桥/密歇根大道桥），桥上车水马龙，无数汽车、黄色出租车和芝加哥交通管理局（CTA）公交车穿梭其间，所有景象均以精准的传统笔触描绘。\n环境细节：下方的芝加哥河上，现代建筑风格的游船、水上出租车和皮划艇穿梭其间。河岸两侧林立着风格各异的芝加哥摩天大楼（形似箭牌大厦和论坛报大厦），以传统的“界画”建筑绘画技法绘制而成。背景中可见高架铁路和正在行驶的“L”型列车。\n人类活动：河滨步道和桥边的人行道上挤满了数百个身着现代休闲服饰的小人。他们有的在慢跑，有的在用智能手机拍照，有的在街头小吃摊（热狗摊）前排队，有的在遛狗。整个场景细节丰富，略显杂乱，并以柔和的复古大地色调呈现。"
