    "prompt": "为我制作一张世界五座最高建筑的信息图 / 制作一张关于地球上最甜蜜事物的彩色信息图",
    "prompt_en": "Create an infographic of the world's five tallest buildings for me / Create a colorful infographic about the sweetest things on Earth.",
