    "author_link": "https://x.com/IqraSaifiii/status/1969868863522423034",
    "revised_prompt": "超逼真的专业室内设计摄影作品，采用竖式构图，展示了一个以蝙蝠侠为灵感的现代极简风格客厅。房间线条干净利落，整体空间色调以高级灰色、深邃黑色和纯净白色为主，并辅以低调的暗金色作为主题色进行细节点缀。占据视觉焦点的主墙上，悬挂着一件大型的蝙蝠侠标志3D壁挂雕塑，雕塑采用哑光黑金属材质，呈现出棱角分明的几何折线设计，充满现代艺术气息。墙面一侧挂着一幅装裱精美的深蓝色背景蓝图风格艺术印刷品，画面是精细的蝙蝠战车内部结构设计图，底部带有清晰的白色英文字段'BATMOBILE MK-IV'。客厅角落矗立着一盏设计灵感源自“蝙蝠探照灯”的现代落地灯，黑色的工业风金属外壳透出温暖的暗金色光芒。一张极简的黑色大理石边桌上，陈列着一个高度风格化、表面光滑的哑光黑蝙蝠侠头盔雕塑作为摆件。客厅中央摆放着一张宽大舒适的深灰色布艺组合沙发，上面错落有致地点缀着暗金色和黑白几何图案的抱枕。沙发前方是一张低矮的矩形茶几，透明玻璃桌面搭配黑色金属底座，桌上摆放着几根白色香薰蜡烛和一本厚重的黑色设计画册。戏剧性的重点射灯从天花板投射而下，精准打在主墙的蝙蝠标志雕塑上，凸显其立体的轮廓与阴影；同时，画面侧面落地窗透入的柔和自然光与灯具散发的温暖环境光相互交织，营造出宜人、静谧的空间氛围。画面光影质感极其细腻，景深过渡自然，整体风格精致优雅，克制而巧妙地将超级英雄元素融入高端家居设计中。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/gallery_97_3.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "An ultra-realistic professional interior design photograph in portrait orientation, showcasing a modern minimalist living room inspired by Batman. The room features clean, sharp lines, with the overall color palette dominated by sophisticated gray, deep black, and pure white, accented with subtle dark gold as a thematic detail color. On the main wall commanding the visual focal point hangs a large Batman logo 3D wall-mounted sculpture made of matte black metal, featuring angular geometric faceted design full of contemporary art sensibility. On one side of the wall hangs an elegantly framed art print with a dark blue background in blueprint style, depicting a detailed internal structural schematic of the Batmobile, with a clear white English caption 'BATMOBILE MK-IV' at the bottom. In a corner of the living room stands a modern floor lamp whose design is inspired by the \"Bat-Signal,\" its black industrial-style metal housing emanating a warm dark gold glow. On a minimalist black marble side table sits a highly stylized, smooth-surfaced matte black Batman helmet sculpture displayed as a decorative object. At the center of the living room is a wide, comfortable dark gray fabric sectional sofa, tastefully adorned with scattered dark gold and black-and-white geometric-patterned throw pillows. In front of the sofa is a low rectangular coffee table with a transparent glass top on a black metal base, upon which rest several white aromatherapy candles and a hefty black design art book. Dramatic accent spotlights project down from the ceiling, precisely illuminating the Batman logo sculpture on the main wall, accentuating its three-dimensional contours and shadows; meanwhile, soft natural light filtering through floor-to-ceiling windows on the side interweaves with the warm ambient glow from the lighting fixtures, creating a pleasant, tranquil spatial atmosphere. The light and shadow quality in the image is extraordinarily refined, with natural depth-of-field transitions, and the overall style is sophisticated and elegant, restrainedly yet ingeniously integrating superhero elements into high-end interior design.",
    "prompt_zh": "一个超逼真、专业的室内设计摄影作品，展示以 [超级英雄] 为灵感的现代客厅。\n房间线条干净，色调以灰色、黑色和白色为主，辅以 [主题色] 点缀。主墙上有一件大型风格化的 [超级英雄] 3D 壁挂雕塑，占据视觉焦点。\n房间中布置了细腻的主题元素，例如蓝图风格的装裱艺术印刷品、一盏设计灵感来源于特定元素（如盾牌或标志）的落地灯，以及摆放少量道具（如风格化头盔）的边桌。\n家具现代简约，大型舒适沙发搭配低矮茶几。戏剧性的重点灯光突出主墙雕塑，同时来自窗户和灯具的温暖环境光营造出宜人的氛围。\n整体风格精致优雅，微妙地致敬超级英雄，而非明显的粉丝向致敬。"
