    "title_en": "Coffee Cup Typography Illustration",
    "prompt": "创建一个 [OBJECT] 形状的文字插画，文字本身构成该形状——\n\n字体风格：粗体且活泼，填满整个轮廓\n\n文字沿对象的曲线和轮廓自然排列\n\n色彩：鲜明对比且契合主题\n\n背景：纯色，以突出主体形状\n\n风格：矢量风格，干净整洁\n\n分辨率高，适合海报格式\n\n长宽比：1:1",
    "prompt_en": "Create a typographic illustration in the shape of a [OBJECT], where the text itself forms the shape—\n\nFont style: Bold and playful, filling the entire outline\n\nText flows naturally along the curves and contours of the object\n\nColors: Vivid contrast and thematically appropriate\n\nBackground: Solid color to make the main shape stand out\n\nStyle: Vector style, clean and neat\n\nHigh resolution, suitable for poster format\n\nAspect ratio: 1:1",
