    "author_link": "https://x.com/IqraSaifiii/status/1969868863522423034",
    "revised_prompt": "一张矢量风格的排版文字插画海报。画面中心是一个由各种英文字母和单词巧妙排列组合而成的咖啡杯（带有底碟和上方升腾的热气）的具象形状。这些文字构成了咖啡杯的所有轮廓和体积。构成上方升腾热气的三道波浪形文字分别为：左侧弯曲变形的 'AROMA'，中间垂直拉长的 'HOT'，以及右侧蜿蜒的 'MORNING'。杯体的上半部由巨大的粗体单词 'COFFEE' 构成，字母的顶部边缘平滑贴合杯口的水平椭圆弧度。杯体中部由不同字号、互相紧凑穿插拼接的单词组成：'ESPRESSO'、'LATTE'、'CAPPUCCINO'、'MOCHA'。杯身下半部分排列着向下收窄、随杯壁弧度压缩变形的 'AMERICANO'、'MACCHIATO'、'BREW' 和 'BEANS'。右侧半圆形的杯把手由沿着弧线弯曲排版的单词 'ENERGY' 构成，首尾完美连接杯壁。下方的椭圆形杯托底碟由横向拉伸变扁的单词 'TASTY' 和 'CAFE' 上下堆叠组成。所有的文字均采用极其粗体且活泼的无衬线字体，字母之间几乎没有空隙，字符被挤压、拉伸并沿着咖啡杯固有的曲线和轮廓自然流畅地排列，完全填满整个对象的内部区域，形成了坚实而饱满的视觉块面。色彩方面，文字交替使用深咖啡色、焦糖色和亮眼的暖橙色，色彩组合鲜明且完美契合咖啡主题。背景为一块干净整洁的纯米黄色，没有任何多余的装饰、渐变或阴影，极致地突出了中央由文字构建的咖啡杯主体。整体为清晰平滑的矢量插画风格，边缘锐利，高分辨率质感，横向构图，咖啡杯主体居中放置于画面中央，四周留有适宜的纯色空间，呈现出强烈的海报设计感。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/gallery_98_4.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "A vector-style typographic illustration poster. At the center of the image is a representational shape of a coffee cup (complete with a saucer and rising steam above) ingeniously formed by the arrangement and combination of various English letters and words. These words constitute all the contours and volume of the coffee cup. The three wavy lines of text forming the rising steam above are: the curved and warped 'AROMA' on the left, the vertically elongated 'HOT' in the middle, and the meandering 'MORNING' on the right. The upper half of the cup body is formed by the massive bold word 'COFFEE', with the top edges of the letters smoothly conforming to the horizontal elliptical curvature of the cup rim. The middle section of the cup body is composed of tightly interlocking words in varying font sizes: 'ESPRESSO', 'LATTE', 'CAPPUCCINO', 'MOCHA'. The lower half of the cup body features words that narrow downward and compress along the curvature of the cup walls: 'AMERICANO', 'MACCHIATO', 'BREW', and 'BEANS'. The semicircular handle on the right side is formed by the word 'ENERGY' typeset along a curved arc, with its beginning and end seamlessly connecting to the cup wall. The elliptical saucer below is composed of the horizontally stretched and flattened words 'TASTY' and 'CAFE' stacked vertically. All text uses an extremely bold and lively sans-serif typeface, with virtually no spacing between letters; the characters are squeezed, stretched, and arranged naturally and fluidly along the inherent curves and contours of the coffee cup, completely filling the entire interior area of the object, forming solid and full visual masses. In terms of color, the text alternates between deep coffee brown, caramel, and a vibrant warm orange, a striking color combination that perfectly complements the coffee theme. The background is a clean, neat solid cream/beige color with no extraneous decoration, gradients, or shadows, maximally highlighting the central coffee cup form constructed from text. The overall style is a crisp, smooth vector illustration with sharp edges and a high-resolution quality, in landscape orientation, with the coffee cup centrally placed in the middle of the image, surrounded by ample solid-color space, presenting a strong poster design aesthetic.",
    "prompt_zh": "创建一个 [OBJECT] 形状的文字插画，文字本身构成该形状——\n\n字体风格：粗体且活泼，填满整个轮廓\n\n文字沿对象的曲线和轮廓自然排列\n\n色彩：鲜明对比且契合主题\n\n背景：纯色，以突出主体形状\n\n风格：矢量风格，干净整洁\n\n分辨率高，适合海报格式\n\n长宽比：1:1"
