    "author_link": "https://x.com/nobisiro_2023/status/1968677481486914022",
    "revised_prompt": "一张垂直排版的极简风格象形图（Pictogram）海报，主题为手冲咖啡指南。背景为统一的干净米白色。画面采用扁平化矢量设计，由深棕色粗线条和暖橙色辅助色块构成高度简化的象形图标，无渐变或3D阴影效果，视觉语言如公共指示牌般直观易懂。画面顶部居中是一行深棕色粗体无衬线大字标题：'POUR-OVER COFFEE GUIDE'。标题下方沿着垂直中轴线均匀分布着四个步骤区块，每个区块包含一个大号象征性图标和说明文字。第一个区块：左侧是一个极简的手摇磨豆机图形，右侧配有两行文字，第一行是加粗的橙色字 'STEP 1'，第二行是深棕色文字 'GRIND 20G COFFEE BEANS'。第二个区块：左侧是一个带有圆形温度计刻度的细颈手冲壶图形，右侧文字为橙色 'STEP 2' 和深棕色 'BOIL WATER TO 92°C'。第三个区块：左侧展示手冲壶壶嘴向V型滤杯中注水的动态图形，滤杯上方有三根代表蒸汽的波浪线，右侧文字为橙色 'STEP 3' 和深棕色 'POUR 40G WATER, WAIT 30S'。第四个区块：左侧是一个圆润的咖啡马克杯图形，杯口飘着热气线条，右侧文字为橙色 'STEP 4' 和深棕色 'POUR REMAINING WATER & ENJOY'。画面最底部有一条横向的深棕色细虚线作为视觉收尾，虚线下方居中有一行较小的装饰性文字：'ENJOY YOUR DAILY COFFEE'。整体构图严谨对齐，信息层级分明，完美契合竖版画幅比例。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/gallery_99_4.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "A vertically formatted minimalist pictogram poster themed as a pour-over coffee guide. The background is a uniform clean off-white. The design employs a flat vector style, composed of highly simplified pictographic icons rendered in dark brown thick outlines with warm orange accent color blocks, free of gradients or 3D shadow effects, with a visual language as intuitive and legible as public signage. Centered at the top of the image is a line of dark brown bold sans-serif large title text: 'POUR-OVER COFFEE GUIDE'. Below the title, four step blocks are evenly distributed along the vertical central axis, each block containing a large symbolic icon and accompanying text. The first block: on the left is a minimalist hand-crank coffee grinder graphic; on the right are two lines of text—the first line in bold orange reading 'STEP 1', the second in dark brown reading 'GRIND 20G COFFEE BEANS'. The second block: on the left is a slender-necked pour-over kettle graphic with a circular thermometer dial; the right-side text reads orange 'STEP 2' and dark brown 'BOIL WATER TO 92°C'. The third block: on the left is a dynamic graphic depicting the kettle spout pouring water into a V-shaped filter dripper, with three wavy lines representing steam above the dripper; the right-side text reads orange 'STEP 3' and dark brown 'POUR 40G WATER, WAIT 30S'. The fourth block: on the left is a rounded coffee mug graphic with steam lines rising from the rim; the right-side text reads orange 'STEP 4' and dark brown 'POUR REMAINING WATER & ENJOY'. At the very bottom of the image is a horizontal dark brown thin dashed line serving as a visual closure, with a smaller line of decorative text centered beneath it reading: 'ENJOY YOUR DAILY COFFEE'. The overall composition is rigorously aligned with clear information hierarchy, perfectly suited to a vertical aspect ratio.",
    "prompt_zh": "将此说明图转换为象形图"
