    "title": "玩具盒中的国家立体模型",
    "title_en": "Country Diorama in a Toy Box",
    "prompt": "一张超写实的俯拍摄影作品，展示了一个米色纸板盒内的3D打印立体模型，盒盖由两只人手撑开。盒子内部展现了[国家名称]的微缩景观，包含标志性地标、地形、建筑、河流、植被以及大量微小精细的人物模型。该立体模型充满了鲜活且符合地理特征的元素，全部采用触感舒适、玩具般的风格，使用哑光3D打印纹理制作，并带有可见的打印层纹。在顶部，盒盖内侧用大号、色彩鲜艳的凸起塑料字母显示“[国家名称]”字样——每个字母颜色各异，均为亮色。光线温暖且具有电影感，突出了纹理和阴影，营造出一种真实感和魅力，仿佛观看者正在打开一个神奇的国家微缩版本。",
    "prompt_en": "An ultra-realistic top-down photograph of a 3D-printed diorama inside a beige cardboard box, with the lid being held open by two human hands. The interior of the box reveals a miniature landscape of [COUNTRY NAME], featuring iconic landmarks, terrain, buildings, rivers, vegetation, and crowds of tiny, detailed human figures. The diorama is filled with vibrant, geographically appropriate elements, all crafted in a tactile, toy-like style using matte 3D-printed textures with visible layer lines. At the top, the inside of the box lid displays the phrase “[COUNTRY NAME]” in large, colorful, raised plastic letters—each letter in a different bright color. The lighting is warm and cinematic, highlighting the textures and shadows to evoke a sense of realism and charm, as if the viewer is opening a magical miniature version of the nation\n",
    "source": "https://x.com/TheRelianceAI/status/1925223613055017251",
    "type": "t2i",
    "author": "@TheRelianceAI",
    "author_link": "https://x.com/TheRelianceAI/status/1925223613055017251",
    "revised_prompt": "超写实的竖版俯拍摄影画面中，两只真实的人手正从左右两侧撑开一个米色瓦楞纸板盒的盒盖并向外翻起。翻开的盒盖内侧顶部，排列着大号、色彩鲜艳的凸起塑料字母，清晰地拼出 'ITALY' 字样，每个字母颜色各异：'I' 为亮红色，'T' 为亮蓝色，'A' 为亮黄色，'L' 为鲜绿色，'Y' 为亮橙色。盒子内部装有一个极其精细的意大利主题微缩景观3D打印立体模型。景观中包含了标志性的建筑地标，如逼真的微缩罗马斗兽场、倾斜的比萨斜塔、带有蔚蓝水流与微小黑色贡多拉的威尼斯运河，以及起伏的绿色托斯卡纳丘陵、成片的红顶白墙房屋群和微小的常绿乔木。在街道、桥梁和广场的微缩地形上，密布着大量极其微小但形态各异的人物模型。整个微缩世界充满了鲜活且符合地理特征的细节，所有元素均采用触感舒适、类似玩具的质感，表面呈现出哑光材质，且带有清晰可见的一层层3D打印平行层纹。画面的光线温暖而具有电影感，柔和的顶侧光照亮了模型，在地形、建筑的深处和纸盒内壁上投射出清晰的阴影，完美突出了模型的哑光材质纹理与立体感。米色粗糙纸板与内部色彩丰富的微缩世界形成对比，营造出观看者正亲手打开一个神奇微缩国度的沉浸式与真实体验。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/gallery_105_4.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "In a hyper-realistic vertically formatted top-down photography shot, two real human hands reach in from the left and right sides, prying open and flipping outward the flaps of a beige corrugated cardboard box. Along the top of the opened flap interior, large, brightly colored raised plastic letters are arranged, clearly spelling out 'ITALY', each letter in a different color: 'I' in bright red, 'T' in bright blue, 'A' in bright yellow, 'L' in vivid green, and 'Y' in bright orange. Inside the box sits an extraordinarily detailed Italy-themed miniature landscape 3D-printed three-dimensional model. The landscape includes iconic architectural landmarks such as a realistic miniature Colosseum, a leaning Tower of Pisa, Venice canals with azure water and tiny black gondolas, as well as rolling green Tuscan hills, clusters of red-roofed white-walled houses, and tiny evergreen trees. Across the miniature terrain of streets, bridges, and piazzas, a multitude of extremely tiny yet varied human figure models are densely populated. The entire miniature world is brimming with vivid, geographically authentic details; all elements feature a comfortable, toy-like tactile quality with matte surface finishes and clearly visible parallel layer lines characteristic of 3D printing. The lighting is warm and cinematic, with soft top-side illumination lighting the model and casting distinct shadows into the recesses of terrain, buildings, and the inner walls of the cardboard box, perfectly accentuating the matte material texture and three-dimensionality of the model. The rough beige cardboard contrasts with the colorfully rich miniature world within, creating an immersive and realistic experience as if the viewer is personally opening a magical miniature country.",
    "prompt_zh": "一张超写实的俯拍摄影作品，展示了一个米色纸板盒内的3D打印立体模型，盒盖由两只人手撑开。盒子内部展现了[国家名称]的微缩景观，包含标志性地标、地形、建筑、河流、植被以及大量微小精细的人物模型。该立体模型充满了鲜活且符合地理特征的元素，全部采用触感舒适、玩具般的风格，使用哑光3D打印纹理制作，并带有可见的打印层纹。在顶部，盒盖内侧用大号、色彩鲜艳的凸起塑料字母显示“[国家名称]”字样——每个字母颜色各异，均为亮色。光线温暖且具有电影感，突出了纹理和阴影，营造出一种真实感和魅力，仿佛观看者正在打开一个神奇的国家微缩版本。"
