    "title": "手工微缩树屋景观模型",
    "title_en": "Handmade Miniature Treehouse Landscape Model",
    "prompt": "{\n    \"style\": \"miniature handcrafted diorama\",\n    \"material\": \"tree branches, cardboard, clay, moss, dried flowers, paper\",\n    \"surface_texture\": \"organic, rough and varied (wood grain, soft moss, paper texture)\",\n    \"lighting\": {\n        \"type\": \"soft ambient natural light\",\n        \"intensity\": \"low to moderate\",\n        \"direction\": \"diffused overhead\",\n        \"accent_colors\": [\n            \"forest green\",\n            \"earth brown\",\n            \"soft beige\",\n            \"muted pink\"\n        ],\n        \"reflections\": false,\n        \"refractions\": false,\n        \"dispersion_effects\": false,\n        \"bloom\": false\n    },\n    \"color_scheme\": {\n        \"primary\": \"natural greens and browns\",\n        \"secondary\": \"soft neutral tones (cardboard, clay, paper)\",\n        \"highlights\": \"light falling on the open book and cat’s glasses\",\n        \"rim_light\": \"subtle natural edge light from the forest opening\"\n    },\n    \"background\": {\n        \"color\": \"natural moss green\",\n        \"vignette\": false,\n        \"texture\": \"moss and dried floral structure\"\n    },\n    \"post_processing\": {\n        \"chromatic_aberration\": false,\n        \"glow\": false,\n        \"high_contrast\": false,\n        \"sharp_details\": true,\n        \"film_grain\": false\n    },\n    \"form_composition\": {\n        \"scene_elements\": [\n            \"a small girl sitting on a balcony holding an open miniature book\",\n            \"a cat with glasses observing the book's illustrations\",\n            \"a treehouse made from twigs, cardboard, and clay\",\n            \"balcony and surrounding forest made of moss and dried flowers\"\n        ],\n        \"scale\": \"miniature\",\n        \"theme\": \"childlike wonder and storytelling in a handcrafted world\",\n        \"visual_metaphor\": [\n            \"curiosity\",\n            \"quiet companionship\",\n            \"imagination in nature\"\n        ]\n    },\n    \"metadata\": {\n        \"artist\": \"-Zho-\",\n        \"series\": \"ZH4O\"\n    }\n}",
    "prompt_en": "{\n    \"style\": \"miniature handcrafted diorama\",\n    \"material\": \"tree branches, cardboard, clay, moss, dried flowers, paper\",\n    \"surface_texture\": \"organic, rough and varied (wood grain, soft moss, paper texture)\",\n    \"lighting\": {\n        \"type\": \"soft ambient natural light\",\n        \"intensity\": \"low to moderate\",\n        \"direction\": \"diffused overhead\",\n        \"accent_colors\": [\n            \"forest green\",\n            \"earth brown\",\n            \"soft beige\",\n            \"muted pink\"\n        ],\n        \"reflections\": false,\n        \"refractions\": false,\n        \"dispersion_effects\": false,\n        \"bloom\": false\n    },\n    \"color_scheme\": {\n        \"primary\": \"natural greens and browns\",\n        \"secondary\": \"soft neutral tones (cardboard, clay, paper)\",\n        \"highlights\": \"light falling on the open book and cat’s glasses\",\n        \"rim_light\": \"subtle natural edge light from the forest opening\"\n    },\n    \"background\": {\n        \"color\": \"natural moss green\",\n        \"vignette\": false,\n        \"texture\": \"moss and dried floral structure\"\n    },\n    \"post_processing\": {\n        \"chromatic_aberration\": false,\n        \"glow\": false,\n        \"high_contrast\": false,\n        \"sharp_details\": true,\n        \"film_grain\": false\n    },\n    \"form_composition\": {\n        \"scene_elements\": [\n            \"a small girl sitting on a balcony holding an open miniature book\",\n            \"a cat with glasses observing the book's illustrations\",\n            \"a treehouse made from twigs, cardboard, and clay\",\n            \"balcony and surrounding forest made of moss and dried flowers\"\n        ],\n        \"scale\": \"miniature\",\n        \"theme\": \"childlike wonder and storytelling in a handcrafted world\",\n        \"visual_metaphor\": [\n            \"curiosity\",\n            \"quiet companionship\",\n            \"imagination in nature\"\n        ]\n    },\n    \"metadata\": {\n        \"artist\": \"-Zho-\",\n        \"series\": \"ZH4O\"\n    }\n}",
    "source": "https://x.com/ZHO_ZHO_ZHO/status/1925878276133708224",
    "type": "t2i",
    "author": "@ZHO_ZHO_ZHO",
    "author_link": "https://x.com/ZHO_ZHO_ZHO/status/1925878276133708224",
    "revised_prompt": "一张展现手工微缩景观（Diorama）艺术风格的照片，画面横向展开，呈现出一个充满童趣与想象力的精美微缩世界。整体场景完全由树枝、硬纸板、黏土、青苔、干花和纸张手工制作而成，视觉上充满了粗糙木纹、柔软苔藓和纸张的自然有机纹理。画面中央是一座搭建在错落树枝上的微缩树屋，建筑主体由不规则的细树枝、棕色硬纸板和质朴的黏土拼接塑造。树屋前方延伸出一个简易的小阳台，阳台周围及底部紧密包裹着蓬松的绿色天然苔藓和几簇暗粉色的干燥小花。\n\n阳台上坐着一个由黏土和纸张质感制成的小女孩，她穿着浅米色的裙子，手中捧着一本打开的微缩纸质书。书本内页平摊，上面绘制着微小的彩色植物与森林插图。小女孩身旁紧贴着蹲着一只小猫，小猫的鼻梁上架着一副极微小的金属丝圆框眼镜，它的头部微微前倾，视线正全神贯注地聚焦在书本的插图上。\n\n光线为柔和的自然漫反射顶光，光照强度中等偏低，呈现出静谧的氛围。柔和的光线在翻开的书页和小猫的金属眼镜边缘形成了细微的高光。从周围微缩森林的开口处透入一丝微妙的自然边缘光（Rim light），轻轻勾勒出女孩、小猫和树屋的轮廓。色彩方案以自然的森林绿和泥土棕为基调，硬纸板和纸张带来柔和的中性色调。背景被密集的苔藓和干花植物结构填满，呈现出深邃自然的苔绿色。画面细节极其锐利清晰，没有暗角、发光、折射或胶片颗粒效果，完美捕捉了微缩材质的物理质感，整体氛围传达出安静的陪伴感与自然叙事感，带有艺术家-Zho-的ZH4O系列标志性的手工质感与童话隐喻。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/gallery_13_2.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "A photograph showcasing a handmade diorama art style, with the frame extending horizontally to present an exquisitely crafted miniature world brimming with childlike wonder and imagination. The entire scene is constructed entirely by hand from twigs, cardboard, clay, moss, dried flowers, and paper, visually rich with the natural organic textures of rough wood grain, soft moss, and paper. At the center of the frame is a miniature treehouse built upon an irregular arrangement of branches, its main structure assembled and sculpted from irregular thin twigs, brown cardboard, and rustic clay. Extending from the front of the treehouse is a simple small balcony, closely enveloped around and beneath by fluffy green natural moss and a few clusters of dark pink dried small flowers.\n\nSeated on the balcony is a small girl crafted with clay and paper textures, wearing a light beige dress and holding an open miniature paper book in her hands. The book's inner pages lie flat, illustrated with tiny colorful plants and forest drawings. Nestled closely beside the girl is a small cat in a crouching position, perched on whose nose bridge is a pair of extremely tiny wire-frame round glasses, its head tilted slightly forward with its gaze fully focused on the illustrations in the book.\n\nThe lighting is soft natural diffused overhead light at a medium-low intensity, conveying a tranquil atmosphere. The gentle light forms subtle highlights on the open book pages and the edges of the cat's metal glasses. A trace of subtle natural rim light filters through openings in the surrounding miniature forest, delicately outlining the silhouettes of the girl, the cat, and the treehouse. The color palette is grounded in natural forest greens and earth browns, with cardboard and paper contributing soft neutral tones. The background is densely filled with moss and dried flower plant structures, presenting a deep, natural moss-green color. Image details are extremely sharp and clear, with no vignetting, glow, refraction, or film grain effects, perfectly capturing the physical textures of the miniature materials. The overall atmosphere conveys a sense of quiet companionship and natural narrative, bearing the signature handcrafted quality and fairytale metaphor characteristic of artist Zho's ZH4O series.",
    "prompt_zh": "{\n    \"style\": \"微缩手工立体透视模型\",\n    \"material\": \"树枝、纸板、黏土、苔藓、干花、纸张\",\n    \"surface_texture\": \"有机质感、粗糙且多样（木纹、柔软苔藓、纸张纹理）\",\n    \"lighting\": {\n        \"type\": \"柔和环境自然光\",\n        \"intensity\": \"低至中等\",\n        \"direction\": \"漫射顶光\",\n        \"accent_colors\": [\n            \"森林绿\",\n            \"大地棕\",\n            \"柔米色\",\n            \"哑粉色\"\n        ],\n        \"reflections\": false,\n        \"refractions\": false,\n        \"dispersion_effects\": fal"
}, {
    "filename": "gallery_15_3.png",
    "index": 719,
    "title": "刺绣风格狐狸森林插画",
    "title_en": "Embroidery-Style Fox Forest Illustration",
    "prompt": "A handcrafted illustration that simulates traditional embroidery using colorful threads on linen fabric. All elements are “stitched” with visible yarn textures, using techniques like satin stitch, backstitch, and French knots. Raised contours and directional thread flow create a tactile, cozy appearance. The background is made of woven linen, with gentle pastel or folk-inspired colors. The composition is friendly and magical, evoking a storybook charm. Include decorative details such as flowers, suns, clouds, trees or symbols to enhance the folk embroidery style.",
    "prompt_en": "A handcrafted illustration that simulates traditional embroidery using colorful threads on linen fabric. All elements are “stitched” with visible yarn textures, using techniques like satin stitch, backstitch, and French knots. Raised contours and directional thread flow create a tactile, cozy appearance. The background is made of woven linen, with gentle pastel or folk-inspired colors. The composition is friendly and magical, evoking a storybook charm. Include decorative details such as flowers, suns, clouds, trees or symbols to enhance the folk embroidery style.",
    "source": "https://x.com/Artedeingenio/status/1924032621220188340",
    "type": "t2i",
    "author": "@Artedeingenio",
    "author_link": "https://x.com/Artedeingenio/status/1924032621220188340",
    "revised_prompt": "一幅模拟传统手工刺绣的横向插画，背景是一块未经漂白的米色编织亚麻布，清晰可见其经纬交错的布料纹理。画面描绘了一个充满童话魅力的神奇自然场景，所有视觉元素均呈现出由彩色绣线缝制而成的真实质感。画面中央是一只风格化的可爱橙红色小狐狸，其身体由密集的缎面绣（satin stitch）构成，带有光泽的绣线顺着毛发生长的方向排列，呈现出微微凸起的立体轮廓和强烈的触感。狐狸脚下是起伏的草地，由深浅不一的绿色绣线以平针绣铺陈。画面的左上角绣着一个金黄色的太阳，光芒用放射状的粗线迹表现；天空中飘浮着几朵蓬松的白云，边缘用精细的回针绣（backstitch）勾勒，内部填充着饱满的白色纱线。狐狸周围环绕着繁茂的民间刺绣风格装饰元素，包括各种色彩柔和的粉色、淡紫色和黄色花朵，花瓣线条圆润，花蕊由密集的法国结（French knots）组成，形成明显的立体颗粒感。画面两侧对称分布着几棵童话般的矮树，树冠呈圆润的几何图案，树干带有清晰的缝线痕迹。亚麻布的留白处散布着十字形符号、小星星和红色浆果状的法国结作为点缀。整体色调以柔和的粉彩色系与传统的民间色彩为主，光线巧妙地在绣线上打出微小的阴影，增强了纱线的厚度与材质感，营造出一种温馨、舒适且充满魔法气息的故事书氛围。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/gallery_15_3.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "A horizontal illustration simulating traditional hand embroidery, set against a background of unbleached beige woven linen with clearly visible warp-and-weft fabric texture. The scene depicts a magical, fairy-tale natural landscape in which all visual elements exhibit the authentic texture of colored embroidery threads stitched onto cloth. At the center of the composition is a stylized, adorable orange-red little fox, its body formed by dense satin stitch with lustrous threads aligned along the direction of fur growth, creating a slightly raised three-dimensional contour and a strong tactile quality. Beneath the fox's feet, undulating meadows are laid out in flat stitch using green threads of varying shades. In the upper left corner, a golden sun is embroidered with radial, bold stitch marks representing its rays; several puffy white clouds float in the sky, their edges outlined with fine backstitch and their interiors filled with plump white yarn. Surrounding the fox are lush decorative elements in a folk embroidery style, including various softly colored pink, pale purple, and yellow flowers with rounded petal lines, their pistils composed of dense French knots that form distinctly raised, granular textures. On both sides of the composition, several fairy-tale-like small trees are symmetrically arranged, their canopies rendered in rounded geometric patterns and their trunks bearing visible stitch marks. The blank linen areas are dotted with cross-shaped symbols, tiny stars, and red berry-like French knots as accents. The overall palette is dominated by soft pastel tones and traditional folk colors, with light skillfully casting tiny shadows on the embroidery threads to enhance the thickness and materiality of the yarn, creating a warm, cozy, and magically enchanting storybook atmosphere.",
    "prompt_zh": "一幅手工制作的插画，模拟在亚麻织物上使用彩色丝线进行传统刺绣的效果。所有元素均以\"缝制\"方式呈现，带有可见的纱线纹理，运用缎面绣、回针绣和法式结粒绣等技法。凸起的轮廓和有方向性的线迹走向营造出触感丰富、温馨舒适的外观。背景由编织亚麻布构成，采用柔和的粉彩色调或民间风格配色。构图友好而富有魔幻感，唤起故事书般的魅力。加入花朵、太阳、云朵、树木或符号等装饰细节，以增强民间刺绣风格。"
}, {
