    "prompt": "Transform this image into a 1920s fairy tale illustration in the style of Arthur Rackham. Use muted watercolor tones and intricate ink linework. Fill the scene with whimsical forest creatures, twisted tree branches, and hidden magical objects. The overall tone should be mysterious, enchanting, and slightly eerie. Add handwritten calligraphy-style captions and riddles.",
