    "revised_prompt": "一张1950年代世纪中期现代主义风格的复古旅游宣传海报，采用纵向构图。画面完全由扁平、纯粹的几何色块构成，没有复杂的光影过渡和渐变，呈现出经典的丝网印刷质感和轻微的复古纸张纹理。整体色调温暖、乐观且怀旧，主要使用薄荷绿、暖橙色、芥末黄、深海军蓝和珊瑚粉等具有时代特征的色彩。\n\n画面背景展现了高度抽象概括的加州自然风光：上方是一个巨大的半圆形暖橙色太阳，下方交叠着由锐利三角形构成的珊瑚粉色山脉以及由平滑波浪线条勾勒的海军蓝色海洋。画面中下部，一条淡黄色的蜿蜒公路穿过画面，公路上行驶着一辆由简单几何图形拼贴而成的红色1950年代流线型复古敞篷跑车，车内有两个戴着墨镜的极简人物剪影。公路两侧矗立着几棵高耸的棕榈树，深褐色的树干笔直细长，树冠由锋利的几何绿色多边形组成，纵向延伸并打破了背景的水平线条。\n\n海报融入了强烈的排版设计和醒目的文字元素：画面顶端横跨整个宽度，印有巨大的粗体无衬线英文字母大标题，文字内容为深海军蓝色的 'CALIFORNIA'。在这排大标题的正上方，对齐排列着一行较小的芥末黄色文字标语 'VISIT SUNNY'。画面最底部由一个宽阔的暖橙色横向矩形色块托底，色块中央排布着醒目的白色大写英文宣传标语 'THE GOLDEN STATE AWAITS YOU!'。此外，画面中还散落着复古的地标标签：在左侧粉色山脉的色块上，叠印着一个黑色的小型箭头标签，内部写有白色的英文字母 'PALM SPRINGS'；右侧海岸线附近的薄荷绿区域，带有另一个指向海洋的黑色标签，上面写着 'PACIFIC COAST HIGHWAY'。整幅海报充满设计感，完美契合二十世纪中期的平面美学与积极向上的商业宣传氛围。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/gallery_21_1.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "A 1950s mid-century modern style vintage travel promotional poster in a vertical composition. The image is composed entirely of flat, pure geometric color blocks with no complex light-shadow transitions or gradients, exhibiting a classic silkscreen printing texture and a slight vintage paper grain. The overall palette is warm, optimistic, and nostalgic, primarily utilizing period-characteristic colors such as mint green, warm orange, mustard yellow, deep navy blue, and coral pink.\n\nThe background presents a highly abstracted and stylized California natural landscape: above is a large semicircular warm orange sun, below which overlap coral pink mountain ranges composed of sharp triangles and a navy blue ocean delineated by smooth, wavy lines. In the lower-middle portion, a pale yellow winding road cuts through the scene, upon which travels a red 1950s streamlined vintage convertible sports car assembled from simple geometric shapes, carrying two minimalist silhouetted figures wearing sunglasses. Flanking the road stand several towering palm trees with straight, slender dark brown trunks and canopies made of sharp geometric green polygons that extend vertically and break through the horizontal lines of the background.\n\nThe poster incorporates bold typographic design and prominent text elements: spanning the full width at the top of the image is a massive bold sans-serif uppercase English title in deep navy blue reading 'CALIFORNIA'. Directly above this large title, a smaller line of mustard yellow text is aligned, reading 'VISIT SUNNY'. At the very bottom, a wide warm orange horizontal rectangular color block serves as a base, with prominent white uppercase English promotional text centered within it reading 'THE GOLDEN STATE AWAITS YOU!'. Additionally, vintage landmark labels are scattered throughout: on the pink mountain range color block to the left, a small black arrow-shaped label is overprinted containing white English lettering reading 'PALM SPRINGS'; near the coastline on the right in a mint green area, another black label pointing toward the ocean reads 'PACIFIC COAST HIGHWAY'. The entire poster is rich in design sensibility, perfectly embodying mid-twentieth-century graphic aesthetics and an upbeat commercial promotional atmosphere.",
    "prompt_zh": "将这张图片转化为1950年代的海报，采用世纪中叶现代主义平面设计师的风格。使用扁平的几何色块搭配强烈的字体排版元素。整体基调应乐观、怀旧，具有宣传感。添加醒目的地名标签和宣传标语。"
