    "title": "彩色手绘风格表情包",
    "title_en": "Colorful Hand-Drawn Style Emoji Pack",
    "prompt": "为我生成图中角色的绘制 Q 版的，LINE 风格的半身像表情包，注意头饰要正确\n彩色手绘风格，使用 4x6 布局，涵盖各种各样的常用聊天语句，或是一些有关的娱乐 meme\n其他需求：不要原图复制。所有标注为手写简体中文。\n生成的图片需为 4K 分辨率 16:9",
    "prompt_en": "Second photo: The person is slightly turned to the side, head tilted slightly, with a soft gaze carrying a subtle emotional hint — as if caught in the moment transitioning from stillness to a smile.",
    "source": "https://x.com/Gorden_Sun/status/1992778144605212912",
    "type": "t2i",
    "author": "@Gorden_Sun",
    "author_link": "https://x.com/Gorden_Sun/status/1992778144605212912",
    "revised_prompt": "这是一张16:9比例的插画，展示了一套LINE风格的Q版二次元少女半身像表情包集合。整体采用彩色手绘风格，色彩明快，线条圆润，每个表情图案外围带有LINE贴纸标志性的白色粗描边，背景为纯白色。画面采用整齐的4行6列网格布局，共包含24个不同的独立表情。\n\n角色统一设定为一名Q版动漫少女：拥有银色长发和碧绿色眼眸，头戴一个非常显眼的深蓝色大蝴蝶结（蝴蝶结中央带有金色星星装饰），身穿深蓝色水手服配红色领结。每个表情旁边或下方都配有清晰的黑色可爱手写体简体中文标注。\n\n具体布局与内容如下：\n第一排（从左至右）：1. 少女开心地招手微笑，配字'你好呀'。2. 少女双颊泛红双手捂脸，配字'哎呀'。3. 少女双手叉腰得意地仰起头，配字'看我的！'。4. 少女趴在桌面上流着宽面条泪，配字'太难了'。5. 少女单眼Wink并向前竖起大拇指，配字'牛逼！'。6. 少女双眼变成星星状，双手合十祈求，配字'拜托拜托'。\n\n第二排（从左至右）：7. 少女震惊到下巴掉落，眼睛瞪得浑圆，配字'什么鬼？！'。8. 少女用力咬着吸管喝奶茶，腮帮子鼓起，配字'吨吨吨'。9. 少女双眼无神平躺在地，嘴里飘出半透明的灵魂，配字'我废了'。10. 少女微笑着向前递出一支红玫瑰，配字'送给你'。11. 少女怒气冲冲，头顶冒出红色的火焰特效，配字'生气了！'。12. 少女拿着一把放大镜凑近观察，面带疑惑，配字'让我康康'。\n\n第三排（从左至右）：13. 少女戴着黑色墨镜，双手抱胸装酷，嘴角上扬，配字'小场面'。14. 少女闭眼敲击身前的木鱼，表情安详，配字'阿弥陀佛'。15. 少女满头大汗，无奈地举起一面小白旗，配字'投降'。16. 少女双手化为残影疯狂敲击面前的电脑键盘，配字'在做了在做了'。17. 少女挠着后脑勺闭眼傻笑，配字'嘿嘿嘿'。18. 少女手里拿着一把塑料玩具刀，半张脸陷入阴影，露出阴险的笑容，配字'你再说一遍？'。\n\n第四排（从左至右）：19. 少女拿着红色大喇叭大声呼喊，配字'早上好！'。20. 少女全身裹在厚厚的棉被里瑟瑟发抖，配字'好冷'。21. 少女高举双手欢呼，周围有五颜六色的彩带飘落，配字'好耶！'。22. 少女捂着胸口吐出一口彩虹色的血并向后倒去，配字'受到暴击'。23. 少女戴着条纹睡帽闭着眼睛，鼻尖冒出半透明的睡眠气泡，配字'晚安'。24. 少女背着小挎包，转身欢快地挥手告别，配字'拜拜啦'。\n\n整体画面排版紧凑且充满活力，将常用的聊天语境与网络meme完美视觉化。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/gallery_28_1.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "This is a 16:9 ratio illustration showcasing a collection of LINE-style chibi (Q-version) anime girl half-body portrait sticker set. The overall style employs colorful hand-drawn illustration with bright colors and rounded lines; each expression icon features the signature thick white outline border characteristic of LINE stickers, set against a pure white background. The layout follows a neat 4-row by 6-column grid, containing a total of 24 different individual expressions.\n\nThe character has a unified design as a chibi anime girl: she has silver long hair and emerald green eyes, wearing a very prominent large dark blue bow on her head (with a gold star decoration at the center of the bow), dressed in a dark blue sailor uniform with a red necktie. Each expression is accompanied by clear black cute handwritten Simplified Chinese annotations placed beside or below.\n\nSpecific layout and content are as follows:\nRow 1 (left to right): 1. The girl happily waves and smiles, captioned '你好呀' (Hello there). 2. The girl blushes with both cheeks red and covers her face with both hands, captioned '哎呀' (Oh my). 3. The girl stands with hands on hips, tilting her head up proudly, captioned '看我的！' (Watch me!). 4. The girl lies slumped on a desk with wide noodle-like tears streaming down, captioned '太难了' (Too hard). 5. The girl winks with one eye and gives a thumbs-up forward, captioned '牛逼！' (Awesome!). 6. The girl's eyes turn into star shapes, hands pressed together in prayer, captioned '拜托拜托' (Please please).\n\nRow 2 (left to right): 7. The girl is shocked with her jaw dropping and eyes wide open in perfect circles, captioned '什么鬼？！' (What the heck?!). 8. The girl bites hard on a straw drinking milk tea, cheeks puffed out, captioned '吨吨吨' (Gulp gulp gulp). 9. The girl lies flat on the ground with lifeless eyes, a semi-transparent soul floating out of her mouth, captioned '我废了' (I'm done for). 10. The girl smiles and extends a red rose forward, captioned '送给你' (For you). 11. The girl is furious, with red flame effects bursting from the top of her head, captioned '生气了！' (I'm angry!). 12. The girl holds a magnifying glass up close to examine something, wearing a puzzled expression, captioned '让我康康' (Let me see see).\n\nRow 3 (left to right): 13. The girl wears black sunglasses, arms crossed acting cool, corners of her mouth turned up, captioned '小场面' (No big deal). 14. The girl closes her eyes and taps a wooden fish (mokugyo) in front of her, expression serene, captioned '阿弥陀佛' (Amitabha). 15. The girl is drenched in sweat, helplessly raising a small white flag, captioned '投降' (I surrender). 16. The girl's hands become motion-blurred afterimages frantically typing on a computer keyboard in front of her, captioned '在做了在做了' (Working on it, working on it). 17. The girl scratches the back of her head with eyes closed, grinning sheepishly, captioned '嘿嘿嘿' (Hehehe). 18. The girl holds a plastic toy knife, half of her face cast in shadow, revealing a sinister smile, captioned '你",
    "prompt_zh": "为我生成图中角色的绘制 Q 版的，LINE 风格的半身像表情包，注意头饰要正确\n彩色手绘风格，使用 4x6 布局，涵盖各种各样的常用聊天语句，或是一些有关的娱乐 meme\n其他需求：不要原图复制。所有标注为手写简体中文。\n生成的图片需为 4K 分辨率 16:9"
