    "prompt_en": "Third photo: The person is more relaxed, showing a gentle smile. Hair falls naturally, posture is easygoing, conveying confidence and comfort.\n\nThis progression from \"composed → relaxed → smiling\" gives the entire set a sense of dynamic narrative.\n\nLighting and Skin Texture\n• The lighting is even and soft, with no harsh shadows.\n• The lighting angle creates very subtle dimensional shadows on the cheeks and nose bridge, accentuating facial contours without being overly sharp.\n• Skin tone is natural with fine reflections, presenting a soft-focus quality with a slight film or Japanese-style filter effect.\n\nClothing and Material\n\nThe person wears a light grayish-blue camisole top with thin straps; the fabric is soft and form-fitting, reflecting a gentle sheen. Under the light, it presents",
