    "revised_prompt": "超写实风格的高角度抓拍照片。画面采用16:9的宽幅构图，展现了一个自然随性的生活场景。视觉中心是一位年轻的亚洲女生，她正蹲坐在带有粗糙质感和轻微斑驳的水泥地庭院中。女生侧身向后回望，目光微微上扬，与镜头产生对视。她的面部细节极为逼真，肌肤瓷白细腻，散发着自然的柔光；双唇紧闭，嘴角带着害羞含蓄的笑容，大而明亮的圆眼睛和明显的卧蚕衬托出俏皮可爱的神情。她身穿一件鼠尾草绿色的针织露背长袖上衣，柔软的针织纹理清晰可见，长袖自然垂下覆盖住了大半个手掌；下身搭配浅蓝色的牛仔短裤，双脚赤裸穿着一双棕褐色的平底凉鞋。女生的一只手臂向外舒展，正在逗弄身旁一只姜黄色的猫咪，猫咪脖子上拴着一根细长的牵引绳，毛发蓬松且色泽温暖。在画面的另一侧，摆放着一张质朴的木质桌子，桌上覆盖着一块粉色的民族风桌布，桌布上带有复杂的几何花纹和流苏边缘。整体光线柔和明亮，色彩搭配和谐，鼠尾草绿、姜黄、粉色与灰色的水泥地形成丰富的视觉层次。画面具备8K分辨率级别的极致清晰度，从针织衫的毛线纤维、人物的皮肤肌理到猫咪的根根毛发都得到了真实的还原，充满生活气息与抓拍的动态美感。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/gallery_32_2.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "A hyper-realistic high-angle candid photograph. The image adopts a 16:9 wide-format composition, presenting a natural and casual everyday scene. At the visual center is a young Asian girl, crouching and sitting in a cement courtyard with a rough texture and slight mottling. The girl is turned sideways, looking back over her shoulder with her gaze slightly upward, making eye contact with the camera. Her facial details are extremely lifelike—her skin is porcelain-white and delicate, radiating a natural soft glow; her lips are closed with a shy, subtle smile at the corners of her mouth, and her large, bright round eyes paired with prominent aegyo-sal (charming under-eye fat) accentuate her playful and adorable expression. She wears a sage green knitted open-back long-sleeve top, with the soft knit texture clearly visible and the long sleeves naturally draping down to cover most of her palms; on the bottom, she pairs it with light blue denim shorts, her bare feet in a pair of tan flat sandals. One of the girl's arms stretches outward, teasing a ginger-colored cat beside her; the cat has a slender leash tied around its neck, with fluffy fur in a warm tone. On the other side of the frame, a rustic wooden table is placed, draped with a pink ethnic-style tablecloth featuring intricate geometric patterns and fringed edges. The overall lighting is soft and bright, with a harmonious color palette—sage green, ginger, pink, and the gray cement ground create rich visual layers. The image possesses 8K-resolution-level extreme clarity, faithfully reproducing every detail from the yarn fibers of the knit sweater, the skin texture of the subject, to each individual strand of the cat's fur, brimming with a sense of everyday life and the dynamic beauty of a candid capture.",
    "prompt_zh": "以超写实风格，从高角度捕捉一张自然随性的抓拍照片：年轻的亚洲女生蹲坐在水泥地的庭院中，侧身向后回望，目光微微上扬对视镜头；她嘴唇紧闭，带着害羞含蓄的笑容，眼睛大而明亮、圆润，明显的卧蚕衬托出俏皮可爱的神情。肌肤瓷白细腻，散发着自然的柔光。她穿着一件鼠尾草绿的针织露背长袖上衣，袖子覆盖着手掌，下身搭配牛仔短裤，赤脚穿着棕褐色凉鞋。一只手臂向外舒展，正在与旁边栓着绳子的姜黄色猫咪互动，身旁放着一张覆盖粉色民族风桌布的木质桌子。图片呈现8K分辨率，风格真实、细节丰富。"
