    "revised_prompt": "一幅竖向构图的水下微距摄影特写人像，画面紧凑裁剪，仅展示了一位年轻女性脸部的左半部分。她的面部完全沉浸在清澈的水中，皮肤白皙且具有极高的超写实纹理细节。画面焦点精准落在她的左眼上，眼睛清澈明亮，眼神平静安详却透着深邃而强烈的凝视感。光线透过水面折射，在她的肌肤上形成了复杂而迷人的焦散反射与流体般的波光斑驳，清脆明亮的高光与电影感柔和的阴影交织在一起。利用浅景深效果，前景和背景中模糊悬浮着微细的水滴和细密的气泡，为画面增添了强烈的空间立体感。在画面的右侧边缘，深色的发丝隐约可见，如丝带般在水中自然舒展漂浮。画面中没有可见的衣物，纯粹聚焦于水、光线与人物肌肤的交织互动，整体色调清透，营造出一种超现实、梦幻、空灵且宁静的视觉氛围。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/gallery_35_2.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "A vertically composed underwater macro photography close-up portrait, tightly cropped to reveal only the left half of a young woman's face. Her face is fully submerged in crystal-clear water, with fair skin rendered in extremely high hyperrealistic textural detail. The focal point lands precisely on her left eye—clear and bright, with a calm and serene gaze that nonetheless conveys a profound and intense sense of staring. Light refracts through the water surface, casting intricate and mesmerizing caustic reflections and fluid-like dappled ripples of light across her skin, where crisp, bright highlights interweave with cinematically soft shadows. Utilizing a shallow depth of field, the foreground and background feature blurred, suspended fine water droplets and delicate bubbles, adding a strong sense of spatial dimensionality. Along the right edge of the frame, dark strands of hair are faintly visible, drifting and unfurling naturally in the water like ribbons. No clothing is visible in the frame; the composition focuses purely on the interplay of water, light, and the subject's skin. The overall color tone is clear and translucent, creating a surreal, dreamlike, ethereal, and tranquil visual atmosphere.",
    "prompt_zh": "保持图片中的内容简洁，仅保留主标题"
