    "prompt": "{\n  \"image_info\": {\n    \"width\": 768,\n    \"height\": 1365,\n    \"aspect_ratio\": \"9:16\",\n    \"orientation\": \"vertical\"\n  },\n\n  \"subject\": {\n    \"type\": \"close-up portrait\",\n    \"description\": \"A young East Asian woman making a heart shape with her hands directly in front of the camera, with her head gently tilted\"\n  },\n\n  \"clothing\": {\n    \"visible\": false,\n    \"notes\": \"No clothing visible within the framing\"\n  },\n\n  \"hair\": {\n    \"color\": \"black\",\n    \"style\": \"straight\",\n    \"details\": \"Loose strands falling naturally across her face\"\n  },\n\n  \"face\": {\n    \"eyes\": {\n      \"shape\": \"almond-shaped\",\n      \"color\": \"dark brown\",\n      \"makeup\": \"subtle eyeliner, defined lashes, soft shimmer on lids\",\n      \"expression\": \"one eye winked, the other softly open\"\n    },\n    \"eyebrows\": \"natural, slightly arched\",\n    \"skin\": \"smooth, natural glow\",\n    \"lips\": {\n      \"shape\": \"full\",\n      \"color\": \"pink glossy tint\",\n      \"expression\": \"kiss face (puckered lips)\"\n    },\n    \"other_details\": \"small mole under the left eye\"\n  },\n\n  \"accessories\": {\n    \"visible\": false\n  },\n\n  \"environment\": {\n    \"background\": \"not visible; fully obscured by the extreme close-up framing\"\n  },\n\n  \"lighting\": {\n    \"type\": \"soft diffused light\",\n    \"effects\": \"even illumination, minimal shadows, natural skin highlights\"\n  },\n\n  \"camera\": {\n    \"framing\": \"extreme close-up (eyes, nose, and lips filling the frame)\",\n    \"angle\": \"straight-on\",\n    \"depth_of_field\": \"very shallow\",\n    \"focus\": \"sharp on eyes and lips\",\n    \"foreground_elements\": \"hands forming a heart shape in front of the face\"\n  },\n\n  \"style\": {\n    \"aesthetic\": \"soft, playful, intimate\",\n    \"texture\": \"high-resolution portrait with film-like softness\",\n    \"vibe\": \"cute, expressive, flirtatious\"\n  }\n}",
    "prompt_en": "{\n  \"image_info\": {\n    \"width\": 768,\n    \"height\": 1365,\n    \"aspect_ratio\": \"9:16\",\n    \"orientation\": \"vertical\"\n  },\n\n  \"subject\": {\n    \"type\": \"close-up portrait\",\n    \"description\": \"A young East Asian woman making a heart shape with her hands directly in front of the camera, with her head gently tilted\"\n  },\n\n  \"clothing\": {\n    \"visible\": false,\n    \"notes\": \"No clothing visible within the framing\"\n  },\n\n  \"hair\": {\n    \"color\": \"black\",\n    \"style\": \"straight\",\n    \"details\": \"Loose strands falling naturally across her face\"\n  },\n\n  \"face\": {\n    \"eyes\": {\n      \"shape\": \"almond-shaped\",\n      \"color\": \"dark brown\",\n      \"makeup\": \"subtle eyeliner, defined lashes, soft shimmer on lids\",\n      \"expression\": \"one eye winked, the other softly open\"\n    },\n    \"eyebrows\": \"natural, slightly arched\",\n    \"skin\": \"smooth, natural glow\",\n    \"lips\": {\n      \"shape\": \"full\",\n      \"color\": \"pink glossy tint\",\n      \"expression\": \"kiss face (puckered lips)\"\n    },\n    \"other_details\": \"small mole under the left eye\"\n  },\n\n  \"accessories\": {\n    \"visible\": false\n  },\n\n  \"environment\": {\n    \"background\": \"not visible; fully obscured by the extreme close-up framing\"\n  },\n\n  \"lighting\": {\n    \"type\": \"soft diffused light\",\n    \"effects\": \"even illumination, minimal shadows, natural skin highlights\"\n  },\n\n  \"camera\": {\n    \"framing\": \"extreme close-up (eyes, nose, and lips filling the frame)\",\n    \"angle\": \"straight-on\",\n    \"depth_of_field\": \"very shallow\",\n    \"focus\": \"sharp on eyes and lips\",\n    \"foreground_elements\": \"hands forming a heart shape in front of the face\"\n  },\n\n  \"style\": {\n    \"aesthetic\": \"soft, playful, intimate\",\n    \"texture\": \"high-resolution portrait with film-like softness\",\n    \"vibe\": \"cute, expressive, flirtatious\"\n  }\n}",
    "source": "https://x.com/SDT_side/status/1994133786632806832",
    "type": "t2i",
    "author": "@SDT_side",
    "author_link": "https://x.com/SDT_side/status/1994133786632806832",
    "revised_prompt": "高分辨率的极度特写人像摄影照片，带有胶片般的柔和质感，采用竖向构图。画面主体为一名年轻的东亚女性，她的脸部（眼睛、鼻子和嘴唇）几乎填满了整个画面，没有任何衣物或背景显露出来。女性的头部微微倾斜，她的双手直接在镜头前方比出一个清晰的心形手势，作为画面的前景元素。\n\n她拥有一头黑色的直发，几缕零星的散发自然地垂落在她的脸庞和眼角处。人物皮肤光滑，泛着自然透亮的光泽。她的眉毛呈现自然微拱的形状。她长着深棕色的杏眼，眼妆包括精致的眼线、根根分明的睫毛以及眼睑处柔和的珠光微闪。她的表情十分俏皮生动：一只眼睛调皮地闭上眨眼（wink），另一只眼睛则柔和地睁开，左眼下方清晰可见一颗小小的泪痣；她丰满的嘴唇上涂着亮粉色的镜面光泽唇彩，正做出嘟嘴亲吻的表情。画面中没有任何可见的珠宝或配饰，背景也因极度特写的取景被完全遮挡不可见。\n\n光线为柔和的漫反射光，整体照明均匀，面部阴影极少，皮肤上呈现出自然细腻的高光质感。镜头采用正视平拍的角度，景深极浅，焦点锐利地落在她睁开的眼睛和嘟起的嘴唇上，而位于脸部前方比心的双手则带有自然的轻微虚化效果。整体画面传达出一种可爱、俏皮、亲密且充满表现力的美学氛围。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/gallery_37_2.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "A high-resolution extreme close-up portrait photograph with a film-like soft quality, in vertical composition. The subject is a young East Asian woman whose face—eyes, nose, and lips—fills nearly the entire frame, with no clothing or background visible. Her head is slightly tilted, and her hands are held directly in front of the lens, forming a clear heart-shaped hand gesture as a foreground element.\n\nShe has straight black hair, with a few stray strands naturally falling across her face and the corners of her eyes. Her skin is smooth with a naturally translucent, luminous glow. Her eyebrows have a naturally soft-arched shape. She has dark brown almond-shaped eyes, with eye makeup comprising delicate eyeliner, individually defined lashes, and a soft pearlescent shimmer on the eyelids. Her expression is playful and lively: one eye is cheekily closed in a wink while the other is softly open, with a small beauty mark (teardrop mole) clearly visible beneath the left eye. Her full lips are coated in a bright pink mirror-gloss lip glaze, pursed in a pouty kiss expression. No jewelry or accessories are visible in the frame, and the background is entirely obscured due to the extreme close-up framing.\n\nThe lighting is soft diffused light with even overall illumination, minimal facial shadows, and a naturally delicate highlight quality on the skin. The lens angle is a straight-on, eye-level shot with an extremely shallow depth of field; the focus falls sharply on her open eye and pouted lips, while her hands forming the heart shape in front of her face carry a natural, slight bokeh effect. The overall image conveys a cute, playful, intimate, and highly expressive aesthetic atmosphere.",
    "prompt_zh": "图片中使用英文文字"
