    "title": "胶片闪光灯女性肖像",
    "title_en": "Film Flash Female Portrait",
    "prompt": "A young woman, same face preserved, lit by a harsh on-camera flash from a thrift-store film camera. Her hair is loosely pinned, stray strands shadowing her eyes. She gives a knowing half-smirk. She’s wearing a charcoal cardigan with texture. Behind her: a cluttered wall of handwritten notes and torn film stills. The shot feels like a raw indie-movie still — grain-heavy, imperfect, intentional.",
    "prompt_en": "A young woman, same face preserved, lit by a harsh on-camera flash from a thrift-store film camera. Her hair is loosely pinned, stray strands shadowing her eyes. She gives a knowing half-smirk. She’s wearing a charcoal cardigan with texture. Behind her: a cluttered wall of handwritten notes and torn film stills. The shot feels like a raw indie-movie still — grain-heavy, imperfect, intentional.",
    "source": "https://twitter.com/kingofdairyque/status/1992082212913860858",
    "type": "t2i",
    "author": "@kingofdairyque",
    "author_link": "https://twitter.com/kingofdairyque/status/1992082212913860858",
    "revised_prompt": "一张呈现原始独立电影剧照风格的竖幅人物摄影照片，画面布满强烈的胶片颗粒感，带有刻意为之的不完美与粗糙质感。画面中央处于近景特写的是一位年轻女子。她的头发被松散地别在脑后，几缕凌乱的发丝自然垂落，在强烈的直射光下于她的眼眸周围投下明显的阴影。她正对着镜头，嘴角微微上扬，露出一抹似乎看透一切的戏谑半微笑。她身穿一件带有明显针织纹理的炭灰色开衫。画面的打光呈现出二手胶片相机典型的强烈机顶闪光灯效果，高强度的正面硬光照亮了女子的脸部和上半身，同时在她身后的墙面上投下了浓重且边缘锐利的黑色人物轮廓阴影。女子的身后是一面杂乱的背景墙，上面贴满了各种纸张。其中包括几张边缘被撕裂的黑白电影剧照，画面隐约可见模糊的雨夜街景与暗调的人物剪影。剧照之间穿插着许多用透明胶带随意贴着的泛黄便签、撕下来的笔记本纸条，上面带有黑色的手写英文笔记。可以清晰辨认出纸条上的文字包括：视线左侧一张写着 'Scene 04: The Encounter'，右侧一张稍大的纸片上写着 'Where do we go from here?'，靠近女子肩部的角落里一小块纸条上写着 'Don't forget to breathe'，还有一张似乎是日常清单的便签上写着 'Milk, bread, film rolls'。整体色调偏向冷暗，高反差的生硬光影与充满质感的衣物、细节丰富的背景墙共同构建出一种真实、颓废且充满故事感的独立电影氛围。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/gallery_51_4.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "A vertical portrait photograph in the style of a raw independent film still, the image saturated with intense film grain and carrying a deliberate imperfection and rough texture. At the center of the frame in a close-up shot is a young woman. Her hair is loosely pinned back, with several disheveled strands falling naturally, casting noticeable shadows around her eyes under the strong direct light. She faces the camera straight on, the corners of her lips slightly upturned in a wry half-smile that seems to see through everything. She wears a charcoal-gray cardigan with a distinctly visible knit texture. The lighting exhibits the characteristic harsh on-camera flash effect typical of secondhand film cameras—high-intensity frontal hard light illuminates the woman's face and upper body while casting a heavy, sharp-edged black silhouette shadow of her figure onto the wall behind her. Behind the woman is a cluttered background wall covered with various papers. These include several black-and-white film stills with torn edges, their images faintly showing blurred rainy night street scenes and dark-toned human silhouettes. Interspersed among the stills are many yellowed sticky notes and torn notebook scraps casually affixed with transparent tape, bearing handwritten English notes in black ink. The text on the notes can be clearly made out: on the left side of the frame, one reads 'Scene 04: The Encounter'; on the right, a slightly larger piece of paper reads 'Where do we go from here?'; in the corner near the woman's shoulder, a small note reads 'Don't forget to breathe'; and another note resembling an everyday list reads 'Milk, bread, film rolls'. The overall color tone leans cool and dark, and the high-contrast harsh lighting combined with the textured clothing and the detail-rich background wall collectively construct an authentic, decadent, and narratively charged indie film atmosphere.",
    "prompt_zh": "一位年轻女性，保持相同面孔，被廉价胶片相机的机顶闪光灯harsh地照亮。她的头发松散地别着，散落的发丝在眼前投下阴影。她露出一个意味深长的半笑。她穿着一件有纹理质感的炭灰色开衫。她身后：一面贴满手写笔记和撕下的电影剧照的杂乱墙壁。画面感觉像一张原始的独立电影剧照——颗粒感强烈、不完美、却是刻意为之。"
}, {
    "filename": "gallery_55_2.png",
    "index": 1813,
    "title": "神经网络工厂剖面图",
    "title_en": "Neural Network Factory Cross-Section",
    "prompt": "Generate a diagram of a two-layer neural network in the style of Stephen Biesty",
    "prompt_en": "Generate a diagram of a two-layer neural network in the style of Stephen Biesty",
    "source": "https://twitter.com/jon_barron/status/1991554563233779822",
    "type": "t2i",
    "author": "@jon_barron",
    "author_link": "https://twitter.com/jon_barron/status/1991554563233779822",
    "revised_prompt": "一幅采用斯蒂芬·比斯蒂（Stephen Biesty）标志性手绘剖面图风格的横幅插画，将双层神经网络（Two-layer neural network）具象化为一座庞大且极其复杂的工业运转工厂。画面为横向布局，从左至右呈现数据的物理处理流程。画风以极细致的黑白钢笔线条勾勒，并辅以复古的淡彩水彩渲染，展现出建筑与机械的内部横截面，充满密集的微观细节。\n\n画面最上方用复古衬线字体写着大标题 'TWO-LAYER NEURAL NETWORK'。\n\n画面左侧为“输入层”，被描绘为四个高耸的砖石与铸铁混合材质的进料筒仓。筒仓外壁被剖开，露出内部的螺旋传送带和粉碎机。大量微小的工人正推着矿车，将发光的蓝色水晶矿石（代表原始数据）倾倒入顶部的漏斗中。细长的黑色引线连接着这些结构，标注文字为：'Input Data Sorter'、'Input 1'、'Input 2'、'Input 3'、'Input 4'。\n\n画面中央为“隐藏层”，由五个巨大的、内部结构错综复杂的球状处理锅炉并排组成。从左侧四个输入筒仓延伸出密密麻麻、如蜘蛛网般交错的黄铜管道，确保每个筒仓都有管道连接到中央的每一个锅炉（具象化全连接层）。管道上设有巨大的手轮调节阀门。锅炉内部被剖开，展示出多层齿轮、搅拌轴和底部发光的红色蒸汽燃烧室（具象化激活函数）。数百个穿着蓝色工装的微小工人活动于复杂的金属脚手架、楼梯和栈桥上，有的正合力转动沉重的黄铜阀门（代表权重调整），有的在读取仪表盘，还有一名工人正坐在悬空的钢梁上喝着咖啡休息。该区域的引线标注文字包括：'Synaptic Weight Valve'、'Hidden Layer Chamber'、'Bias Input Pump'、'Activation Function Generator'。\n\n画面右侧为“输出层”，包含两个高耸的精密蒸馏塔。从中央五个隐藏层锅炉延伸出的粗壮管道汇聚于这两个蒸馏塔中。塔身内部展示着多层过滤网和离心机，最终提炼出金色的液体流入底部的带刻度的收集槽。几名身穿白大褂的小人正拿着记录板在槽边记录。该区域的引线标注文字为：'Output Signal Refiner'、'Prediction Output 1'、'Prediction Output 2'。\n\n整体背景为带有羊皮纸质感的米白色，使庞大复杂的机械结构脱颖而出。色彩以工业时代的黄铜色、生锈的红砖色、钢铁灰为主，数据流的蓝、红、金三色作为高光点缀。构图宏大，机械逻辑严密，充满探索趣味。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/gallery_55_2.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "A horizontal illustration in the signature hand-drawn cutaway style of Stephen Biesty, visualizing a two-layer neural network as a massive and extraordinarily complex industrial processing factory. The layout is horizontal, presenting the physical data-processing flow from left to right. The art style is rendered in extremely fine black-and-white pen linework, supplemented with vintage light watercolor washes, revealing architectural and mechanical interior cross-sections brimming with dense, microscopic details.\n\nAt the very top of the image, a large title in a vintage serif typeface reads 'TWO-LAYER NEURAL NETWORK'.\n\nOn the left side of the image is the \"Input Layer,\" depicted as four towering feed silos constructed from a hybrid of brick masonry and cast iron. The outer walls of the silos are cut away to expose internal spiral conveyors and crushers. Numerous tiny workers push minecarts, tipping glowing blue crystal ore (representing raw data) into hoppers at the top. Slender black leader lines connect to these structures with annotation text reading: 'Input Data Sorter', 'Input 1', 'Input 2', 'Input 3', 'Input 4'.\n\nAt the center of the image is the \"Hidden Layer,\" composed of five enormous spherical processing boilers with intricately complex internal structures, arranged side by side. From the four input silos on the left, a dense, spider-web-like tangle of brass pipes extends outward, ensuring that every silo has a pipe connecting to each and every one of the central boilers (visualizing the fully connected layer). The pipes are fitted with large hand-wheel regulating valves. The boilers are cut away to reveal multiple layers of gears, agitator shafts, and glowing red steam combustion chambers at the bottom (visualizing the activation function). Hundreds of tiny workers in blue overalls move about on complex metal scaffolding, staircases, and catwalks—some are collaboratively turning heavy brass valves (representing weight adjustment), others are reading instrument panels, and one worker is sitting on a suspended steel beam drinking coffee on a break. Leader-line annotations in this area include: 'Synaptic Weight Valve', 'Hidden Layer Chamber', 'Bias Input Pump', 'Activation Function Generator'.\n\nOn the right side of the image is the \"Output Layer,\" containing two towering precision distillation columns. Thick pipes extending from the five hidden-layer boilers at the center—",
    "prompt_zh": "生成一张两层神经网络的示意图，采用Stephen Biesty的画风。"
