    "title": "文字拼接跑车剪影海报",
    "title_en": "Typography Sports Car Silhouette Poster",
    "prompt": "创建一个[OBJECT]形状的文字插画,文字本身构成该形状。字体风格为粗体且活泼,填满整个轮廓,文字沿对象的曲线和轮廓自然排列。色彩选择鲜明对比且契合主题的。背景为纯色,以突出主体形状。风格采用矢量风格,干净整洁。分辨率高,适合海报格式。",
    "prompt_en": "Create a text illustration in the shape of a [OBJECT], where the text itself forms the shape. The font style should be bold and playful, filling the entire outline, with the text naturally arranged along the curves and contours of the object. Use vivid, contrasting colors that match the theme. The background should be a solid color to make the main shape stand out. Use a clean, vector-style aesthetic. High resolution, suitable for poster format.",
    "source": "https://adg.csdn.net/694e3f255b9f5f31781b0c9e.html",
    "type": "t2i",
    "author": "@gnrlyxyz",
    "author_link": "https://adg.csdn.net/694e3f255b9f5f31781b0c9e.html",
    "revised_prompt": "一张横幅矢量文字插画海报。画面的背景为纯净的深藏青色，中心主体是一个完全由英文单词变形、拼接而成的复古跑车侧面剪影。跑车的造型横跨整个宽幅画面，所有文字均采用粗体且充满活力的无衬线字体，文字的边缘、拉伸方向和排版走向完美贴合跑车的流线型曲线与物理轮廓，内部被文字填满，不留多余空隙。\n\n跑车的车顶至车头引擎盖的流畅抛物线由巨大的亮红色单词 'ADRENALINE' 构成，字母被拉伸并随车身的空气动力学弧度自然弯曲。侧车门区域由鲜黄色的粗重区块字体 'CLASSIC' 填满，字母上下紧密挤压排列，构成厚实的车身侧面。车窗部分由倾斜的纯白色单词 'FREEDOM' 组成，字母的倾斜角度恰好勾勒出挡风玻璃与侧窗的几何形状。\n\n跑车的底盘和轮胎同样由文字塑造：前轮由白色的单词 'SPEED' 首尾相接弯曲成完美的圆形；后轮由白色的单词 'POWER' 弯曲成等大的圆形；两个车轮的中心轮毂位置分别点缀着小号的亮黄色单词 'SPIN'。车头大灯位置由明黄色的单词 'GLOW' 构成，而车尾排气管位置则由一段向外发散的橙色单词 'ROAR' 形成，带有强烈的动感。\n\n整体色彩采用极具视觉冲击力的高对比度配色，红、黄、白色的文字在深藏青色背景的衬托下极为醒目。画面风格干净整洁，边缘清晰锐利，没有渐变或杂乱的背景元素，纯粹依靠文字的形变与阵列构建出跑车的体积感与速度感。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/gallery_57_3.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "A horizontal vector typographic illustration poster. The background is a pure deep navy blue, and the central subject is a vintage sports car side-profile silhouette composed entirely of deformed, interlocking English words. The car's form spans the entire wide-format image. All text is set in bold, dynamic sans-serif typefaces, with the edges, stretch directions, and typographic flow of the words perfectly conforming to the streamlined curves and physical contours of the sports car, the interior filled completely with text, leaving no excess gaps.\n\nThe smooth parabolic line from the car's rooftop to the hood is formed by the large, bright red word 'ADRENALINE', its letters stretched and naturally curved to follow the aerodynamic arc of the body. The side door area is filled with the bold, heavy block letters of 'CLASSIC' in vivid yellow, the letters tightly compressed top-to-bottom to form the solid flank of the car body. The window section is composed of the angled, pure white word 'FREEDOM', the tilt of the letters precisely delineating the geometric shapes of the windshield and side windows.\n\nThe chassis and tires of the sports car are likewise sculpted from text: the front wheel is formed by the white word 'SPEED' bent end-to-end into a perfect circle; the rear wheel is formed by the white word 'POWER' curved into an equally sized circle; at the hub center of each wheel, the small bright yellow word 'SPIN' is placed as an accent. The headlight position at the front is formed by the bright yellow word 'GLOW', while the exhaust pipe at the rear is formed by the orange word 'ROAR' radiating outward, conveying a strong sense of motion.\n\nThe overall color scheme employs a highly visually impactful, high-contrast palette—red, yellow, and white text stands out strikingly against the deep navy blue background. The style is clean and neat, with crisp, sharp edges, no gradients or cluttered background elements, relying purely on the deformation and arrangement of text to construct the sports car's volume and sense of speed.",
    "prompt_zh": "创建一个[OBJECT]形状的文字插画,文字本身构成该形状。字体风格为粗体且活泼,填满整个轮廓,文字沿对象的曲线和轮廓自然排列。色彩选择鲜明对比且契合主题的。背景为纯色,以突出主体形状。风格采用矢量风格,干净整洁。分辨率高,适合海报格式。"
}, {
    "filename": "gallery_60_3.png",
    "index": 1994,
    "title": "咖啡品牌矢量贴纸设计集",
    "title_en": "Coffee Brand Vector Sticker Design Set",
    "prompt": "[BRAND NAME]. Act as a vector illustrator designing a trendy, high-end \"Sticker Sheet\" set.\nTHE TASK:\nDeconstruct the brand identity of [BRAND NAME] into a playful, cohesive set of approximately 8-10 unique sticker designs arranged on a single sheet.\nContent Generation: Do not just make logos. Autonomously invent a mix of:\nMascots/Characters: Stylized busts of people wearing brand-relevant accessories or expressing emotions.\nKey Products: Iconic items associated with the brand.\nSymbols/Objects: Abstract shapes or tools relevant to the brand's lifestyle.\n\nVISUAL STYLE (MONOLINE VECTOR):\nThe art style must strictly match \"Modern Trendy Line Art.\"\nLine Work: Use a THICK, UNIFORM line weight (monoline) for all internal details. The lines should be smooth, rounded, and confident.\nColoring: The stickers must be filled with Solid Off-White or Cream, utilizing the line color for details. NO gradients, NO shading, NO 3D effects. Flat 2D vector look.\nThe \"Sticker\" Effect: Every element must have a thick, distinct White (or Cream) Die-Cut Border surrounding it, separating it from the background.\nCOLOR PALETTE (HIGH CONTRAST):\nBackground: A solid, deep, saturated color to create maximum contrast.\nStickers: High-brightness Cream or White fill with Dark (Black or Dark Brown) outlines.\nCOMPOSITION:\nThe stickers are scattered naturally across the sheet (knolling layout) with even spacing. No overlapping.",
    "prompt_en": "[BRAND NAME]. Act as a vector illustrator designing a trendy, high-end \"Sticker Sheet\" set.\nTHE TASK:\nDeconstruct the brand identity of [BRAND NAME] into a playful, cohesive set of approximately 8-10 unique sticker designs arranged on a single sheet.\nContent Generation: Do not just make logos. Autonomously invent a mix of:\nMascots/Characters: Stylized busts of people wearing brand-relevant accessories or expressing emotions.\nKey Products: Iconic items associated with the brand.\nSymbols/Objects: Abstract shapes or tools relevant to the brand's lifestyle.\n\nVISUAL STYLE (MONOLINE VECTOR):\nThe art style must strictly match \"Modern Trendy Line Art.\"\nLine Work: Use a THICK, UNIFORM line weight (monoline) for all internal details. The lines should be smooth, rounded, and confident.\nColoring: The stickers must be filled with Solid Off-White or Cream, utilizing the line color for details. NO gradients, NO shading, NO 3D effects. Flat 2D vector look.\nThe \"Sticker\" Effect: Every element must have a thick, distinct White (or Cream) Die-Cut Border surrounding it, separating it from the background.\nCOLOR PALETTE (HIGH CONTRAST):\nBackground: A solid, deep, saturated color to create maximum contrast.\nStickers: High-brightness Cream or White fill with Dark (Black or Dark Brown) outlines.\nCOMPOSITION:\nThe stickers are scattered naturally across the sheet (knolling layout) with even spacing. No overlapping.",
    "source": "https://x.com/AmirMushich/status/2009717451710509473",
