    "author_link": "https://x.com/AmirMushich/status/2009717451710509473",
    "revised_prompt": "一张现代流行矢量线稿插画风格的贴纸套装（Sticker Sheet）设计图，竖版构图。画面的背景是单一的高对比度深藏蓝色（Deep Navy Blue）。画面中均匀散布（平铺排列/knolling layout）着10个互不重叠的独立贴纸设计，围绕虚构的高端咖啡品牌‘AURA COFFEE’的主题展开。所有贴纸严格遵循极简扁平的2D矢量外观，完全没有任何渐变、阴影或3D效果。每个贴纸的内部细节都采用粗细绝对均匀、平滑、圆润的纯黑色单线（monoline）勾勒，贴纸的内部填充色全部为纯正的米白色（Off-White），而每个贴纸的外围都包裹着一圈厚重且轮廓分明的纯白色模切边框（Die-Cut Border），将其与深色背景清晰地隔离开来。这10个具体的贴纸内容如下：1. 一个戴着圆形复古墨镜的短发女孩半身像，她正用吸管喝着一杯冰咖啡，神态十分悠闲。2. 一个标志性的带盖外带热咖啡纸杯，杯身正中央写有英文大写的品牌名 'AURA'。3. 一台极简线条构成的意式浓缩咖啡机，清晰可见冲煮头、手柄和蒸汽棒。4. 一杯从正上方俯视视角的拿铁咖啡与底碟，咖啡表面有精致的爱心拉花线条。5. 一个带有摇把的复古手摇咖啡豆研磨机。6. 一个轮廓饱满的可颂面包，表面有几道平滑的弧线表现酥皮纹理。7. 一个可爱的拟人化咖啡豆角色，有着纤细的手臂和腿，脸上挂着调皮的微笑并举起一只手打招呼。8. 一个采用粗胖泡泡字（Bubble letter）设计的纯文字贴纸，内容为英文大写 'BREW'。9. 一个带有波浪形丝带外框的文字贴纸，丝带中央写有英文大写 'AURA COFFEE'。10. 一组由三颗咖啡豆堆叠组成的图案，周围点缀着两颗简单的四芒星闪光符号。整体画面视觉高级、干净且充满潮流感。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/gallery_60_3.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "A modern trendy vector line-art illustration style sticker sheet design in portrait orientation. The background is a single high-contrast Deep Navy Blue. Evenly distributed across the canvas in a knolling layout are 10 non-overlapping independent sticker designs, themed around the fictional premium coffee brand 'AURA COFFEE'. All stickers strictly adhere to a minimalist flat 2D vector appearance, with absolutely no gradients, shadows, or 3D effects. The internal details of each sticker are rendered in absolutely uniform-weight, smooth, rounded pure black monoline strokes. The interior fill color of all stickers is a pure Off-White, and each sticker is surrounded by a thick, well-defined pure white die-cut border that clearly separates it from the dark background. The 10 specific sticker contents are as follows: 1. A half-body portrait of a short-haired girl wearing round vintage sunglasses, casually sipping an iced coffee through a straw with a laid-back demeanor. 2. An iconic lidded takeaway hot coffee paper cup with the brand name 'AURA' written in uppercase English at the center of the cup body. 3. An espresso machine composed of minimalist lines, with the brew head, portafilter handle, and steam wand clearly visible. 4. A top-down overhead view of a latte with saucer, featuring delicate heart-shaped latte art lines on the coffee surface. 5. A vintage hand-crank coffee bean grinder with a crank handle. 6. A plump-contoured croissant with several smooth curved lines on its surface to convey the flaky pastry texture. 7. A cute anthropomorphic coffee bean character with slender arms and legs, wearing a playful smile on its face and raising one hand to wave hello. 8. A text-only sticker designed in chunky bubble letter style, reading 'BREW' in uppercase English. 9. A text sticker with a wavy ribbon-shaped outer frame, with 'AURA COFFEE' written in uppercase English at the center of the ribbon. 10. A motif composed of three coffee beans stacked together, accented with two simple four-pointed star sparkle symbols around them. The overall visual is premium, clean, and full of trendy appeal.",
    "prompt_zh": "[BRAND NAME]。作为一名矢量插画师，设计一套时尚高端的\"贴纸合集\"。\n任务：\n将[BRAND NAME]的品牌形象解构为一组有趣且风格统一的贴纸设计，约8-10个独特贴纸排列在一张纸上。\n内容生成：不要只做logo。自主创作以下混合内容：\n吉祥物/角色：佩戴品牌相关配饰或表达情绪的风格化人物半身像。\n核心产品：与品牌相关的标志性物品。\n符号/物件：与品牌生活方式相关的抽象形状或工具。\n\n视觉风格（单线矢量）：\n该艺术风格"
}, {
