    "revised_prompt": "一张高精度、电影级画质的特写人物肖像照片。画面中心是一位拥有金色长卷发的女性，面貌精致。她正处于真实且充满喜悦的大笑之中，头部微微向后仰起，双眼紧闭，表情生动自然且富有极强的感染力。人物的皮肤展现出极为逼真的纹理细节，毛孔与细微的表情纹路清晰可辨。她身穿一件挺括的纯白色系扣正装衬衫，在衬衫的衣领处夹着一个小巧的黑色领夹式麦克风，麦克风的材质和衬衫布料的细腻纹理被精准刻画。背景是一面极简、光滑的浅灰色摄影棚墙壁，没有任何多余杂物，将视觉焦点完全集中在主体人物身上。整体采用柔和且专业的室内摄影棚布光，光影过渡细腻柔和，完美凸显了人物的面部轮廓与服饰质感。画面构图为纵向特写，重点展示人物的头部至胸部上方，氛围轻松愉悦，呈现出极高的写实度与艺术感。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/gallery_64_3.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "A high-precision, cinematic-quality close-up portrait photograph. At the center of the frame is a woman with long, golden curly hair and refined features. She is in the midst of a genuine, joyful burst of laughter, her head tilted slightly backward, eyes tightly shut, her expression vivid, natural, and highly infectious. The skin of the subject exhibits extremely lifelike textural detail, with pores and subtle expression lines clearly discernible. She is wearing a crisp, pure white button-up formal dress shirt, and clipped at the collar of the shirt is a small black clip-on lavalier microphone, the material of the microphone and the fine texture of the shirt fabric rendered with precision. The background is a minimalist, smooth light gray studio wall with no extraneous objects, directing the visual focus entirely onto the subject. The overall lighting employs soft, professional indoor studio illumination, with delicate and smooth light-to-shadow transitions that perfectly accentuate the subject's facial contours and clothing textures. The composition is a vertical close-up, focusing on the area from the head to just above the chest, conveying a relaxed and cheerful atmosphere with an exceptionally high degree of realism and artistic quality.",
    "prompt_zh": "{\n  \"action\": \"image_generation\",\n  \"action_input\": {\n    \"prompt\": \"一张高细节8K特写肖像，与之前图片中相同面部特征和金色长卷发的同一位女性。她被捕捉到发自内心开怀大笑的瞬间，头部微微后仰，双眼闭合。她穿着一件挺括的白色纽扣社交衬衫，领口处别着一个小型黑色领夹式麦克风。背景是极简、平滑的浅灰色摄影棚墙壁。灯光柔和且专业，突出面料的纹理质感和她表情的自然细节。电影感"
}, {
