    "revised_prompt": "一张休闲街头风格的摄影肖像照，采用竖屏中近景构图，视角与人物眼睛齐平，聚焦于人物的脸部与上半身。画面主体是一位年轻女性，她留着齐肩的铂金白金色头发，发丝呈现柔和的波浪卷理，中分并自然垂落。她的皮肤白皙，在阳光下泛着健康的光泽；眉毛为自然的棕色，形状柔和；双眼是浅绿灰色的，正带着柔和友好的目光直视镜头。她化着极简的自然裸妆，嘴唇呈现柔和的淡粉色，带着轻松自然的微笑。\n\n她身穿一件修身的浅黄绿色罗纹吊带背心，胸前带有小巧的蓝绿色三角龙图案。她的左耳佩戴着一只白色的无线耳机，脖子上戴着一条纤细的金色金属颈圈项链，双肩上可见黑色的双肩背包背带。\n\n人物站在一座具有欧洲城市风格的建筑室外。背景中有一扇蓝灰色的金属门，门上有一个标牌，清晰地印有德文 'Notausgang freihalten'。画面左侧露出了一部分被粉刷成橙色的墙面。画面光线为傍晚黄金时刻的自然光，温暖的侧面定向光照在人物身上，并在后方的墙壁上投射出柔和的阴影。整体色调温暖，呈现出日常、放松且平易近人的城市生活氛围。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/gallery_65_2.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "A casual street-style photographic portrait shot in vertical medium close-up composition, with the viewpoint at eye level with the subject, focusing on the face and upper body. The main subject is a young woman with shoulder-length platinum blonde hair, the strands exhibiting soft wavy curls, parted in the middle and falling naturally. Her skin is fair, glowing with a healthy sheen under the sunlight; her eyebrows are a natural brown with a soft shape; her eyes are light green-gray, gazing directly into the camera with a soft, friendly look. She wears minimal natural no-makeup makeup, her lips a soft light pink, with a relaxed, natural smile.\n\nShe is wearing a fitted light yellow-green ribbed tank top with a small teal triceratops graphic on the chest. On her left ear, she wears a white wireless earbud, around her neck is a delicate gold metal choker necklace, and black backpack straps are visible on both shoulders.\n\nThe subject is standing outside a building with a European urban architectural style. In the background is a blue-gray metal door with a sign clearly printed with the German text 'Notausgang freihalten'. On the left side of the frame, a portion of a wall painted orange is partially visible. The lighting is natural light during the golden hour of early evening, with warm directional sidelight illuminating the subject and casting soft shadows on the wall behind her. The overall color tone is warm, conveying an everyday, relaxed, and approachable urban life atmosphere.",
    "prompt_zh": "nano banana pro 🍌\n\n{\n  \"prompt\": \"休闲街头风格肖像，年轻女性，铂金白金色齐肩波浪卷发，面带温柔微笑看向镜头，浅绿灰色眼睛，自然淡妆配柔粉色唇妆，耳朵里戴着白色无线耳机，佩戴细金属choker项链，穿着淡黄绿色罗纹背心上面有一个小型蓝色三角龙恐龙刺绣图案，黑色双肩包背带在肩膀上可见，站在建筑物外面，蓝灰色金属门上有德文标识写着Notausgang freihalten，左侧可见橙色墙面部分，温暖的黄金时段阳光"
}, {
