    "revised_prompt": "一张纵向排版的摄影三联画，采用35mm胶片摄影质感。画面被垂直划分为上下堆叠的三个等大面板，每块区域展示同一名年轻女性在户外阳光下的不同姿态。女性有着深色、略显凌乱的微卷发，几缕发丝被微风自然吹起，她穿着一件简约的白色吊带背心。三幅画面的背景均为晴朗、明亮、无云的湛蓝天空。上层画面采用低角度仰拍，女性低头静静注视着镜头，眼神直接且带着一丝沉思，明亮的下午阳光从侧面照亮她的半边脸庞和肩膀，形成柔和自然的阴影。中层画面采用平视微带仰角的视角，人物略偏离画面中心以强调广阔的天空，她将头转向画面右侧，目光眺望远方，神态显得深思而抽离，画面左下角边缘隐约可见一小块棕色柱状的屋顶结构。下层画面为极近的面部侧颜特写镜头，女性轻轻闭着双眼，头部微微向后仰起，表情极其平静而恬淡，明媚的阳光精准地勾勒出她优美的面部起伏和颈部轮廓线。整体影像采用大光圈拍摄，人物面部焦点锐利，呈现浅景深效果。色调上，温暖真实的自然肤色与鲜艳明亮的蓝天形成对比，画面具有明显的胶片颗粒感、怀旧气息和高级杂志编辑人像风格。光线为纯粹的自然散射日光，没有人工布光和数码美颜修饰痕迹，保留了皮肤真实的纹理与微小瑕疵，整体氛围宁静、空灵、清新且极具呼吸感。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/gallery_66_1.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "A vertically oriented photographic triptych with a 35mm film photography aesthetic. The frame is divided vertically into three equally sized panels stacked top to bottom, each depicting different poses of the same young woman outdoors in sunlight. The woman has dark, slightly tousled wavy hair with a few strands naturally lifted by a gentle breeze, and she wears a simple white camisole top. The background across all three panels is a clear, bright, cloudless azure sky. The upper panel employs a low-angle upward shot; the woman looks down quietly at the camera with a direct yet slightly contemplative gaze, bright afternoon sunlight illuminating one side of her face and shoulder from the side, creating soft, natural shadows. The middle panel uses an eye-level perspective with a slight upward tilt; the subject is positioned slightly off-center to emphasize the expansive sky, her head turned toward the right side of the frame, gazing into the distance with a pensive and detached expression; a small brownish columnar rooftop structure is faintly visible at the lower-left edge of the frame. The lower panel is an extreme close-up side-profile shot of her face; the woman has her eyes gently closed, her head tilted slightly back, her expression supremely calm and serene, the bright sunlight precisely delineating the elegant contours of her facial features and the line of her neck. The overall imagery is shot with a wide aperture, with sharp focus on the subject's face and a shallow depth of field. In terms of color palette, warm and authentic natural skin tones contrast with the vivid, bright blue sky. The images exhibit pronounced film grain, a nostalgic atmosphere, and the style of high-end editorial magazine portraiture. The lighting is purely natural diffused sunlight with no artificial lighting or digital skin-retouching, preserving the skin's genuine texture and minor imperfections. The overall mood is tranquil, ethereal, fresh, and imbued with a remarkable sense of airiness.",
