    "revised_prompt": "一张特写视角的横向抓拍自拍照片，采用低角度仰拍，从现代汽车内部向上拍摄，呈现出复古时尚与俏皮活力的“it-girl”氛围。画面左侧是一位年轻的棕发女性，留着长波浪卷发。她戴着一副带有暗色镜片的复古黑色长方形墨镜，头上包着一条丝绸头巾并在下巴处打结。头巾上印有粉色、紫色和柔和绿色的水彩花卉图案。她的表情俏皮，正嘟起嘴唇做出亲吻的姿态。画面右侧是一位年轻的金发女性，她充满活力，嘴巴张大做出大喊或尖叫的夸张姿势，舌头可见，视线微微向上。她戴着复古的金边猫眼暗色墨镜，脖子上佩戴着一条经典的多层珍珠项链。她的头上同样包着一条在下巴处打结的鲜艳丝绸头巾，上面印有亮蓝色、黄色和黄绿色的几何花卉图案。两人的头部亲密地倾斜靠在一起，占据画面视觉中心。背景是汽车内部的车顶，正上方有一个玻璃天窗，天窗玻璃上散布着晶莹清晰的雨滴。透过云层和车窗透进来的光线是雨天特有的柔和漫反射阴天自然光，在人物细腻逼真的皮肤和嘴唇上形成自然的高光，墨镜镜片上反射出微妙的环境倒影。画面具有智能手机广角镜头拍摄的质感，面部焦点极其锐利，带有轻微的动态模糊以增强抓拍的生动感。整体画面具有电影级色彩分级，织物纹理和皮肤细节超写实且极其清晰，呈现出极高的保真度。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/gallery_73_4.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "A close-up, landscape-oriented candid selfie photograph taken from a low upward angle, shot from inside a modern car looking up, exuding a retro-chic and playfully vibrant \"it-girl\" vibe. On the left side of the frame is a young brunette woman with long wavy curls. She wears a pair of vintage black rectangular sunglasses with dark lenses, and her head is wrapped in a silk headscarf tied in a knot beneath her chin. The scarf features a watercolor floral pattern in pink, purple, and soft green tones. Her expression is playful, with her lips pursed in a kissing pose. On the right side of the frame is a young blonde woman, full of energy, her mouth wide open in an exaggerated shouting or screaming gesture with her tongue visible, her gaze directed slightly upward. She wears retro gold-rimmed cat-eye dark sunglasses and a classic multi-strand pearl necklace around her neck. Her head is likewise wrapped in a vibrant silk headscarf tied beneath the chin, printed with a geometric floral pattern in bright blue, yellow, and chartreuse. The two women's heads are intimately tilted together, occupying the visual center of the frame. The background is the car's interior ceiling, with a glass sunroof directly above, its surface scattered with crystal-clear, well-defined raindrops. The light filtering through the clouds and car windows is the soft, diffused, overcast natural light characteristic of a rainy day, creating natural highlights on the subjects' finely detailed, lifelike skin and lips, while the sunglass lenses reflect subtle ambient reflections. The image has the quality of a smartphone wide-angle lens capture, with extremely sharp facial focus and slight motion blur to enhance the spontaneous, candid feel. The overall image features cinematic-grade color grading, with fabric textures and skin details rendered in hyperrealistic and exceptionally crisp clarity, exhibiting an extremely high degree of fidelity.",
