    "revised_prompt": "宏观微缩食物摄影照片（Macro Photography）、“食物风景”（Foodscape）。画面呈现超现实主义的美食微缩景观风格，采用横向宽幅构图与移轴摄影（Tilt-Shift）技术。画面中心区域的城市核心区对焦清晰锐利，四周及背景逐渐呈现柔和的虚化散景，背景外围隐约可见一张质朴的深色木质餐桌纹理，凸显出1:87比例的微缩景深感。整个场景构建在一个巨大的黑色陶瓷拉面碗内部，光滑的碗壁边缘构成了这个“微缩世界”的物理地平线和防波堤。水域层：碗内浓郁的棕黄色豚骨拉面汤化作城市的宽阔海港与交错水道，汤面上漂浮的圆形油花反射着晶莹的高光。陆地层：大量金黄色的粗拉面条相互交织重叠，构成了城市中蜿蜒起伏的高架桥和盘根错节的高速公路网络。几块带有炙烤焦边的巨大圆形叉烧肉平铺在汤面上，形成了宽广平坦的城市广场和坚实的人造岛屿。植被点缀：切碎的鲜绿色葱花密集地散布在叉烧肉广场的边缘、面条公路的缝隙间，充当了微缩城市里的草坪、公园绿地和行道树。建筑构造：密集的东京风格微缩建筑物直接从面条和叉烧肉的基底上拔地而起，仿佛是与底层食物一起烹饪成型。高耸的摩天大楼由整齐堆叠的方形炸豆腐块和竖直排列的金黄炸薯条搭建而成，表面带有逼真的油炸酥脆纹理与气孔；两片带有亮粉色螺旋花纹的鸣门卷（鱼板）被垂直插立在面条地基中，化作圆柱形的现代地标观光塔；在城市群后方，一片巨大的方形深绿色海苔片如同巨型城市挡风墙或广告牌般竖立，表面用白色的浓稠沙拉酱挤出了醒目清晰的英文字母 'TOKYO'。微缩叙事细节：在拉面汤港口中，几艘微型塑料质感的货轮和渡轮模型正漂浮在汤汁上航行，船体周围泛起微小的油花涟漪；拉面条高架桥上错落排列着微小的汽车模型；在叉烧肉岛屿表面，散布着1:87比例的微缩人类模型，部分行人在葱花绿地旁行走穿梭，部分微缩人物则围坐在由散落的金黄色玉米粒充当的小圆桌旁进行露天用餐。暖色调的食物造型打光（Food Styling Light）从侧面上方照入，完美勾勒出面条的湿润反光、炸豆腐楼房的粗糙纹理以及汤底的浓郁色泽。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/gallery_74_2.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "A macro photography \"foodscape\" image. The scene presents a surrealist miniature culinary landscape, composed in a horizontal wide-format with tilt-shift photography technique. The central urban core area is in sharp, crisp focus, while the surrounding areas and background gradually dissolve into soft bokeh; the outer background faintly reveals the texture of a rustic dark wooden dining table, accentuating a 1:87 scale miniature depth-of-field effect. The entire scene is constructed inside a large black ceramic ramen bowl, whose smooth rim forms the physical horizon and breakwater of this \"miniature world.\" Water layer: the rich, brownish-yellow tonkotsu ramen broth within the bowl transforms into the city's broad harbor and intersecting waterways, with circular oil droplets floating on the broth surface reflecting glistening highlights. Land layer: abundant golden thick ramen noodles interweave and overlap to form winding elevated highways and an intricate expressway network throughout the city. Several large round chashu pork slices with seared, caramelized edges lie flat on the broth surface, forming expansive, flat city plazas and solid artificial islands. Vegetation accents: finely chopped, vivid green scallion pieces are densely scattered along the edges of the chashu plazas and in the gaps of the noodle highways, serving as lawns, park greenery, and roadside trees in the miniature city. Architectural structures: dense Tokyo-style miniature buildings rise directly from the noodle and chashu base, as if cooked and formed together with the underlying food. Towering skyscrapers are constructed from neatly stacked cubes of fried tofu and vertically arranged golden French fries, their surfaces bearing realistic deep-fried crispy textures and air pockets; two narutomaki (fish cake) slices with bright pink spiral patterns are inserted vertically into the noodle foundation, transformed into cylindrical modern landmark observation towers; behind the urban cluster, a large square sheet of deep green nori seaweed stands upright like a giant city windbreak or billboard, with the bold, clearly legible English letters 'TOKYO' piped onto its surface in thick white mayonnaise. Miniature narrative details: in the ramen broth harbor, several miniature plastic-textured cargo ships and ferry models float and navigate on the broth, with tiny oil-slick ripples emanating around their hulls; small model cars are arrayed along the ramen noodle overpasses; on the chashu island surfaces, 1:87 scale miniature human figurines are scattered about—some pedestrians walk and weave past the scallion greenery, while other miniature figures sit gathered around small round tables fashioned from scattered golden corn kernels, dining al fresco. Warm-toned food styling lighting (fo—",
    "prompt_zh": "<instruction>\n\n输入A是一道具体菜品\n输入B是一座城市或一处风景\n将食材映射为地理特征：如果未提供输入A，则选择该城市或风景中具有代表性的食材\n液体（水域）：识别酱汁、高汤或糖浆。\n（例如，披萨酱 -> 运河。拉面汤 -> 港口。糖浆 -> 河流）。\n固体（陆地）：识别主要的碳水化合物或蛋白质。\n（例如，融化的奶酪 -> 路面/沙地。面条 -> 蜿蜒的道路。煎饼叠层 -> 山地高原）。\n装饰（植被）：识别香草或蔬菜。\n（例如，罗勒/西兰花 -> 树木。"
