    "title": "手绘等距城市街道示意图",
    "title_en": "Hand-Drawn Isometric City Street Diagram",
    "prompt": "绘制这条街道的手绘等距示意图",
    "prompt_en": "Draw a hand-drawn isometric illustration of this street.",
    "source": "https://x.com/AmirMushich/status/1992704354990907793?s=20",
    "type": "t2i",
    "author": "@AmirMushich",
    "author_link": "https://x.com/AmirMushich/status/1992704354990907793?s=20",
    "revised_prompt": "一张宽幅的手绘等距示意图插画。画面采用标准的等距视角（无透视消失点的45度斜上俯视），一条繁华的街道从画面的左下角沿对角线延伸至右上角。街道两侧排列着高低错落的建筑。街道左侧最前方是一家咖啡馆，一层外墙为浅米色，伸出红白相间的条纹遮阳篷，门头招牌上清晰地写着黑体英文字母 'CAFE'；咖啡馆外的露天区域摆放着两张木质圆桌和四把靠背椅。咖啡馆紧挨着一家外墙为青灰色的两层书店，木质招牌上写着 'BOOKS'。书店二层是带有黑色铁艺栏杆的公寓阳台，阳台上摆放着三盆绿植。街道右侧是一栋红砖外墙的三层住宅楼，底层是一家花店，墨绿色的雨棚下摆满了色彩斑斓的花卉盆栽，上方招牌写着 'FLOWER SHOP'。\n\n街道中央是灰色的柏油马路，画有白色的虚线中线和横穿路口的斑马线。路面上有丰富的交通细节：一辆黄色的老式出租车正驶过斑马线，一辆蓝色的厢式送货小货车停靠在书店门前的路边，花店旁的人行道上停着一辆红色的自行车。街道两旁的人行道铺设着橙黄色的方形地砖，沿途错落有致地种植着三棵修剪成圆球形的翠绿行道树，并设有四盏黑色的复古路灯、一个红色的消防栓和一个绿色的邮筒。几个人物以微缩模型的比例分布在场景中：两名路人正在斑马线上并肩行走，一名顾客坐在咖啡馆外喝咖啡，还有一人在右侧人行道上牵着一条白色的狗。\n\n画面风格带有强烈的手绘感，所有物体和建筑轮廓均由带有轻微抖动感和粗细变化的深棕色墨水线条勾勒。上色呈现出通透的水彩质感，色彩明快、饱和度适中，整体色调温暖。为了突出示意图的特性，画面空间中悬浮着带有细线指示箭头和手写体风格的中文标注文字：一条箭头指向左侧建筑群，旁边的文字为 '商业街'；一条箭头指向右侧红砖楼，文字为 '住宅区'；一条箭头指向树木，文字为 '公共绿化'；两条箭头分别指向马路的不同区域，文字分别为 '非机动车道' 和 '步行街'。背景四周留白，整体带有淡米色的水彩纸纹理效果。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/gallery_78_1.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "A wide-format hand-drawn isometric schematic illustration. The scene adopts a standard isometric perspective (a 45-degree oblique top-down view with no perspective vanishing points), with a bustling street extending diagonally from the lower left corner to the upper right corner of the image. Buildings of varying heights line both sides of the street. At the foremost position on the left side of the street is a café with a light beige first-floor exterior wall, a red-and-white striped awning extending outward, and a storefront sign clearly displaying the bold English letters 'CAFE'; in the outdoor seating area outside the café, two wooden round tables and four chairs with backrests are arranged. Adjacent to the café is a two-story bookstore with a blue-gray exterior wall, bearing a wooden sign that reads 'BOOKS'. The second floor of the bookstore features an apartment balcony with black wrought-iron railings, on which three potted green plants are placed. On the right side of the street stands a three-story residential building with a red brick exterior; the ground floor is a flower shop, beneath a dark green awning filled with colorful potted flowers, with a sign above reading 'FLOWER SHOP'.\n\nThe center of the street is a gray asphalt road, marked with white dashed center lines and a zebra crossing at the intersection. The road surface features rich traffic details: a yellow vintage taxi is driving across the zebra crossing, a blue box-type delivery van is parked at the curb in front of the bookstore, and a red bicycle is parked on the sidewalk next to the flower shop. The sidewalks on both sides of the street are paved with orange-yellow square tiles, along which three globe-trimmed verdant street trees are planted at staggered intervals, accompanied by four black vintage street lamps, a red fire hydrant, and a green mailbox. Several figures are distributed throughout the scene at miniature model scale: two pedestrians are walking side by side on the zebra crossing, a customer is sitting outside the café drinking coffee, and another person is walking a white dog on the right-side sidewalk.\n\nThe style of the image carries a strong hand-drawn feel, with all objects and building outlines delineated by dark brown ink lines that exhibit slight wobble and variations in thickness. The coloring presents a translucent watercolor texture, with bright and moderately saturated colors and an overall warm tone. To emphasize the schematic nature, Chinese annotation texts in a handwritten style with fine-line indicator arrows float in the space of the image: one arrow points to the building cluster on the left, with the text '商业街' (Commercial Street) beside it; one arrow points to the red brick building on the right, with the text '住宅区' (Residential Area); one arrow points to the trees, with the text '公共绿化' (Public Greenery); and two arrows point to different areas of the road, with the texts '非机动车道' (Non-motorized Vehicle Lane) and '步行街' (Pedestrian Street) respectively. The surrounding background is left white, with an overall light beige watercolor paper texture effect.",
    "prompt_zh": "绘制这条街道的手绘等距示意图"
