    "revised_prompt": "一张二次元角色设计与上色展示图，采用横向宽屏构图。画面被划分为两部分，左侧偏中占据大部分空间，展示一位已完成精细上色的二次元少女半身像；右侧边缘整齐排列着一组垂直的色卡调色板，展示了人物上色所使用的准确色彩。\n\n左侧的少女留着齐肩的枫叶红色短发，发丝带有细腻的高光，眼瞳为明亮的琥珀色，正微笑着注视前方。她穿着一件质感柔软的米白色宽松针织开衫，内搭深棕色长袖衬衫，领口规整地系着一个金黄色的蝴蝶结领结。她的肤色白皙，脸颊透着淡淡的红晕。人物的上色风格为高品质的赛璐璐平涂，边缘线清晰流畅，明暗交界线干净利落，色彩饱和且光影立体感强。\n\n画面右侧有一列由五个正方形色块组成的调色板，色块自上而下分别对应人物身上的主色调：枫叶红（头发）、米白色（外套）、深棕色（衬衫）、金黄色（领结）和肉粉色（肤色）。每个色块正下方带有清晰的黑色无衬线字体，标识着颜色的十六进制代码，依次为：'#C84B31'、'#F6E6CB'、'#3D2C23'、'#F6C90E'、'#FFDDCB'。在色卡的最上方，有一行清晰的黑色粗体英文标题，写着 'COLOR PALETTE'。\n\n背景为纯净的浅灰白色（接近纯白），没有任何多余的场景元素或渐变，以最大程度突出人物本身和色彩搭配的准确性与对应关系。整体画面呈现出专业原画角色设定图的风格，排版整洁，色调温暖、统一且极具视觉舒适度。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/gallery_86_2.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "A 2D anime-style character design and coloring presentation sheet in a horizontal widescreen composition. The image is divided into two sections: the left-center portion occupies the majority of the space, showcasing a finely colored upper-body portrait of an anime girl; the right edge features a neatly arranged vertical color swatch palette displaying the exact colors used in the character's coloring.\n\nThe girl on the left has shoulder-length maple-red short hair with delicate highlights in the strands, bright amber-colored irises, and is smiling while gazing forward. She wears a soft-textured off-white loose knit cardigan over a dark brown long-sleeved shirt, with a golden bow tie neatly fastened at the collar. Her complexion is fair, with a faint rosy blush on her cheeks. The coloring style of the character is high-quality cel-shading flat coloring, with clean and smooth outlines, crisp shadow boundaries, saturated colors, and a strong sense of three-dimensional light and shadow.\n\nOn the right side of the image is a column of five square color swatches forming a palette, corresponding from top to bottom to the main color tones on the character: maple red (hair), off-white (cardigan), dark brown (shirt), golden yellow (bow tie), and flesh pink (skin tone). Directly below each color swatch is clear black sans-serif text indicating the hexadecimal color code, in order: '#C84B31', '#F6E6CB', '#3D2C23', '#F6C90E', '#FFDDCB'. At the very top of the color palette, there is a line of clear black bold English title text reading 'COLOR PALETTE'.\n\nThe background is a pure light grayish-white (close to pure white), with no extraneous scene elements or gradients, to maximally highlight the character herself and the accuracy and correspondence of the color scheme. The overall image presents the style of a professional concept art character design sheet, with a clean layout and warm, unified tones that are highly visually comfortable.",
