    "prompt": "以九宫格的方式生成这个人不同发型的头像",
    "prompt_en": "Generate avatars of this person with different hairstyles in a 3x3 grid layout.",
    "source": "https://x.com/balconychy/status/1960665038504779923",
    "type": "t2i",
