    "author_link": "https://x.com/balconychy/status/1960665038504779923",
    "revised_prompt": "垂直构图的2D数字插画排版图，背景为纯净的浅灰白色。画面顶部居中位置印有黑色的粗体大写英文标题 'HAIRSTYLE VARIATIONS'，其下方紧挨着一行较小的副标题 'Character Design Reference'。画面的核心主体是一个3x3的九宫格布局，展示了九张同一位年轻亚洲女性的半身头像。为了契合垂直的画幅，每张头像采用了偏修长的竖版矩形比例，且行与行之间留有宽裕的垂直间距。女性的面部特征在所有头像中保持高度一致：拥有白皙的皮肤、杏仁状的棕色大眼睛、清晰的双眼皮、秀挺的鼻子和柔和的浅粉色嘴唇，统一穿着简约的白色V领T恤，以凸显发型的变化。第一排左侧的头像为黑色顺滑的黑直长发，披散在肩头，底部标有黑色的文字 'Long Straight Hair'；第一排中间是黑色齐刘海波波头，发尾刚好与下巴平齐，底部标有文字 'Classic Bob'；第一排右侧是将棕色长发高高扎起的充满活力的高马尾，脸颊两侧有碎发修饰，底部标有文字 'High Ponytail'。第二排左侧为金色的侧分大波浪卷发，发丝富有体积感，底部标有文字 'Wavy Curls'；第二排中间是浅棕色头发扎成的低双马尾，用细黑丝带绑着，底部标有文字 'Twin Tails'；第二排右侧是栗色头发盘在头顶的随性丸子头，略带凌乱感，底部标有文字 'Messy Bun'。第三排左侧是极其干练的深色超短精灵头（Pixie Cut），露出完整的耳朵和纤细的脖颈，底部标有文字 'Pixie Cut'；第三排中间是蜜棕色的法式侧边麻花辫，顺着一侧肩膀垂下，底部标有文字 'French Braid'；第三排右侧是长度及锁骨的深棕色中长发，搭配优雅的八字刘海，底部标有文字 'Collarbone Hair'。整体画面采用柔和均匀的棚拍光效，画风为精致的半写实二次元风格，发丝的光泽感和纹理细节极其清晰，构图规整，极具设计感与参考价值。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/gallery_88_3.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "A vertically composed 2D digital illustration layout with a pure light grayish-white background. At the top center of the image, a black bold uppercase English title 'HAIRSTYLE VARIATIONS' is printed, immediately followed below by a smaller subtitle line reading 'Character Design Reference'. The core subject of the image is a 3×3 grid layout showcasing nine upper-body headshots of the same young Asian female. To suit the vertical format, each headshot adopts a slightly elongated vertical rectangular proportion, with generous vertical spacing between rows. The female's facial features remain highly consistent across all headshots: fair skin, almond-shaped large brown eyes, distinct double eyelids, a refined nose, and soft light pink lips, uniformly wearing a simple white V-neck T-shirt to emphasize the hairstyle variations. The first row, left headshot features smooth black long straight hair draped over the shoulders, labeled at the bottom with black text 'Long Straight Hair'; the first row, center features a black blunt-bangs bob cut with hair ends exactly level with the chin, labeled 'Classic Bob'; the first row, right features brown long hair pulled up into an energetic high ponytail with loose strands framing the cheeks, labeled 'High Ponytail'. The second row, left features golden side-parted voluminous wavy curls, labeled 'Wavy Curls'; the second row, center features light brown hair tied into low twin tails secured with thin black ribbons, labeled 'Twin Tails'; the second row, right features chestnut hair gathered into a casual messy bun atop the head with a slightly tousled look, labeled 'Messy Bun'. The third row, left features an extremely sleek dark ultra-short pixie cut, revealing the full ears and slender neck, labeled 'Pixie Cut'; the third row, center features a honey-brown French side braid draped down over one shoulder, labeled 'French Braid'; the third row, right features collarbone-length dark brown medium-length hair paired with elegant curtain bangs, labeled 'Collarbone Hair'. The overall image employs soft, even studio lighting, rendered in a refined semi-realistic anime style, with exceptionally clear hair gloss and texture details, a neat composition, and a highly",
