    "revised_prompt": "一张仿宋代张择端《清明上河图》风格的宽屏横幅风俗画插画。画面采用散点透视和横向展开的全景构图，展现了繁华的古代水陆市井风貌。整体色调呈现出古旧的泛黄绢本茶褐色，采用中国画的工笔界画技法，线条（铁线描）细腻勾勒，辅以赭石、花青、汁绿等传统淡彩，光线均匀柔和。画面中央偏右是一条横贯的宽阔河流（汴河），水波以极细密的波纹线刻画。河面上有多艘体量庞大的木制客船与漕船，船只吃水很深，甲板上的船夫们有的正在用力撑篙，有的在摇橹，还有的在调整风帆。河流上方横跨着一座气势宏伟的木制拱桥（虹桥），桥梁的榫卯结构清晰可见。桥面上人头攒动，交通极为繁忙：有推着满载货物的独轮车的商贩，有骑着高头大马前呼后拥的官员，有挑着扁担步履蹒跚的苦力，还有趴在桥栏杆上俯瞰河面船只的文人食客。桥梁两端连接着宽阔的土路街道，街道两旁错落有致地排列着密集的宋代风格木结构建筑，屋顶覆盖着青灰色的瓦片，飞檐翘角，门窗雕花精细。街道上店铺林立，业态丰富。左侧有一座气派的两层酒楼，门前搭建着繁复的彩楼欢门，二楼敞开的窗户内可见围坐饮茶喝酒的客人们，酒楼外高挑出一面青边白底的酒旗，上面写着黑色的繁体汉字'孫羊正店'。酒楼旁是一排低矮的商铺，其中一家当铺门前的木制立牌上写着一个显眼的'解'字；另一侧的茶馆外挂着一块写有'新茶'的木板。街市上熙熙攘攘，充满市井百态：有穿着长衫的士人驻足交谈，有穿着粗布短褐的小贩沿街叫卖，有戴着帷帽的妇女带着孩童逛街，还有一支由五六头毛驴组成的驼队正驮着木炭缓缓前行，路边甚至还有算命先生的摊位和卖糖葫芦的游商。画面细节极度丰富，每个人物的神态和动作都栩栩如生，生动还原了古代城市经济繁荣的景象。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/gallery_8_3.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "A widescreen horizontal genre painting illustration in the style of the Song dynasty artist Zhang Zeduan's *Along the River During the Qingming Festival* (*Qingmingshanghe Tu*). The composition employs a multi-point (scattered) perspective and a laterally unfolding panoramic layout, depicting a bustling ancient waterfront and overland marketplace. The overall color tone resembles aged, yellowed silk with a tea-brown patina, rendered in the Chinese painting techniques of fine-line *gongbi* and architectural *jiehua* methods. The outlines are meticulously delineated using *tiexianmiao* (iron-wire line drawing), supplemented by traditional light washes of *zheshi* (burnt sienna), *huaqing* (indigo blue), and *zhilü* (sap green), with even, soft lighting throughout. Slightly right of center flows a broad river (the Bian River) running horizontally across the composition, its water surface depicted with extremely fine, dense ripple lines. On the river float several massive wooden passenger boats and grain-tribute barges (*caochuan*), sitting deep in the water. On the decks, boatmen are variously exerting force to punt with long poles, working the sculling oars (*yaofu*), or adjusting sails. Spanning the river above is a grand wooden arch bridge (a rainbow bridge, *hongqiao*), its mortise-and-tenon joinery clearly visible. The bridge surface teems with people, and traffic is extremely busy: vendors pushing single-wheeled carts fully loaded with goods, officials on tall horses surrounded by attendants and escorts, laborers shuffling along under shoulder-pole (*biandan*) loads, and literati and diners leaning over the bridge railings to gaze down at the boats on the river. Both ends of the bridge connect to broad, unpaved earthen roads lined on either side with a dense, staggered arrangement of Song-dynasty-style timber-framed buildings, their roofs covered with blue-gray tiles and adorned with upturned flying eaves (*feiyan qiaojiao*), their doors and windows featuring finely carved ornamentation. Shops line the streets in great abundance and variety of trades. On the left stands an imposing two-story wine house (*jiulou*), its entrance fronted by an elaborate, polychrome decorative gateway (*cailou huanmen*). Through the open second-floor windows, guests can be seen seated together drinking tea and wine. Outside the wine house, a tall pole flies a blue-bordered, white-ground wine banner (*jiuqi*) inscribed in black traditional Chinese characters reading '孫羊正店' (Sun Yang Zheng Dian). Beside the wine house is a row of low shopfronts; a wooden standing sign before one pawnshop bears the prominent character '解' (*jiě*, meaning \"pawn/redeem\"); on the other side, a teahouse has a wooden board hanging outside inscribed with '新茶' (New Tea). The streets bustle with all manner of city life: scholars in long robes stop to converse, peddlers in coarse, short hemp jackets hawk their wares along the road, women in veiled hats (*weimao*) stroll with children, a pack train of five or six donkeys plods along laden with charcoal, and by the roadside there are even fortune-teller stalls and itinerant vendors selling candied hawthorn skewers (*tanghulu*). The painting is extraordinarily rich in detail—every figure's expression and gesture is rendered with lifelike vividness, vividly recreating the scene of a thriving ancient urban economy.",
    "prompt_zh": "请生成一张清明上河图风格的画作。"
