    "title": "安检流程象形图说明",
    "title_en": "Security Check Pictogram Guide",
    "prompt": "将此说明图转换为象形图",
    "prompt_en": "Convert this instructional diagram into a pictogram.",
    "source": "https://x.com/nobisiro_2023/status/1968677481486914022",
    "type": "t2i",
    "author": "@nobisiro_2023",
    "author_link": "https://x.com/nobisiro_2023/status/1968677481486914022",
    "revised_prompt": "一张扁平化、极简主义风格的象形图（Pictogram）说明图。画面采用横向布局，背景为纯白色，没有任何多余的背景装饰。整体设计高度符号化，使用深灰色作为主要图形颜色，并以亮黄色作为提示和强调色。画面完全没有透视效果，所有人物和物体均由纯粹的几何图形（如正圆形头部、等宽粗线条构成的四肢和躯干）组成，人物没有任何面部表情特征。\n\n画面顶部居中位置有两行清晰的黑色粗体文字，上排为中文'安检流程'，下排为稍小的英文'Security Check'。文字下方由四个从左至右水平排列的象形图标组成了完整的操作步骤说明，每个步骤之间有一个向右的黄色实心箭头连接，引导视觉顺序。\n\n最左侧为第一个步骤，画面展示一个深灰色的象形人物站立，伸出右臂将一个带有证件标志的方形小册子递给左侧柜台后的另一名头戴鸭舌帽的象形安检员。该场景下方有两排居中对齐的文字：'1. 证件核验'以及'ID Check'。\n\n向右的第二个步骤，展示了一条水平的传送带和一台内部带有黄色扫描线的方形X光安检机。一个象形人物正微微弯腰，双手将一个带有拉杆和滚轮的矩形行李箱放置在传送带上。下方配有文字：'2. 行李检查'以及'Baggage X-Ray'。\n\n第三个步骤中，画面主体是一个打开的笔记本电脑图标和一个带有液滴标志的圆柱形水瓶图标，这两个物品被一个黄色的虚线方框包裹，方框下方有一个向下的箭头，指向一个长方形的托盘，示意将物品放入盘中。下方配有文字：'3. 取出电子产品及液体'以及'Electronics & Liquids'。\n\n最右侧为第四个步骤，一个象形人物正站在一个倒U形的金属探测门正中央，双臂向身体两侧抬起。探测门右侧站着一名安检员，手持一个短棒状的扫描探测器对准该人物。下方配有文字：'4. 人身检查'以及'Body Scan'。\n\n整体版面布局工整，图标视觉比例协调一致，信息层级分明，严格遵循国际通用的公共信息导向系统图形符号设计规范。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/gallery_99_3.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "A flat, minimalist-style pictogram instructional diagram. The layout is horizontal with a pure white background, devoid of any extraneous background decoration. The overall design is highly symbolic, using dark gray as the primary graphic color with bright yellow as an accent and emphasis color. The image has absolutely no perspective effect; all figures and objects are composed of pure geometric shapes (such as perfectly circular heads and equal-width thick lines forming limbs and torsos), and the figures have no facial expression features whatsoever.\n\nAt the top center of the image are two lines of clear, bold black text: the upper line reads in Chinese '安检流程,' and the lower line reads in slightly smaller English 'Security Check.' Below the text, four pictographic icons are arranged horizontally from left to right to form a complete set of operational step instructions. Each step is connected by a solid yellow rightward-pointing arrow, guiding the visual sequence.\n\nOn the far left is the first step: a dark gray pictographic figure stands upright, extending the right arm to hand a small square booklet bearing an ID document symbol to another pictographic security officer wearing a peaked cap, positioned behind a counter to the left. Beneath this scene are two lines of centered text: '1. 证件核验' and 'ID Check.'\n\nThe second step to the right depicts a horizontal conveyor belt and a square X-ray security scanner with yellow scanning lines inside. A pictographic figure is slightly bending forward, placing a rectangular suitcase with a pull handle and rolling wheels onto the conveyor belt with both hands. Below it reads: '2. 行李检查' and 'Baggage X-Ray.'\n\nIn the third step, the main elements are an open laptop icon and a cylindrical water bottle icon bearing a liquid droplet symbol. These two items are enclosed within a yellow dashed-line box, beneath which a downward arrow points to a rectangular tray, indicating that the items should be placed into the tray. Below it reads: '3. 取出电子产品及液体' and 'Electronics & Liquids.'\n\nOn the far right is the fourth step: a pictographic figure stands in the center of an inverted U-shaped metal detector gate with both arms raised out to the sides of the body. To the right of the detector gate stands a security officer holding a short, baton-shaped handheld scanning wand aimed at the figure. Below it reads: '4. 人身检查' and 'Body Scan.'\n\nThe overall page layout is neat and orderly, the icons are visually proportionate and consistent, the information hierarchy is clearly defined, and the design strictly adheres to internationally standardized public information signage conventions.",
    "prompt_zh": "将此说明图转换为象形图"
}, {
