    "title_en": "Chalkboard-Style Café Hand-Drawn Menu",
    "prompt": "黒板のチョーク画風に変換してください。",
    "prompt_en": "Please convert this into a blackboard chalk drawing style.",
    "source": "https://x.com/TlanoAI/status/1960583251460022626",
    "type": "t2i",
    "author": "@TlanoAI",
    "author_link": "https://x.com/TlanoAI/status/1960583251460022626",
    "revised_prompt": "一幅竖向构图的黑板粉笔插画，呈现复古咖啡厅手绘菜单的风格。背景是一块深绿色的黑板，表面布满了轻微的白色粉笔灰和被黑板擦擦拭过留下的模糊晕染痕迹，极具真实的物理质感。画面中的所有元素均由粉笔特有的颗粒感线条和交叉排线绘制而成，色彩以纯白、浅黄和浅棕色为主。画面顶部居中位置画有一个飘带形状的边框，框内用粗体白色粉笔字写着英文 'CAFE & BAKERY'。飘带下方紧挨着一行较小的日文手写体 '本日のおすすめ'。画面中央是视觉焦点，用白色和浅棕色粉笔细致描绘了一杯放在圆形杯垫上的热拿铁，咖啡杯面上勾勒出心形的拉花图案，杯口上方画有三条卷曲的波浪线代表升腾的热气。咖啡杯的右下方，画着一个牛角面包，利用浅黄色和白色的粉笔线条表现出面团的层叠感与酥脆阴影。咖啡的周围点缀着几颗散落的咖啡豆和简约的四角星图案。画面的下半部分是排版整齐的菜单列表，左侧为项目，右侧为价格，中间由稀疏的粉笔虚线连接。从上到下依次写有：'Hot Coffee' 对应 '¥450'，'Cafe Latte' 对应 '¥500'，'Croissant' 对应 '¥300'，'Pancake' 对应 '¥650'。画面的最底部边缘，用飘逸的连笔英文写着营业时间 'Open 10:00 - Close 20:00'。整体光线均匀，强烈的深底色与明亮的粉笔笔触形成鲜明对比，手绘风格浓郁。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/gallery_9_1.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "A vertically composed blackboard chalk illustration in the style of a vintage café hand-drawn menu. The background is a deep green chalkboard, its surface covered with slight white chalk dust and blurred, hazy smudge marks left by a chalkboard eraser, conveying a highly realistic physical texture. All elements in the image are rendered with the characteristic grainy lines and cross-hatching of chalk, primarily in pure white, pale yellow, and light brown. At the top center of the image is a ribbon-shaped border frame, inside which bold white chalk lettering reads 'CAFE & BAKERY.' Directly beneath the ribbon is a smaller line of handwritten Japanese: '本日のおすすめ' (Today's Recommendations). The visual focal point at the center of the image is a meticulously drawn hot latte in white and light brown chalk, sitting on a circular coaster. A heart-shaped latte art pattern is traced on the surface of the coffee, and above the rim of the cup three curling wavy lines represent rising steam. To the lower right of the coffee cup is a croissant, its layered dough texture and crispy shadows rendered with pale yellow and white chalk strokes. Scattered around the coffee are a few loose coffee beans and simple four-pointed star motifs. The lower half of the image contains a neatly typeset menu list, with items on the left, prices on the right, and sparse chalk dotted lines connecting them in between. From top to bottom, the entries read: 'Hot Coffee' — '¥450,' 'Cafe Latte' — '¥500,' 'Croissant' — '¥300,' 'Pancake' — '¥650.' Along the very bottom edge of the image, the business hours are written in flowing cursive English: 'Open 10:00 - Close 20:00.' The lighting is even throughout, and the strong dark background contrasts sharply with the bright chalk strokes, imbuing the piece with a rich hand-drawn aesthetic.",
