    "title_en": "Hand-Drawn Isometric City Street Illustration",
    "prompt": "Draw a hand-drawn isometric diagram of this street",
    "prompt_en": "Draw a hand-drawn isometric diagram of this street",
    "source": "https://x.com/AmirMushich/status/1992704354990907793?s=20",
    "type": "t2i",
    "author": "@AmirMushich",
    "author_link": "https://x.com/AmirMushich/status/1992704354990907793?s=20",
    "revised_prompt": "手绘风格的等距视角（轴测）城市街道示意图。画面采用宽幅比例横向展开，基于标准的45度平行投影绘制，无透视收缩，呈现出建筑草图般的马克笔与水彩手绘质感。\n\n画面中央是一条呈对角线延伸的城市双向沥青街道。道路中间画有白色虚线，路口设有清晰的白色斑马线。街道左侧是一栋三层高的红砖混合用途建筑。底层是一家咖啡馆，外立面有宽大的玻璃窗和墨绿色的折叠遮阳篷，门上方的木制招牌上用白色字体写着 'Corner Coffee'。咖啡馆外的人行道上摆放着两张带遮阳伞的铁艺圆桌，两名顾客正坐着交谈。建筑的二层和三层是住宅，带有黑色锻铁阳台和几盆悬垂的绿植。\n\n街道右侧是一排两层高的联排商铺。左边是一家面包店，有着淡黄色的墙面，招牌上写着 'Sunny Bakery'，透过橱窗可以看到展示柜里的法棍和糕点；右边是一家书店，深蓝色的招牌上写着 'City Books'。街道上有一辆明黄色的经典造型出租车正在行驶，面包店门口的人行道旁停着一辆带后备货箱的红色送货摩托车。\n\n人行道上分布着丰富的街道家具：复古样式的黑色路灯、等距排列的方形树池及里面繁茂的行道树，以及一个带透明玻璃顶棚的公交车站。公交车站内部有一块海报广告牌，上面写着大字 'New Arrival'。路口转角处立着一根绿色的街道指示牌，标牌上清晰地标有白字 'Maple Street'。\n\n画面中点缀着几个手绘风格的小人：一名穿着红色外套的行人正牵着一只白狗走过斑马线，另一名背着双肩包的行人正走向书店的大门。画面线条清晰肯定，边缘带有自然的铅笔手绘肌理感。光线设定为明确的左上方主光源，在建筑物、车辆和树木右下方投下统一规则的平行斜向阴影，极大地强化了等距视角的立体几何感。整体色调明快、温馨，色彩以低饱和度的水彩晕染平铺为主，街道布局严谨、比例精确且生活细节丰富。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/gallery_101_1.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "A hand-drawn style isometric (axonometric) city street schematic. The image adopts a wide aspect ratio extending horizontally, rendered based on a standard 45-degree parallel projection without perspective foreshortening, presenting an architectural sketch-like marker and watercolor hand-drawn texture.\n\nAt the center of the image is a two-way asphalt city street extending diagonally. White dashed lines are drawn in the middle of the road, and the intersection features clearly marked white zebra crossings. On the left side of the street stands a three-story red brick mixed-use building. The ground floor is a café with large glass windows and dark green folding awnings on the façade; a wooden sign above the door reads 'Corner Coffee' in white lettering. On the sidewalk outside the café, two wrought-iron round tables with parasols are set up, with two customers sitting and conversing. The second and third floors are residential, featuring black wrought-iron balconies and several pots of trailing greenery.\n\nOn the right side of the street is a row of two-story terraced shops. On the left is a bakery with pale yellow walls and a sign reading 'Sunny Bakery'; through the display window, baguettes and pastries can be seen in the showcase. On the right is a bookstore with a dark blue sign reading 'City Books'. On the street, a bright yellow classic-styled taxi is driving, and a red delivery motorcycle with a rear cargo box is parked by the sidewalk in front of the bakery.\n\nThe sidewalks feature abundant street furniture: vintage-style black lampposts, evenly spaced square tree pits with lush street trees inside, and a bus stop with a transparent glass canopy. Inside the bus stop is a poster billboard with the large text 'New Arrival'. At the corner of the intersection stands a green street sign post, with the sign clearly marked in white text reading 'Maple Street'.\n\nThe scene is dotted with several hand-drawn style small figures: a pedestrian wearing a red coat is walking a white dog across the zebra crossing, and another pedestrian carrying a backpack is heading toward the bookstore entrance. The linework is clean and confident, with edges carrying a natural pencil hand-drawn texture. The lighting is set as a definite upper-left key light source, casting uniform, regular parallel diagonal shadows to the lower right of buildings, vehicles, and trees, greatly reinforcing the three-dimensional geometric quality of the isometric perspective. The overall color palette is bright and warm, with colors predominantly rendered in low-saturation watercolor washes applied in flat tones; the street layout is rigorous, proportions are precise, and everyday life details are abundant.",
    "prompt_zh": "绘制这条街道的手绘等距图"
}, {
