    "revised_prompt": "一张手绘风格的等距视角（Isometric）街道示意图，横向构图。画面采用精细的黑色针管笔线条勾勒，呈现出建筑草图般的严谨质感，背景为带有淡淡米黄色的纸张材质，局部带有柔和的低饱和度水彩晕染（如砖红、浅灰、淡绿）以区分不同材质。画面的主体是一条从左下向右上呈对角线延伸的城市商业街区。街道包含双向车道、密集的交叉阴影表示的柏油路面肌理、清晰的斑马线，以及一条绘制了自行车图标的专用车道。作为示意图，街道各处带有细直线引出的手写体英文标注：指向道路中心处的文字为 'Main Street'，指向自行车道处的文字为 'Bike Lane'。街边靠右停泊着一辆复古造型的经典小轿车和一辆带后备箱的送货踏板摩托车。人行道边缘排列着三栋两至三层的连排建筑。最左侧是一个转角咖啡馆，带有复古的条纹遮阳篷、三张配有椅子的户外圆桌，正门上方的木质招牌清晰写有 'CAFÉ LUMA'，建筑旁带有引线标注文字 'Local Coffee Shop'。中间是一栋带有网格玻璃橱窗的两层书店，二楼有外凸的飘窗，店头招牌写着 'BOOKS & CO.'。右侧是一栋带有细致砖墙排线纹理的住宅楼，二楼有一个探出的铸铁阳台，阳台上挂满藤蔓植物。街道基础设施细节丰富，包含两盏复古造型的铸铁路灯、一个美式消防栓、一个顶棚透明的公交站台，以及种植在方形树池中的繁茂行道树，一根引线指向树冠，旁边手写标注 'Oak Tree'。画面中点缀着几个手绘简笔画风格的微缩人物：一人正在斑马线上遛狗，两人坐在咖啡馆外侧交谈，另一人正准备推开书店的门。整体画面没有透视消失点，严格遵循30度角的等距立体投影法则，通过建筑和物体右下侧统一的斜线排线（cross-hatching）来表现立体阴影，结构清晰，信息丰富，具有浓厚的专业建筑手绘插图氛围。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/gallery_101_2_v2.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "A hand-drawn style isometric street schematic in a horizontal composition. The image is delineated with fine black technical pen (needle-point pen) linework, presenting the rigorous quality of an architectural sketch, with a background of paper texture in a faint cream-yellow tone, and selective areas of soft, low-saturation watercolor washes (such as brick red, light gray, pale green) to differentiate materials. The main subject of the image is a commercial city block street extending diagonally from the lower left to the upper right. The street includes two-way lanes, asphalt road surface texture represented by dense cross-hatching, clearly drawn zebra crossings, and a dedicated bike lane marked with a bicycle icon. As a schematic, the street features handwritten English annotations in various places, drawn out with thin leader lines: the text pointing to the center of the road reads 'Main Street', and the text pointing to the bike lane reads 'Bike Lane'. Parked along the right side of the street are a vintage classic compact car and a delivery scooter with a rear cargo box. Three two- to three-story terraced buildings are lined along the sidewalk edge. The leftmost is a corner café with a vintage striped awning, three outdoor round tables with chairs, and a wooden sign above the front door clearly reading 'CAFÉ LUMA', with a leader line annotation beside the building reading 'Local Coffee Shop'. In the middle is a two-story bookstore with gridded glass display windows and a protruding bay window on the second floor, with the storefront sign reading 'BOOKS & CO.'. On the right is a residential building with finely hatched brick wall texture, featuring a projecting cast-iron balcony on the second floor draped with trailing vine plants. The street infrastructure details are rich, including two vintage cast-iron lampposts, an American-style fire hydrant, a bus shelter with a transparent canopy, and lush street trees planted in square tree pits; a leader line points to the tree canopy with handwritten annotation reading 'Oak Tree'. The scene is dotted with several miniature figures in a hand-drawn sketch style: one person is walking a dog on the zebra crossing, two people are sitting outside the café conversing, and another is about to push open the bookstore door. The overall image has no vanishing point, strictly adhering to the 30-degree isometric projection principles, with unified diagonal cross-hatching on the lower-right side of buildings and objects to represent volumetric shadows. The composition is structurally clear, information-rich, and exudes a strong professional architectural hand-drawn illustration atmosphere.",
