    "revised_prompt": "一张定格动画风格的毛毡艺术照片。画面主体是一个由羊毛毡手工制作的拟人化小狐狸，呈现出强烈的触感、柔软的纤维、不均匀的缝线和明显的毛毡纹理。小狐狸位于画面中央偏下，拥有橙色的毛毡身体和白色的脸颊，眼睛是用黑色小珠子缝制的，它穿着一件红色毛毡连帽斗篷，斗篷边缘有故意保留的粗糙白色缝线，手里提着一个用细麻线编织的微型小篮子。\n\n小狐狸置身于一个微型透视景箱中，整体呈现适合竖屏的垂直构图。背景由层层叠叠的柔和色调织物构成，浅蓝色和薄荷绿色的毛毡堆叠成远处的山峦和天空。小狐狸周围环绕着童话般的柔和色彩道具：地面铺着深绿色的粗呢面料，一条由米色粗纱线盘绕而成的小径蜿蜒向前；两旁生长着几株毛毡制作的粉色和浅蓝色蘑菇，伞盖上缝着白色的波点；草丛中点缀着几朵用碎布头和彩色纽扣缝制而成的小花。画面两侧有由棕色卷曲毛毡构成的树干，树冠是层叠的不规则绿色毡片，向画面上方延伸，填满垂直空间。\n\n画面的光线温暖柔和，从侧上方打下，边缘带有微微的暖黄色光晕，完美突显了羊毛纤维的蓬松感、缝线的起伏以及织物的物理厚度。整体景深较浅，背景略微模糊，散发出温馨的童话魅力，宛如一部完全由毛毡、纱线和布料构成的触感极佳的定格动画童话静帧。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/gallery_17_3.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "A stop-motion animation style felt art photograph. The main subject is a handcrafted anthropomorphic little fox made of wool felt, exhibiting a strong tactile quality, soft fibers, uneven stitching, and pronounced felt texture. The little fox is positioned slightly below center in the frame, with an orange felt body and white cheeks; its eyes are made of small black beads sewn on. It wears a red felt hooded cloak with deliberately retained rough white stitching along the edges, and holds in its hand a miniature basket woven from thin jute twine.\n\nThe little fox is set within a miniature diorama box, with an overall vertical composition suited for portrait orientation. The background is composed of layered, softly toned fabrics, with light blue and mint green felt pieces stacked to form distant mountains and sky. Surrounding the little fox are fairy tale-like, softly colored props: the ground is covered with dark green tweed fabric, and a small path made of coiled beige thick yarn winds forward; on either side grow several felt-crafted pink and pale blue mushrooms with white polka dots sewn onto their caps; among the grass are scattered small flowers sewn from fabric scraps and colorful buttons. On both sides of the frame are tree trunks formed from brown curled felt, with canopies of layered, irregularly shaped green felt pieces extending upward, filling the vertical space.\n\nThe lighting is warm and soft, cast from the upper side, with a slight warm yellow halo at the edges, perfectly highlighting the fluffiness of the wool fibers, the undulation of the stitching, and the physical thickness of the fabrics. The overall depth of field is shallow, with the background slightly blurred, exuding a warm fairy tale charm—as if a still frame from a stop-motion animated fairy tale constructed entirely of felt, yarn, and fabric with exquisite tactile quality.",
    "prompt_zh": "一个由羊毛毡制成的[subject]人偶，手工制作，带有柔软的纤维、不均匀的缝线和可见的纹理。置于由层叠织物和柔和色调道具搭建的微缩立体场景中，整个画面散发着温馨的故事书般的魅力，犹如一部完全由毛毡和线制成的触感定格动画童话中的一帧静止画面。"
