    "revised_prompt": "这是一张垂直竖版构图（比例约3:4）的高清超写实食品摄影与编辑级信息图海报。画面整体呈现8K超高清画质，采用中心加权的垂直构图，无任何画面裁剪与缩放。摄影风格带有浅景深效果，食物主体清晰锐利，背景柔和虚化。布光为电影级影棚灯光，柔和的定向主光勾勒出食物极其逼真的质感，边缘伴有微妙的轮廓光，高光部分控制得恰到好处。画面被分为上下两个场景模块，均包含悬浮或掉落的运动定格元素。所有信息图的指示线皆为细长平滑的圆角金线，连接的文字标签由金属金色的优雅衬线字体（用于成分名称）和纯白色的简洁无衬线字体（用于成分描述）组成。\n\n海报的上半部分背景为柔和的粉彩粉色平滑渐变，光线均匀且无生硬阴影。画面中心是一个垂直堆叠的各式蛋糕切片组合，悬浮在一个白色陶瓷圆盘上方。蛋糕主体包含香草海绵蛋糕层、洁白的鲜奶油层、覆盆子奶油层以及顶部的巧克力奶油。在蛋糕周围的空中，动态悬浮着新鲜的覆盆子、蓝莓、草莓、香草与巧克力口味的马卡龙、牛奶巧克力块、薄荷叶、细小的坚果碎粒，以及定格在空中的面包碎屑。该部分附带五组指示线及文字标签：\n第一根金线指向香草蛋糕层，文字为：'Vanilla Cake – soft, fluffy sponge cake layered with white cream filling'\n第二根金线指向悬浮的马卡龙，文字为：'Macaron – creamy filling between almond meringue shells'\n第三根金线指向覆盆子，文字为：'Raspberries – juicy, fresh raspberries'\n第四根金线指向巧克力块，文字为：'Chocolate Bar – chunks of smooth milk chocolate'\n第五根金线指向覆盆子奶油层，文字为：'Raspberry Cream – soft sponge cake layered with creamy, fruity raspberry cream'\n\n海报的下半部分场景切换为温暖质朴的传统厨房环境，柔和的虚化背景中可见温暖的灯笼环境光、木质台面以及黄铜和紫铜材质的厨房用具。该部分的主体是一份垂直放置的传统叙利亚卷甜点。甜点有着卷曲的白色奶酪面团外层，内部溢出浓郁的奶油夹心。一道金色的糖浆正从上方垂直倾倒而下，呈现出完美的流体动态冻结效果。甜点表面和内部撒满了开心果碎，周围的空气中有开心果碎屑和糖浆滴落的运动定格画面。该部分附带三组指示线及文字标签：\n第一根金线指向白色奶酪面团，文字为：'White Cheese Dough – soft outer layer made from cheese and semolina'\n第二根金线指向溢出的奶油，文字为：'Cream Filling – creamy filling inside the roll'\n第三根金线指向开心果碎，文字为：'Pistachios – crushed pistachios sprinkled over and inside the rolls'",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/gallery_61_2.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "This is a high-definition, hyper-realistic food photography and editorial-grade infographic poster in a vertical portrait orientation (approximately 3:4 ratio). The image presents 8K ultra-high-definition quality, employing a center-weighted vertical composition with no cropping or scaling. The photographic style features a shallow depth of field, with the food subject rendered crisp and sharp while the background is softly blurred. Lighting is cinematic studio-grade, with soft directional key light sculpting the extremely lifelike textures of the food, accompanied by subtle rim light along the edges, and highlights controlled to perfection. The image is divided into upper and lower scene modules, both containing suspended or falling freeze-frame motion elements. All infographic leader lines are thin, smooth, rounded gold lines, connecting text labels composed of metallic gold elegant serif typography (for ingredient names) and pure white clean sans-serif typography (for ingredient descriptions).\n\nThe upper half of the poster features a soft pastel pink smooth gradient background, with even lighting and no harsh shadows. At the center of the frame is a vertically stacked assortment of cake slices, levitating above a white ceramic round plate. The cake body comprises vanilla sponge cake layers, pristine white fresh cream layers, raspberry cream layers, and chocolate cream on top. Suspended dynamically in the air around the cake are fresh raspberries, blueberries, strawberries, vanilla and chocolate-flavored macarons, milk chocolate chunks, mint leaves, fine crushed nut fragments, and breadcrumbs frozen in mid-air. This section includes five sets of leader lines and text labels:\nThe first gold line points to the vanilla cake layer, with the text: 'Vanilla Cake – soft, fluffy sponge cake layered with white cream filling'\nThe second gold line points to the floating macarons, with the text: 'Macaron – creamy filling between almond meringue shells'\nThe third gold line points to the raspberries, with the text: 'Raspberries – juicy, fresh raspberries'\nThe fourth gold line points to the chocolate chunks, with the text: 'Chocolate Bar – chunks of smooth milk chocolate'\nThe fifth gold line points to the raspberry cream layer, with the text: 'Raspberry Cream – soft sponge cake",
    "prompt_zh": "{\n  \"global_settings\": {\n    \"resolution\": \"8K超高清分辨率\",\n    \"aspect_ratio\": \"3:4\",\n    \"camera_style\": \"影棚美食摄影，配合电影级灯光\",\n    \"depth_of_field\": \"浅景深，主体清晰，背景柔和\",\n    \"lighting\": \"柔和定向主光，微妙轮廓光，可控高光\",\n    \"style\": \"超写实美食插画，叠加编辑风格的信息图层\",\n    \"composition_rules\": [\n      \"不缩放\",\n      \"不裁剪\",\n      \"居中加权竖向构图\",\n      \"悬浮元素定格于运动瞬间\"\n    ],\n    \"text_design\": {"
