    "author": "@Gdgtify",
    "author_link": "https://x.com/Gdgtify/status/2012280198931070979",
    "revised_prompt": "一张竖幅构图的宏观摄影与食物微缩景观（Foodscape）图像，展现了一个以披萨为载体的微缩威尼斯水城。画面主体是一个占据中心的圆形披萨，其最外围是金黄焦脆、布满烘焙气泡的厚实披萨边，如同高耸的城墙般将整个微缩世界包裹在内。内部空间被巧妙地改造成威尼斯城市地貌：“水域”由浓郁鲜亮的红色番茄酱构成，化作蜿蜒曲折的主运河与交错的水道，表面泛着诱人的油脂光泽；“陆地”与广场由融化的拉丝马苏里拉奶酪铺就，带有微微焦黄的斑点，形成街道和步道；“植被”由新鲜的罗勒叶和点缀的西兰花簇组成，模拟出郁郁葱葱的树木与灌木。在奶酪地基上，拔地而起一座座威尼斯风格的微缩建筑，这些房屋的墙体由带有烘焙纹理的面团构成，与底部无缝融合，屋顶则覆盖着微微卷曲的红色意式香肠片（Pepperoni），完美还原了赤陶瓦屋顶。按照1:87（HO比例）布置的微小细节赋予了画面生机：番茄酱运河上漂浮着微型的贡多拉小船，船上站着极小的船夫；奶酪广场和披萨边海岸线上，散布着正在漫步或在微缩餐桌旁用餐的微小人物模型。画面的背景是一张带有粗糙纹理的质朴木质餐桌，向上下两端延伸。拍摄采用移轴镜头（Tilt-Shift）技术，焦点清晰锐利地集中在披萨中心的运河与建筑群上，而披萨边缘及木桌背景则呈现出柔和的虚化散景，以此强调微缩比例。整体采用暖色调的美食摄影灯光，完美捕捉了酱汁的晶莹剔透与饼皮的酥脆质感，营造出既令人垂涎又充满超现实感的美食立体透视模型（Edible Diorama）氛围。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/gallery_74_1.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "A vertical-format macro photography and foodscape image depicting a miniature Venice waterscape built upon a pizza as its foundation. The main subject is a circular pizza occupying the center of the frame, its outermost ring a golden-crisp, thick crust covered in baking bubbles, enclosing the entire miniature world like towering city walls. The interior space has been ingeniously transformed into Venetian urban topography: the \"waterways\" are formed from rich, vibrant red tomato sauce, winding into a sinuous Grand Canal and intersecting smaller channels, their surfaces glistening with an appetizing sheen of oil; the \"land\" and piazzas are paved with melted, stringy mozzarella cheese bearing slightly browned spots, forming streets and walkways; the \"vegetation\" consists of fresh basil leaves and clusters of broccoli florets, simulating lush trees and shrubs. Rising from the cheese foundations are miniature Venetian-style buildings whose walls are constructed from baked-textured dough, seamlessly merging with the base, their rooftops covered with slightly curled red pepperoni slices, perfectly replicating terracotta tile roofs. Tiny details arranged at 1:87 (HO scale) bring the scene to life: miniature gondolas float on the tomato sauce canals, with tiny gondoliers standing aboard; across the cheese piazzas and along the pizza-crust shoreline, tiny figure models are scattered—some strolling, others dining at miniature tables. The background of the image is a rustic wooden table with coarse texture, extending toward both the top and bottom edges. The shot employs tilt-shift lens technique, with the focal point sharply concentrated on the canals and building clusters at the pizza's center, while the pizza crust edges and wooden table background dissolve into soft bokeh, emphasizing the miniature scale. The overall warm-toned food photography lighting perfectly captures the translucent sheen of the sauce and the crispy texture of the crust, creating an atmosphere that is both mouthwatering and surreal—an edible diorama rendered as a three-dimensional food perspective model.",
    "prompt_zh": "<instruction>\n\n输入A是一道具体菜品\n输入B是一座城市或一处风景\n将食材映射为地理特征：如果未提供输入A，则选择该城市或风景中受欢迎的食材\n液体（水域）：识别酱汁、汤汁或糖浆。\n（例如：披萨酱 -> 运河。拉面汤汁 -> 港湾。糖浆 -> 河流）。\n固体（陆地）：识别主要的碳水化合物或蛋白质。\n（例如：融化的奶酪 -> 路面/沙地。面条 -> 蜿蜒道路。煎饼叠层 -> 山顶高原）。\n点缀（植被）：识别香草或蔬菜。\n（例如：罗勒/西兰花 -> 树木。"
