    "revised_prompt": "一张纪录片视频播放界面的高清截图，展示了传统玻璃吹制工艺的制作过程。画面主体位于一间光线昏暗、充满颗粒感的传统玻璃工坊内。画面中央偏左，一名身着深灰色的粗布长袖衬衫、外搭做旧的棕色厚实皮围裙的男性工匠，正坐在一张边缘磨损的木制工作台旁。工匠戴着黑色的防护护目镜，满脸胡茬，额头和脸颊上布满被高温烤出的汗珠，他的脸部和上半身被前方的高温玻璃照亮，呈现出强烈的暖橙色光影。他双手紧紧握着一根长约一米的黑色金属吹管，正鼓起腮帮子用力向管口吹气。吹管的另一端位于画面中央偏右，连接着一团约排球大小、正在散发着耀眼明亮橙黄色光芒的熔融状态玻璃球。画面背景深处是一个用耐火砖砌成的巨大熔炉，炉口敞开，内部燃烧着熊熊的红黄色火焰，照亮了背景墙面上悬挂的各种长柄金属钳和塑形工具。空气中隐约可见漂浮的微小灰尘和高温产生的火星。画面右上角悬浮着一个半透明的白色频道水印文字 'CRAFT MASTERS'。画面底部边缘分布着视频播放器的UI元素：最底端是一条贯穿左右的红色播放进度条，进度条左上方显示白色的当前播放时间与总时长 '12:34 / 45:00'，右上方依次排列着白色的暂停图标、音量喇叭图标、齿轮设置图标、高清画质标识 '4K' 以及矩形的全屏图标。在进度条上方、画面底部的居中位置，显示着两行带有黑色描边的清晰白色字幕，上排为中文：'我们需要在1100度的高温下，迅速将这团熔融的玻璃塑形。'，下排为对应的较小字号英文：'We need to shape this blob of molten glass quickly at a high temperature of 1100 degrees.'。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/gallery_76_2_v2.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "A high-definition screenshot of a documentary video playback interface, showcasing the process of traditional glassblowing craftsmanship. The main scene is set inside a dimly lit, grainy traditional glass workshop. Slightly left of center, a male craftsman wearing a dark gray coarse-cloth long-sleeve shirt layered with a distressed, thick brown leather apron is seated beside a wooden workbench with worn edges. The craftsman wears black protective goggles, has a stubbly face, and beads of sweat induced by intense heat cover his forehead and cheeks. His face and upper body are illuminated by the high-temperature glass in front of him, casting a strong warm orange glow. He grips tightly with both hands a black metal blowpipe approximately one meter long, cheeks puffed out as he blows forcefully into the mouthpiece. The other end of the blowpipe, positioned slightly right of center, is attached to a volleyball-sized glob of molten glass in a fluid state, radiating a dazzlingly bright orange-yellow luminescence. Deep in the background stands a massive furnace constructed from refractory bricks, its mouth wide open, with roaring red-yellow flames burning inside, illuminating various long-handled metal tongs and shaping tools hanging on the background wall. Faintly visible in the air are floating tiny dust particles and sparks generated by the extreme heat. In the upper right corner of the frame, a semi-transparent white channel watermark text reads 'CRAFT MASTERS'. Along the bottom edge of the frame are video player UI elements: at the very bottom is a red playback progress bar spanning the full width; above the left end of the progress bar, the current playback time and total duration are displayed in white as '12:34 / 45:00'; above the right end, white icons are arranged in sequence—a pause icon, a volume speaker icon, a gear settings icon, a high-definition quality label '4K', and a rectangular fullscreen icon. Above the progress bar, centered at the bottom of the frame, two lines of clear white subtitles with black outlines are displayed; the upper line in Chinese reads: '我们需要在1100度的高温下，迅速将这团熔融的玻璃塑形。', and the lower line in corresponding smaller English text reads: 'We need to shape this blob of molten glass quickly at a high temperature of 1100 degrees.'",
