    "revised_prompt": "竖版彩色动漫风格人物插画。画面中央绘制着一位年轻女性的半身至膝盖立绘，占据了画面的主要视觉空间。她拥有微卷的深棕色长发，发丝线条流畅分明，头戴一顶深红色的毛呢贝雷帽。她身穿一件质感厚实的米白色长款风衣，内搭一件鲜艳的橙色粗线高领针织毛衣，下半身穿着深棕色的格纹百褶裙。她双手在胸前捧着一个纯白色的纸质咖啡杯，杯口有三条白色的波浪形热气线条升腾，人物表情温和，嘴角微微上扬，双眼为明亮的琥珀色，带有精致的白色高光。\n\n整个画面的色彩严格遵循了一套特定的秋季暖色调色卡进行精准上色。为了直观展示色彩参考标准，画面左上角边缘垂直排列着五个正方形的色卡模块。这五个色块从上到下依次填充为：米白色、深红色、橙色、深棕色和浅橄榄绿色。每个色块的右侧均附带清晰的黑色无衬线字体，逐字抄录依次标注着对应的十六进制色彩代码：'#F5F5DC'、'#8B0000'、'#FFA500'、'#654321'、'#8FBC8F'。\n\n插画的背景设定为纯粹平面的浅橄榄绿色，与色卡中最底端的颜色完全一致，没有其他杂物干扰。人物的上色技法采用了干净利落的赛璐璐平涂风格，明暗交界线清晰锐利，色彩纯度高且无杂色过渡。整体轮廓的线稿采用深红棕色勾勒，线条精细，与温暖的整体色彩搭配完美融合，呈现出强烈的色彩设计感与严谨的上色规范。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/gallery_85_1.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "A vertical, full-color anime-style character illustration. Drawn at the center of the frame is a young woman depicted from the upper body to the knees in a standing pose, occupying the primary visual space. She has slightly wavy, deep brown long hair with smooth and distinct strand lines, topped with a dark red wool beret. She wears a thick-textured, off-white long trench coat over a vivid orange chunky-knit turtleneck sweater, with a dark brown plaid pleated skirt on the lower half. Both hands hold a pure white paper coffee cup in front of her chest, with three white wavy steam lines rising from the cup's rim. Her expression is gentle, the corners of her mouth slightly upturned, and her eyes are a bright amber color with delicate white highlights.\n\nThe entire image's coloring strictly follows a specific autumn warm-tone color palette for precise coloring. To intuitively showcase the color reference standard, five square color swatch modules are vertically arranged along the upper-left edge of the frame. These five swatches are filled from top to bottom with: off-white, dark red, orange, dark brown, and light olive green. To the right of each swatch, clear black sans-serif text is appended, transcribed character by character, annotating the corresponding hexadecimal color codes: '#F5F5DC', '#8B0000', '#FFA500', '#654321', '#8FBC8F'.\n\nThe illustration's background is set as a purely flat light olive green, perfectly matching the bottommost color in the color palette, with no other distracting elements. The character's coloring technique employs a clean and crisp cel-shading flat-fill style, with sharp and clearly defined shadow boundaries, high color saturation, and no muddy color transitions. The overall outline lineart is rendered in dark reddish-brown, with fine lines that blend perfectly with the warm overall color scheme, presenting a strong sense of color design and rigorous coloring standards.",
    "prompt_zh": "准确使用图2色卡为图1人物上色"
