    "title": "咖啡机使用步骤象形图",
    "title_en": "Coffee Machine Step-by-Step Pictogram",
    "prompt": "将此说明图转换为象形图",
    "prompt_en": "Convert this instructional diagram into a pictogram.",
    "source": "https://x.com/nobisiro_2023/status/1968677481486914022",
    "type": "t2i",
    "author": "@nobisiro_2023",
    "author_link": "https://x.com/nobisiro_2023/status/1968677481486914022",
    "revised_prompt": "一张扁平化极简风格的象形图表（Pictogram Infographic），背景为纯米白色。画面采用横向构图，由顶部的标题区和下方的2排3列网格步骤图组成。所有图形均为无透视、无明暗细节、无五官的实心二维矢量剪影，类似公共场所的标准指示牌风格。顶部居中位置写有深棕色的大号粗体文字'如何使用自动咖啡机'，其下方紧跟较小的橙色大写英文'HOW TO USE THE COFFEE MACHINE'，标题左侧配有一个由两个椭圆组成的极简咖啡豆图标。下方分为六个步骤区块，每个区块包含一个中心图形和底部双语文字。左上角第一个区块展示一个深棕色的象形人半身剪影，正将一个马克杯放在横线上，下方写着深棕色文字'1. 放置水杯'和橙色小字'PLACE YOUR MUG'。上方中间第二个区块显示两滴水和两颗咖啡豆的符号，右侧有一个绿色的实心圆圈内含白色对勾，下方文字为'2. 检查原料'和'CHECK WATER & BEANS'。右上角第三个区块特写一只深棕色的手部剪影，食指正在按压一个方形按钮，按钮上镂空显示出咖啡杯轮廓，下方文字为'3. 选择饮品'和'SELECT BEVERAGE'。左下角第四个区块显示一个倒梯形的咖啡机喷嘴剪影，下方有橙色直线代表液体流入杯中，杯子右侧有一个极简的沙漏图标，下方文字为'4. 等待片刻'和'WAIT A MOMENT'。下方中间第五个区块展示一个杯子，上方飘着三条橙色的波浪形热气线条，杯子右侧悬浮着一个包含感叹号的橙色警告等边三角形，下方文字为'5. 小心烫口'和'CAUTION: HOT'。右下角第六个区块展示一只象形手的剪影正拿着一块方形抹布，擦拭着几条横线代表的托盘网格，下方文字为'6. 保持清洁'和'KEEP IT CLEAN'。整体色调以深棕色和米白色为主，辅以橙色作为视觉重点，排版对齐整齐，信息传达清晰直观。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/gallery_99_1.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "A flat, minimalist-style pictogram infographic with a pure off-white background. The image uses a landscape composition, consisting of a title area at the top and a 2-row by 3-column grid of step illustrations below. All graphics are perspective-free, shading-free, faceless solid two-dimensional vector silhouettes, resembling the style of standard signage found in public spaces. At the top center, large bold text in dark brown reads '如何使用自动咖啡机', immediately followed below by smaller orange uppercase English text 'HOW TO USE THE COFFEE MACHINE'. To the left of the title is a minimalist coffee bean icon composed of two ellipses. Below are six step blocks, each containing a central graphic and bilingual text at the bottom. The first block in the upper left shows a dark brown pictographic half-body human silhouette placing a mug onto a horizontal line, with dark brown text below reading '1. 放置水杯' and orange small text 'PLACE YOUR MUG'. The second block in the upper middle displays two water droplets and two coffee bean symbols, with a green solid circle containing a white checkmark to the right, and text below reading '2. 检查原料' and 'CHECK WATER & BEANS'. The third block in the upper right features a close-up of a dark brown hand silhouette with the index finger pressing a square button that has a coffee cup outline cut out of it, with text below reading '3. 选择饮品' and 'SELECT BEVERAGE'. The fourth block in the lower left shows an inverted trapezoidal coffee machine nozzle silhouette, with orange straight lines below representing liquid flowing into a cup, and a minimalist hourglass icon to the right of the cup, with text below reading '4. 等待片刻' and 'WAIT A MOMENT'. The fifth block in the lower middle presents a cup with three orange wavy steam lines floating above it, and an orange warning equilateral triangle containing an exclamation mark hovering to the right of the cup, with text below reading '5. 小心烫口' and 'CAUTION: HOT'. The sixth block in the lower right shows a pictographic hand silhouette holding a square cloth, wiping several horizontal lines representing a tray grid, with text below reading '6. 保持清洁' and 'KEEP IT CLEAN'. The overall color scheme is dominated by dark brown and off-white, accented with orange as the visual focal color. The layout is neatly aligned, and the information is conveyed clearly and intuitively.",
    "prompt_zh": "将此说明图转换为象形图"
