    "prompt": "中景，有阳光的午后，胶片质感，拍摄地面，秋天的落叶、树枝、银杏叶和桂花在平面上拼成了一个小猫的样子，旁边放着一杯一次性咖啡杯",
    "prompt_en": "Medium shot, a sunny afternoon, film grain texture, camera shooting the ground, autumn fallen leaves, twigs, ginkgo leaves, and osmanthus flowers arranged flat on the ground to form the shape of a small cat, with a disposable coffee cup placed beside it.",
