    "title": "动漫转真人",
    "title_en": "Anime to Real Life",
    "prompt": "1:1变真人",
    "prompt_en": "1:1 convert to a real person.",
    "source": "https://x.com/ZHO_ZHO_ZHO/status/1991573512713347181",
    "type": "t2i",
    "author": "@ZHO_ZHO_ZHO",
    "author_link": "https://x.com/ZHO_ZHO_ZHO/status/1991573512713347181",
    "revised_prompt": "这是一张16:9画幅的左右拼接对比图，展示了一个动漫角色“1:1变真人”的视觉效果。画面被一条居中的细白线垂直平分为左右两半。\n\n左半部分为纯正的二次元日系动漫风格，画面左上角带有发光效果的白色文字标记‘2D原画’。画面主体是一名赛博朋克风格的少女，她留着银色齐刘海短发，左侧鬓角有一绺紫发。角色身穿黑色机能风皮夹克，衣领处有亮蓝色的发光线条，脖子上戴着一条金属项圈。她右手将一把散发着霓虹粉色光芒的武士刀扛在肩上，眼神冷酷地直视前方。背景是手绘风格的赛博朋克雨夜街道，背景虚化，点缀着模糊的红蓝霓虹灯招牌。\n\n右半部分是完美的真人化摄影级别再现，画面右上角带有白色文字标记‘真人实拍’。右侧的真人模特完美复刻了左侧角色的五官特征、发型、服饰穿搭与姿态，比例与构图达到1:1精确对齐。模特的皮肤具有极其真实的纹理和光泽，可以看清细微的毛孔、面部的立体阴影以及雨滴带来的湿润感。银紫相间的头发展现出真实的毛发质感与光影散射，黑色机能风皮夹克呈现出高级的皮革褶皱、材质纹理与金属拉链的锐利反光。肩膀上的发光武士刀投射出真实的粉色环境光，自然地照亮了模特的右侧脸颊与发丝。背景同样是虚化的赛博朋克街道，但转变为真实的摄影大光圈景深效果，雨滴在镜头前形成逼真的光斑。\n\n整体画面光影对比强烈，色调以冷蓝与霓虹粉为主，左侧扁平化赛璐璐上色与右侧极其逼真的物理光照渲染形成强烈的视觉冲击。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/item_1053_3.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "This is a 16:9 aspect ratio side-by-side comparison image, showcasing the visual effect of a \"1:1 anime-to-real-person\" transformation of an anime character. The image is vertically bisected into left and right halves by a thin centered white line.\n\nThe left half is rendered in an authentic nijigen Japanese anime style, with glowing white text labeled '2D原画' (2D Original Art) in the upper-left corner. The main subject is a cyberpunk-style girl with silver blunt-bangs short hair and a streak of purple hair at the left temple. The character wears a black techwear leather jacket with glowing bright blue lines at the collar, and a metal choker around her neck. She carries a katana emitting neon pink luminescence over her right shoulder, staring coolly straight ahead. The background is a hand-drawn style cyberpunk rainy night street, blurred with bokeh, dotted with indistinct red and blue neon signs.\n\nThe right half is a flawless photorealistic live-action recreation, with white text labeled '真人实拍' (Live-Action Photography) in the upper-right corner. The real-life model on the right perfectly replicates the left-side character's facial features, hairstyle, outfit styling, and pose, achieving precise 1:1 alignment in proportion and composition. The model's skin exhibits extremely realistic texture and sheen, with fine pores, three-dimensional facial shadows, and a wet gleam from raindrops clearly visible. The silver-and-purple hair displays authentic hair texture and light scattering, while the black techwear leather jacket presents premium leather creases, material texture, and sharp reflections off metal zippers. The glowing katana on the shoulder casts realistic pink ambient light, naturally illuminating the model's right cheek and hair strands. The background is similarly a blurred cyberpunk street, but transformed into a genuine photographic wide-aperture depth-of-field effect, with raindrops forming lifelike bokeh orbs in front of the lens.\n\nThe overall image features strong light-and-shadow contrast, with a color palette dominated by cool blue and neon pink. The flat cel-shading coloring on the left and the extremely realistic physically-based lighting rendering on the right create a striking visual impact.",
    "prompt_zh": "1:1变真人"
