    "revised_prompt": "一张展示巧克力制作过程的彩色手绘风格信息流程图海报。背景为浅米色的做旧纸张纹理。画面正上方有醒目的棕色加粗标题文字，内容为 '巧克力的制作过程'，下方有一行较小的英文副标题 'How Chocolate is Made'。画面主体由六个通过棕色虚线箭头连接的步骤图块组成，呈上下两排分布，形成Z字形视觉引导路径。左上角是第一个步骤，插画描绘了一棵结满可可果的树，旁边放着一个被切开的紫红色可可果，露出内部包裹着白色果肉的豆子，图块下方有棕色文字 '第一步：采摘果实'。上方中间是第二个步骤，画着几个长方形木箱，里面堆满正在发酵、颜色已变成棕褐色的可可豆，下方有文字 '第二步：木箱发酵'。右上角是第三个步骤，画着一轮太阳照耀在平铺着可可豆的草席上进行晾晒，下方有文字 '第三步：阳光干燥'。左下角是第四个步骤，画着一台复古的金属滚筒烘烤机，可可豆在舱内翻滚并向上冒出白色的热气线条，下方有文字 '第四步：高温烘焙'。下方中间是第五个步骤，画着一台带有双层石磨的研磨机，底部出口正流出棕色浓稠的巧克力浆，下方有文字 '第五步：研磨成浆'。右下角是最终步骤，画着一条流水线，巧克力浆正被注入网格状的方形模具中，模具旁边放置着一块已经剥开一半银色包装纸的排块巧克力，下方有文字 '第六步：调温成型'。画面的四个边角处散落点缀着几片手绘的绿色可可树叶和零星的单颗棕色可可豆。整体色调以温暖的棕褐色、奶油色、暗红色和墨绿色为主，线条细腻，排版结构清晰。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/item_107_1.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "A colorful, hand-drawn style informational flowchart poster illustrating the chocolate-making process. The background features a light beige aged paper texture. At the very top of the image, there is a prominent bold brown title reading '巧克力的制作过程' (The Chocolate-Making Process), with a smaller English subtitle 'How Chocolate is Made' beneath it. The main body of the image consists of six step-by-step illustrated blocks connected by brown dashed-line arrows, arranged in two rows (top and bottom) forming a Z-shaped visual guide path. The upper-left corner shows the first step, with an illustration depicting a tree laden with cacao pods, beside which sits a cut-open purplish-red cacao pod revealing beans wrapped in white pulp inside; brown text below reads '第一步：采摘果实' (Step 1: Harvesting the Pods). The upper-center shows the second step, illustrating several rectangular wooden crates filled with fermenting cacao beans that have turned a brownish-tan color, with text below reading '第二步：木箱发酵' (Step 2: Wooden Crate Fermentation). The upper-right corner shows the third step, depicting a sun shining down on cacao beans spread out on grass mats for drying, with text below reading '第三步：阳光干燥' (Step 3: Sun Drying). The lower-left corner shows the fourth step, illustrating a vintage metal drum roaster with cacao beans tumbling inside the chamber and white heat-line wisps rising upward, with text below reading '第四步：高温烘焙' (Step 4: High-Temperature Roasting). The lower-center shows the fifth step, depicting a grinding machine with a double-layer stone mill, from whose bottom outlet a thick brown chocolate paste flows out, with text below reading '第五步：研磨成浆' (Step 5: Grinding into Paste). The lower-right corner shows the final step, illustrating a production line where chocolate paste is being poured into grid-pattern square molds, with a chocolate bar that has been half-unwrapped from its silver foil placed beside the molds, and text below reading '第六步：调温成型' (Step 6: Tempering and Molding). Scattered across the four corners of the image are decorative hand-drawn green cacao leaves and a few individual brown cacao beans. The overall color palette is dominated by warm brownish-tan, cream, dark red, and dark green tones, with delicate line work and a clear, well-organized layout.",
    "prompt_zh": "我想看这个是如何制作出来的"
