    "title_en": "Statue of Liberty AR Data Overlay",
    "prompt": "A photorealistic wide-angle landscape shot of the Statue of Liberty with the New York City skyline and harbor in the background. Superimposed on the scene is a white, hand-drawn augmented reality technical overlay. Features include: 1. Sketchy white leader lines pointing to key details like the \"Torch,\" \"Crown Rays,\" and \"Copper Shell\" with handwritten text labels. 2. Large dimensional vertical measurement arrows indicating the total height from ground to torch. 3. Small floating wireframe icons showing wind load data and material composition. Aesthetic: Structural engineering analysis, F1 broadcast graphics style, bright outdoor daylight, architectural blueprint overlay.",
    "prompt_en": "A photorealistic wide-angle landscape shot of the Statue of Liberty with the New York City skyline and harbor in the background. Superimposed on the scene is a white, hand-drawn augmented reality technical overlay. Features include: 1. Sketchy white leader lines pointing to key details like the \"Torch,\" \"Crown Rays,\" and \"Copper Shell\" with handwritten text labels. 2. Large dimensional vertical measurement arrows indicating the total height from ground to torch. 3. Small floating wireframe icons showing wind load data and material composition. Aesthetic: Structural engineering analysis, F1 broadcast graphics style, bright outdoor daylight, architectural blueprint overlay.",
    "source": "https://x.com/azed_ai/status/1992263499398205640",
    "type": "t2i",
    "author": "@azed_ai",
    "author_link": "https://x.com/azed_ai/status/1992263499398205640",
    "revised_prompt": "带有一层白色手绘风格增强现实（AR）技术信息叠加层的写实广角风景照片。画面采用竖版构图，中央矗立着宏伟的自由女神像（Statue of Liberty）。雕像后方延伸出广阔的纽约市（New York City）天际线以及波光粼粼的港口水面。环境光线为明亮的户外日光，色彩真实自然，画面清晰锐利。\n\n叠加在写实风景之上的是纯白色的工程蓝图式数据分析图形，呈现出类似F1赛事转播中的高级技术图解风格。雕像的关键部位被带有手绘质感的白色粗略引线标出：一条引线指向高举的火炬，末端带有手写体标签 'Torch'；一条引线指向头部的光环，带有标签 'Crown Rays'；第三条引线指向雕像的躯干，带有标签 'Copper Shell'。\n\n在雕像的一侧，绘制有一组巨大的垂直尺寸测量箭头，起于地面基座，止于火炬最顶端，旁边标注了手写体的总高度数据 'Total Height: 305 ft 1 in'。此外，半空中还悬浮着白色的微型线框图标：一个带有气流线条的微型风速计图标旁边标注着风载荷数据 'Wind Load: 50 mph'，另一个呈现几何微观结构的图标旁边标注着材料成分 'Material Composition: Copper & Iron'。整体视觉将逼真的城市自然风光与精密的结构工程分析完美融合。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/item_1081_4.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "A realistic wide-angle landscape photograph with an overlaid layer of white hand-drawn style augmented reality (AR) technical information. The image uses a vertical (portrait) composition, with the majestic Statue of Liberty standing prominently in the center. Behind the statue extends the expansive New York City skyline and the shimmering waters of the harbor. The ambient lighting is bright outdoor daylight, with true-to-life natural colors and a sharp, crisp image.\n\nSuperimposed over the realistic landscape are pure white engineering-blueprint-style data analysis graphics, rendered in an advanced technical overlay style reminiscent of F1 race broadcast telemetry graphics. Key parts of the statue are marked with white, hand-drawn-textured rough leader lines: one leader line points to the raised torch, with a handwritten-style label 'Torch' at its end; another leader line points to the crown on the head, labeled 'Crown Rays'; a third leader line points to the statue's torso, labeled 'Copper Shell.'\n\nOn one side of the statue, a set of large vertical dimension measurement arrows is drawn, starting from the ground pedestal and terminating at the very top of the torch, with the total height data annotated in handwritten script beside it: 'Total Height: 305 ft 1 in.' Additionally, small white wireframe icons float in mid-air: a miniature anemometer icon with airflow lines annotated with wind load data 'Wind Load: 50 mph,' and another icon displaying a geometric microstructure annotated with the material composition 'Material Composition: Copper & Iron.' The overall visual seamlessly merges the lifelike urban natural scenery with precise structural engineering analysis.",
    "prompt_zh": "一张逼真的广角风景照片，展示自由女神像，背景为纽约市天际线和港口。场景上叠加了白色手绘增强现实技术标注层。特征包括：1. 草图风格的白色引线指向关键细节，如\"火炬\"\"皇冠光芒\"\"铜质外壳\"，并配有手写文字标签。2. 大型纵向尺寸测量箭头，标示从地面到火炬的总高度。3. 小型悬浮线框图标，显示风载荷数据和材料组成。美学风格：结构工程分析，F1 bro"
