    "prompt": "Create an image of the different patterns that makes up this shoe. lay them out individually against a neutral surface",
    "prompt_en": "Create an image of the different patterns that makes up this shoe. lay them out individually against a neutral surface",
    "source": "https://x.com/LinusEkenstam/status/1992105428873056499",
    "type": "t2i",
    "author": "@LinusEkenstam",
    "author_link": "https://x.com/LinusEkenstam/status/1992105428873056499",
    "revised_prompt": "一张产品拆解平铺摄影图。在一个浅灰色的哑光无缝平面上，整齐地平铺着构成一只经典复古帆布运动鞋的各个独立裁片和部件。画面采用俯视视角（Top-down view）和整理摆放（Knolling）构图，各个零件之间保持着均匀且精确的间距，横向展开以适应宽幅画面。\n\n画面上方放置着鞋底部分：一块米白色的橡胶外底，清晰地展示着底部的波浪形防滑纹路；其旁是一条长长的白色橡胶沿条（包边），边缘带有一根极细的黑色饰线，自然地呈现出柔和的弧形弯曲。\n\n画面中部居中排列着主要的面料裁片：两片灰色的粗斜纹帆布鞋面主裁片，分别展现出鞋帮左右两侧的流线型轮廓，裁片边缘清晰可见预留的缝线孔距；在两片鞋面之间，放置着一块半圆形的白色哑光橡胶鞋头盖；紧挨着鞋面，平铺着两根细长的灰色帆布鞋眼片，上面各镶嵌着八个闪亮的银色金属鞋眼孔。\n\n画面下方陈列着配件与内部结构：一条修长的灰色帆布鞋舌；一块米色的泡沫材质鞋垫，带有符合人体工学的足弓凸起设计，鞋垫脚跟部位印有黑色的复古粗体英文字母 'VINTAGE' 和正下方的 'FOOTWEAR'；两根纯白色的棉质鞋带被极为规整地盘绕成两个对称的椭圆线圈；旁边散落着两块用于后跟加固的半月形小块帆布裁片，以及一张正方形的白色织物鞋标，鞋标上清晰地印有黑色的无衬线字体 'SIZE 42' 和下方稍小一号的 '100% COTTON'。\n\n光线采用均匀柔和的顶部漫反射照明，消除了强烈的投影，使每一种材料的质感——帆布的粗糙纤维、橡胶的微涩表面、金属的高光反光——都得到了极致的还原。整体色调温和、中性偏冷，呈现出极简主义风格与工业制鞋工艺的严谨美学，画面拥有极高的清晰度和锐利度。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/item_1083_3.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "A product teardown flat-lay photograph. On a light gray matte seamless surface, the individual cut pieces and components constituting a classic vintage canvas sneaker are neatly laid out flat. The image is shot from a top-down view using a knolling composition, with all parts maintaining even and precise spacing between them, spread horizontally to suit a wide-format frame.\n\nThe upper portion of the image displays the sole components: a piece of off-white rubber outsole, clearly showing the wavy anti-slip tread pattern on its underside; beside it is a long white rubber foxing strip (binding tape) with an extremely fine black accent line along its edge, naturally presenting a gentle arcing curve.\n\nThe central portion of the image features the main fabric cut pieces arranged in the middle: two pieces of gray coarse twill canvas upper panels, each displaying the streamlined contour of the left and right sides of the shoe upper, with pre-punched stitch holes clearly visible along the edges of the cut pieces; placed between the two upper panels is a semi-circular white matte rubber toe cap; immediately adjacent to the uppers, two slender gray canvas eyelet strips are laid flat, each inset with eight shiny silver metal eyelets.\n\nThe lower portion of the image displays the accessories and internal structures: a slender gray canvas tongue; an off-white foam insole with an ergonomic arch support design, featuring black retro bold English lettering 'VINTAGE' printed at the heel area with 'FOOTWEAR' directly beneath it; two pure white cotton laces coiled extremely neatly into two symmetrical oval loops; scattered nearby are two small crescent-shaped canvas reinforcement pieces for the heel counter, as well as a square white fabric shoe label clearly printed with the black sans-serif text 'SIZE 42' and slightly smaller text '100% COTTON' below it.\n\nThe lighting employs even, soft overhead diffused illumination, eliminating harsh shadows, so that the texture of every material — the rough fibers of the canvas, the slightly tacky surface of the rubber, the specular highlights of the metal — is rendered with utmost fidelity. The overall color tone is gentle, neutral with a cool bias, presenting a minimalist aesthetic combined with the rigorous craftsmanship of industrial shoemaking, with the image possessing extremely high clarity and sharpness.",
    "prompt_zh": "创建一张图片，展示组成这只鞋的不同纹样部件，将它们逐一拆解平铺在中性色背景表面上。"
