    "title": "动漫与现实分屏肖像",
    "title_en": "Anime vs. Reality Split-Screen Portrait",
    "prompt": "A cinematic 16:9 wide shot featuring a single centered headshot of Naruto Uzumaki, face split vertically in half. A distinct black line separates the two art styles down the center. [LEFT HALF]: Classic anime style, bright blonde spiky hair, blue anime eye, black whisker marks, metal headband with bold lines. [RIGHT HALF]: Gritty realism, realistic dirty blonde textured hair, piercing blue human eye, whisker marks as faint scars, weathered metal texture on the headband with rust. The headband and facial features align perfectly to form a single, unified character portrait, rendered in Unreal Engine 5.",
    "prompt_en": "A cinematic 16:9 wide shot featuring a single centered headshot of Naruto Uzumaki, face split vertically in half. A distinct black line separates the two art styles down the center. [LEFT HALF]: Classic anime style, bright blonde spiky hair, blue anime eye, black whisker marks, metal headband with bold lines. [RIGHT HALF]: Gritty realism, realistic dirty blonde textured hair, piercing blue human eye, whisker marks as faint scars, weathered metal texture on the headband with rust. The headband and facial features align perfectly to form a single, unified character portrait, rendered in Unreal Engine 5.",
    "source": "https://x.com/_MehdiSharifi_/status/1992018970078065032",
    "type": "t2i",
    "author": "@_MehdiSharifi_",
    "author_link": "https://x.com/_MehdiSharifi_/status/1992018970078065032",
    "revised_prompt": "一幅由虚幻引擎5（Unreal Engine 5）渲染的电影级数字艺术肖像，采用垂直画幅和居中的头部特写构图。画面主体是漩涡鸣人（Naruto Uzumaki），他的面部被正中央的一条清晰的黑色垂直细线一分为二，展现出两种截然不同的艺术风格。尽管风格迥异，但左右两侧的五官轮廓与额头上的护额在物理位置上完美对齐，融合为一个统一且连贯的人物肖像。画面的左半部分呈现经典的动漫风格：拥有明亮高饱和度的金黄色刺猬头，一只典型二次元特征的大而明亮的蓝色眼睛，脸颊上印有标志性且轮廓清晰的黑色胡须状纹理，佩戴的金属护额带有粗犷的黑色勾线与平面的光影效果。画面的右半部分则呈现出粗犷冷峻的写实风格（Gritty realism）：头发表现为具有真实毛发质感、略带凌乱的暗金色碎发，眼睛是一只深邃、锐利且包含真实虹膜细节的蓝色人类眼球，脸颊上的胡须纹理转化为皮肤上淡淡的真实疤痕，右侧的金属护额呈现出饱经风霜的质感，表面布满划痕与逼真的铁锈。整体光影具有电影级的层次感，完美展现了二次元与三维写实之间的强烈对比与巧妙融合。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/item_1092_3.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "A cinematic-grade digital art portrait rendered in Unreal Engine 5, utilizing a vertical frame with a centered close-up headshot composition. The subject is Naruto Uzumaki, whose face is bisected down the exact center by a crisp, thin black vertical line, revealing two distinctly different artistic styles. Despite the stark stylistic contrast, the facial features and the forehead protector on both sides align perfectly in physical position, merging into a unified and coherent character portrait. The left half of the image presents a classic anime style: bright, highly saturated golden-yellow spiky hair, one large and luminous blue eye with typical two-dimensional characteristics, iconic and crisply outlined black whisker-like markings on the cheek, and a metal forehead protector rendered with bold black outlines and flat shading. The right half presents a gritty realism style: the hair is depicted as realistically textured, slightly disheveled dark-gold strands, the eye is a deep, sharp blue human eyeball containing authentic iris detail, the whisker markings on the cheek transform into faint, realistic scars on the skin, and the metal forehead protector on the right side exhibits a weathered appearance, its surface covered in scratches and convincing rust. The overall lighting possesses cinematic depth and layering, perfectly showcasing the striking contrast and ingenious fusion between two-dimensional anime and three-dimensional photorealism.",
    "prompt_zh": "一张电影感的16:9宽幅镜头，画面中央为漩涡鸣人的单人头像特写，面部沿垂直中线一分为二。一条明显的黑色线条将两种艺术风格从中间分隔开来。[LEFT HALF]：经典动漫风格，明亮的金色刺猬头发，蓝色动漫眼睛，黑色猫须印记，线条粗犷的金属额带。[RIGHT HALF]：粗粝写实风格，逼真的脏金色质感头发，锐利的蓝色真人眼睛，猫须印记呈现为淡淡的疤痕，额带为风化金属质感并带有锈迹。额带和面部特征完美对齐，形成一幅统一的角色肖像，以Unreal E引擎渲染。"
