    "author_link": "https://x.com/ZHO_ZHO_ZHO/status/1992181199473938774",
    "revised_prompt": "一幅涂鸦风格的横向插画。画面主体是一只被幽默夸张化的胖橘猫（具体化原提示词中的抽象主体）。橘猫的身体被画成了一个巨大的不规则圆形，而它的四肢和尾巴则像火柴棍一样细长且弯曲，呈现出强烈的比例反差和滑稽感。猫的脸上戴着一副硕大的歪斜黑框墨镜，嘴巴被画成一条随意的波浪线，显得慵懒且不耐烦。它正坐在一张摇摇欲坠的极小的三条腿木凳上，两只小爪子捧着一个比它脑袋还大的亮蓝色不规则马克杯。杯口冒出几根像弹簧一样的黑色粗线条，代表升腾的热气。画面整体采用稚拙的线条表现，轮廓边缘粗糙、随性，带有马克笔手绘的质感。背景为干净的米白色纸张纹理，在橘猫左右两侧的宽阔空间里，随意散落着几根黑色螺旋线、不对称的四角星图案以及几颗夸张放大的咖啡豆。在画面的右上角，用粗糙的手写体涂鸦写着一行黑色的英文大写字母：'NEED COFFEE!'，字母大小不一，排列得歪歪扭扭，完美契合整体的稚拙与幽默风格。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/item_1094_2.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "A doodle-style horizontal illustration. The main subject is a humorously exaggerated fat orange tabby cat. The cat's body is drawn as a massive irregular circle, while its four limbs and tail are stick-thin and bent like matchsticks, creating a strong proportional contrast and comedic effect. The cat's face sports an oversized pair of crooked black-framed sunglasses, and its mouth is drawn as a casual wavy line, appearing lazy and impatient. It is sitting on a wobbly, extremely tiny three-legged wooden stool, its two small paws clutching an irregular bright-blue mug larger than its own head. A few thick black lines coiling like springs rise from the rim of the mug, representing wafting steam. The overall artwork employs naïve, crude linework with rough, casual contour edges, carrying the texture of hand-drawn marker illustrations. The background features a clean off-white paper texture, and in the broad open spaces on either side of the orange cat, a few black spiral lines, asymmetrical four-pointed star patterns, and several exaggeratedly enlarged coffee beans are casually scattered. In the upper-right corner of the image, a line of black uppercase English letters is scrawled in rough handwritten doodle lettering: 'NEED COFFEE!', with letters varying in size and arranged crookedly, perfectly matching the overall naïve and humorous style.",
    "prompt_zh": "涂鸦风格的[subject]，稚拙的线条，幽默夸张的造型变形。"
