    "author_link": "https://x.com/ZHO_ZHO_ZHO/status/1992181199473938774",
    "revised_prompt": "手绘涂鸦风格的插画，横向构图。画面中央是一只造型幽默夸张的胖猫。这只猫的身体被极度放大，呈现出不规则的巨大椭圆球状，而它的四肢被画得极其短小且粗细不均，正别扭地踩在一个极其袖珍、线条歪歪扭扭的滑板上。猫的面部表情滑稽，双眼由一大一小两个圆圈组成，瞳孔位置不对称，嘴巴是一条随意的波浪线，脸颊两旁支出几根长短不一、方向凌乱的胡须。它的尾巴像一根弹簧般卷曲竖立在身后。\n\n画面的线条呈现出强烈的稚拙感，类似儿童随手使用的蜡笔或粗马克笔涂鸦，轮廓线时断时续、不完全闭合且粗细不均。滑板的轮子是不规则的多边形，滑板下方和左侧后方画有几道简单平行的粗糙短线和飞溅的墨点，用来示意向前滑行的速度感。猫的头顶偏右上方，用扭曲粗糙的手写体写着英文单词 'Wheee!'，字母大小不一，排列高低错落。\n\n整个背景大面积留白，仅在画面左上方用凌乱的螺旋圈圈线条画了一朵形状夸张的云彩。整体配色以黑色的粗糙线条为主，猫的身体上随意涂抹了几块完全超出黑色轮廓线的橘黄色色块，滑板板面被涂成亮绿色。画面通过极度不成比例的形状夸张和简陋纯真的笔触，营造出轻松幽默的视觉效果。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/item_1094_4.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "A hand-drawn doodle-style illustration in horizontal composition. At the center of the image is a humorously exaggerated fat cat. The cat's body is extremely enlarged, presenting an irregularly shaped giant elliptical blob, while its four limbs are drawn extremely short and uneven in thickness, awkwardly standing on a ridiculously tiny skateboard with wobbly, crooked lines. The cat's facial expression is comical—its eyes consist of two circles of mismatched sizes with asymmetrically placed pupils, its mouth is a casual wavy line, and several whiskers of varying lengths jut out in disorderly directions from both cheeks. Its tail curls upward like a spring, standing erect behind its body.\n\nThe linework exhibits a strong sense of childlike naïveté, resembling doodles casually drawn with crayons or thick markers, with contour lines that are intermittent, not fully closed, and uneven in thickness. The skateboard wheels are irregular polygons, and beneath the skateboard and to its left-rear, several simple parallel rough short lines and splattered ink dots are drawn to suggest the sense of forward-gliding speed. Above and to the upper right of the cat's head, the English word 'Wheee!' is written in distorted, rough handwriting, with letters varying in size and arranged at staggered heights.\n\nThe entire background is largely left blank, with only a cloud of exaggerated shape drawn in messy spiraling scribble lines in the upper-left area of the image. The overall color palette is dominated by rough black linework, with a few patches of orange-yellow color casually smeared onto the cat's body, completely exceeding the black contour lines, and the skateboard deck is colored in bright green. Through extremely disproportionate shape exaggeration and crude, innocent brushstrokes, the image creates a lighthearted and humorous visual effect.",
    "prompt_zh": "涂鸦风格的[subject]，稚拙的线条，幽默夸张的造型变形。"
