    "title_en": "Claymation Sci-Fi Movie Poster",
    "prompt": "Restyle the reference movie poster in claymation style. Keep the original layout, composition, and lighting exactly as in the reference. Transform all characters, objects, and elements into handcrafted clay models with visible fingerprints, soft edges, and subtle imperfections. Preserve the background and colors, but give everything a realistic clay texture and dimensional feel, as if it were photographed from a stop-motion clay animation set",
    "prompt_en": "Restyle the reference movie poster in claymation style. Keep the original layout, composition, and lighting exactly as in the reference. Transform all characters, objects, and elements into handcrafted clay models with visible fingerprints, soft edges, and subtle imperfections. Preserve the background and colors, but give everything a realistic clay texture and dimensional feel, as if it were photographed from a stop-motion clay animation set",
    "source": "https://x.com/TechieBySA/status/1987128144470679641",
    "type": "t2i",
    "author": "@TechieBySA",
    "author_link": "https://x.com/TechieBySA/status/1987128144470679641",
    "revised_prompt": "一幅横宽比的科幻冒险题材电影海报。整体画面呈现出极其逼真的定格粘土动画（claymation）风格。画面中所有的角色、物体和环境元素均表现为手工捏制的粘土模型，表面带有清晰可见的指纹印记、柔和圆润的边缘以及手工制作带来的细微瑕疵，仿佛是在定格动画微缩片场中用微距镜头拍摄的真实照片。\n\n画面中央站着一位复古宇航员，其宇航服由白色和橙色的粘土拼接塑形而成，关节处的粘土带有自然的褶皱和轻微的捏痕，头盔的透明面罩反射着片场的光线。宇航员身旁是一个圆柱形的银灰色粘土机器人，带有一颗发光的蓝色粘土眼睛，机身上的拼接缝隙和不规则的边缘清晰可见。\n\n背景是一个外星荒野的微缩模型布景。地面由红棕色的粗糙粘土铺成，表面布满陨石坑和雕塑工具留下的刮痕与颗粒感。远处的夜空背景是深紫色的，上面点缀着白色的粘土小星星，天空中悬挂着一颗巨大的星球，由黄色和红色粘土混合揉捏而成，呈现出大理石般交融的色彩纹理。画面的光影布局模拟了真实的影棚聚光灯，侧逆光勾勒出人物和地形的立体感，投射出柔和的物理阴影，完美凸显了粘土的真实材质与厚重感。\n\n海报正上方印有清晰明了的白色宣传标语：'BEYOND THE STARS, A NEW ADVENTURE BEGINS.'。画面正下方的视觉中心是巨大的立体电影标题：'COSMIC QUEST'，这些字母呈现出手工捏制的黄色粘土质感，字体厚重、立体且带有自然的轻微歪斜感。海报最底部有一行较小的白色主创名单排版：'A CLAYMATION FILM DIRECTED BY JOHN DOE PRODUCED BY JANE SMITH'。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/item_1104_1.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "A widescreen sci-fi adventure movie poster. The overall image presents an extremely realistic claymation style. All characters, objects, and environmental elements in the scene appear as handcrafted clay models, with clearly visible fingerprint impressions on their surfaces, soft rounded edges, and subtle imperfections inherent to handmade craftsmanship, as if captured with a macro lens as a real photograph on a miniature stop-motion animation set.\n\nStanding at the center of the frame is a retro astronaut, whose spacesuit is shaped from white and orange clay pieces joined together, with natural wrinkles and slight pinch marks at the joints, and the helmet's transparent visor reflecting the set lighting. Beside the astronaut is a cylindrical silver-gray clay robot with a single glowing blue clay eye, its seam lines and irregular edges clearly visible on the body.\n\nThe background is a miniature model set of an alien wilderness. The ground is laid with rough reddish-brown clay, its surface covered with craters and the scratches and granular texture left by sculpting tools. The distant night sky backdrop is deep purple, dotted with small white clay stars, and a massive planet hangs in the sky, formed by kneading yellow and red clay together, displaying marble-like swirling color patterns. The lighting layout simulates real studio spotlights, with rim lighting from the side-back delineating the three-dimensionality of the characters and terrain, casting soft physical shadows that perfectly highlight the authentic material quality and substantial weight of the clay.\n\nPrinted clearly at the very top of the poster is a white tagline: 'BEYOND THE STARS, A NEW ADVENTURE BEGINS.' At the visual center of the bottom of the frame is the large three-dimensional movie title: 'COSMIC QUEST,' with the letters exhibiting a handcrafted yellow clay texture—bold, dimensional, and with a naturally slight unevenness. At the very bottom of the poster is a smaller line of white credits: 'A CLAYMATION FILM DIRECTED BY JOHN DOE PRODUCED BY JANE SMITH.'",
    "prompt_zh": "将参考电影海报重新风格化为黏土动画风格。保持原始布局、构图和光照与参考完全一致。将所有角色、物体和元素转化为手工制作的黏土模型，带有可见的指纹痕迹、柔和的边缘和细微的瑕疵。保留背景和色彩，但赋予所有元素逼真的黏土质感和立体感，仿佛是在定格黏土动画片场中拍摄的照片。"
