    "revised_prompt": "一张超写实的高品质摄影特写人像照片，采用横向构图。画面中心是一位展现韩国街头时尚与现代摩登气质的年轻女子。她有着深色浓密的长发，被精心编成两根高高扎起的艺术感发辫，自然垂落在耳朵上方。几缕松散的发丝被几只造型各异的哑光棕色个性发夹随意固定，另有几缕碎发自然散落，巧妙地修饰着她的脸颊。她穿着一件系带设计的抽绳挂脖上衣。女子的鼻梁上架着一副粗框的棕色猫眼眼镜，眼镜位置被刻意微微拉低，露出她柔和的榛子色眼睛。她的妆容精致且具有艺术感：画着棕色的艺术眼线，涂抹了带有水光感的蜜桃色腮红，柔和的暖色调眼影晕染在眼部，眼下和脸颊处点缀着细腻的珠光与亮片，双唇涂着水润丰满的红色唇彩，肌肤呈现出自然透亮的水光肌质感，面部皮肤的毛孔与纹理在超高画质下纤毫毕现。女子头部微微倾斜，眼神放松且充满自信地直视镜头，摆出单手轻托脸颊的姿势。画面背景为极简主义的室内影棚环境，横向画幅让人物两侧留有宽裕的米色与棕色调背景空间，营造出高级的留白感。光线方面，一道来自正前方的明亮强光直射在人物面部与身体上，犹如相机的闪光灯直打，极大地凸显了人物皮肤、发丝、妆容亮片以及服饰的材质纹理；同时背景伴有柔和的影棚辅助布光。整体画面呈现出电影级别的质感与温暖的米棕色调，85mm镜头的视角带来了极具韩国时尚杂志内页大片氛围的视觉冲击力。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/item_1105_1.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "A hyper-realistic, high-quality close-up portrait photograph in landscape orientation. At the center of the frame is a young woman embodying Korean street fashion and modern chic. She has dark, voluminous long hair, meticulously braided into two high, artistically styled plaits that fall naturally above her ears. A few loose strands are casually secured by several uniquely shaped matte brown accent hair clips, while other wispy strands fall freely, artfully framing her cheeks. She wears a halter-neck top with a drawstring tie design. Perched on her nose bridge is a pair of thick-framed brown cat-eye glasses, deliberately pulled slightly low to reveal her soft hazel eyes. Her makeup is refined and artistic: brown artistic eyeliner, dewy peach-toned blush, soft warm-toned eyeshadow blended around the eyes, delicate pearlescent shimmer and glitter accenting the under-eye area and cheeks, lips coated in a glossy, plump red lip gloss, and skin presenting a naturally luminous, dewy \"glass skin\" finish, with facial pores and skin texture rendered in exquisite detail under ultra-high resolution. The woman's head is slightly tilted, her gaze relaxed yet confident as she looks directly into the camera, posing with one hand gently cradling her cheek. The background is a minimalist indoor studio setting; the landscape format allows generous beige and brown-toned background space on both sides of the subject, creating an elevated sense of negative space. In terms of lighting, a bright, direct light from the front illuminates the subject's face and body, akin to a camera flash fired head-on, dramatically accentuating the material textures of her skin, hair, makeup glitter, and clothing; simultaneously, soft studio fill lighting accompanies in the background. The overall image conveys a cinematic quality with a warm beige-brown tone, and the perspective of an 85mm lens delivers striking visual impact reminiscent of a Korean fashion magazine editorial spread.",
    "prompt_zh": "使用附带图片中的精确面部特征，创建一张超写实高质量的时尚年轻女性近景肖像。她浓密的深色长发扎成两个高高的艺术感编发辫子，垂落在耳侧，几缕松散的碎发用不同款式的哑光棕色造型发夹固定，几缕散落的发丝飘过并勾勒出她的脸庞。身穿抽绳挂脖上衣，佩戴粗框棕色猫眼眼镜微微下滑，柔和的榛子色眼眸，光泽感红色嘟嘟唇，蜜桃色水光腮红，搭配柔和暖色调眼影，略带闪粉和亮片。"
