    "title_en": "Hand-Drawn Fashion Style Concept Breakdown",
    "prompt": "A fashion-style concept breakdown sheet in hand-drawn illustration style. \nCenter: full-body view of a stylish, confident female character with a slightly sexy vibe (not explicit), in a dynamic yet natural pose. \nSurrounding: structured layout of her key components:\n• Clothing layering – show outerwear, innerwear, tights (lace, sheer textures), shapewear with detailed pattern zoom-ins.  \n• Expression sheet – 3-4 facial expressions (neutral, shy, surprised, focused).\n• Close-up zooms – textures of fabric folds, skin details, hand gestures.\n• Lifestyle & accessories – open handbag with daily items: lipstick, perfume, mirror compact, hand cream, diary, supplements.\n• Material annotations – handwritten-style notes beside each item (e.g., “soft lace,” “matte leather,” “shade #520”).\n\nBackground: soft beige or parchment paper texture to evoke a design sketchbook.\nLighting: clean, soft shadows to unify the scene.\nOutput: high-quality 2D illustration in 4K, balanced between sensuality and fashion editorial.\nLanguage: labels in Chinese + English.",
    "prompt_en": "A fashion-style concept breakdown sheet in hand-drawn illustration style. \nCenter: full-body view of a stylish, confident female character with a slightly sexy vibe (not explicit), in a dynamic yet natural pose. \nSurrounding: structured layout of her key components:\n• Clothing layering – show outerwear, innerwear, tights (lace, sheer textures), shapewear with detailed pattern zoom-ins.  \n• Expression sheet – 3-4 facial expressions (neutral, shy, surprised, focused).\n• Close-up zooms – textures of fabric folds, skin details, hand gestures.\n• Lifestyle & accessories – open handbag with daily items: lipstick, perfume, mirror compact, hand cream, diary, supplements.\n• Material annotations – handwritten-style notes beside each item (e.g., “soft lace,” “matte leather,” “shade #520”).\n\nBackground: soft beige or parchment paper texture to evoke a design sketchbook.\nLighting: clean, soft shadows to unify the scene.\nOutput: high-quality 2D illustration in 4K, balanced between sensuality and fashion editorial.\nLanguage: labels in Chinese + English.",
    "source": "https://x.com/cheerselflin/status/1992877077570453712",
    "type": "t2i",
    "author": "@cheerselflin",
    "author_link": "https://x.com/cheerselflin/status/1992877077570453712",
    "revised_prompt": "一幅手绘插画风格的时尚概念拆解图，采用竖版构图。背景为柔和的米色羊皮纸纹理，带有轻微的纸张纤维细节，营造出高级设计手稿簿的质感。整体光线干净、阴影柔和，画面呈现高质量的2D时尚杂志插图质感，完美平衡了高级感与微性感的氛围。\n\n画面中央是一幅时尚女性角色的全身像。她姿态自然且富有动态，重心落在右腿，左手轻插在裤兜中，右手微微抬起撩拨耳侧的波浪长发，散发出自信的魅力。她外穿一件剪裁利落的卡其色中长款收腰风衣，内搭一件黑色半透视植物花纹蕾丝紧身打底衫，隐约透出肌肤纹理；下半身穿着高腰修身哑光皮裤，勾勒出流畅的腿部线条，脚踩一双黑色尖头细跟短靴。\n\n围绕着中心人物，四周分布着结构化的拆解图块与手写体标注，所有标注文字均由细线指向对应的部位，文字采用黑灰色手写字体，中英双语。\n\n左上角为表情板区域，包含四个并排的头部特写：\n第一个表情神情平淡自信，嘴角微扬，旁注文字：'Neutral / 中性'。\n第二个表情脸颊微红，视线微垂，旁注文字：'Shy / 害羞'。\n第三个表情眼眸睁大，嘴唇微张，旁注文字：'Surprised / 惊讶'。\n第四个表情眼神锐利，眉头微蹙，旁注文字：'Focused / 专注'。\n\n左侧及左下角展示服装叠穿与面料特写：\n一个圆形放大图展示风衣袖口的束带与缝线，旁注文字：'Gabardine fabric / 华达呢面料'。\n一个微距放大圈展示内搭打底衫的细腻蕾丝网眼与花型，旁注文字：'Soft lace with floral pattern / 柔软植物纹蕾丝'。\n一个矩形画框展示皮裤表面的微光泽起伏，旁注文字：'Matte leather / 哑光皮革'。\n一幅手部特写，展示修长手指与佩戴的银色关节戒指，旁注文字：'Silver ring details / 银质戒指细节'。\n\n右侧上方为皮肤质感特写：\n展现肩颈与锁骨部位平滑的肌肤阴影，旁注文字：'Skin details & collarbone / 皮肤细节与锁骨'。\n\n右下角为生活方式与配饰区：\n绘制了一只敞开的黑色半月形皮质包，旁注文字：'Classic hobo bag / 经典腋下包'。\n包的旁边散落排列着日常物品：\n一支旋出红色的口红，旁注文字：'Shade #520 / 色号 #520'。\n一瓶透明方形玻璃香水，旁注文字：'Floral perfume / 花香调香水'。\n一个带有小镜子的圆形翻盖粉饼，旁注文字：'Matte compact / 哑光粉饼'。\n一支金属管状护手霜，旁注文字：'Rose hand cream / 玫瑰护手霜'。\n一本绑有细带的日记本，旁注文字：'Leather diary / 皮质日记本'。\n一瓶小巧的胶囊药瓶，旁注文字：'Vitamin C / 维生素C'。\n\n整体排版紧凑有序，视觉引导清晰，各组件比例协调，完美适配竖屏布局。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/item_1172_1.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "A hand-drawn illustration-style fashion concept breakdown sheet in portrait orientation. The background features a soft beige parchment paper texture with subtle paper fiber details, evoking the quality of a high-end design sketchbook. The overall lighting is clean with soft shadows, and the image presents a high-quality 2D fashion magazine illustration aesthetic, perfectly balancing sophistication with a subtly sensual atmosphere.\n\nAt the center of the composition is a full-body illustration of a fashionable female character. Her pose is natural yet dynamic, with her weight on her right leg, left hand casually tucked into a trouser pocket, and right hand slightly raised to brush aside the wavy long hair near her ear, exuding confident charm. She wears a sharply tailored khaki mid-length belted trench coat over a black semi-sheer botanical floral lace fitted base layer that subtly reveals skin texture beneath; on the lower half, high-waisted slim-fit matte leather pants that outline smooth leg contours, and black pointed-toe stiletto ankle boots.\n\nSurrounding the central figure are structured breakdown panels and handwritten annotations distributed around the periphery, with all annotation text connected to corresponding areas by thin lines, rendered in dark gray handwritten font, bilingual in Chinese and English.\n\nThe upper left corner features an expression board area containing four side-by-side head close-ups:\nThe first expression is calm and confident with slightly upturned corners of the mouth, annotated: 'Neutral / 中性.'\nThe second expression shows slightly flushed cheeks with a slightly downcast gaze, annotated: 'Shy / 害羞.'\nThe third expression has widened eyes and slightly parted lips, annotated: 'Surprised / 惊讶.'\nThe fourth expression features a sharp gaze with slightly furrowed brows, annotated: 'Focused / 专注.'\n\nThe left side and lower left corner display layered clothing and fabric close-ups:\nA circular magnified view shows the trench coat cuff's buckle strap and stitching, annotated: 'Gabardine fabric / 华达呢面料.'\nA micro-magnification circle shows the delicate lace mesh and floral pattern of the inner base layer, annotated: 'Soft lace with floral pattern / 柔软植物纹蕾丝.'\nA rectangular frame shows the subtle sheen and surface undulation of the leather pants, annotated: 'Matte leather / 哑光皮革.'\nA hand close-up displays slender fingers wearing silver knuckle rings, annotated: 'Silver ring details / 银质戒指细节.'\n\nThe upper right side features a skin texture close-up:\nDisplaying the smooth skin shadows of the shoulder, neck, and collarbone area, annotated: 'Sk",
    "prompt_zh": "一张时尚风格的角色概念拆解图，采用手绘插画风格。中心：一个时尚自信的女性角色全身视图，略带性感气息（非露骨），姿态动感而自然。周围：她的关键组成部分的结构化布局：\n• 服装分层——展示外套、内搭、紧身袜（蕾丝、透明质感）、塑身衣，配有详细的图案放大细节。\n• 表情图谱——3-4种面部表情（自然、害羞、惊讶、专注）。\n• 特写放大——织物褶皱纹理、皮肤细节、手部姿态。\n• 生活方式与配饰——打开的手提包，内有日常物品。"
