    "revised_prompt": "这是一张竖版比例（9:16）的可爱时尚日历插画，整体呈现清新明亮的水彩手绘质感，色彩鲜艳且柔和。背景为纯白色的极简空间，没有任何多余的装饰元素，以充分凸显主体人物与文字内容。画面居中略偏右的位置是一位年轻时尚的女性角色，她的身形比例略微夸张，头部稍大，腰部纤细，拥有水汪汪的大眼睛和圆润红润的脸颊，面带灿烂的笑容。人物姿态活泼俏皮，左手在脸颊旁举起比着“V”字手势，右手轻轻握着包带。为了体现北京秋季的本地化特色与季节感，角色身穿明黄色的秋季针织开衫，内搭白色高领毛衣，下身穿着红色格纹短裙。她的头上戴着一顶白色的毛绒针织贝雷帽，鼻梁上架着一副复古的圆形金边眼镜，脖子上系着一条印有抽象长城图案的丝巾，身上斜挎着一个带有糖葫芦图案的红色小巧包包。画面的文字部分排版整洁，留白均衡。在画面顶部中央的位置，有巨大且醒目的公历日期数字 '24'。在 '24' 的正下方是英文月份 'OCTOBER'，英文月份下方是年份数字 '2024'。在顶部数字的左右两侧呈对称布局：左侧写有清晰优雅的字体 '星期四' 以及下方的英文 'Thursday'；右侧写有 '农历九月廿二' 以及节气 '霜降'。在画面的左侧留白区域，垂直排列着粗体毛笔手写风格的中文 '宜 赏秋'，字号较大；在 '宜 赏秋' 的右侧，同样以垂直排版的方式，写有一行稍小的匹配手写体励志名言 '保持热爱，奔赴山海'。所有文字清晰可见，不与人物插图重叠或遮挡。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/item_1175_4.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "This is a cute and fashionable calendar illustration in portrait ratio (9:16), presenting an overall fresh and bright watercolor hand-drawn texture with vivid yet soft colors. The background is a pure white minimalist space without any superfluous decorative elements, fully highlighting the main character and text content. Positioned slightly right of center is a young, fashionable female character with slightly exaggerated body proportions—a somewhat oversized head, a slender waist, large dewy eyes, and round rosy cheeks, wearing a radiant smile. Her pose is lively and playful: her left hand is raised beside her cheek making a \"V\" sign, while her right hand gently holds a bag strap. To reflect the localized characteristics and seasonal feel of autumn in Beijing, the character wears a bright yellow autumn knit cardigan over a white turtleneck sweater, paired with a red plaid mini skirt. On her head she wears a white fluffy knitted beret, on the bridge of her nose sits a pair of vintage round gold-rimmed glasses, around her neck is tied a silk scarf printed with an abstract Great Wall pattern, and she carries a small red crossbody bag adorned with a tanghulu (candied hawthorn) motif. The text layout is neat and well-balanced with even white space. At the top center of the image is the large and prominent Gregorian calendar date number '24'. Directly below '24' is the English month 'OCTOBER', and below the English month is the year '2024'. On both sides of the top numerals, arranged symmetrically: the left side displays '星期四' in a clear and elegant font with 'Thursday' beneath it; the right side displays '农历九月廿二' along with the solar term '霜降' (Frost's Descent). In the left white space area of the image, the bold brush-written calligraphic style Chinese characters '宜 赏秋' (Auspicious for Enjoying Autumn) are arranged vertically in a relatively large font size; to the right of '宜 赏秋', also in vertical layout, is a slightly smaller matching handwritten inspirational quote '保持热爱，奔赴山海' (Stay passionate, venture toward mountains and seas). All text is clearly legible and does not overlap with or obscure the character illustration.",
    "prompt_zh": "请创建一张可爱、时尚的日历插画，采用竖版（9:16）布局，风格清新明亮，手绘质感：\n\n插画要求：\n\n- 主角是一位年轻时尚的女性，具有可爱活泼的水彩或手绘质感，色彩鲜艳而柔和。\n- 角色特征包括大眼睛、圆润红润的脸颊，以及大胆时尚的配饰（如太阳镜、圆环耳环、头巾、发箍、蝴蝶结、针织帽等）。服装色彩鲜明，姿态活泼俏皮。比例可适度夸张（如大头、纤腰）。"
