    "revised_prompt": "一张竖版比例的3D微缩卡通风格等距视角（Isometric）渲染图，融合了UI界面元素。画面采用45度俯视视角，构图居中且极简，背景为柔和纯净的淡浅蓝色纯色，整体视觉风格清新、舒缓。画面中央是一组精美细腻的上海标志性建筑群微缩模型，主要包括带有反光金属与玻璃球体质感的东方明珠电视塔、呈优美螺旋上升形态的上海中心大厦、特征鲜明的环球金融中心以及金茂大厦。建筑模型建模精确，采用写实的PBR材质，展现出柔软精致的纹理与逼真的光影反射。场景设定为多云转晴的天气，天气元素被创造性地立体化并融入城市景观中：几团柔软、蓬松的立体白色卡通云朵漂浮并穿插在摩天大楼之间，部分云层环绕着高塔的塔腰。柔和逼真的阳光从侧上方倾洒，为建筑和云朵边缘镀上温暖的高光，并在微缩的黄浦江面和建筑间投下柔和的阴影，营造出沉浸式的动态互动氛围。画面顶部居中位置悬浮着排版整洁的天气UI信息，文字和图标无背景，与下方建筑的塔尖轻微重叠。最上方是大字号的中文城市名称：'上海'；正下方是一个精致突出的3D天气图标，展示一轮圆润的金色太阳半掩在一朵白云之后；图标下方紧接着中等字号的温度范围文本：'18°C - 24°C'；最底部是超小字号的日期文本：'10月24日 星期四'。所有文字均采用清晰的无衬线字体，排版干净统一。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/item_1179_3.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "A portrait-ratio 3D miniature cartoon-style isometric rendering that incorporates UI interface elements. The scene is viewed from a 45-degree overhead angle with a centered, minimalist composition against a soft, pure, light pale blue solid-color background, creating an overall fresh and soothing visual style. At the center of the image is a set of exquisitely detailed miniature models of Shanghai's iconic landmark buildings, primarily including the Oriental Pearl TV Tower with reflective metallic and glass sphere textures, the Shanghai Tower in its gracefully spiraling upward form, the distinctively shaped Shanghai World Financial Center, and the Jin Mao Tower. The architectural models are precisely modeled with realistic PBR materials, showcasing soft and refined textures with lifelike light and shadow reflections. The scene is set in partly cloudy turning sunny weather, with weather elements creatively rendered in 3D and integrated into the cityscape: several soft, fluffy, three-dimensional white cartoon clouds float and intersperse among the skyscrapers, with some cloud layers wrapping around the midsections of the towers. Soft, realistic sunlight cascades from the upper side, gilding the edges of buildings and clouds with warm highlights and casting gentle shadows on the miniature Huangpu River surface and between buildings, creating an immersive, dynamically interactive atmosphere. Centered at the top of the image, neatly typeset weather UI information floats with no background behind the text and icons, slightly overlapping with the spires of the buildings below. At the very top is the Chinese city name in large font: '上海' (Shanghai); directly below is a prominent, refined 3D weather icon showing a round golden sun half-hidden behind a white cloud; immediately below the icon is the temperature range text in medium font: '18°C - 24°C'; at the very bottom is the date text in extra-small font: '10月24日 星期四' (October 24, Thursday). All text uses a clear sans-serif typeface with clean, unified typography.",
    "prompt_zh": "呈现一个清晰的45°俯视角竖版（9:16）等距微缩3D卡通场景，突出标志性地标居中构图，展示精确而精致的建模。\n\n场景采用柔和细腻的质感，配以逼真的PBR材质，以及柔和、自然的光影效果。天气元素巧妙融入城市建筑之中，在城市景观与大气条件之间建立动态交互，营造沉浸式的天气氛围。\n\n采用干净统一的构图，极简美学风格，柔和、纯色。"
