    "revised_prompt_en": "A close-up portrait photograph in portrait ratio. The main subject is a young woman standing on a beach at dusk. Her dark hair is tousled by the sea breeze, with a few strands casually sweeping across her face. The woman's skin texture is natural and realistic, with a subtle flush and a delicate film grain quality. She wears a white thin spaghetti-strap top on her upper body, paired with denim bottoms. Behind the woman is the deep, dark ocean waves and a moody sky, with soft twilight hues blending across it—interweaving gray-pink, blue-gray, and gentle lavender tones, creating a tranquil ambient atmosphere. The image employs a portrait close-up composition with the focal point concentrated on the woman's face and upper body. The overall visual presents a low-saturation, cool-toned cinematic film style with soft natural dusk lighting and gentle contrast. The image carries a layer of hazy atmosphere and slight film grain, exuding a rich melancholic mood. The image details are extremely lifelike, exhibiting 8K-level ultra-high resolution.",
    "prompt_zh": "一位年轻女性黄昏时分站在海滩上，以柔和感性的胶片风格肖像拍摄。\n她的深色头发被海风吹得凌乱，发丝飘过脸庞。\n她的皮肤自然、微微泛红，带有细腻的颗粒质感。\n身穿白色细肩带背心和牛仔下装。\n背景是深色的海浪和情绪感的天空，带有柔和的日落色彩——灰粉色、蓝灰色和低饱和的薰衣草紫。\n整体画面采用低饱和度、冷色调的电影胶片滤镜，具有柔和对比度、轻微颗粒感和朦胧氛围。\n近景肖像，忧郁情绪，自然风格。"
