    "prompt": "1998 年的一张业余照片，照片中一位中年艺术家正在用手将电脑屏幕上的图像复制到绷紧的画布上的油画中，但图像本身却是这位艺术家绘制递归图像时的照片。",
    "prompt_en": "An amateur photograph from 1998 showing a middle-aged artist using their hands to copy an image from a computer screen onto an oil painting on a stretched canvas, but the image itself is a photo of this artist painting the recursive image.",
