ieve twice the results with half the effort—express your creativity boldly.)\n'财运：偏财运不错，但切忌冲动消费，适合做长线理财规划。' (Wealth Fortune: Windfall luck is good, but avoid impulsive spending; it is suitable for long-term financial planning.)\n'幸运色：燕麦色' (Lucky Color: Oatmeal)\n'幸运数字：7' (Lucky Number: 7)\nThe overall layout is well-arranged with staggered elements, richly combining illustrations and text. The hand-drawn lines are fluid and natural, the colors are warm and comfortable, the lighting is soft, and the details are abundant with extremely high clarity, exuding a literary and fresh atmosphere.",
