    "revised_prompt": "横版构图的夜晚街头摄影照片，展现出强烈的2000年代初Y2K美学和原始的狗仔队抓拍风格。画面中央，一名年轻女子站在一台复古的金属公共付费电话旁。她背对电话机，身体微侧，正越过肩膀转头直视镜头，眼神冷漠且疏离。女子穿着一件修身的黑色紧身胸衣（corset top），下身搭配一条宽松的低腰工装牛仔裤，双手插在牛仔裤的后口袋里，姿态随性且不羁。她的面容清晰真实，五官立体，妆容带有千禧年特征，如细挑的眉毛和带有光泽的唇蜜，长直发略带凌乱感。\n\n背景是夜晚的城市街头，在强烈的机顶直打闪光灯作用下，人物主体被高光照亮，并在身后的电话亭和墙壁上投射出清晰、硬朗的黑色阴影。背景迅速变暗，呈现出极高的高光与阴影对比度。远处是失焦的城市夜景，带有模糊、拉长的彩色车灯轨迹（红、黄、白相间的散景光斑），营造出喧嚣且动感的城市夜晚氛围。画面的右下角有一个发光的复古红色数字时间戳，清晰显示着文本 '11 05 2001'。整体画面带有胶片颗粒感和粗糙质感，完美复刻了早期数码相机在夜晚强闪光灯下的生猛视觉效果。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/item_1327_1.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "A landscape-oriented nighttime street photography shot with a strong early-2000s Y2K aesthetic and raw paparazzi-style candid look. At the center of the frame, a young woman stands beside a vintage metallic public payphone. She has her back to the phone, her body slightly angled, turning her head over her shoulder to look directly into the camera with a cold and detached gaze. The woman wears a fitted black corset top paired with loose, low-rise cargo jeans, both hands tucked into the back pockets of the jeans, her posture casual and rebellious. Her face is clear and realistic with well-defined features, her makeup bearing millennial hallmarks such as thinly arched eyebrows and glossy lip gloss, and her long straight hair has a slightly tousled look.\n\nThe background is a nighttime city street. Under the harsh on-camera direct flash, the subject is brightly illuminated, casting sharp, hard-edged black shadows onto the phone booth and the wall behind her. The background falls off rapidly into darkness, producing an extremely high highlight-to-shadow contrast. In the distance, the out-of-focus city nightscape features blurred, elongated streaks of colorful car lights (bokeh spots of red, yellow, and white intermingled), creating a bustling and dynamic urban nighttime atmosphere. In the lower-right corner of the frame, a glowing retro red digital timestamp clearly displays the text '11 05 2001'. The overall image carries a film grain and gritty texture, perfectly replicating the raw visual effect of early digital cameras shooting at night with a strong flash.",
    "prompt_zh": "夜间闪光灯照片，Y2K美学风格，角落带有红色数码时间戳。一位年轻女性站在公共电话亭旁，面容基于上传的图片，回头望向镜头，眼神疏离。身穿束腰上衣和宽松工装牛仔裤，双手插在后口袋里。强烈的闪光灯对比度和城市背景中模糊的车灯光线，原始的2000年代初期狗仔队拍摄风格。"
