    "revised_prompt": "一幅高分辨率的逼真摄影肖像，采用横版构图。在阳光明媚的白天，一位年轻女性坐在游泳池的边缘。她拥有一头蓬松的长卷发，头发的一侧别着一枚精致的白色花朵发夹。她身穿一套复古风格的两件套：上身是一件白色无袖短款上衣，布满淡雅的天蓝色花卉印花，并配有醒目的天蓝色翻领和正面的蝴蝶结；下半身穿着与上衣图案匹配的迷你裙。她面带柔和的表情，目光直视镜头。背景中，宽阔且明亮湛蓝的池水在阳光下波光粼粼，远处是呈现模糊景深效果的热带绿色植物。画面采用明亮且自然的电影级光影，阳光在水面上形成高光折射，并细致地勾勒出人物的发丝纹理、面部轮廓以及服装面料的印花细节，整体色彩明快，充满夏日的清新氛围。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/item_1334_3.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "A high-resolution, realistic photographic portrait in landscape orientation. On a bright, sunny day, a young woman sits at the edge of a swimming pool. She has voluminous long curly hair with a delicate white flower hair clip pinned to one side. She wears a vintage-style two-piece set: the top is a white sleeveless cropped blouse covered in subtle sky-blue floral prints, featuring a prominent sky-blue fold-over collar and a bow at the front; the bottom is a mini skirt with a pattern matching the top. She has a soft expression on her face, gazing directly into the camera. In the background, the expansive and vivid azure pool water shimmers and sparkles under the sunlight, with tropical green foliage rendered in a blurred depth-of-field effect in the distance. The image employs bright and natural cinematic lighting; sunlight creates specular reflections on the water surface and meticulously delineates the texture of the subject's hair strands, facial contours, and the printed details of the fabric, resulting in an overall bright color palette brimming with a fresh, summery atmosphere.",
    "prompt_zh": "一张高质量写实风格的年轻女性肖像，她坐在晴天游泳池边缘。她拥有蓬松的长卷发，一侧用白色花朵发夹装饰。她穿着一套复古风格的配套两件套：白色无袖短上衣，饰有精致的天蓝色碎花印花，搭配醒目的天蓝色带蝴蝶结领口，以及一条配套迷你短裙。她直视镜头，表情柔和。背景是明亮的蓝色粼粼泳池水面和模糊的热带绿植。光线明亮自然，突显细节。"
