    "author_link": "https://x.com/M_w14_/status/1912146666410459618",
    "revised_prompt": "逼真的护照内页微距特写照片，采用横向构图。画面主体是一页展现出真实质感的护照纸张，表面有着清晰可见的细腻纤维纹理和微微起伏的自然纸张形态。纸张背景印有复杂的安全防伪图案，由浅蓝色、淡绿色和浅粉色交织的精细波浪线条以及细微的几何底纹构成。画面的视觉中心是一个醒目的圆形入境章，以略带晕染的深红色墨水印在护照页上。印章整体向右略微倾斜约15度，呈现出如同人工用力压印的真实效果，部分墨水由于浸入纸张纤维而呈现边缘轻微不规则和断点的质感。印章的最外围是一个由精细线条组成的带有装饰性的圆环边框。在印章内侧的上半部分，以粗体英文沿圆弧排列着 'WELCOME TO BEIJING' 字样；内侧下半部分沿圆弧排列着 'BEIJING, CHINA'。印章中央的背景中，巧妙地融入了故宫标志性古建筑的微妙轮廓剪影作为背景细节。在故宫轮廓的正前方，横向排布着醒目的粗体英文字母 'ARRIVAL'，其正下方印有清晰的日期字样 'APR 16 2025'。画面的光线柔和自然，微弱的侧光完美凸显了纸张的微观纹理与红色墨水的印迹深度，整体风格极其写实，色彩对比清晰且真实。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/item_13_4.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "A realistic macro close-up photograph of a passport interior page in landscape orientation. The main subject is a passport page exhibiting authentic texture, with clearly visible fine fiber grain and a subtly undulating natural paper surface. The paper background is printed with intricate security anti-counterfeiting patterns composed of interwoven fine wavy lines in light blue, pale green, and light pink, along with subtle geometric underprints. The visual center of the frame is a prominent circular entry stamp, pressed onto the passport page in slightly smudged dark red ink. The stamp is tilted slightly to the right by approximately 15 degrees, presenting the realistic effect of being manually pressed with force; some of the ink, having seeped into the paper fibers, exhibits slightly irregular edges and broken points in texture. The outermost ring of the stamp is a decorative circular border composed of fine lines. On the upper inner half of the stamp, the words 'WELCOME TO BEIJING' are arranged in bold English along the arc; on the lower inner half, 'BEIJING, CHINA' is arranged along the arc. In the central background of the stamp, the subtle silhouette outline of the Forbidden City's iconic classical architecture is artfully incorporated as a background detail. Directly in front of the Forbidden City silhouette, the bold English letters 'ARRIVAL' are arranged horizontally in a prominent manner, with the clearly printed date 'APR 16 2025' directly beneath it. The lighting in the image is soft and natural, with faint side lighting perfectly accentuating the microscopic texture of the paper and the depth of the red ink impression. The overall style is extremely realistic, with clear and authentic color contrast.",
    "prompt_zh": "创建一个逼真的护照页，并盖上[北京, 中国]的入境章。章面应以粗体英文写明“欢迎来到北京”，并设计成圆形或椭圆形，并带有装饰性边框。章面应包含“ARRIVAL”字样和一个虚构的日期，例如“2025年4月16日”。在章面中加入{故宫}的微妙轮廓作为背景细节。使用深蓝色或红色墨水并略加晕染，以增强真实感。章面应略微倾斜，如同手工压印。护照页应清晰可见纸张纹理和安全图案。"
