    "title": "生成角色设定",
    "title_en": "Character Design Generation",
    "prompt": "为我生成人物的角色设定（Character Design）\n\n比例设定（不同身高对比、头身比等）\n\n三视图（正面、侧面、背面）\n\n表情设定（Expression Sheet） → 就是你发的那种图\n\n动作设定（Pose Sheet） → 各种常见姿势\n\n服装设定（Costume Design）",
    "prompt_en": "Generate a character design for my character (Character Design)\n\nProportion reference sheet (different height comparisons, head-to-body ratios, etc.)\n\nThree-view sheet (front, side, back)\n\nExpression Sheet → the kind of sheet you posted\n\nPose Sheet → various common poses\n\nCostume Design",
    "source": "https://x.com/ZHO_ZHO_ZHO/status/1960669234276753542",
    "type": "t2i",
    "author": "@ZHO_ZHO_ZHO",
    "author_link": "https://x.com/ZHO_ZHO_ZHO/status/1960669234276753542",
    "revised_prompt": "一张垂直画幅的动漫风格角色设定图（Character Design Sheet），背景为带有浅灰色网格的羊皮纸质感，画面内容从上到下排版紧凑且结构清晰。设定角色为一位蒸汽朋克风奇幻女魔法师，拥有银色长发（编成松散的侧麻花辫）和翠绿色的眼睛。\n\n画面最上方有粗体黑色大标题 'CHARACTER DESIGN: ELARA'，下方是副标题 'CLASS: ARCANE MECHANIC'。\n\n第一部分（顶部区域）：三视图与比例设定。左侧有一个垂直的标尺刻度，包含等距的水平辅助线，标注着 'HEIGHT: 165CM' 和 '7 HEADS TALL'。区域中央是角色的正面站姿全身图，左侧为左侧面全身图，右侧为背面全身图。三幅图的下方分别标注着 'FRONT'、'SIDE' 和 'BACK'。\n\n第二部分（中上区域）：服装设定细节展示。画面抽出并放大了角色的三处装备细节：头顶佩戴的黄铜护目镜，旁边配有文字注解 'BRASS GOGGLES'；腰间的暗棕色皮革挎包和一颗发光的蓝色魔法水晶，标注文字 'LEATHER SATCHEL' 与 'MAGIC CRYSTAL'；以及带有齿轮装饰的高筒系带皮靴，标注 'GEARED LEATHER BOOTS'。\n\n第三部分（中下区域）：表情设定。横向排列着五个角色的头部特写，从左到右依次展示不同的面部表情：平静（标注 'NEUTRAL'，面无表情直视前方）、开怀大笑（标注 'JOY'，眼睛微闭，露出牙齿）、愤怒（标注 'ANGER'，眉头紧锁，咬牙切齿）、悲伤流泪（标注 'SORROW'，眼眶含泪，嘴角下撇）以及惊讶（标注 'SHOCK'，双眼圆睁，嘴巴微张）。\n\n第四部分（底部区域）：动作设定。展示了三个不同视角的全身动态姿势。左侧是施法动作，角色手持一根顶端镶嵌蓝色水晶的金属法杖，水晶发光，披风和衣摆向后飘动，下方标注 'CASTING SPELL'；中间是放松姿态，角色单手叉腰，另一只手把玩着一枚护目镜，下方标注 'RELAXED'；右侧是战斗准备姿态，角色重心压低，双手紧握法杖横在胸前，眼神锐利，下方标注 'COMBAT STANCE'。\n\n整体色调以暖色调的复古棕色、黄铜色、深蓝色为主，辅以水晶的亮蓝色作为点缀。角色采用清晰流畅的黑色线稿勾勒，赛璐珞平涂上色风格，阴影边缘明确，光线均匀无死角，完全符合标准的2D动画或游戏角色概念设计图规范。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/item_164_3.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "A vertical-format anime-style character design sheet (Character Design Sheet) with a parchment-textured background featuring a light gray grid. The content is arranged from top to bottom in a compact yet clearly structured layout. The character is a steampunk-style fantasy female mage with long silver hair (braided into a loose side fishtail braid) and emerald green eyes.\n\nAt the very top of the image is a bold black main title 'CHARACTER DESIGN: ELARA', with a subtitle below reading 'CLASS: ARCANE MECHANIC'.\n\nPart One (Top Area): Three-view orthographic and proportion reference. On the left side is a vertical ruler scale with evenly spaced horizontal guide lines, annotated with 'HEIGHT: 165CM' and '7 HEADS TALL'. In the center of the area is the character's front-facing standing full-body view, with the left side view on the left and the back view on the right. Below the three drawings are the respective labels 'FRONT', 'SIDE', and 'BACK'.\n\nPart Two (Upper-Middle Area): Costume and equipment detail showcase. Three enlarged detail callouts of the character's equipment are presented: brass goggles worn on top of the head, accompanied by the text annotation 'BRASS GOGGLES'; a dark brown leather satchel at the waist alongside a glowing blue magic crystal, annotated 'LEATHER SATCHEL' and 'MAGIC CRYSTAL'; and tall lace-up leather boots with gear decorations, annotated 'GEARED LEATHER BOOTS'.\n\nPart Three (Lower-Middle Area): Expression sheet. Five head close-ups of the character are arranged horizontally, displaying different facial expressions from left to right: calm (annotated 'NEUTRAL', expressionless gaze directed forward), hearty laughter (annotated 'JOY', eyes slightly closed, teeth showing), anger (annotated 'ANGER', brows tightly furrowed, teeth clenched), sorrowful tears (annotated 'SORROW', eyes brimming with tears, corners of the mouth turned down), and surprise (annotated 'SHOCK', eyes wide open, mouth slightly agape).\n\nPart Four (Bottom Area): Action poses. Three dynamic full-body poses from different angles are displayed. On the left is a spellcasting action, with the character holding a metal staff topped with a glowing blue crystal, cape and garment hems billowing backward, annotated below as 'CASTING",
    "prompt_zh": "为我生成人物的角色设定（Character Design）\n\n比例设定（不同身高对比、头身比等）\n\n三视图（正面、侧面、背面）\n\n表情设定（Expression Sheet） → 就是你发的那种图\n\n动作设定（Pose Sheet） → 各种常见姿势\n\n服装设定（Costume Design）"
