    "prompt_en": "Create an infographic of the world's five tallest buildings for me / Create a colorful infographic about the sweetest things on Earth.",
    "source": "https://x.com/icreatelife/status/1962998951948517428",
    "type": "t2i",
    "author": "@icreatelife",
    "author_link": "https://x.com/icreatelife/status/1962998951948517428",
    "revised_prompt": "一张关于地球上最甜蜜事物的彩色信息图海报，采用适合竖向显示的排版比例。画面整体采用现代扁平化与轻微3D立体感结合的矢量插画风格，背景是柔和的马卡龙色系渐变（由顶部的淡粉色逐渐过渡到中部的薄荷绿，再到底部的奶油黄）。各个信息区块之间使用粉白色的波浪形奶油状线条分隔，背景中零星散落着彩色的纸屑、微小的马卡龙和棒棒糖图案作为点缀，画面光线明亮、色调鲜艳且对比度高。\n\n画面顶部占据15%的空间为标题区：正中央印有大字号的3D奶油滴落效果艺术字体主标题 'SWEETEST THINGS'，下方紧跟副标题 'ON EARTH'。副标题下方有一行居中排版的小号说明文字：'A colorful guide to nature and human-made sweetness'。\n\n画面自上而下分为五个具体的信息区块：\n第一个区块在画面左侧绘制了一个晶莹剔透的琥珀色蜂蜜罐，罐子上贴着 'HONEY' 的标签，罐口插着一根木制蜂蜜搅拌棒，边缘有金黄色的蜂蜜滴落，旁边有一只飞舞的小蜜蜂。右侧为对齐的文字块，包含加粗标题 '1. Honey' 和正文说明：'Produced by bees from floral nectar, it is one of the oldest natural sweeteners known to humanity.'\n\n第二个区块在画面右侧绘制了两根带有竹节细节的翠绿甘蔗，以及底部堆积的白色糖晶体。左侧为对应的文字块，包含标题 '2. Sugarcane' 和正文内容：'A tall perennial grass that provides the majority of the world's commercial sugar.'\n\n第三个区块在左侧绘制了一颗带有绿叶的鲜红诱人草莓和一个切开成网格状的金黄色芒果。右侧文字块包含标题 '3. Sweet Fruits' 和正文：'Nature's candy, offering fructose paired with vitamins and vibrant flavors.'\n\n第四个区块在右侧绘制了一个带有华夫饼纹理的三层冰淇淋蛋筒（包含粉色草莓、白色香草、棕色巧克力口味，表面撒满彩色糖珠），旁边配有一朵巨大的粉蓝相间云朵状棉花糖。左侧文字块包含标题 '4. Desserts & Candies' 和正文：'Human creations that bring joy and pure sugar rush through colorful confections.'\n\n第五个区块位于靠近底部的居中位置，绘制了一片带有高光效果的鲜绿色甜菊叶。叶片下方居中排列着文字块，标题为 '5. Stevia'，正文内容为：'A natural plant extract that is 200 to 300 times sweeter than regular table sugar, with zero calories!'\n\n海报的最底部角落以深灰色小字印有数据来源脚注：'Data: Global Sweet Index 2024'。整个画面结构紧凑、逻辑清晰，将视觉插画与排版文字完美结合。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/item_179_1.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "A colorful infographic poster about the sweetest things on Earth, with a layout ratio suitable for vertical display. The overall visual adopts a modern flat design combined with a slight 3D dimensional feel in a vector illustration style. The background features a soft macaron color gradient (transitioning from light pink at the top to mint green in the middle, then to cream yellow at the bottom). The information blocks are separated by pink-white wavy cream-like lines, with colorful confetti, tiny macarons, and lollipop motifs scattered sparsely across the background as embellishments. The image is brightly lit with vivid, high-contrast tones.\n\nThe top 15% of the image is the title area: at the center in large font is the main title 'SWEETEST THINGS' rendered in a 3D cream-dripping effect art typeface, with the subtitle 'ON EARTH' directly below. Beneath the subtitle is a centered line of small descriptive text: 'A colorful guide to nature and human-made sweetness'.\n\nThe image is divided from top to bottom into five specific information blocks:\nThe first block features a crystal-clear amber-colored honey jar illustrated on the left side, with a 'HONEY' label affixed to the jar, a wooden honey dipper inserted at the jar's opening, golden honey dripping along the edge, and a small bee flying nearby. On the right is an aligned text block containing the bold title '1. Honey' and body text: 'Produced by bees from floral nectar, it is one of the oldest natural sweeteners known to humanity.'\n\nThe second block features two emerald-green sugarcanes with bamboo-joint details illustrated on the right side, with white sugar crystals piled at the bottom. On the left is the corresponding text block containing the title '2. Sugarcane' and body text: 'A tall perennial grass that provides the majority of the world's commercial sugar.'\n\nThe third block features a fresh, enticing red strawberry with green leaves and a golden mango cut into a crosshatch pattern illustrated on the left side. The right text block contains the title '3. Sweet Fru",
