    "title_en": "Light & Shadow Control",
    "prompt": "图一人物变成图二光影，深色为暗",
    "prompt_en": "Turn the person in Image 1 into the lighting and shadow style of Image 2, with dark areas as shadows.",
    "source": "https://x.com/ZHO_ZHO_ZHO/status/1961779457372602725",
    "type": "t2i",
    "author": "@ZHO_ZHO_ZHO",
    "author_link": "https://x.com/ZHO_ZHO_ZHO/status/1961779457372602725",
    "revised_prompt": "一幅具有强烈的明暗对比（Chiaroscuro）效果的电影级艺术摄影画面。画面采用横向宽幅构图，深邃的纯黑色构成了大面积的背景与人物暗部，完美体现了“深色为暗”的光影基调。画面右侧偏中位置是一位年轻女性的半身特写，她半侧身向左，面容微微上扬，眼神深邃地望向光源方向。她留着微卷的深色及肩发，身穿一件质感细腻的深色外套，身体轮廓大部分隐没在深沉的阴影之中。一束明亮且锐利的硬质光线从画面左上方倾斜投射而下，穿透类似于百叶窗的物理遮挡，在人物的侧脸、脖颈以及左侧空旷的深色背景上，切分出清晰、平行的斜向几何条纹光影。受光面呈现出带有电影质感的温暖琥珀色调，高光精准勾勒出她挺拔的鼻梁、清澈的眼眸和柔和的下颌边缘；而未被光线触及的区域则瞬间过渡并融入极致的纯黑色暗部，形成了极具视觉冲击力的光影切割效果。画面左侧的深色空间中，光影的条纹逐渐变弱消散，营造出深邃的空间延伸感。整体画质清晰锐利，光影过渡干脆，充满神秘与戏剧性的艺术氛围。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/item_195_4.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "A cinematic art photography image with a strong chiaroscuro effect. The composition is in a horizontal wide-format layout, where deep pure black constitutes a large area of the background and the dark portions of the figure, perfectly embodying the \"dark-as-shadow\" tonal foundation. Positioned slightly off-center to the right of the frame is a half-body close-up of a young woman. She is turned half sideways to the left, her face slightly upturned, her deep gaze directed toward the light source. She has slightly wavy, dark, shoulder-length hair and wears a finely textured dark coat, with most of her body contour submerged in deep shadow. A bright, sharp beam of hard light projects diagonally downward from the upper left of the frame, passing through a physical obstruction resembling venetian blinds, carving out crisp, parallel diagonal geometric striped light patterns across the subject's side profile, neck, and the expansive dark background to the left. The lit surfaces exhibit a warm amber tone with a cinematic quality, with highlights precisely delineating her straight nose bridge, clear eyes, and the soft edge of her jawline; areas untouched by the light transition instantly and merge into the extreme pure-black shadows, creating a visually striking light-and-shadow cutting effect. In the dark space on the left side of the frame, the striped light patterns gradually weaken and dissipate, creating a sense of deep spatial extension. The overall image quality is sharp and crisp, the light-to-shadow transitions are clean-cut, and the atmosphere is filled with mystery and dramatic artistry.",
