    "revised_prompt": "一张手绘风格的2D插画，呈现时尚概念拆解图。画面采用宽幅构图，背景为米色羊皮纸纹理，光影干净柔和，极具设计草图氛围。\n\n画面中心是一位时尚自信的年轻女性全身像。她微卷长发，身穿驼色哑光皮质风衣，内搭黑色蕾丝塑身内衣与薄纱紧身裤，姿态自然且充满活力，散发微性感气质。\n\n四周呈发散状排版着结构化元素及中英双语手写体标签：\n\n左上为衣物层拆解：展示内衣组件，旁边写有 'Shapewear & Lingerie / 塑身内衣'，引出材质注记 'soft lace / 柔软蕾丝'。风衣旁标注 'Trench Coat / 经典风衣' 及 'matte leather / 哑光皮革'。紧身裤旁标注 'Leggings / 紧身打底裤' 及 'tulle material / 薄纱材质'。\n\n右上为表情板：包含四个表情头像，分别标注 'Neutral / 平静'、'Shy / 害羞'、'Surprised / 惊讶'、'Focused / 专注'。\n\n右侧中部为特写镜头：放大展示布料纹理标注 'Fabric Folds / 褶皱纹理'，手部姿势标注 'Hand Gesture / 手势'，以及局部皮肤标注 'Skin Texture / 肌理'。\n\n底部为生活配饰：一个敞开的手提包旁标注 'Handbag / 手提包'，散落着日常用品。口红标注 'Lipstick / 口红' 与 'shade #520 / 色号#520'，香水标注 'Perfume / 香水'，粉饼标注 'Compact Powder / 粉饼'，护手霜标注 'Hand Cream / 护手霜'，日记本标注 'Diary / 日记本'，保健药瓶标注 'Supplements / 保健品'。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/item_241_1.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "A hand-drawn style 2D illustration presenting a fashion concept breakdown sheet. The composition is in a wide-format layout with a beige parchment-textured background, clean and soft lighting, and a strong design sketch atmosphere.\n\nAt the center of the image is a fashionable and confident young woman shown in full-body view. She has slightly wavy long hair and wears a camel-colored matte leather trench coat, layered over a black lace shapewear bodysuit and sheer tulle leggings. Her pose is natural yet dynamic, exuding a subtly sensual quality.\n\nRadiating outward around her are structured elements and bilingual Chinese-English handwritten-style labels:\n\nUpper left is the garment layer breakdown: displaying the lingerie components, with 'Shapewear & Lingerie / 塑身内衣' written alongside, leading to a material annotation 'soft lace / 柔软蕾丝'. The trench coat is labeled 'Trench Coat / 经典风衣' with 'matte leather / 哑光皮革'. The leggings are labeled 'Leggings / 紧身打底裤' with 'tulle material / 薄纱材质'.\n\nUpper right is the expression board: containing four expression headshots, labeled respectively 'Neutral / 平静', 'Shy / 害羞', 'Surprised / 惊讶', and 'Focused / 专注'.\n\nRight middle section features close-up shots: a magnified display of fabric texture labeled 'Fabric Folds / 褶皱纹理', hand poses labeled 'Hand Gesture / 手势', and a partial skin detail labeled 'Skin Texture / 肌理'.\n\nThe bottom section shows lifestyle accessories: an open handbag labeled 'Handbag / 手提包' with everyday items scattered around. A lipstick labeled 'Lipstick / 口红' with 'shade #520 / 色号#520', perfume labeled 'Perfume / 香水', a compact labeled 'Compact Powder / 粉饼', hand cream labeled 'Hand Cream / 护手霜', a diary labeled 'Diary / 日记本', and a health supplement bottle labeled 'Supplements / 保健品'.",
    "prompt_zh": "手绘风格时尚概念拆解图。\n\n中心：一个全身照，展示一位时尚、自信、略带性感（但不露骨）的女性角色，姿势自然且充满活力。\n\n周围：她的关键元素的结构化布局：\n\n• 服装层次——展示外套、内衣、打底裤（蕾丝、薄纱材质）、塑身衣，并放大细节纹样。\n\n• 表情表——3-4种面部表情（自然、害羞、惊讶、专注）。\n\n• 特写镜头——面料褶皱质感、皮肤细节、手部姿态。\n\n• 生活方式与配饰——打开的手提包，内含日常物品：口红、香水、"
