    "author": "@AmirMushich",
    "author_link": "https://x.com/AmirMushich/status/1992704354990907793?s=20",
    "revised_prompt": "一幅手绘风格的等距视角（isometric）街道图解，呈横向构图。画面背景为略带颗粒纹理的米白色画纸。中央是一条从左下向右上延伸的城市街道，视角为45度俯视，遵循严格的等距投影规律，无透视形变。街道左侧并排矗立着两栋建筑：左下角是一家咖啡馆，一层设有红白相间的条纹雨篷和两张露天圆桌，门楣的招牌上清晰地写着'CAFÉ'；紧挨其右上侧的是一家花店，门前阶梯上摆满了各色盆栽绿植，木制挂牌上写着'Flora'。街道右侧是一家复古的红砖书店，拥有巨大的落地玻璃橱窗，顶部招牌上写着'BOOKS'。书店前方的人行道边设有一个带透明顶棚的公交车站和一张木质长椅。街道马路上绘制着斑马线和虚线分隔线，一辆黄色的复古出租车正行驶在主路上，一侧的自行车道上有一名骑着自行车的邮递员。人行道铺设着砖块纹理，分布着几盏欧式路灯、圆冠行道树以及两三个正在步行的微缩人物。为了体现图解（diagram）的特征，画面中分布着多根由细黑实线引出的手写体英文标注标签：指向咖啡馆的标注写着'Coffee Shop'，指向花店的写着'Flower Shop'，书店上方标注为'Bookstore'；指向街道中心的箭头旁写着'Main Street'，指向公交站的文字为'Bus Stop'，指向斑马线区域的文字为'Pedestrian Zone'，指向自行车道的文字为'Bike Lane'。画面采用精细的黑色钢笔线条勾勒，线条带有手绘特有的自然轻微抖动与粗细变化，局部区域辅以淡雅柔和的水彩晕染（如砖红色、浅蓝色、鹅黄色和淡绿色），整体风格清新、规整且结构清晰。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/item_250_4.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "A hand-drawn style isometric street diagram in a horizontal composition. The background is an off-white drawing paper with a slightly grainy texture. At the center is a city street extending from the lower left to the upper right, viewed from a 45-degree overhead angle following strict isometric projection rules with no perspective distortion. On the left side of the street stand two buildings side by side: in the lower-left corner is a café, its ground floor featuring a red-and-white striped awning and two outdoor round tables, with a sign on the lintel clearly reading 'CAFÉ'; immediately adjacent to its upper-right side is a flower shop, its front steps filled with various potted plants and greenery, with a wooden hanging sign reading 'Flora'. On the right side of the street is a vintage red-brick bookstore with a large floor-to-ceiling glass display window and a sign on top reading 'BOOKS'. In front of the bookstore, on the sidewalk edge, there is a bus stop with a transparent canopy and a wooden bench. The street surface features painted zebra crossings and dashed dividing lines; a yellow vintage taxi is driving on the main road, and a mail carrier is riding a bicycle in the bike lane on one side. The sidewalk is paved with brick textures and dotted with several European-style lampposts, round-crowned street trees, and two or three miniature walking figures. To embody the characteristics of a diagram, the scene is annotated with multiple handwritten English labels drawn out from thin solid black lines: the label pointing to the café reads 'Coffee Shop', the one pointing to the flower shop reads 'Flower Shop', and the one above the bookstore reads 'Bookstore'; an arrow pointing to the center of the street is labeled 'Main Street', the text pointing to the bus stop reads 'Bus Stop', the text pointing to the zebra crossing area reads 'Pedestrian Zone', and the text pointing to the bike lane reads 'Bike Lane'. The artwork is rendered with fine black pen lines that carry the natural, slight tremor and thickness variation characteristic of hand-drawing, with select areas supplemented by soft, delicate watercolor washes (such as brick red, light blue, goose yellow, and light green). The overall style is fresh, neat, and structurally clear.",
    "prompt_zh": "绘制这条街道的手绘等距图。"
