    "prompt_en": "Please create a pose sheet for this illustration, making various poses!",
    "source": "https://x.com/tapehead_Lab/status/1960878455299694639",
    "type": "t2i",
    "author": "@tapehead_Lab",
    "author_link": "https://x.com/tapehead_Lab/status/1960878455299694639",
    "revised_prompt": "二次元动漫风格的角色动态设定图（pose sheet），画面呈横幅比例，背景为带有浅白色网格线的浅灰色，排版清晰规整。画面中平行横向排列展示了一名活力动漫少女的五个不同身体姿态。少女的统一外观设定为：留着亮橙色的双马尾，头戴黑色发带，穿着带有亮黄色条纹细节的黑色短款拉链夹克，内搭白色露脐T恤，下身是白色百褶裙，搭配不对称的黑色长筒袜和带有黄色细节的黑色厚底运动鞋。\n\n画面最左侧展示的是角色的标准站姿，少女双手叉腰，挺胸抬头，表情自信，正面看向视觉前方。其上方悬浮着黑色的手写体英文文字 'STANDARD'。\n左起第二个姿势为动感的跳跃动作。少女右腿弯曲跳跃起空，左腿向后蹬直，双手在半空中大幅度向外张开，脸上挂着开朗灿烂的笑容，双马尾和夹克下摆随动作高高扬起，充满失重感与活力。下方带有黑色文字标签 'JUMPING'。\n画面正中央的姿势是休息放松的状态。少女盘腿坐在地面上，右手拿着一罐带有白色拉环的红色苏打水易拉罐，左手向后撑地，头微微向左歪斜，对着镜头做出了单眼调皮的wink表情，嘴角上扬。其上方带有黑色文字标签 'RELAX'。\n右起第二个姿势是极具张力的战斗准备动作。少女双腿呈弓步身体压低前倾，双手紧握一根带有黄色斜线涂鸦的黑色金属棒球棍，眼神锐利，眉头微皱，呈现蓄势待发的战斗姿态。下方带有黑色文字标签 'COMBAT MODE'。\n画面最右侧是夸张的惊讶动态。少女双手捂住双颊，身体大幅度后仰，眼睛睁大，嘴巴张成圆形的“O”型，头顶画有三个黄色的感叹号特效。其上方带有黑色文字标签 'SURPRISED!'。\n\n画面左上角写有黑色大号粗体的主标题文字 'CHARACTER POSE SHEET'，紧接着下方有一行较小的副标题文字 'PROJECT: NEON STREET'。画面右上角整齐排列着五个正方形的参考色卡块，分别填充着亮橙色、纯黑色、亮黄色、纯白色和深灰色，展示了角色的核心配色方案。整体画面采用平涂赛璐璐上色风格，边缘线条黑实流畅，色彩鲜明，没有复杂的背景元素干扰，完全聚焦于角色肢体语言的表达。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/item_305_3.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "A character pose sheet in a 2D anime style, presented in a wide horizontal aspect ratio, with a light gray background featuring faint white grid lines and a clean, well-organized layout. The scene displays five different body poses of an energetic anime girl arranged horizontally in parallel. The girl's uniform character design features: bright orange twin tails, a black headband, a black short zip-up jacket with bright yellow stripe details, a white cropped T-shirt underneath, a white pleated skirt on the bottom, asymmetrical black thigh-high socks, and black platform sneakers with yellow details.\n\nOn the far left of the image is the character's standard standing pose: the girl stands with both hands on her hips, chest out and head held high, with a confident expression, looking straight ahead toward the viewer. Above her floats the black handwritten English text 'STANDARD'.\nThe second pose from the left is a dynamic jumping action. The girl leaps into the air with her right leg bent, left leg kicked straight back, both arms spread wide open in mid-air, a bright and cheerful smile on her face, her twin tails and the hem of her jacket flying high with the motion, full of a sense of weightlessness and vitality. Below it is a black text label 'JUMPING'.\nThe pose at the center of the image depicts a resting, relaxed state. The girl sits cross-legged on the ground, holding a red soda can with a white pull-tab in her right hand, her left hand propping her up from behind, her head tilted slightly to the left, giving a playful one-eyed wink at the viewer with the corner of her mouth turned up. Above her is a black text label 'RELAX'.\nThe second pose from the right is a highly dynamic combat-ready action. The girl assumes a lunge stance with her body lowered and leaning forward, both hands tightly gripping a black metal baseball bat with yellow diagonal line graffiti, her gaze sharp and brows slightly furrowed, conveying a coiled, ready-to-strike fighting posture. Below it is a black text label 'COMBAT MODE'.\nOn the far right is an exaggerated surprise reaction. The girl covers both cheeks with her hands, her body leaning dramatically backward, eyes wide open, mouth agape in a round \"O\" shape, with three yellow exclamation mark effects drawn above her head. Above her is a black text label 'SURPRISED!'.\n\nIn the upper-left corner of the image, the main title is written in large bold black text: 'CHARACTER POSE SHEET', with a smaller subtitle line directly below reading 'PROJECT: NEON STREET'. In the upper-right corner, five square reference color swatches are neatly arranged in a row, filled respectively with bright orange, pure black, bright yellow, pure white, and dark gray, showcasing the character's color palette.",
    "prompt_zh": "请为这幅插画创建一个姿势表，制作各种姿势！"
