    "title_en": "Chibi Girl Eight-Expression Sticker Set",
    "prompt": "Using the character from Image 2, generate [x] emoji stickers based on various poses from Image 1.",
    "prompt_en": "Using the character from Image 2, generate [x] emoji stickers based on various poses from Image 1.",
    "source": "https://x.com/vista8/status/1966164427243458977",
    "type": "t2i",
    "author": "@vista8",
    "author_link": "https://x.com/vista8/status/1966164427243458977",
    "revised_prompt": "一张插画，展示了一个包含8个表情贴纸的集合图，排列成2排4列的网格布局。画面背景为浅黄色。所有贴纸的主角均为同一个二次元Q版（Chibi）风格的小女孩角色。该角色拥有粉色的双马尾长发，大大的翠绿色眼睛，穿着带有红色蝴蝶结的浅蓝色水手服和黑色小皮鞋。每个贴纸的边缘都有明显的白色粗轮廓线以及微弱的灰色投影，呈现出实体贴纸的质感。\n\n第一排从左至右有四个贴纸：\n第一个贴纸：角色面带灿烂笑容，闭着双眼，右手高高举起做挥手打招呼状，头顶周围有几颗黄色的四角星装饰，旁边有粉色的手写体文字 'Hi!'。\n第二个贴纸：角色跌坐在地上，双手握拳揉着眼睛，眼泪大颗大颗地像小瀑布一样流下，嘴巴大张大哭，旁边有蓝色的文字 'Uwaaa'。\n第三个贴纸：角色双手环抱在胸前，脸颊气得鼓起，眼神向旁边斜视，头顶右侧有一个红色的愤怒十字符号（井号），旁边有红色的文字 'Hmph!'。\n第四个贴纸：角色双手在胸前比出一个爱心的手势，脸颊泛着红晕，双眼闪烁着光芒，周围漂浮着三个大小不一的粉色爱心，底部有粉色文字 'Love'。\n\n第二排从左至右有四个贴纸：\n第五个贴纸：角色表现出震惊的状态，双眼变成了没有高光的白点，嘴巴张得大大的呈波浪形，双手抱头，背景有几道黄色的闪电特效，旁边有黄色的文字 'What?!'。\n第六个贴纸：角色面向前方，左眼闭起做Wink状（眨眼），右手向前伸出竖起大拇指点赞，旁边有绿色的文字 'Good!'。\n第七个贴纸：角色整个人趴在地上，双眼闭合，表情安详，头顶漂浮着一个睡眠气泡，气泡内有深蓝色的文字 'Zzz'。\n第八个贴纸：角色右手托着下巴，眉头微皱，嘴巴嘟起做思考状，头顶正上方悬浮着一个巨大的黑色问号 '?'。\n\n整体画面色彩明亮、饱和度高，画风可爱，线条流畅圆润，平涂上色，光照均匀，没有任何复杂的背景干扰，突出了表情贴纸的实用性和角色的生动性，完美契合横向构图比例。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/item_316_4.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "An illustration presenting a collection of 8 expression stickers arranged in a 2-row by 4-column grid layout. The background is light yellow. The protagonist of all stickers is the same 2D chibi-style little girl character. The character has pink long twin-tail hair, large emerald-green eyes, and wears a light blue sailor uniform with a red bow and black Mary Jane shoes. Each sticker has a distinct thick white outline along its edge and a faint gray drop shadow, giving the appearance and texture of physical stickers.\n\nThe first row, from left to right, contains four stickers:\nFirst sticker: The character wears a bright smile with both eyes closed, her right hand raised high in a waving hello gesture, with several yellow four-pointed stars decorating the area around her head, and pink handwritten text reading 'Hi!' beside her.\nSecond sticker: The character has fallen sitting on the ground, both fists rubbing her eyes, large tears streaming down like little waterfalls, mouth wide open crying loudly, with blue text reading 'Uwaaa' beside her.\nThird sticker: The character has her arms crossed over her chest, cheeks puffed up in anger, eyes glancing sideways, with a red anger cross symbol (vein mark) on the upper right of her head, and red text reading 'Hmph!' beside her.\nFourth sticker: The character forms a heart gesture with both hands in front of her chest, cheeks blushing, eyes sparkling with light, with three pink hearts of varying sizes floating around her, and pink text reading 'Love' at the bottom.\n\nThe second row, from left to right, contains four stickers:\nFifth sticker: The character displays a state of shock, both eyes turned into white dots without highlights, mouth wide open in a wavy shape, both hands clutching her head, with several yellow lightning bolt effects in the background, and yellow text reading 'What?!' beside her.\nSixth sticker: The character faces forward, her left eye closed in a wink, her right hand extended forward with a thumbs-up, with green text reading 'Good!' beside her.\nSeventh sticker: The character is lying flat on the ground face down, both eyes closed, with a serene expression, a sleep bubble floating above her head containing dark blue text reading 'Zzz'.\nEighth sticker: The character rests her chin on her right hand, brows slightly furrowed, lips pursed in a thinking expression, with a large black question mark '?' hovering directly above her head.\n\nThe overall image is brightly colored with high saturation, featuring a cute art style, smooth and rounded line work, flat coloring, and even lighting, with no complex background distractions, highlighting the practicality of the expression stickers and the vividness of the character, perfectly suited to a horizontal composition ratio.",
    "prompt_zh": "使用图片2中的角色，根据图片1中的各种姿势生成 [x] 个表情贴纸。"
