    "revised_prompt": "一张创意字体设计海报。背景为干净的米白色至浅粉色的柔和渐变，带有细腻的微光质感。画面正中央横向排列着巨大的英文单词 'beautify'，整体色调以玫瑰金、淡紫色和翠绿色为主，字母与象征“美化、美丽”含义的图形巧妙融合。具体细节如下：字母 'b' 的右侧圆弧巧妙地化作一只正在展翅的半透明渐变色蝴蝶翅膀；字母 'e' 的内部卷曲部分演变为一朵含苞待放的粉色玫瑰花瓣；字母 'a' 的左侧线条是一支精致的玫瑰金化妆刷；字母 'u' 的轮廓犹如一个优雅的复古香水瓶；字母 't' 的横杠是一片细长舒展的翠绿色柳叶，竖杠是一根纤细的藤蔓；字母 'i' 上方的点被替换为一颗璀璨闪烁的金色四角星芒；字母 'f' 的顶端如同蘸满流光色彩的画笔，向下拖拽出一条绚丽的丝带；字母 'y' 的尾巴向下优雅地延伸，化作一根缠绕着细碎花朵的藤蔓。字母整体线条流畅华丽，具有轻微的3D立体感、金属光泽与花卉的柔和质感。在单词正下方的居中位置，用优雅简洁的深灰色无衬线字体排版着两行简要说明：第一行文字为 '[ v. ] to make someone or something beautiful or more attractive.'，第二行文字为 '美化；使变得美丽'。光线从左上角柔和投射，在字母和文字下方留下淡淡的阴影，画面构图舒朗，左右两侧留有充足的呼吸空间，呈现出高级、唯美的现代设计风格。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/item_33_4.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "A creative typography design poster. The background is a soft gradient from clean off-white to light pink, with a delicate shimmer texture. Horizontally centered in the middle of the image is the large English word 'beautify', rendered primarily in rose gold, lavender, and emerald green tones, with the letters ingeniously merged with graphics symbolizing the meaning of \"beautification and beauty.\" Specific details are as follows: the right arc of the letter 'b' cleverly transforms into a semi-transparent gradient butterfly wing in mid-spread; the inner curl of the letter 'e' evolves into a pink rosebud petal; the left stroke of the letter 'a' is an exquisite rose gold makeup brush; the outline of the letter 'u' resembles an elegant vintage perfume bottle; the crossbar of the letter 't' is a slender, gracefully extending emerald green willow leaf, while the vertical bar is a delicate vine; the dot above the letter 'i' is replaced by a brilliantly sparkling golden four-pointed starburst; the top of the letter 'f' resembles a paintbrush dipped in iridescent colors, trailing a gorgeous ribbon downward; the tail of the letter 'y' extends elegantly downward, transforming into a vine entwined with tiny flowers. The overall letterforms are fluid and ornate, with a slight 3D dimensional effect, metallic sheen, and the soft texture of florals. Centered directly below the word, two lines of brief explanation are typeset in an elegant, concise dark gray sans-serif font: the first line reads '[ v. ] to make someone or something beautiful or more attractive.', and the second line reads '美化；使变得美丽'. Light casts softly from the upper left corner, leaving faint shadows beneath the letters and text. The composition is open and airy, with ample breathing space on both sides, presenting a sophisticated, aesthetically refined modern design style.",
    "prompt_zh": "在字母中融入单词的含义，将图形和字母巧妙融合在一起。\n单词：{ beautify }\n下面加上单词的简要说明"
}, {
    "filename": "item_356_4.png",
    "index": 356,
    "title": "涂鸦风未来教育信息图",
    "title_en": "Doodle-Style Future Education Infographic",
    "prompt": "Ayúdame a generar múltiples imágenes de estilo doodle en formato 16:9 para explicar el concepto de \"futuros\" a estudiantes de secundaria. Las imágenes deben tener un estilo consistente de dibujo a mano con lápiz grueso y colorido, ser ricas en información, presentar texto en inglés, usar fondos de colores sólidos, tener contornos alrededor de las tarjetas e incluir títulos uniformes, similar a una presentación de PowerPoint.",
    "prompt_en": "Ayúdame a generar múltiples imágenes de estilo doodle en formato 16:9 para explicar el concepto de \"futuros\" a estudiantes de secundaria. Las imágenes deben tener un estilo consistente de dibujo a mano con lápiz grueso y colorido, ser ricas en información, presentar texto en inglés, usar fondos de colores sólidos, tener contornos alrededor de las tarjetas e incluir títulos uniformes, similar a una presentación de PowerPoint.",
    "source": "https://x.com/op7418/status/1961811274683310110",
    "type": "t2i",
    "author": "@op7418",
    "author_link": "https://x.com/op7418/status/1961811274683310110",
    "revised_prompt": "涂鸦风格的教育幻灯片信息图，宽高比为16:9。整体背景为平面的纯浅黄色。画面采用彩色粗线条铅笔手绘风格，色彩鲜艳丰富，具有明显的涂鸦笔触质感。画面顶部居中是一个带有黑色粗边框的醒目手绘大标题，用黑色粗体英文字母写着：'WHAT ARE FUTURES?'。主标题下方，整齐排列着四个带有粗黑色手绘轮廓线的白色圆角矩形卡片，呈2x2网格布局。左上角的卡片顶部带有统一的蓝色手涂背景标题横幅，写着 '1. The Problem'；卡片内部画着一个戴草帽的农夫拿着一株绿色小麦，旁边是一个戴着白色高帽的面包师指着一个冒热气的烤箱，他们头顶都有带有红色问号的思考气泡；下方手绘英文字体写着完整文本：'Farmer Bob grows wheat. Baker Sue needs wheat for bread. Both worry about price changes!'。右上角的卡片顶部带有绿色横幅，写着 '2. The Agreement'；内部画着两只手正在握手，中间悬浮着一份卷轴状的纸张，纸张上画着一把金色的锁和几枚硬币；下方写着完整文本：'They sign a \"Futures Contract\". They agree to trade wheat for $5 in 3 months.'。左下角的卡片顶部带有红色横幅，写着 '3. Locking the Price'；内部画着一把巨大的银色挂锁，牢牢锁住了一个标有 '$5' 的绿色价格标签，旁边画着一本翻开的日历，日历页上有一个时钟图标；下方完整文本为：'No matter what happens to the market, Bob gets $5 and Sue pays $5. It is safe!'。右下角的卡片顶部带有紫色横幅，写着 '4. Summary'；内部画着一个背着蓝色书包、戴着红边墨镜的年轻学生，他旁边亮起一个发光的黄色灯泡，背景有向上的绿色折线图箭头；下方完整文本为：'Futures are just promises to buy or sell later at a set price today. They reduce risk!'。所有文本均为清晰的黑色手写体英文字母，易于阅读。每张卡片边缘都有稍微不规则的粗铅笔轮廓，完美还原了面向中学生的生动、信息丰富的课堂PPT视觉体验。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/item_356_4.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "A doodle-style educational slide infographic with a 16:9 aspect ratio. The overall background is a flat, solid light yellow. The image adopts a colorful, thick-lined colored pencil hand-drawn style with vibrant, rich colors and a distinctly doodled brushstroke texture. At the top center of the image is a prominent hand-drawn large title with a thick black border, written in bold black English letters: 'WHAT ARE FUTURES?'. Below the main title, four white rounded-rectangle cards with thick black hand-drawn outlines are neatly arranged in a 2×2 grid layout. The upper-left card has a uniform blue hand-painted background title banner at the top reading '1. The Problem'; inside the card, a farmer wearing a straw hat holds a green wheat stalk, beside a baker wearing a tall white hat pointing at a steaming oven, both with thought bubbles above their heads containing red question marks; below, in hand-drawn English lettering, the full text reads: 'Farmer Bob grows wheat. Baker Sue needs wheat for bread. Both worry about price changes!'. The upper-right card has a green banner at the top reading '2. The Agreement'; inside, two hands are shaking, with a scroll-like piece of paper floating between them, on which a golden lock and several coins are drawn; below, the full text reads: 'They sign a \"Futures Contract\". They agree to trade wheat for $5 in 3 months.'. The lower-left card has a red banner at the top reading '3. Locking the Price'; inside, a large silver padlock firmly locks a green price tag marked '$5', with an open calendar drawn beside it featuring a clock icon on the calendar page; the full text below reads: 'No matter what happens to the market, Bob gets $5 and Sue pays $5. It is safe!'. The lower-right card has a purple banner at the top reading '4. Summary'; inside, a young person wearing a blue backpack and red-rimmed sunglasses is drawn.",
    "prompt_zh": "帮我生成多张16:9比例的涂鸦风格图片，用于向中学生解释\"期货\"的概念。图片应保持统一的手绘风格，使用粗线条彩色铅笔，信息丰富，文字使用英文，采用纯色背景，卡片周围带有轮廓边框，并包含统一的标题，类似于PowerPoint演示文稿的风格。"
}, {
    "filename": "item_391_2.png",
