    "title": "浮世绘闪卡",
    "title_en": "Ukiyo-e Flash Cards",
    "prompt": "この画像を浮世絵スタイルのフラッシュカードに変換してください。",
    "prompt_en": "Convert this image into a ukiyo-e style flash card.",
    "source": "https://x.com/MANISH1027512/status/1960583251460022626",
    "type": "t2i",
    "author": "@MANISH1027512",
    "author_link": "https://x.com/MANISH1027512/status/1960583251460022626",
    "revised_prompt": "一张竖版长方形的语言学习闪卡，采用传统的日本浮世绘木版画风格设计。画面整体分为上下两个部分，四周环绕着深蓝色的日本传统青海波纹样边框，背景带有做旧的米黄色和纸粗糙纹理。\n\n画面上方约占三分之二的区域为浮世绘风格的插画。画面中央是一只呈端坐姿态的三花猫（白、黑、橘色斑块相间），体态丰满，脖子上系着一根红色的细绳，挂着一颗金色的圆形小铃铛。猫的绘制采用了传统的平涂技法和细腻的黑色勾线。猫的背景是一幅经典的日本风景：远景是蓝白相间的富士山轮廓，山顶覆盖着白雪；中景是几抹风格化的层云；近景有几片粉红色的樱花花瓣正在半空中随风飘落。插画的右下角有一个红色的方形仿古印章，印章内包含篆体汉字'猫'。整个插画区域色彩以靛蓝、朱红、苔绿和米色为主，具有木版画特有的套色错位感和复古韵味。\n\n画面下方约占三分之一的区域为闪卡的信息展示区，排版居中且结构清晰。最上方是一行稍小的日文平假名注音'ねこ'；紧接着下方是醒目且字号最大的日文汉字'猫'；汉字的正下方是较小的罗马音拼写'neko'；再下方是黑体字体的英文翻译'Cat'。在下半部的最底端，包含一段双语例句，上方为日文'猫が桜の木の下で寝ている。'，下方为对应的英文翻译'The cat is sleeping under the cherry tree.'。所有的文字均为黑色，字体带有些许毛笔书写的笔触感，与整体的浮世绘古风视觉完美融合。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/item_391_2.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "A vertical rectangular language learning flashcard designed in the traditional Japanese ukiyo-e woodblock print style. The image is divided into upper and lower sections, surrounded by a dark blue Japanese traditional seigaiha (wave pattern) border, with an aged, rough-textured cream-yellow washi paper background.\n\nThe upper area, occupying approximately two-thirds of the image, features a ukiyo-e style illustration. At the center of the image sits a calico cat (with white, black, and orange patches) in an upright seated posture, plump in physique, with a thin red cord tied around its neck from which hangs a small golden round bell. The cat is rendered using traditional flat-color application techniques and delicate black outlines. The cat's background is a classic Japanese landscape: in the far distance, the blue-and-white silhouette of Mount Fuji with snow-capped peaks; in the middle ground, a few stylized layered clouds; in the foreground, several pink cherry blossom petals drifting in mid-air with the wind. In the lower-right corner of the illustration is a red square faux-antique seal containing the seal script Chinese character '猫'. The entire illustration area is colored primarily in indigo, vermilion, moss green, and cream, possessing the characteristic registration offset feel and vintage charm unique to woodblock prints.\n\nThe lower area, occupying approximately one-third of the image, serves as the flashcard's information display section, centered and clearly structured. At the very top is a slightly smaller line of Japanese hiragana reading 'ねこ'; directly below is the most prominent and largest Japanese kanji '猫'; directly beneath the kanji is the smaller romanized spelling 'neko'; further below is the English translation 'Cat' in bold typeface. At the very bottom of the lower half, a bilingual example sentence is included, with the Japanese '猫が桜の木の下で寝ている。' on top and the corresponding English translation 'The cat is sleeping under the cherry tree.' below. All text is in black, with fonts carrying a slight brush-written stroke quality, perfectly harmonizing with the overall ukiyo-e classical visual aesthetic.",
    "prompt_zh": "请将这张图片转换为浮世绘风格的闪卡。"
}, {
    "filename": "item_405_1.png",
    "index": 405,
    "title": "手绘等距视图",
    "title_en": "Hand-Drawn Isometric View",
    "prompt": "手描きのアイソメトリックビューを作成してください。",
    "prompt_en": "Create a hand-drawn isometric view.",
    "source": "https://x.com/AmirMushich/status/1960583251460022626",
    "type": "t2i",
    "author": "@AmirMushich",
    "author_link": "https://x.com/AmirMushich/status/1960583251460022626",
    "revised_prompt": "一张手绘风格的插画，采用经典的等距视角（Isometric View）。画面中心是一栋被剖开的两层温馨咖啡馆兼书店的立体建筑模型，横向构图，背景为淡米色留白以突出主体结构。建筑分为上下两层。一层为咖啡馆区域，地面铺设着黑白相间的复古格纹地砖。左侧是一个L型的木制吧台，吧台上摆放着一台银色的意式半自动咖啡机、几个白色的咖啡杯以及一个透明的糕点展示柜，柜内陈列着牛角面包。吧台后方站着一位穿着棕色围裙的年轻男咖啡师，正在专注地冲泡咖啡。吧台前方并排摆放着三把木制高脚吧台椅。右侧墙壁上挂着一块黑板，上面用白色手写体清晰地写着菜单：'Espresso'、'Latte'、'Matcha'、'Pastry'。一层的角落里有一盆茂盛的龟背竹。通过一组带有木制扶手的L型楼梯可以通向二层阁楼阅读区。二层铺着原木色地板，中央铺有一块波西米亚风格的几何纹理地毯。地毯上放置着一把芥末黄色的单人沙发椅，旁边是一个小圆桌，桌上放着一台打开的银色笔记本电脑和一杯冒着热气的咖啡。二层后方的墙壁是一整面通顶的实木书架，上面密密麻麻地摆满了各种颜色的书籍。侧面墙上贴着一张复古海报，上面印着文字 'Jazz Night'。建筑外部保留了部分红砖墙面，墙面上攀爬着绿色的常春藤。门外有一条灰色的鹅卵石小径，小径旁立着一盏黑色的复古街灯。建筑入口的上方悬挂着一个黑色铸铁双面招牌，上面用优雅的字体写着店名 'Café de la Lune'。画面采用精细的钢笔勾线结合温暖明亮的水彩晕染风格，线条带有手绘特有的自然质感。色调以温暖的木色、砖红、复古绿和暖黄色为主，光线设定为柔和的午后阳光，在地面和物体上投下干净、平行的斜向阴影，呈现出一种舒适、惬意且细节丰富的微缩模型视觉效果。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/item_405_1.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "A hand-drawn style illustration rendered in a classic isometric view. At the center of the image is a cutaway three-dimensional architectural model of a cozy two-story café-cum-bookstore, composed in a horizontal layout, with a light beige blank background to highlight the main structure. The building is divided into two floors. The first floor is the café area, with black-and-white vintage checkered floor tiles. On the left side is an L-shaped wooden bar counter, on which sit a silver semi-automatic Italian espresso machine, several white coffee cups, and a transparent pastry display case containing croissants. Behind the counter stands a young male barista wearing a brown apron, intently brewing coffee. In front of the counter are three wooden high-legged bar stools arranged side by side. On the right wall hangs a blackboard with the menu clearly written in white hand-lettered script: 'Espresso', 'Latte', 'Matcha', 'Pastry'. In a corner of the first floor sits a lush Monstera deliciosa plant. An L-shaped staircase with wooden handrails leads up to the second-floor loft reading area. The second floor has natural wood-toned flooring, with a Bohemian-style geometric-patterned rug laid in the center. On the rug is a mustard-yellow single-seat armchair, beside which is a small round table holding an open silver laptop and a steaming cup of coffee. Along the back wall of the second floor is a full-height solid wood bookshelf stretching from floor to ceiling, densely packed with books of various colors. On the side wall is a vintage poster printed with the text 'Jazz Night'. The building's exterior retains portions of red brick wall surface, with green ivy climbing across it. Outside the door is a gray cobblestone path, beside which stands a black vintage street lamp. Above the building's entrance hangs a black cast-iron double-sided sign with the shop name 'Café de la Lune' written in elegant lettering. The artwork employs a style of fine pen linework combined with warm, bright watercolor washes, with lines possessing the natural texture characteristic of hand-drawing. The color palette is dominated by warm wood tones, brick red, vintage green, and warm yellow. The lighting is set as soft afternoon sunlight, casting clean, parallel diagonal shadows on the ground and objects, presenting a comfortable, leisurely, and detail-rich miniature model visual effect.",
    "prompt_zh": "请创建一幅手绘等距视图。"
}, {
    "filename": "item_44_1.png",
    "index": 44,
    "title": "Q版角色表情包",
    "title_en": "Chibi Character Emoji Pack",
    "prompt": "请创作一套以 [参考图片中的角色] 为主角的Q版表情包，共9个，排列成3x3网格。\n设计要求：\n- 透明背景。\n- 1:1正方形构图。\n- 统一的Q版吉卜力卡通风格，色彩鲜艳。\n- 每个表情的动作、神态、内容各不相同，需要体现“骚、贱、萌、抓狂”等多样情绪，例如：翻白眼、捶地狂笑、灵魂出窍、原地石化、撒钱、干饭状态、社交恐惧发作等。可融入打工人和网络热梗元素。\n- 每个表情形象完整，无残缺。\n- 每个表情均带有统一的白色描边，呈现贴纸效果。\n- 画面中无多余、分离的元素。\n- 严格禁止出现任何文字，或确保文字内容准确无误（优先选择无文字）。",
    "prompt_en": "Please create a set of 9 Chibi stickers featuring [the character in the reference image], arranged in a 3x3 grid.\nDesign requirements:\n- Transparent background.\n- 1:1 square aspect ratio.\n- Consistent Chibi Ghibli cartoon style with vibrant colors.\n- Each sticker must have a unique action, expression, and theme, reflecting diverse emotions like \"sassy, mischievous, cute, frantic\" (e.g., rolling eyes, laughing hysterically on the floor, soul leaving body, petrified, throwing money, foodie mode, social anxiety attack). Incorporate elements related to office workers and internet memes.\n- Each character depiction must be complete, with no missing parts.\n- Each sticker must have a uniform white outline, giving it a sticker-like appearance.\n- No extraneous or detached elements in the image.\n- Strictly no text, or ensure any text is 100% accurate (no text preferred).\n",
    "source": "https://x.com/leon_yuan2001/status/1923712069209293014",
    "type": "t2i",
