    "author_link": "https://x.com/leon_yuan2001/status/1923712069209293014",
    "revised_prompt": "这是一张横版插画，展示了一套3x3网格排列的Q版表情包设计。画面主体为一个经典的吉卜力卡通风格的Q版少女，她留着棕色齐耳短发，身穿白色短袖衬衫和红色背带裙。整体色彩鲜艳明快，线条圆润，光线均匀柔和。每一个表情图案的外轮廓都带有明显的较粗白色描边，呈现出实体的贴纸效果，背景为干净的纯色以凸显贴纸质感。画面中没有任何文字内容。九个表情在画面中呈三行三列整齐排列，具体内容如下：\n\n第一行左侧：少女双手抱胸，眼睛夸张地向上翻，露出大面积眼白，嘴角不屑地下撇，展现出极度无语、翻白眼的表情。\n第一行中间：少女整个人趴在地上，一只手疯狂捶打地面，眼睛笑成了两条弯弯的月牙缝，嘴巴大张着，眼角飞出一滴巨大的蓝色泪珠，呈现捶地狂笑的状态。\n第一行右侧：少女双腿摊开瘫坐在地，双眼变成两个空洞的黑圈，嘴巴呆滞地微张，一个半透明的白色小幽灵正从她的嘴巴里飘向空中，表现‘灵魂出窍’。\n\n第二行左侧：少女保持着张嘴震惊的站立姿态，但整个人从头到脚变成了灰白色调的石头质感，身上布满黑色的碎裂纹路，头顶画着几道垂直的黑色阴影线，表现‘原地石化’。\n第二行中间：少女戴着一副倒三角的黑色墨镜，嘴角挂着自信且得意的坏笑，双手正将一沓绿色的钞票抛向空中，身体周围有许多飘落的纸币，呈现‘暴富撒钱’的姿态。\n第二行右侧：少女双手各握着一把大木勺，面前放着一个装满白米饭、堆得像小山一样的巨大饭碗，她的双颊塞满食物高高鼓起，眼睛变成闪亮的金色星星，周围飘着星星特效，表现极度的‘干饭热情’。\n\n第三行左侧：少女蜷缩在一个棕色开口纸箱里，双手扒着纸箱边缘，只露出上半张脸，大眼睛惊恐地向左侧斜视，额头挂着一滴巨大的蓝色冷汗，头顶悬浮着一朵灰色的乌云，表现‘社交恐惧症发作’。\n第三行中间：少女坐在办公桌前，双眼布满夸张的红血丝，头发凌乱，双手化作模糊的残影疯狂敲击着一个灰色的电脑键盘，键盘上迸发出黄色的火花，表现打工人‘疯狂赶工抓狂’的状态。\n第三行右侧：少女双手捧着脸颊，微微歪头，眼睛变得水汪汪且巨大，脸颊上画着两团夸张的粉色红晕，身体周围飘浮着大大小小的粉色爱心，呈现出极其乖巧无害的‘极致卖萌’神态。\n\n整张图片没有任何分离的多余元素，所有道具均与角色紧密结合，白色贴纸描边完整包裹住角色与道具，每个形象都完整无残缺，画面布局紧凑且充满趣味。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/item_44_1.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "This is a horizontal illustration showcasing a set of Q-version (chibi) emoji sticker designs arranged in a 3×3 grid. The main subject is a classic Ghibli cartoon-style chibi girl with brown ear-length bob hair, wearing a white short-sleeve blouse and a red pinafore dress. The overall colors are vivid and cheerful, with rounded linework and evenly soft lighting. Each emoji has a distinctly thick white outline around its outer contour, producing a physical sticker effect, set against a clean solid-color background to accentuate the sticker quality. There is no text whatsoever in the image. The nine expressions are neatly arranged in three rows and three columns, with the specific content as follows:\n\nTop row, left: The girl stands with arms crossed over her chest, eyes dramatically rolled upward showing large areas of white, the corners of her mouth turned down disdainfully, displaying an expression of extreme exasperation and eye-rolling.\nTop row, center: The girl is lying flat on the ground, one hand frantically pounding the floor, eyes squeezed into two curved crescent slits from laughing, mouth wide open, with an oversized blue teardrop flying from the corner of her eye, depicting a state of floor-pounding hysterical laughter.\nTop row, right: The girl sits slumped on the ground with legs splayed apart, eyes turned into two hollow black circles, mouth slightly agape in a dazed manner, with a semi-transparent white miniature ghost floating upward out of her mouth into the air, representing 'soul leaving the body.'\n\nMiddle row, left: The girl maintains a standing pose with mouth agape in shock, but her entire body from head to toe has turned into a gray-white stone texture, covered with black cracking lines, with several vertical black hatching lines drawn above her head, representing 'petrified on the spot.'\nMiddle row, center: The girl wears a pair of inverted-triangle black sunglasses, with a confident and smug smirk at the corners of her mouth, both hands tossing a stack of green banknotes into the air, with numerous bills fluttering around her body, presenting a 'striking it rich and throwing money' pose.\nMiddle row, right: The girl grips a large wooden spoon in each hand, with an enormous rice bowl in front of her piled high like a small mountain with white rice. Her cheeks are stuffed full of food, puffed up high, eyes turned into gleaming golden stars, with star effects floating around her, expressing extreme 'eating enthusiasm.'\n\nBottom row, left: The girl is curled up inside a brown open-top cardboard box, hands gripping the edges of the box, only the upper half of her face visible, her large eyes fearfully glancing to the left, a huge blue drop of cold sweat hanging from her forehead, with a gray rain cloud hovering above her head, representing 'social anxiety attack.'\nBottom row, center: The girl sits at an office desk, eyes covered in exaggerated red blood vessels, hair disheveled, both hands turned into blurred afterimages frantically hammering away at a gray computer keyboard, with yellow sparks bursting from the keyboard, representing the office worker 'frantically rushing to meet a deadline.'",
    "prompt_zh": "请创作一套以 [参考图片中的角色] 为主角的Q版表情包，共9个，排列成3x3网格。\n设计要求：\n- 透明背景。\n- 1:1正方形构图。\n- 统一的Q版吉卜力卡通风格，色彩鲜艳。\n- 每个表情的动作、神态、内容各不相同，需要体现“骚、贱、萌、抓狂”等多样情绪，例如：翻白眼、捶地狂笑、灵魂出窍、原地石化、撒钱、干饭状态、社交恐惧发作等。可融入打工人和网络热梗元素。\n- 每个表情形象完整，无残缺。\n- 每个表情均带有统一的白色描边，呈现贴纸效果。\n- 画面中无多余、分离的元素。\n- 严格禁止出现任何文字，或确保文字内容准确无误（优先选择无文字）。"
