    "author": "@icreatelife",
    "author_link": "https://x.com/icreatelife/status/1962724040205803773",
    "revised_prompt": "一张商业广告产品摄影图。画面采用16:9的宽幅构图，中央居中放置着一款作为视觉焦点的产品——一个透明的细长圆柱形玻璃瓶，瓶内装有色泽鲜艳的翠绿色冷压果蔬汁。瓶身表面布满冷凝水珠，呈现极简风格，完全没有附带任何文字、商标或标签。\n\n围绕着这个中心玻璃瓶，是一组以“爆炸”形式向外放射状飞溅的新鲜生食原料，呈现出极具动感的瞬间定格效果。向四周悬浮飞舞的具体食材包括：几片脉络清晰、翠绿卷曲的羽衣甘蓝叶；切开的青苹果块；晶莹剔透的黄瓜薄片；对半切开且带有四溅汁水的黄柠檬；几截新鲜带叶的芹菜茎；以及几块带有粗糙表皮的生姜块。这些食材伴随着无数细小的透明水滴和绿色的汁液飞溅物，在空中呈3D立体分布，向画面的左右两侧张扬地延伸。\n\n背景设定为极具戏剧性的现代纯色空间，采用了代表健康与品牌的色彩：背景中心为高亮的祖母绿，向画面的四周边缘平滑过渡为深邃的暗绿色，形成强烈的暗角效果，使得中心的产品尤为突出。\n\n光影与视觉细节方面，画面采用专业商业摄影的戏剧性布光，明亮的侧面轮廓光精准地勾勒出玻璃瓶和半空中每一块食材的边缘轮廓，强化了物体的立体感和清脆感。处于焦平面的瓶身和中心食材极其锐利，而最靠近镜头边缘和最远处的飞舞食材则带有轻微的动态模糊效果，增强了向外爆发现场的纵深感与速度感。整个场景完全无文字，色彩具有极高的饱和度，光影对比鲜明，客观呈现出食材的新鲜度与生机。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/item_590_4.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "A commercial advertising product photography image. The frame adopts a 16:9 wide-format composition, with a product placed centrally as the visual focal point—a transparent, slender cylindrical glass bottle filled with vivid emerald-green cold-pressed fruit and vegetable juice. The bottle surface is covered with condensation droplets, presenting a minimalist style with absolutely no text, logos, or labels attached.\n\nSurrounding this central glass bottle is a group of fresh raw ingredients radiating outward in an \"explosion\" formation, splashing in all directions, presenting a highly dynamic freeze-frame effect. The specific ingredients suspended and flying in all directions include: several curled, vividly green kale leaves with clearly visible veins; cut green apple chunks; translucent thin cucumber slices; yellow lemons cut in half with juice splashing in all directions; several stalks of fresh celery with leaves attached; and several pieces of raw ginger with rough skin. These ingredients are accompanied by countless tiny transparent water droplets and green juice splashes, distributed in 3D throughout the air, extending dramatically toward both the left and right sides of the frame.\n\nThe background is set as a dramatically modern solid-color space, employing colors that represent health and brand identity: the background center is a bright highlight emerald green, smoothly transitioning toward the edges of the frame into deep dark green, creating a strong vignette effect that makes the central product particularly prominent.\n\nIn terms of lighting and visual details, the image employs dramatic lighting typical of professional commercial photography. Bright side rim lights precisely delineate the edge contours of the glass bottle and every piece of ingredient suspended in mid-air, reinforcing the three-dimensionality and crispness of the objects. The bottle and central ingredients on the focal plane are extremely sharp, while the flying ingredients closest to the lens edges and farthest away carry a slight motion blur effect, enhancing the sense of depth and velocity of the outward explosion scene. The entire scene is completely free of text, with extremely high color saturation and stark light-shadow contrast, objectively conveying the freshness and vitality of the ingredients.",
    "prompt_zh": "以戏剧化的现代场景拍摄该产品，产品周围搭配新鲜、生的核心原料以爆炸式向外扩散的动态排列方式飞散，象征其新鲜度和营养价值。无文字，突出产品，以品牌核心色作为背景，呈现促销广告拍摄效果。"
