    "revised_prompt": "一张简约且富有创意的横版广告图。画面采用极致的纯白色背景。视觉中心放置着一个真实的物体：一根色彩鲜艳、带有真实摄影光影质感的亮黄色香蕉。这根香蕉与手绘的黑色墨水涂鸦巧妙结合，涂鸦线条松散、俏皮且带有随意的速写感。涂鸦将香蕉的弧形轮廓巧妙地变成了腊肠犬的身体，具体描绘为：在香蕉的左侧顶端画着腊肠犬的头部，包含耷拉的黑色长耳朵、圆圆的眼睛和俏皮的鼻子；在香蕉的下方画有四条短短的黑色狗腿，呈现出轻快行走的动态；香蕉的右侧末端则画着一条正在欢快摇摆的短尾巴。真实的高饱和度水果与二维的黑白简笔画以富有想象力的方式产生了无缝互动。在画面顶部中央，用粗体黑色无衬线字体醒目地排布着广告文案：'Unleash Your Energy'。紧接其下方是一行较小的黑色副标题：'Real fruit, crazy fun.'。在画面的底部正中央，清晰地放置着品牌标志，由一个黑色的简约动物脚印图标和紧挨着的大写英文字母 'MONKEY PET' 组成。整体视觉效果干净利落、幽默有趣，黑白黄三色形成了强烈的视觉对比度，展现出构思巧妙的现代广告设计风格。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/item_59_2.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "A minimalist and creative horizontal banner ad. The image uses an extremely pure white background. At the visual center is a real object: a vibrantly colored bright yellow banana with realistic photographic lighting and shadow textures. This banana is ingeniously combined with hand-drawn black ink doodles, featuring loose, playful lines with a casual sketch feel. The doodle cleverly transforms the curved silhouette of the banana into the body of a dachshund, specifically depicted as follows: on the left tip of the banana, a dachshund's head is drawn, complete with droopy black long ears, round eyes, and a perky nose; beneath the banana, four short black dog legs are drawn, displaying a lively walking motion; at the right end of the banana, a short tail wagging happily is drawn. The real, highly saturated fruit and the two-dimensional black-and-white line drawing interact seamlessly in an imaginative way. At the top center of the image, bold black sans-serif type prominently displays the ad copy: 'Unleash Your Energy'. Directly below it is a smaller black subtitle: 'Real fruit, crazy fun.' At the bottom center of the image, the brand logo is clearly placed, consisting of a black minimalist animal paw print icon alongside the uppercase English letters 'MONKEY PET'. The overall visual effect is clean, crisp, humorous, and fun, with the black-white-yellow tricolor creating strong visual contrast, showcasing a cleverly conceived modern advertising design style.",
    "prompt_zh": "一则简约且富有创意的广告，设置在纯白背景上。\n一个真实的 [真实物体] 与手绘黑色墨水涂鸦相结合，线条松散而俏皮。涂鸦描绘了：[涂鸦概念及交互：以巧妙、富有想象力的方式与物体互动]。在顶部或中部加入粗体黑色 [广告文案] 文字。在底部清晰放置 [品牌标志]。视觉效果应简洁、有趣、高对比度且构思巧妙。"
