    "revised_prompt": "一张带有截面效果的建筑室内3D渲染图，采用等距视角（Isometric view）俯瞰一栋狭长型住宅的完整户型，呈现出极高的照片级真实感。画面为竖向构图，没有屋顶，墙壁在顶部被平齐截断，露出白色的墙体厚度，以便清晰展示内部的空间布局。明亮而柔和的自然光从右侧的窗户斜射进来，在地板和家具上留下逼真的光影分布，全局光照和材质纹理细腻逼真。室内空间从画面底部到顶部依次划分为三个主要生活区域：\n\n画面底部是入户玄关与客厅区域，地面铺设着温馨的原木色鱼骨拼地板。右下角是深灰色的入户防盗门，旁边贴墙放置着一个极简换鞋凳和衣帽架。客厅中央摆放着一张L型浅灰色布艺沙发，沙发下方铺着带有黑白几何图案的编织地毯，前方是一张双层圆形原木茶几，上面随意放着几本杂志和一杯咖啡。左侧墙面上壁挂着一台黑色平板电视，下方是白色的悬空电视柜。右侧墙面有巨大的落地玻璃窗，窗边角落摆放着一盆茂盛的大型龟背竹。\n\n画面中部平滑过渡到开放式的厨房与餐厅区域，地面材质从木地板转变为浅灰色哑光防滑瓷砖。左侧贴墙设计了L型的现代纯白亚克力橱柜和石英石操作台，内嵌有不锈钢烤箱和微波炉。台面上设有单槽洗手池、一台意式咖啡机、几把刀具和黑色的调料罐，最左侧立着一台银色双开门冰箱。偏右的位置摆放着一张长方形的胡桃木餐桌，搭配四把现代风格的黑色皮质餐椅，餐桌正中央放着一个插满白色洋桔梗的透明玻璃花瓶。\n\n画面顶部是相对私密的休息与卫浴区域。左上方是一间宽敞的卧室，地面恢复为木地板。房间中央是一张舒适的双人床，铺有纯白色床单、蓬松的枕头和一条藏蓝色的针织床尾毯。床的两侧各有一个带抽屉的木质床头柜，上面亮着暖黄色的金属台灯。卧室左侧墙面定制了一整排到顶的百叶门衣柜。右上方的空间是一间干湿分离的现代浴室，地面铺设黑白相间的六角形马赛克地砖。浴室内有一个由透明玻璃隔断的淋浴间（内有银色花洒）、一个白色的壁挂式智能马桶，以及一个悬空的橡木洗手台，洗手台上方安装着一面带有背光灯带的宽大矩形梳妆镜。整个画面色彩比例和谐，光影过渡自然，生动展现了一个现代、舒适且充满生活气息的居住环境。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/item_620_4.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "A 3D architectural interior rendering with a cross-section effect, using an isometric view to overlook the complete floor plan of a narrow elongated residential unit, presenting an extremely high level of photorealistic quality. The image is in vertical composition, with no roof, and the walls are cut flat at the top, exposing the white wall thickness, to clearly display the internal spatial layout. Bright, soft natural light streams in diagonally from windows on the right side, casting realistic light and shadow distributions on the floors and furniture, with refined and lifelike global illumination and material textures. The interior space is divided from the bottom to the top of the image into three main living zones:\n\nAt the bottom of the image is the entrance foyer and living room area, with floors laid in warm-toned natural wood herringbone parquet. In the lower right corner is a dark gray security entrance door, with a minimalist shoe-changing bench and a coat rack placed against the adjacent wall. At the center of the living room is an L-shaped light gray fabric sofa, with a woven rug featuring black-and-white geometric patterns beneath it, and a double-tiered round natural wood coffee table in front, casually topped with a few magazines and a cup of coffee. On the left wall, a black flat-screen TV is wall-mounted, with a white floating TV console below it. The right wall features a large floor-to-ceiling glass window, with a lush, large Monstera deliciosa plant placed in the corner by the window.\n\nThe middle of the image transitions smoothly into an open-plan kitchen and dining area, where the floor material changes from wood flooring to light gray matte anti-slip ceramic tiles. Along the left wall is an L-shaped modern pure white acrylic cabinet system with a quartz stone countertop, with a built-in stainless steel oven and microwave. On the countertop are a single-basin sink, an Italian espresso machine, several knives, and black spice jars, with a silver double-door refrigerator standing at the far left. Slightly to the right is a rectangular walnut dining table, paired with four modern-style black leather dining chairs, with a transparent glass vase filled with white lisianthus (Eustoma) placed at the center of the dining table.\n\nAt the top of the image is the relatively private resting and bathroom area. The upper left contains a spacious bedroom, with the floor returning to wood flooring. At the center of the room is a comfortable double bed, dressed with pure white bed sheets, fluffy pillows, and a navy blue knitted bed-end throw blanket. On each side of the bed is a wooden nightstand with drawers, each topped with a warm yellow metallic desk lamp. On the left wall of the bedroom, a full row of floor-to-ceiling louvered-door wardrobes is custom-fitted. The upper right space is a modern bathroom with wet-dry separation, with floors laid in black-and-white hexagonal mosaic tiles. Inside the bathroom are a shower enclosure with transparent glass partition (with a silver showerhead), a white wall-mounted smart toilet, and a floating oak wash",
    "prompt_zh": "将这张住宅户型平面图转换为房屋的等距、照片级真实感3D渲染图。"
