    "revised_prompt": "这是一张极具创意的高级静物摄影照片，采用竖向构图。画面正中央是一尊高度写实的雄狮雕塑，整体完全由各种烘焙面包精心组合与雕刻而成，完美契合画面的垂直空间。狮子呈端庄威严的坐姿，其华丽蓬松的鬃毛由层层叠叠、金黄酥脆的法式可颂面包构成，表面带有诱人的油润光泽，能清晰地看到一层层薄如蝉翼、即将掉落的起酥纹理。狮子的面部、躯干和粗壮的前肢主要由烤得焦黄的法棍和全麦硬欧包制作，表面保留了面包天然的粗糙质感、不规则的孔洞和龟裂的硬壳，这些面包的自然属性被巧妙地用来模拟狮子紧实的肌肉结构和面部轮廓。狮子的眼睛由深色的黑麦面包块精细打磨而成，瞳孔处点缀着南瓜籽；鼻尖部分则是一小块撒着密集白芝麻的法式小圆包。整体色调呈现出温暖、丰富且极其逼真的金棕色、焦糖色和烘焙色。画面采用专业的影棚柔光照明，光线柔和细腻地打在雕塑上，精准勾勒出面包表面的每一处起伏、裂纹与酥脆质感，并在右侧投下柔和的过渡阴影。背景为纯净的深暖灰色无缝背景纸，将视觉焦点完全集中在雕塑主体上。画质呈现超高清的微距细节，连面包表皮的微小气孔、底座上散落的几片酥皮碎屑和几粒芝麻都清晰可见。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/item_699_1.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "This is a highly creative, high-end still life photography image in vertical composition. At the very center of the frame is a highly realistic lion sculpture, entirely crafted and carved from an assortment of baked breads, perfectly fitting the vertical space of the image. The lion is seated in a dignified and majestic posture. Its luxuriant, voluminous mane is composed of layers upon layers of golden, crispy French croissants with an appetizing buttery sheen, where each paper-thin, ready-to-flake puff pastry layer is clearly visible. The lion's face, torso, and stout forelimbs are primarily made from well-browned baguettes and whole-wheat rustic European-style hard breads, whose surfaces retain the natural rough texture, irregular holes, and crackled hard crusts of real bread — these natural bread characteristics are ingeniously used to simulate the lion's taut muscular structure and facial contours. The lion's eyes are finely polished from dark rye bread blocks, with pumpkin seeds placed as pupils; the tip of the nose is a small French bread roll densely sprinkled with white sesame seeds. The overall color palette presents a warm, rich, and extremely lifelike range of golden-brown, caramel, and toasted baking hues. The image uses professional studio soft lighting, with gentle and delicate light falling upon the sculpture, precisely delineating every undulation, crack, and crispy texture on the bread surfaces, while casting soft, gradual shadows on the right side. The background is a pure, deep warm-gray seamless backdrop paper, directing all visual focus entirely onto the sculpture subject. The image quality delivers ultra-high-definition macro details — even the tiny pores on the bread crust, a few scattered flaky pastry crumbs and several sesame seeds on the base are all clearly visible.",
    "prompt_zh": "一个高度逼真的[object]雕塑，完全由[bread type]制成，具有超精细的纹理和色彩。表面展现面包的天然质感——金棕色、光泽感、酥脆或硬壳质地，在适当位置可见层次结构或种子颗粒，摄影棚灯光，柔和光线。"
