    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/item_716_4.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "A widescreen-ratio minimalist creative advertisement image. The frame features a pure white background with generous negative space, and the overall style is clean, high-contrast, and imaginative. Positioned slightly left of center is a real, vibrantly colored red tomato with a realistic surface sheen, natural three-dimensional shadows, and a green stem on top. This real tomato is cleverly integrated into a set of black hand-drawn ink line doodles. Loose and playful black single-line strokes sketch several converging ropes beneath the tomato, connecting to a simple line-drawn small square basket of a hot air balloon below. Inside the basket is a drawn stick figure wearing aviator goggles with a scarf fluttering behind its neck, holding up a monocular telescope and gazing toward the right side of the frame. The real red tomato is creatively repurposed here as the envelope (balloon) of the hot air balloon. Around the tomato, simple black brushstrokes depict several parallel arc lines indicating wind flow, along with two or three casually outlined clouds.\n\nCentered at the very top of the frame, in prominent bold black sans-serif English typeface, the advertising copy reads: 'FRESH IDEAS TAKE FLIGHT'. Centered at the very bottom of the frame, the brand logo is clearly arranged: bold black text 'NATURE FARMS', with a small tilted leaf icon drawn in minimalist black lines placed immediately to the left of the text. The overall visual is an interplay of real, colorful still life objects interwoven with whimsical black-and-white two-dimensional doodles — a clever concept with strong visual impact.",
