    "revised_prompt": "一幅具有微距摄影质感的手工刺绣肖像特写。画面中央绣着一位面容安详的森林女神，构图充满整个竖版画面。背景是深灰褐色的粗纺亚麻布，布料的经纬交织纹理和微小的纤维毛边清晰可见。女神的肖像由多种大地色系的绣线构成，主要包括暗金色、深绿色、铜棕色和米白色。刺绣的针脚立体且富有层次，清晰展示了缎面绣、平针和法国结等手工走线痕迹。女神的面部轮廓用细腻的米白色和浅棕色细线勾勒，双眼微闭，神态具有一种庄严而神圣的气息。她的长发由粗细不一的暗金色和铜棕色绣线层叠盘绕，发丝间穿插着深绿色线绣成的蕨类植物叶片、手工几何图腾和微小的花朵图案。侧面的柔和光线照射在刺绣表面，在凸起的绣线和亚麻布底纹上投射出细微的立体阴影，凸显了材料的厚重感与真实触感，整体画面散发出一种质朴、自然且充满神圣感的艺术氛围。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/item_721_2.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "A close-up of a hand-embroidered portrait with a macro photography texture. At the center of the frame is an embroidered forest goddess with a serene countenance, composed to fill the entire vertical canvas. The background is a dark grayish-brown coarse-spun linen fabric, with clearly visible warp-and-weft weave texture and tiny fiber fringes. The goddess's portrait is composed of embroidery threads in various earth-tone hues, primarily including dark gold, deep green, copper-brown, and off-white. The stitches are three-dimensional and richly layered, clearly showcasing handmade stitch traces such as satin stitch, running stitch, and French knots. The goddess's facial contours are delineated with delicate off-white and light brown fine threads; her eyes are gently closed, her expression exuding a solemn and sacred aura. Her long hair is formed by layered and coiled embroidery threads of varying thickness in dark gold and copper-brown, interspersed among the strands are fern leaves embroidered in deep green thread, handcrafted geometric totems, and tiny floral motifs. Soft sidelight illuminates the embroidery surface, casting subtle three-dimensional shadows on the raised threads and the linen base texture, accentuating the material's heft and tactile authenticity. The overall image radiates a rustic, natural, and profoundly sacred artistic atmosphere.",
    "prompt_zh": "一幅[subject]的刺绣肖像，[colors]色丝线绣在深色亚麻织物上。可见的针脚工艺、层叠的纹理和手工图案赋予其质朴、神圣的质感。"
