    "prompt_en": "a pillow fort in the backyard, shaded by a big old tree. Sunlight filters through the leaves, and a young boy and his golden retriever naps beside a tray of lemonade and cookies. Wind chimes tinkle gently in the breeze. Warm afternoon light, playful and nostalgic, children's book illustrated feeling",
