    "revised_prompt": "一幅垂直构图的儿童绘本插画，呈现出充满童趣与怀旧气息的夏日午后场景。画面背景是一个宁静的绿色后院，主体被一棵高大繁茂的老树遮蔽。老树粗壮的棕褐色树干从画面一侧向上延伸，巨大的树冠占据了画面上方的空间，绿色的树叶层层叠叠。温暖的午后阳光透过树叶的缝隙，在地面和草坪上洒下斑驳的金色光影。较高的树枝上悬挂着一串金属与木质结合的风铃，风铃微微倾斜，呈现出被微风轻轻吹拂的动态。\n\n老树下方的地面上，是一个用五颜六色的枕头、碎花床单和柔软的针织毛毯搭建而成的“枕头堡垒”。毛毯的一角被巧妙地悬挂并固定在较低的树枝上，形成一个舒适的帐篷状半封闭空间。堡垒内部铺着厚实的地毯，周围堆叠着大小不一的条纹和纯色靠枕。\n\n堡垒内部的阴凉处，一个小男孩正躺在柔软的垫子上安静地午睡。他留着蓬松的短发，穿着舒适的夏日棉质短袖和短裤，胸前随意搭着一条薄毯，睡容恬静。在他的身旁，蜷缩着一只毛发金黄柔顺的金毛猎犬，金毛犬闭着眼睛，头靠在两只前爪上，正陪伴着男孩一起酣睡。\n\n在男孩和金毛犬前方的草地上，放置着一个浅色的木质托盘。托盘里放着一个装满淡黄色柠檬水、漂浮着新鲜柠檬片和冰块的透明玻璃壶，旁边配有一个插着红白条纹吸管的玻璃杯，以及一个装满巧克力豆曲奇饼干的白色陶瓷盘。整体色调偏暖，以充满生命力的自然绿、温暖的阳光金和柔和的布艺色彩为主，画面光线柔和，散发着慵懒、静谧且令人怀念的舒适氛围。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/item_776_3.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "A vertically composed children's picture book illustration, presenting a summer afternoon scene brimming with childlike charm and nostalgic warmth. The background depicts a tranquil green backyard, with the main subject shaded beneath a tall, lush old tree. The tree's stout tawny-brown trunk extends upward from one side of the frame, its enormous canopy occupying the upper portion of the composition with layers upon layers of green leaves. Warm afternoon sunlight filters through gaps in the foliage, casting dappled golden light and shadow across the ground and lawn. A string of wind chimes combining metal and wood hangs from a higher branch, slightly tilted, conveying the dynamic of being gently swayed by a breeze.\n\nOn the ground beneath the old tree is a \"pillow fort\" constructed from colorful pillows, floral-print bed sheets, and soft knitted blankets. One corner of a blanket is cleverly draped and secured over a lower branch, forming a cozy tent-like semi-enclosed space. The interior of the fort is lined with a thick rug, surrounded by striped and solid-colored throw pillows of various sizes.\n\nIn the cool shade inside the fort, a little boy lies on a soft cushion, quietly napping. He has fluffy short hair and wears comfortable summer cotton short sleeves and shorts, with a thin blanket casually draped over his chest, his sleeping expression peaceful. Beside him, a golden retriever with soft, golden fur is curled up, eyes closed, head resting on its two front paws, dozing off alongside the boy.\n\nOn the grass in front of the boy and the golden retriever sits a light-colored wooden tray. On the tray rests a clear glass pitcher filled with pale yellow lemonade with fresh lemon slices and ice cubes floating inside, accompanied by a glass with a red-and-white striped straw, and a white ceramic plate filled with chocolate chip cookies. The overall color palette leans warm, dominated by vibrant natural greens, warm sunlight golds, and soft fabric hues. The lighting is gentle, exuding a lazy, tranquil, and nostalgically comforting atmosphere.",
    "prompt_zh": "后院里的枕头堡垒，被一棵古老的大树遮荫。阳光透过树叶洒落，一个小男孩和他的金毛寻回犬在一盘柠檬水和饼干旁打盹。风铃在微风中轻轻作响。温暖的午后光线，俏皮而怀旧，儿童绘本插画风格"
