    "filename": "item_807_3.png",
    "index": 807,
    "title": "日式机甲设计图",
    "title_en": "Japanese Mecha Design Blueprint",
    "prompt": "Transform this image into a stylized mechanical design sheet inspired by Japanese anime mecha blueprints.\nRender the subject with precise, clean linework and semi-realistic cel-shading, as if it were a technical illustration from an anime artbook.\nBreak down the design into parts (e.g. head, hand, accessory, full body) and arrange them like a reference sheet, with different angles and views.\nInclude soft handwritten notes or Japanese characters scattered like concept annotations.\nUse muted digital colors (red, gray, metallic tones) and draw the background in a loose watercolor anime landscape style — cliffs, cityscapes, or grassland ruins.\nThe final composition should feel like an official design page for an animated sci-fi series or manga.\nKeep the format horizontal, like a blueprint or character sheet, with a balance between precision and artistic flair.",
    "prompt_en": "Transform this image into a stylized mechanical design sheet inspired by Japanese anime mecha blueprints.\nRender the subject with precise, clean linework and semi-realistic cel-shading, as if it were a technical illustration from an anime artbook.\nBreak down the design into parts (e.g. head, hand, accessory, full body) and arrange them like a reference sheet, with different angles and views.\nInclude soft handwritten notes or Japanese characters scattered like concept annotations.\nUse muted digital colors (red, gray, metallic tones) and draw the background in a loose watercolor anime landscape style — cliffs, cityscapes, or grassland ruins.\nThe final composition should feel like an official design page for an animated sci-fi series or manga.\nKeep the format horizontal, like a blueprint or character sheet, with a balance between precision and artistic flair.",
    "source": "https://x.com/Artedeingenio/status/1931711452160651654",
    "type": "t2i",
    "author": "@Artedeingenio",
    "author_link": "https://x.com/Artedeingenio/status/1931711452160651654",
    "revised_prompt": "一张日式动漫风格的科幻机甲机械设定图（横幅插画）。画面整体采用精确干净的线条和半写实的赛璐璐阴影技法，呈现出动漫设定集官方设计页面的质感。主色调为柔和的暗红色、中灰色和金属色。画面主体是一台被拆解展示的科幻机甲，呈参考表形式排版布局。\n\n画面左侧偏中占据较大空间的是机甲的全身主视图，呈斜侧面站立姿态，展示出修长的四肢、层叠的红灰相间装甲板、外露的金属液压杆和复杂的膝部关节；胸部装甲厚重，肩甲宽大并带有排气百叶窗。画面右上方是机甲的头部特写，包含正面和侧面视图，展示了流线型的红色头部外壳、银灰色的面甲、额头金色的V型天线以及发光的绿色主监视器（眼睛）。画面右下方展示了手部和武器的特写，包括机械手指张开与握拳的精细关节构造，以及一把带有瞄准镜和能量弹匣的大型金属光束步枪的侧视图。画面中下方有背部推进器的局部特写，展示了喷射口、折叠金属翼和内部精细的涡轮结构。\n\n各个部件周围散落着引出线和手写风格的日文及英文概念注释。全身图上方有醒目的标题：'TYPE-04 ASSAULT MECHA'，紧接着较小的日文：'強襲型機動兵器 零四式'。头部特写旁标注有：'メインカメラ'、'V字型アンテナ'以及手写笔记'センサー感度調整必要'。武器特写旁标注：'高出力ビームライフル'和'エネルギーパック'。推进器旁标注：'メインスラスター'。画面边缘还有零散的笔记：'Note: Armor joints need more flexibility.'和'装甲の軽量化'。\n\n背景采用宽松的水彩动漫风景风格绘制，色调淡雅不喧宾夺主。画面底部和远景描绘了长满青苔的草原废墟、散落的巨大混凝土块，远处背景隐约可见陡峭的悬崖轮廓和未来科幻城市的天际线。画面四角带有细微的十字定位准星和参考线，完美平衡了工业蓝图的严谨性与动漫插画的艺术感染力。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/item_807_3.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "A Japanese anime-style sci-fi mecha mechanical design sheet (horizontal illustration). The overall image employs precise, clean linework and semi-realistic cel-shading techniques, presenting the quality of an official anime setting collection design page. The dominant color palette consists of soft dark red, medium gray, and metallic tones. The main subject is a sci-fi mecha displayed in an exploded/deconstructed view, laid out in a reference sheet format.\n\nOn the left-center of the frame, occupying a larger area, is the mecha's full-body front view in an angled three-quarter standing pose, showcasing slender limbs, layered red-and-gray alternating armor plates, exposed metallic hydraulic rods, and complex knee joint assemblies; the chest armor is heavy, and the shoulder pauldrons are broad with exhaust louvers. The upper right of the frame features a head close-up, including front and side views, displaying the streamlined red head casing, silver-gray faceplate, a gold V-shaped antenna on the forehead, and glowing green main monitor (eyes). The lower right showcases hand and weapon close-ups, including the intricate joint construction of mechanical fingers in open and clenched-fist positions, as well as a side view of a large metallic beam rifle equipped with a scope and energy magazine. The lower center of the frame features a partial close-up of the dorsal thrusters, displaying exhaust nozzles, folding metal wings, and intricate internal turbine structures.\n\nScattered around the various components are leader lines and handwritten-style concept annotations in Japanese and English. Above the full-body view is a prominent title: 'TYPE-04 ASSAULT MECHA', followed by smaller Japanese text: '強襲型機動兵器 零四式'. Beside the head close-up are annotations: 'メインカメラ', 'V字型アンテナ', and a handwritten note 'センサー感度調整必要'. Beside the weapon close-up: '高出力ビームライフル' and 'エネルギーパック'. Beside the thrusters: 'メインスラスター'. Along the edges of the frame are scattered notes: 'Note: Armor joints need more flexibility.' and '装甲の軽量化'.\n\nThe background is rendered in a loose watercolor anime landscape style, with subdued, understated tones that do not overpower the foreground. The bottom of the frame and the distant background depict moss-covered grassland ruins with scattered massive concrete blocks, while the far background faintly reveals steep cliff silhouettes and a futuristic sci-fi city skyline. The four corners of the frame feature subtle crosshair registration marks and reference lines, perfectly balancing the rigor of an industrial blueprint with the artistic expressiveness of anime illustration.",
    "prompt_zh": "将这张图片转化为受日本动漫机甲蓝图启发的风格化机械设计图。以精确、干净的线稿和半写实赛璐璐上色渲染主体，仿佛出自动漫设定集中的技术插图。将设计拆解为各部分（如头部、手部、配件、全身），以设定参考图的形式排列，包含不同角度和视图。加入散落的柔和手写注释或日文字符，如同概念标注。使用低饱和度数码色彩（红色、灰色、金属色调），背景以松散的水彩动漫风景绘制"
