    "revised_prompt": "数字摄影作品，采用竖版构图。画面中央呈现了一个极其复杂且精致的埃菲尔铁塔（Eiffel Tower）折纸模型。该模型由带有明显纤维质感的暖灰色与浅金色纸张折叠而成，精确再现了铁塔的四方底座、层级观景台以及高耸的塔尖，纸张的层叠错落有致，几何结构严谨。由于是竖向画幅，铁塔修长的身形在画面中下部得到了充分的舒展展示。\n\n在铁塔模型的正上方，呈现一个由粗体折纸风格立体字母组成的单词 'PARIS'。这五个字母呈优雅的拱形排列悬浮，采用法国国旗的经典色彩——深蓝色、纯白色和鲜红色的高饱和度纸张折成。每个字母自身也具有清晰的折痕和多面立体的块面感。\n\n背景是柔和且极简的浅米色中性色调，表面带有微妙的粗糙水彩纸纹理以及极浅的抽象几何压纹，营造出干净透气的空间。柔和漫反射的自然光从画面左侧偏上方打入，在折纸的棱角处形成细腻的高光，并在纸张内部层叠处和背景上投射出柔和渐变的阴影。光影处理极大地增强了每一道折痕的视觉深度与锐利度。整体视觉风格逼真写实，充满手工制作的匠心，凸显了纸张的物质纹理、几何学的精确性以及整体色彩的和谐美感。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/item_841_4.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "A digital photography work in portrait orientation. At the center of the frame is an extremely complex and exquisite origami model of the Eiffel Tower. The model is folded from paper with a noticeable fibrous texture in warm gray and light gold tones, accurately reproducing the tower's four-sided base, tiered observation decks, and soaring spire. The layers of paper are meticulously staggered, and the geometric structure is rigorous. Thanks to the vertical format, the slender silhouette of the tower is fully displayed and stretched out in the lower-center portion of the frame.\n\nDirectly above the tower model, the word 'PARIS' appears, composed of bold, origami-style three-dimensional letters. The five letters are arranged in an elegant arch formation, appearing to float, and are folded from highly saturated paper in the classic colors of the French flag—deep blue, pure white, and vivid red. Each letter itself features clearly visible creases and a multi-faceted, blocky three-dimensional quality.\n\nThe background is a soft and minimalist light beige neutral tone, with a surface bearing subtle rough watercolor paper texture and very faint abstract geometric embossing, creating a clean and airy space. Soft, diffused natural light enters from the upper-left side of the frame, forming delicate highlights along the edges and ridges of the origami, while casting soft, gradient shadows within the layered folds of the paper and onto the background. The light and shadow treatment greatly enhances the visual depth and sharpness of every crease. The overall visual style is realistic and lifelike, brimming with the craftsmanship of handmade artistry, highlighting the material texture of the paper, the precision of the geometry, and the harmonious aesthetic of the overall color palette.",
    "prompt_zh": "一张正方形1:1格式的数码照片，展示一个精致的纸质折纸模型，呈现(MONUMENT_NAME)，由带纹理的彩色纸折叠而成，居中于画面。上方，(CITY_NAME)字样以粗体折纸风格字母呈现，使用该国国旗颜色的鲜艳纸张折叠而成，排列成优雅的拱形。背景柔和而简洁，为浅粉彩色或中性色调，带有细微的纸质纹理或抽象几何细节。光线柔和且漫射，投射出自然阴影，增强每个折痕的深度和锐度。整体风格干净、"
