    "revised_prompt": "一幅横向构图的童话故事书插画，采用具有强烈速度感和动感的侧后方跟随视角。画面主体是一个穿着蓝白条纹宽松睡衣的小男孩，他正在一片奇幻的空间中向前全速冲刺。男孩身体大幅度前倾，头顶的长条形睡帽和衣角在风中剧烈向后飘动。他的右手紧紧提着一盏复古黄铜提灯，提灯散发出明亮的光芒。随着他的奔跑，提灯和他的身体后方拖拽出一条长长的、由无数闪烁的金色星尘和发光微粒组成的星光轨迹。\n\n男孩穿梭在一个由梦境元素构成的悬浮迷宫中。画面四周和深处错落有致地漂浮着各种各样的门：右侧有一扇半开的厚重红木门，门缝透出刺眼的白光；左上方悬浮着一扇缠绕着发光藤蔓的拱形石门；视线远端还有几扇大小不一的彩色小木门。空间中散布着形态各异的钟表，有表面扭曲如同融化般的巨大怀表，也有悬浮在半空中、表盘数字错乱的古董落地钟。空气中具象化的“低语”化作一条条发光的半透明丝带和碎纸片在男孩周围飞舞，丝带上清晰可见发光的斜体英文单词：'Wake up'、'Hurry' 和 'Follow the light'。\n\n画面的主色调由深邃的靛蓝色和温暖的琥珀金色构成。背景是深不可测的靛蓝色梦境虚空，而提灯的光晕、星光拖尾、表盘的指针以及发光的文字丝带则呈现出明亮的琥珀金色，形成极具视觉冲击力的冷暖对比。整体绘画风格具有典型的水彩童话插画质感，色彩过渡自然，光影柔和梦幻，充分展现了异想天开的奇妙氛围与快节奏的紧迫感。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/item_907_4.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "A horizontally composed fairy tale storybook illustration, employing a rear-side tracking perspective with a strong sense of speed and dynamism. The main subject is a young boy wearing loose blue-and-white striped pajamas, sprinting at full speed through a fantastical space. The boy's body leans dramatically forward, with his long, pointed nightcap and the edges of his clothing fluttering violently backward in the wind. His right hand tightly grips a vintage brass lantern that emits a bright glow. As he runs, a long trail of countless shimmering golden star dust and luminous particles streams behind the lantern and his body.\n\nThe boy dashes through a floating labyrinth composed of dreamscape elements. Scattered throughout the frame and into its depths, various doors float at staggered heights: on the right side, a heavy mahogany door stands half-open with blinding white light piercing through the gap; in the upper left, an arched stone door entwined with glowing vines hovers in mid-air; further in the distance, several small colorful wooden doors of varying sizes can be seen. Clocks of various forms are scattered throughout the space—there are enormous pocket watches with surfaces warped and distorted as if melting, as well as antique grandfather clocks suspended in mid-air with scrambled dial numbers. Materialized \"whispers\" in the air take the form of glowing, semi-transparent ribbons and scraps of paper swirling around the boy. On the ribbons, glowing italicized English words are clearly visible: 'Wake up', 'Hurry', and 'Follow the light'.\n\nThe dominant color palette of the scene consists of deep indigo blue and warm amber gold. The background is an unfathomably deep indigo-blue dreamscape void, while the lantern's glow, the starlight trail, the clock hands, and the glowing text ribbons all present a bright amber gold, creating a visually striking contrast between cool and warm tones. The overall painting style has a quintessential watercolor fairy tale illustration quality, with natural color transitions and soft, dreamlike lighting, fully conveying a whimsical, wondrous atmosphere along with a fast-paced sense of urgency.",
    "prompt_zh": "[Character] 疾跑穿过梦境元素，绘本插画风格，由漂浮的门、时钟和低语构成的迷宫，灯笼辉光与环绕的光点拖尾，[Color1]和[Color2]，奇幻且节奏紧凑，跟随镜头风格带有拖尾的追随视角"
}, {
