    "revised_prompt": "高质量的户外自然摄影照片，呈现出明亮清新的热带度假肖像风格。画面采用16:9的宽幅比例和轻微仰拍的特写视角。画面主体是一位女性，身体微微侧向一侧。她正举起一只手臂，指尖轻轻触摸上方质朴的木制屋顶结构。她的面容保持自然真实的特征，肌肤呈现出被阳光亲吻过的健康光泽，脸颊带着柔和自然的腮红。她有着一头长长的、略显凌乱的深色秀发，一侧头发别在耳后，耳际佩戴着一朵硕大的白色鸡蛋花。她的目光柔和而充满好奇，视线望向镜头之外。脖子上佩戴着一条纤细的金色链条项链。服装方面，她外穿一件宽大的米色长袖纽扣衬衫，面料轻薄，顶部几颗纽扣敞开，胸前可见一个微小的刺绣‘Polo Ralph Lauren’品牌徽标；衬衫敞开处清晰地露出内搭的动物印花露脐上衣。人物身处一个热带海滩小屋或海滨木制凉亭中，画面上方横亘着原木色的木梁和茅草屋顶。得益于宽幅构图，人物身后的广阔背景得以充分展现且清晰可见。背景是一片湛蓝清澈的海洋，上方是飘浮着零星白云的明亮天空。在视野的远处，可以清晰辨认出绵延的城市天际线和沿海建筑群。明亮的自然阳光洒落，在人物的皮肤和衣物上形成温暖的高光。整体景深清晰，主体人物和背景均保持锐利，色调鲜艳明快，充满沿海的生机，传达出悠闲、温暖且放松的热带度假氛围。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/item_1342_2.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "A high-quality outdoor natural photograph presenting a bright and fresh tropical vacation portrait style. The frame adopts a 16:9 wide aspect ratio with a slight low-angle close-up perspective. The main subject is a female figure, her body turned slightly to one side. She is raising one arm, with her fingertips gently touching the rustic wooden roof structure above. Her facial features remain natural and authentic, with skin exhibiting a healthy, sun-kissed glow and cheeks bearing a soft, natural blush. She has long, slightly tousled dark hair, with one side tucked behind her ear, adorned with a large white frangipani flower at the temple. Her gaze is soft and filled with curiosity, looking beyond the camera. Around her neck, she wears a delicate gold chain necklace. In terms of clothing, she wears an oversized beige long-sleeved button-up shirt in lightweight fabric, with the top few buttons left undone, revealing a tiny embroidered 'Polo Ralph Lauren' brand logo on the chest; through the open shirt, a cropped animal-print top worn underneath is clearly visible. The subject is situated in a tropical beach hut or a seaside wooden gazebo, with natural-toned wooden beams and a thatched roof spanning across the top of the frame. Thanks to the wide-format composition, the expansive background behind the subject is fully displayed and clearly visible. The background features a stretch of clear, azure ocean beneath a bright sky dotted with scattered white clouds. In the far distance, an extending city skyline and coastal buildings can be clearly discerned. Bright natural sunlight cascades down, creating warm highlights on the subject's skin and clothing. The overall depth of field is sharp, with both the main subject and background remaining crisp. The color tones are vivid and lively, full of coastal vitality, conveying a leisurely, warm, and relaxed tropical vacation atmosphere.",
