    "revised_prompt": "一张横幅宽比例的复古胶片摄影照片。画面主体是一位年轻女子，她正坐在一辆高速行驶的复古汽车的副驾驶座上，上半身向后仰，探出敞开的车窗外。她拥有一头长长的棕色卷发，头发在极度狂风的吹拂下剧烈地向后飘散在空中，呈现出充满张力的动态。她身穿一件白色的露肩针织上衣。背景设定在夜晚的城市或公路，由于汽车的高速运动和黑暗的环境，车窗外的景象化作了完全模糊、拉丝的深色轨迹与温暖的光带，无法辨识出任何具体的建筑或物体形状。画面采用了重度的动态模糊和柔焦效果，表面覆盖着明显的复古胶片粗糙颗粒感。光线处于低光环境，女子主要被一束温暖、柔和的复古相机闪光灯照亮，与背景中拖曳拉丝的街道环境灯光交织混融。整体色调偏暗，光影与模糊的背景共同营造出一种梦幻、忧郁且充满风中氛围的视觉体验，宽幅构图强化了人物探出车窗的动作与背景光轨延伸的速度感。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/item_1350_2.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "A vintage film photography photo in a wide banner aspect ratio. The main subject is a young woman sitting in the passenger seat of a fast-moving vintage car, leaning her upper body back and out through the open car window. She has long brown curly hair that is violently blown backward through the air by the extreme wind, creating a dynamic full of tension. She wears a white off-shoulder knitted top. The background is set on a nighttime city road or highway; due to the car's high speed and the dark environment, the scenery outside the window dissolves into completely blurred, streaked dark trails and warm light bands, with no discernible shapes of any specific buildings or objects. The image employs heavy motion blur and soft focus effects, with the surface covered in prominent vintage film coarse grain texture. The lighting is in a low-light environment, with the woman primarily illuminated by a warm, soft vintage camera flash, interweaving and blending with the trailing, streaked ambient street lights in the background. The overall color tone is dark, and the interplay of light, shadow, and the blurred background collectively creates a dreamy, melancholic, and wind-swept atmospheric visual experience. The wide-format composition reinforces the sense of speed conveyed by the woman leaning out of the car window and the extending light trails in the background.",
    "prompt_zh": "{\"图片提示词结构\":{\"元数据\":{\"类型\":\"复古胶片摄影\",\"尺寸\":\"1200x1200px\"},\"风格与氛围\":{\"美学\":\"暗调、颗粒感的复古胶片质感（例如 Kodak Portra 800）\",\"情绪\":\"梦幻、忧郁、模糊、氛围感\",\"效果\":\"因运动和风造成的强烈运动模糊，柔焦\"},\"主体\":{\"身份指令\":\"关键：不要改变参考身份的面部特征。保持头部姿态不变。\",\"外貌\":{\"头发\":\"棕色长波浪卷发，被风大幅吹散\"},\"服装\":\"白色露肩针织上衣\"},\"动作与姿势\":{\"描述\":\"主体"
