    "revised_prompt": "一张复古直闪光摄影快照。画面采用微仰视的低角度构图，展现了一位20岁出头的年轻女性盘腿坐在一张略显破旧的复古沙发中央。她肤色白皙，五官柔和自然，留着一头黑色长发，梳成两条松散的麻花辫，发丝间带有逼真的细碎毛躁感。女孩化着极简的清透底妆，脸颊和双唇透出柔和的粉色，眼神直视镜头，神态平静、私密且略带俏皮。她身穿一件紧身的白色棉质细吊带上衣和配套的白色高腰短裤，头上戴着一副黑色包耳式游戏耳机，耳机线自然地垂搭在肩膀上。她的双手自然地握着一个黑色无线游戏手柄。\n\n在女孩身旁的沙发上，放着一只小巧的皮卡丘（Pikachu）毛绒玩具，她的身后靠着一个带有纹理的红色抱枕。沙发的角落里挤着其他几个毛绒玩具，附近还散落着几只复古游戏手柄。背景是一个氛围昏暗、充满生活气息的复古游戏室。后方立着密集的黑色置物架，上面堆满了各种收藏品，包括层叠堆放的复古游戏主机、尺寸各异的盒装动作手办、掌上游戏机和成排的复古游戏卡带盒。货架下层隐约可见一台老式 CRT 显示器。\n\n画面的光影具有鲜明的特点：强烈的机顶直闪光直接打在人物正面，在面部和纯白色的衣物上形成明亮的高光，并在人物和物体后方投下锐利的深色阴影。背景深处有一盏散发暖黄色柔光的钨丝落地灯，提供了温馨的环境底光。整体色调以暖色为基调，女孩洁白的衣着与背景货架上玩具包装混杂的红色、黑色和暗霓虹色形成鲜明对比。画面呈现出强烈的80至90年代胶片快照风格，带有清晰可见的胶片颗粒感和高对比度，人物面部及衣物纹理极其锐利，完美传达出一种怀旧、私密且充满自信的宅家游戏氛围。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/item_1367_4.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "A vintage direct-flash photography snapshot. The image uses a slightly low-angle, upward-tilted composition, showing a young woman in her early 20s sitting cross-legged in the center of a slightly worn vintage sofa. She has fair skin, soft and natural features, and long black hair styled into two loose braids with realistic fine flyaway frizz between the strands. The girl wears minimal sheer base makeup, with a soft pink hue on her cheeks and lips, gazing directly into the camera with a calm, intimate, and slightly playful expression. She is dressed in a tight white cotton thin-strap camisole top with matching white high-waisted shorts, and wears a pair of black over-ear gaming headphones on her head, with the headphone cable draping naturally over her shoulders. Her hands casually hold a black wireless gaming controller.\n\nOn the sofa beside the girl sits a small Pikachu plush toy, and behind her rests a textured red throw pillow. The corner of the sofa is crammed with several other plush toys, and a few vintage game controllers are scattered nearby. The background is a dimly lit, lived-in vintage game room. Behind her stand densely packed black shelving units loaded with various collectibles, including stacked vintage game consoles, boxed action figures of assorted sizes, handheld game devices, and rows of vintage game cartridge cases. On the lower shelves, an old CRT monitor is faintly visible.\n\nThe lighting of the image has distinctive characteristics: a strong on-camera direct flash hits the subject from the front, creating bright highlights on her face and pure white clothing, while casting sharp dark shadows behind the subject and objects. Deep in the background, a tungsten floor lamp emits a warm yellow soft glow, providing a cozy ambient fill light. The overall color palette is warm-toned, with the girl's pristine white attire contrasting sharply against the mixed red, black, and dark neon colors of the toy packaging on the background shelves. The image exhibits a strong 1980s-to-1990s film snapshot aesthetic, with clearly visible film grain and high contrast. The facial details and clothing textures are extremely sharp, perfectly conveying a nostalgic, intimate, and confidently at-home gaming atmosphere.",
