    "revised_prompt": "一幅超写实的竖版摄影作品，展现了一个现代高端企业会议室的场景。画面采用竖向构图，视觉焦点是一块巨大的壁挂式玻璃白板。在白板旁，站着一位身穿商务正装的演讲者，他正侧身面向白板和观众，手臂伸出做着讲解的手势。画面下方，几位穿着职场装扮的专业人士围坐在一张光滑的黑色会议桌旁，背对或侧对镜头，抬头全神贯注地注视着白板。\n\n玻璃白板上用深钴蓝色的马克笔写满了自然的人类手写体内容。最上方是粗体、全大写且略带手写不完美感的大标题：'THE FUTURE OF AI IN HEALTHCARE'。标题下方自上而下分布着三个带有手绘图标和边框的集群结构：\n\n第一个集群副标题为斜体的 'DIAGNOSTICS'，下方带有小而整洁的笔记 'Early Detection' 和 'Image Analysis'，旁边画着一个手绘的放大镜图标。\n第二个集群副标题为斜体的 'TREATMENT'，下方的笔记写着 'Personalized Medicine' 和 'Robotic Surgery'，配有一个手绘的医疗十字图标。\n第三个集群副标题为斜体的 'PATIENT CARE'，笔记内容为 '24/7 Monitoring' 和 'Virtual Assistants'，旁边画着一个带心电图线条的手绘爱心图标。\n\n在这些文字区块之间，穿插着带有轻微手部抖动和压力变化的手绘连线与箭头。白板的右下方画着一个粗略的条形图，横坐标标记着 '2024'、'2025'、'2026'，纵坐标写着 'Growth'。底部还有一个圆形的迷你时间轴，标注着 'Phase 1'、'Phase 2'、'Phase 3'。\n\n白板上的蓝色墨水质感极度逼真，能清晰看到笔画边缘颜色较深，中间带有细微的墨水条纹和高光反射，笔画末端还有微小的墨水晕染和污迹。光滑的玻璃表面倒映出会议室的顶灯光晕以及坐在桌前的与会者的模糊身影。背景中可以看到高大的落地窗，窗外隐约透出现代城市的高楼轮廓。整体画面采用电影级的高级办公照明，光影极具立体感，呈现出8K分辨率级别的极致清晰度和丰富的材质细节。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/item_1378_3.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "A hyper-realistic vertical-format photographic work depicting the scene of a modern high-end corporate conference room. The image uses a vertical composition, with the visual focal point being a large wall-mounted glass whiteboard. Standing beside the whiteboard is a presenter dressed in business formal attire, turned sideways to face both the whiteboard and the audience, with an arm extended in an explanatory gesture. In the lower portion of the frame, several professionally dressed individuals sit around a sleek black conference table, with their backs or sides to the camera, looking up and fully focused on the whiteboard.\n\nThe glass whiteboard is filled with natural human handwriting in deep cobalt blue marker. At the very top is a bold, all-caps title with a slightly imperfect handwritten feel: 'THE FUTURE OF AI IN HEALTHCARE.' Below the title, arranged from top to bottom, are three cluster structures with hand-drawn icons and borders:\n\nThe first cluster has the subtitle in italics, 'DIAGNOSTICS,' with small, neat notes below reading 'Early Detection' and 'Image Analysis,' accompanied by a hand-drawn magnifying glass icon.\nThe second cluster has the subtitle in italics, 'TREATMENT,' with notes reading 'Personalized Medicine' and 'Robotic Surgery,' accompanied by a hand-drawn medical cross icon.\nThe third cluster has the subtitle in italics, 'PATIENT CARE,' with notes reading '24/7 Monitoring' and 'Virtual Assistants,' accompanied by a hand-drawn heart icon with an ECG line.\n\nInterspersed between these text blocks are hand-drawn connecting lines and arrows with slight hand tremor and pressure variations. In the lower right of the whiteboard is a rough bar chart, with the horizontal axis labeled '2024,' '2025,' '2026,' and the vertical axis labeled 'Growth.' At the bottom is a circular mini timeline annotated with 'Phase 1,' 'Phase 2,' 'Phase 3.'\n\nThe blue ink texture on the whiteboard is extremely realistic, with clearly visible darker edges on strokes, subtle ink striations and specular highlights in the middle, and tiny ink bleeds and smudges at stroke endings. The smooth glass surface reflects the overhead light halos of the conference room and the blurred silhouettes of the attendees seated at the table. In the background",
