    "revised_prompt": "一张休闲户外生活方式的人像摄影照片。画面的主体是一位女性，她正坐在一个缆车吊厢内部的长椅上。女性面带温暖柔和的微笑，眼神放松，头部微微向下倾斜并注视着镜头。她留着一头棕色头发，发丝松散蓬松、微微凌乱，脸颊两侧有自然垂落的碎发修饰脸型。她身穿浅灰色的休闲运动套装，上半身是一件细肩带的修身吊带露脐上衣，下半身是一条舒适的浅灰色宽松阔腿运动裤。脚上穿着一双带有黑色条纹的白色阿迪达斯（Adidas）运动鞋。她的右手腕上佩戴着一块白色智能手表。\n\n在姿态方面，她侧身坐在长椅上，身体直立但状态放松，肩膀微微转向镜头。她的双腿自然放松并微微弯曲，一只手臂随意地搭在膝盖上，另一只手臂轻轻支撑着身体以保持平衡。\n\n环境与背景方面，透过缆车的窗户，可以看到生机勃勃的自然景观。背景包含茂盛的绿树、大片的森林以及远处的起伏山丘，天空中可以清晰地看到延伸的缆车缆绳线条。\n\n视觉与构图方面，画面采用中全景的竖版构图，摄影机视角呈现轻微的低角度，正对主体。焦点清晰地集中在女性身上，背景进行了轻微的柔焦虚化处理以突出人物。光线是柔和的自然日光，带有温暖的黄金时刻色调，阳光在女性的皮肤和衣物上洒下柔和的光晕。整体色调由大自然的绿色、天空的柔和蓝色、衣物的浅灰色以及温暖的肤色交织而成，呈现出清新、放松、阳光且自然的氛围。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/item_1385_3.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "A casual outdoor lifestyle portrait photography shot. The main subject of the image is a woman seated on a bench inside a cable car gondola. The woman wears a warm, gentle smile with relaxed eyes, her head tilted slightly downward while gazing at the camera. She has brown hair that is loosely tousled and slightly disheveled, with natural wispy bangs framing her face on both sides of her cheeks. She is dressed in a light gray casual athletic outfit—the upper half featuring a slim-fit spaghetti-strap crop top, and the lower half a pair of comfortable light gray loose wide-leg sweatpants. On her feet, she wears a pair of white Adidas sneakers with black stripes. On her right wrist, she wears a white smartwatch.\n\nIn terms of posture, she is seated sideways on the bench, her body upright yet relaxed, with her shoulders turned slightly toward the camera. Her legs are naturally relaxed and slightly bent, one arm casually resting on her knee, while the other arm gently supports her body to maintain balance.\n\nRegarding the environment and background, through the cable car windows, vibrant natural scenery is visible. The background includes lush green trees, expansive forests, and rolling hills in the distance, with cable car cable lines clearly visible stretching across the sky.\n\nIn terms of visuals and composition, the image employs a medium-full shot in vertical composition, with the camera angle presenting a slight low angle, facing the subject directly. The focus is sharply concentrated on the woman, with the background given a slight soft-focus bokeh treatment to emphasize the subject. The lighting is soft natural daylight with warm golden hour tones, sunlight casting a gentle glow on the woman's skin and clothing. The overall color palette is woven from nature's greens, the sky's soft blues, the light gray of her clothing, and warm skin tones, presenting a fresh, relaxed, sunny, and natural atmosphere.",
