    "revised_prompt": "超写实风格的电影级肖像摄影作品，采用竖版构图。画面中央是一位年轻女性，呈现四分之三侧面视角，脸部略微向上仰起。她留着一头黑色的短发，发丝柔软且略带随性的凌乱感。女性面带自信的微笑，目光自然，双臂交叉抱于胸前，身穿一件纯青色的长袖圆领衬衫。背景是深邃的纯黑色工作室布景。画面呈现出强烈的戏剧性灯光效果：右侧投射出明亮的红色轮廓光，精准地勾勒出她右侧的发丝、脸部轮廓、肩膀及手臂的边缘线；左侧则打下柔和的冷蓝色补光，照亮了她的左侧脸颊和衣服细节。红蓝双色光影在人物身上形成鲜明的冷暖对比，极大地增强了画面的立体感与电影氛围。人物面孔刻画极其细腻，皮肤纹理、毛孔以及眼球中的眼神光均清晰逼真。在画面的边缘角落位置，清晰可见一行签名字母：'Shreya Yadav'。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/item_1394_4.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "A hyper-realistic, cinematic-grade portrait photography work in vertical composition. At the center of the frame is a young woman, presented in a three-quarter profile view with her face tilted slightly upward. She has short black hair, the strands soft with a casually tousled feel. The woman wears a confident smile with a natural gaze, her arms crossed over her chest, dressed in a solid cyan long-sleeve crew-neck shirt. The background is a deep, pure black studio setting. The image exhibits dramatic lighting effects: from the right side, a bright red rim light is cast, precisely outlining the edges of her hair, facial contour, shoulders, and arms on the right; from the left side, a soft cool blue fill light illuminates her left cheek and clothing details. The red and blue dual-tone lighting creates a striking warm-cool contrast on the subject, greatly enhancing the three-dimensionality and cinematic atmosphere of the image. The rendering of the subject's face is extremely detailed, with skin texture, pores, and catchlights in the eyes all clearly and realistically depicted. At the edge corners of the frame, a line of signature letters is clearly visible: 'Shreya Yadav'.",
    "prompt_zh": "{\"prompt\":\"一张超写实的年轻女性肖像，短而凌乱的黑发，柔和的短发造型与参考图匹配，自信微笑，双臂交叉，穿着青色长袖圆领衫。右侧有戏剧性的红色轮廓光，左侧有冷蓝色补光，纯黑色摄影棚背景。四分之三视角，略微仰视，电影感肖像摄影。使用提供的参考图像作为面部——不要改变面部。\",\"reference_face\":\"use_reference_image\",\"style\":\"电影感、超写实、戏剧性灯光\",\"lighting"
