    "revised_prompt_en": "A portrait-orientation indoor portrait photography shot. At the center of the frame is a young woman seated on a light brown rattan sofa, her upper body twisted backward, looking back over her shoulder toward the camera with a friendly, natural smile. She has long dark brown hair, one side pinned back with a simple hair clip. She wears a loose, beige casual short-sleeve T-shirt, with a printed graphic partially visible on the back featuring the uppercase letters 'FRISTON' along with some graphic design elements. On the lower half, she wears light blue washed denim shorts and a pair of white sneakers.\n\nThe sofa is fitted with comfortable white cushions. On the floor around the sofa, a few everyday clothing items are casually scattered, creating a relaxed, languid atmosphere rich with authentic, lived-in charm. The background consists of light-colored interior walls.\n\nThe shot is framed in a medium view with a slightly elevated eye level. The lighting is soft, warm indoor light, and the overall color palette is dominated by off-white, light denim blue, rattan brown, and white, presenting a cozy warm tone. The photographic style carries a strong documentary and candid snapshot quality, with moderate depth of field and a subtly soft, blurred background. The image bears a hint of subtle film grain, with slightly desaturated colors, exuding the classic charm of film photography.",
