    "revised_prompt": "一张具有电影感的夜间车载肖像摄影照片，采用竖屏构图。画面主体为一名年轻女性，正坐在行驶中的汽车内。她身体微微向敞开的车窗倾斜，但重心依然安稳地保留在车内座椅上，转头向后方注视着镜头。她的表情放松、自然，眼神中透出亲密感，嘴角带着一丝略显俏皮的微笑。她的头发被车窗外灌入的夜风向后扬起，发丝在半空中凌乱飘散。人物的面部细节清晰逼真，肤色呈现出柔和温暖的光泽。她身穿一件宽松的奶油色针织毛衣，领口慵懒地滑落至一侧，露出单侧肩膀和锁骨，毛衣柔软的针织纹理清晰可见。\n\n镜头视角设定在车内，距离人物极近，构图紧凑，营造出极强的亲密感。焦点精准锁定在人物的脸部和被风吹拂的头发上，画面前景边缘隐约可见模糊的车窗框轮廓。\n\n车窗外是昏暗的夜间道路背景。天空呈现深邃的海军蓝色，朦胧的月光透过薄云在天际漫射开来。道路两侧的柔和路灯因为车辆的快速移动而拉长，在背景中化作一道道发光的低饱和度光轨。画面的整体色调混合了深海军蓝色与低饱和度的冷色调，并巧妙地点缀着柔和的粉色光晕。光影对比度低，充满情绪张力，整体笼罩在一种微妙的复古蓝灰色电影氛围中，画面表面还覆盖着一层柔和、梦幻的细腻胶片颗粒质感。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/item_1447_2.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "A cinematic nighttime in-car portrait photography shot in portrait orientation. The main subject is a young woman seated inside a moving car. She leans slightly toward the open car window while her center of gravity remains securely on the car seat, turning her head back to gaze at the camera. Her expression is relaxed and natural, her eyes conveying a sense of intimacy, with a hint of a playful smile at the corners of her lips. Her hair is swept backward by the night wind rushing in through the car window, with strands scattering loosely in mid-air. The facial details of the subject are crisp and lifelike, her skin exhibiting a soft, warm glow. She wears a loose cream-colored knit sweater with the neckline lazily slipping off to one side, revealing a bare shoulder and collarbone, the soft knit texture of the sweater clearly visible.\n\nThe camera angle is positioned inside the car, extremely close to the subject, with a tight composition that creates an intense sense of intimacy. The focus is precisely locked on the subject's face and her wind-swept hair, while the edges of the foreground faintly reveal the blurred outline of the car window frame.\n\nOutside the car window lies a dim nighttime road backdrop. The sky displays a deep navy blue, with hazy moonlight diffusing through thin clouds across the horizon. The soft streetlights lining both sides of the road are elongated by the vehicle's rapid movement, transforming into streaks of glowing, desaturated light trails in the background. The overall color palette blends deep navy blue with desaturated cool tones, artfully punctuated by soft pink halos of light. The light-shadow contrast is low, brimming with emotional tension, the entire scene enveloped in a subtle vintage blue-gray cinematic atmosphere, with the image surface overlaid by a layer of soft, dreamlike, fine film grain texture.",
