    "revised_prompt": "一张2006年的数码抓拍照片，呈现出横向宽幅构图与早期数码相机略带颗粒感的影像质感。画面主体是一位留着浓密胡须的男子，身穿深蓝与米色相间的横条纹长袖衬衫，正坐在一家西雅图咖啡馆内，双手拿着一份展开的报纸专注阅读。报纸版面上印有清晰的黑色英文大写报头 'The Seattle Times'，下方是粗体头条新闻标题 'CITY COUNCIL DEBATES TRANSIT EXPANSION' 以及侧边栏小标题 'WEATHER: RECORD RAINFALL CONTINUES'。男子面前是一张带有深浅不一的划痕和褪色包浆的做旧实木桌子，桌面上除了报纸，还放置着一只白色的厚底陶瓷马克杯，杯旁边放着一把银色金属小勺。男子身后是一扇宽大的玻璃窗，占据了画面的大半个背景。玻璃上布满了密集的雨水条痕和凝结的水珠，雨水的折射使得窗外的街景变得模糊不清，仅能辨认出灰蓝色的阴雨天空、潮湿的柏油路面轮廓，以及街道上穿行的汽车所透出的模糊红色尾灯与黄色车头灯光晕。咖啡馆内散发着暖黄色的灯光，一盏复古吊灯的轮廓隐约倒映在满是雨水的玻璃窗上，与室外冷灰色的雨景形成强烈的冷暖色调对比。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/item_1545_2.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "A digitally captured snapshot from 2006, featuring a horizontal wide-format composition with the slightly grainy image quality characteristic of early digital cameras. The main subject is a man with a thick beard, wearing a long-sleeve shirt with horizontal stripes in dark blue and beige, seated inside a Seattle coffee shop, holding an open newspaper with both hands and reading intently. The newspaper's masthead displays clear black uppercase English lettering reading 'The Seattle Times,' with a bold headline below reading 'CITY COUNCIL DEBATES TRANSIT EXPANSION' and a sidebar sub-headline reading 'WEATHER: RECORD RAINFALL CONTINUES.' In front of the man is a distressed solid wood table with scratches of varying depth and a faded patina. On the tabletop, besides the newspaper, sits a white thick-bottomed ceramic mug, with a small silver metal spoon placed beside it. Behind the man is a large glass window occupying most of the background. The glass is covered with dense rain streaks and condensed water droplets, the refraction of the rainwater rendering the street scene outside blurred and indistinct—only a grey-blue overcast sky, the outline of wet asphalt pavement, and the blurred red taillights and yellow headlight halos of cars passing along the street can be made out. The interior of the coffee shop is bathed in warm yellow lighting, and the silhouette of a vintage pendant lamp is faintly reflected on the rain-covered glass window, creating a striking warm-cool color contrast with the cold grey rain scene outside.",
