    "revised_prompt": "这是一张呈现千禧年代Y2K原生夜景摄影风格的照片。采用适合896x1200比例的竖版中景构图，视角为平视。画面主体为坐在深夜汽车后座的一对男女，两人紧密相依，面部特征和比例保持自然写实。男人身穿全黑西装套装，内搭黑色衬衫，他正温柔地用手臂环抱着女人的脖颈，低头轻吻她的太阳穴。女人双眼微闭，神态宁静，身体柔和地向男人倾斜。女人穿着一件优雅的黑色长袖高领连衣裙，衣服材质为厚实的哑光面料，肩膀被完全遮盖，呈现经典的修身轮廓。画面模拟85毫米人像镜头的浅景深效果，采用强烈的正面直射机顶闪光灯照明。强光在人物皮肤和带有雨水的湿润车窗玻璃上形成了锐利的高光，并在人物背后的座椅上投下边缘清晰的黑色阴影，呈现出极高的明暗对比。车内环境幽暗，冷夜空气带来一丝微妙的雾气感。背景是起雾的车窗玻璃，表面布满清晰的雨滴，玻璃上局部反射着强烈的闪光灯白光。透过车窗的柔和虚化背景中，深邃的暗夜里隐约透出车外城市街道温暖的模糊灯光光斑。整体视觉表现亲切、平静，具有浓郁的复古纪实氛围。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/item_1582_2.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "This is a photograph exhibiting the native nighttime photography aesthetic of the Y2K millennial era. It employs a vertical mid-shot composition suited to an 896×1200 aspect ratio, with an eye-level perspective. The main subjects are a man and a woman seated in the back seat of a car late at night, leaning closely together, with facial features and proportions kept naturally realistic. The man wears an all-black suit ensemble with a black shirt underneath, tenderly wrapping his arm around the woman's neck and leaning down to gently kiss her temple. The woman's eyes are softly closed, her expression serene, her body leaning gently toward the man. She is dressed in an elegant black long-sleeve high-neck dress made of a thick matte fabric, with shoulders fully covered, presenting a classic fitted silhouette. The image simulates the shallow depth-of-field effect of an 85mm portrait lens, lit with strong direct on-camera flash illumination. The harsh light creates sharp highlights on the subjects' skin and on the rain-wet car window glass, while casting hard-edged black shadows on the seat behind them, producing extremely high contrast between light and dark. The car interior is dim, with a subtle haze lent by the cold night air. The background consists of fogged car window glass, its surface covered with distinct raindrops, with portions of the glass reflecting the intense white flash light. Through the softly defocused background beyond the car windows, warm blurred light spots from city street lights outside faintly emerge in the deep darkness of night. The overall visual impression is intimate and tranquil, imbued with a rich retro documentary atmosphere.",
    "prompt_zh": "{\"generation_constraints\": {\"identity_preservation\": \"严格锁定参考照片中两位主体的完整身份特征\", \"facial_features\": \"不得改变面部、比例或自然表情\", \"style_reference\": \"原始Y2K夜拍风格\"}, \"camera_settings\": {\"lens\": \"85mm人像镜头\", \"focus\": \"浅景深\", \"angle\": \"平视角度\", \"framing\": \"中景镜头\", \"technique\": \"强烈的正面直射闪光灯（机顶闪光灯）\"}, \"subject_details\": {\"pose_interaction\": {\"position\": \"在汽车后座紧挨着坐在一起\", \"man_action\": \"轻柔地搂住女性的脖子，亲吻她的太阳穴\", \"woman_action\": \"…"
}, {
    "filename": "item_1583_3.png",
    "index": 1583,
    "title": "相机屏幕中的人像",
    "title_en": "Portrait Through Camera Screen",
    "prompt": "Use facial feature of attached photo. A close-up shot of a young woman displayed on the screen of a compact Canon digital camera. The camera body surrounds the image with its buttons, dials, and textured surface visible, including the FUNC/SET wheel, DISP button, and the “IMAGE STABILIZER” label along the side. The photo on the screen shows the woman indoors at night, illuminated by a bright built-in flash that creates sharp highlights on her face and hair. She has long dark hair falling across part of her face in loose strands, with a soft, slightly open-lip expression. The flash accentuates her features against a dim, cluttered kitchen background with appliances, shelves, and metallic surfaces softly blurred. The mood is candid, raw, nostalgic, and reminiscent of early 2000s digital camera snapshots. Colors are slightly muted with cool undertones, strong flash contrast, and natural grain from the display. No text, no logos inside the photo preview itself.Scale ratio: 4:5 verticalCamera: compact digital camera simulationLens: equivalent to 28–35mmAperture: f/2.8ISO: 400Shutter speed: 1/60 with flashWhite balance: auto flashLighting: harsh direct flash on subject, ambient low light in the backgroundColor grading: nostalgic digital-camera tones, high contrast flash, subtle display grain, authentic screen glow",
    "prompt_en": "Use facial feature of attached photo. A close-up shot of a young woman displayed on the screen of a compact Canon digital camera. The camera body surrounds the image with its buttons, dials, and textured surface visible, including the FUNC/SET wheel, DISP button, and the “IMAGE STABILIZER” label along the side. The photo on the screen shows the woman indoors at night, illuminated by a bright built-in flash that creates sharp highlights on her face and hair. She has long dark hair falling across part of her face in loose strands, with a soft, slightly open-lip expression. The flash accentuates her features against a dim, cluttered kitchen background with appliances, shelves, and metallic surfaces softly blurred. The mood is candid, raw, nostalgic, and reminiscent of early 2000s digital camera snapshots. Colors are slightly muted with cool undertones, strong flash contrast, and natural grain from the display. No text, no logos inside the photo preview itself.Scale ratio: 4:5 verticalCamera: compact digital camera simulationLens: equivalent to 28–35mmAperture: f/2.8ISO: 400Shutter speed: 1/60 with flashWhite balance: auto flashLighting: harsh direct flash on subject, ambient low light in the backgroundColor grading: nostalgic digital-camera tones, high contrast flash, subtle display grain, authentic screen glow",
    "source": "https://twitter.com/kingofdairyque/status/1993121789111935437",
    "type": "t2i",
    "author": "@ZaraIrahh",
    "author_link": "https://twitter.com/kingofdairyque/status/1993121789111935437",
    "revised_prompt": "一张聚焦于紧凑型佳能数码相机背面的特写照片，采用竖屏构图，呈现出‘画中画’的视觉效果。相机机身占据了画面框架，展现出带有细微纹理的表面材质，屏幕边缘环绕着物理按键与拨盘。清晰可见的UI和按键包括一个圆形的 'FUNC/SET' 滚轮按键、一个 'DISP.' 按钮，以及位于机身侧面的 'IMAGE STABILIZER' 标签。相机中央发光的LCD屏幕上显示着一张年轻女子的半身特写快照。屏幕中的女子处于夜间室内环境，长长的黑发自然披散，几缕松散的发丝垂落在脸颊上，她的嘴唇微微张开，表情柔和而自然。强烈的相机内置直射闪光灯照亮了她，在她的脸颊和发丝上形成了锐利且刺眼的高光，面部特征在强光下格外突出。女子身后的背景是一个昏暗且稍显杂乱的厨房，由于景深和弱光关系，背景中的厨房电器、置物架和带有微光的金属表面均呈现出柔和的失焦模糊状态。屏幕内的照片预览画面中没有附带任何文字或标志。整张图片的色调略显柔和并带有冷色调底色，屏幕画面带有自然的液晶显示器颗粒感和微弱的屏幕辉光，完美复刻了2000年代初数码相机的怀旧、原始与纪实抓拍感，强烈的闪光灯对比与背景的幽暗形成了极具年代感的视觉张力。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/item_1583_3.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "A close-up photo focused on the back of a compact Canon digital camera, composed in portrait orientation, presenting a 'picture-within-a-picture' visual effect. The camera body occupies the frame, revealing a surface material with subtle texture, with physical buttons and dials surrounding the screen edges. Clearly visible UI elements and buttons include a circular 'FUNC/SET' scroll wheel button, a 'DISP.' button, and an 'IMAGE STABILIZER' label on the side of the body. The glowing LCD screen at the center of the camera displays a half-body close-up snapshot of a young woman. The woman on the screen is in a nighttime indoor setting, with long black hair cascading naturally, a few loose strands falling across her cheeks, her lips slightly parted, her expression soft and natural. The strong built-in direct on-camera flash illuminates her, creating harsh and glaring highlights on her cheeks and hair strands, with facial features rendered particularly prominent under the intense light. Behind the woman, the background is a dim and slightly cluttered kitchen, where kitchen appliances, shelving, and metallic surfaces with faint glimmers all appear in soft, out-of-focus blur due to depth of field and low light. The photo preview on the screen contains no accompanying text or logos. The overall color tone of the image is slightly muted with a cool undertone, the screen image carries a natural LCD grain texture and faint screen glow, perfectly replicating the nostalgic, raw, and documentary snapshot feel of early 2000s digital cameras, with the strong flash contrast against the dark background creating a visually striking tension evocative of the era.",
    "prompt_zh": "使用附带照片的面部特征。一张年轻女性的特写照片，显示在一台紧凑型佳能数码相机的屏幕上。相机机身环绕着图像，其按钮、拨盘和纹理表面清晰可见，包括 FUNC/SET 转轮、DISP 按钮以及侧面的\"IMAGE STABILIZER\"标签。屏幕上的照片显示该女性在夜间室内，被明亮的内置闪光灯照亮，在她的面部和头发上形成锐利的高光。她有长长的黑发，松散的发丝垂落遮住部分面庞，嘴唇微张，表情柔和。闪光灯突出了"
