    "filename": "item_1611_3.png",
    "index": 1611,
    "title": "粉色双马尾少女聊天表情包",
    "title_en": "Pink Twin-Tail Girl Chat Emoji Pack",
    "prompt": "为我生成图中角色的绘制 Q 版的，LINE 风格的半身像表情包，注意头饰要正确 彩色手绘风格，使用 4x6 布局，涵盖各种各样的常用聊天语句，或是一些有关的娱乐 meme 其他需求：不要原图复制。所有标注为手写简体中文。 生成的图片需为 4K 分辨率 16:9",
    "prompt_en": "Generate a Q-version, LINE-style bust emoji sticker sheet of the character in the image. Pay attention to getting the headwear correct. Use a colorful hand-drawn style with a 4x6 layout, covering a variety of commonly used chat phrases and some related entertainment memes. Other requirements: do not directly copy the original image. All text labels should be in handwritten Simplified Chinese. The generated image should be in 4K resolution, 16:9 aspect ratio.",
    "source": "https://twitter.com/planxyou/status/1992975148140396782",
    "type": "t2i",
    "author": "@CharaspowerAI",
    "author_link": "https://twitter.com/planxyou/status/1992975148140396782",
    "revised_prompt": "一张彩色手绘风格的二次元 Q 版 LINE 聊天表情包排版图，画面比例为 16:9 宽幅。整体采用 4行6列 的网格布局，整齐排列着 24 个独立的半身像表情。背景为纯白色，以突出表情包主体。\n\n画面主体为同一个设定的二次元少女角色：拥有粉色双马尾，头戴醒目的黑色大蝴蝶结与白色蕾丝边发箍（头饰在所有表情中均保持正确的结构与高度一致），穿着带有红色领结的蓝白水手服。每个表情旁边均配有清晰可辨的黑色手写简体中文，覆盖了常用聊天语句和网络 meme，具体画面如下：\n\n第一行：\n第一列：少女微笑挥手打招呼，旁边文字为 '早上好！'\n第二列：双眼变成闪亮的星星，双手合十充满期待，文字为 '谢谢大佬！'\n第三列：眼泪汪汪，咬着白色手帕，文字为 '呜呜呜...'\n第四列：双手交叉抱胸，脸颊鼓起气呼呼的样子，文字为 '生气了！'\n第五列：低头鞠躬，额头带有一滴巨大的蓝色冷汗，文字为 '对不起嘛'\n第六列：歪着头，头顶出现一个红色的立体大问号，文字为 '啊？'\n\n第二行：\n第一列：身体像液体一样瘫软在桌上，嘴里吐出白色的半透明灵魂，文字为 '不想上班'\n第二列：双手捧着一杯珍珠奶茶正在用力吸，脸颊鼓鼓的，文字为 '吨吨吨'\n第三列：双眼燃烧着熊熊火焰，双手带残影快速敲击面前的键盘，文字为 '开卷！'\n第四列：闭眼安详地趴着，鼻尖冒出一个带有Zzz字符的睡眠泡泡，文字为 '晚安'\n第五列：双手捂脸，眼睛瞪大，嘴巴夸张地张成O型，文字为 '震惊！'\n第六列：自信地闭起一只眼睛Wink，伸出右手竖起大拇指，文字为 '包在我身上'\n\n第三行：\n第一列：低头看着发光的手机屏幕，脸上泛起红晕捂嘴偷笑，文字为 '磕到了'\n第二列：双手举着一个画有红色叉号的抗议木牌，表情冷漠，文字为 '退退退！'\n第三列：闭着眼睛张大嘴巴，一手用力拍打桌面，周围带有震动线条，文字为 '哈哈哈哈哈'\n第四列：戴着黑色像素风墨镜，嘴角上扬露出自信的歪嘴笑，文字为 '拿捏'\n第五列：双手握着一把发光的卡通大剑指向前方，眼神犀利，文字为 '拔剑吧！'\n第六列：身体融化成一滩水状，只剩头部和完整的头饰浮在上面，头上冒着热气，文字为 '热化了'\n\n第四行：\n第一列：伸出右手食指指着前方，半眯着眼睛做怀疑状，文字为 '你不对劲'\n第二列：双手捧着一块红瓤西瓜正在啃，眼睛睁得大大的在旁边围观，文字为 '吃瓜'\n第三列：单手向前送出飞吻，周围环绕飘散着粉色爱心特效，文字为 '爱你哟~'\n第四列：将一个空空的棕色钱包翻转过来倒，什么也没掉出来，眼角挂着宽面条泪，文字为 '吃土了'\n第五列：闭着眼睛露出享受的表情，头顶有一只带有线条示意的手正在抚摸她的头，文字为 '摸摸头'\n第六列：背对着画面挥手，身体下半部分呈现奔跑扬起灰尘的残影效果，文字为 '溜了溜了'\n\n整体色调明快鲜艳，线条清晰流畅，Q 版大头小身的比例夸张可爱，完美适配即时通讯软件的表情包视觉规范。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/item_1611_3.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "A color hand-drawn style two-dimensional chibi (Q-version) LINE chat sticker sheet, in a 16:9 wide-format aspect ratio. The overall layout adopts a 4-row by 6-column grid arrangement, neatly displaying 24 individual half-body portrait stickers. The background is pure white to highlight the sticker subjects.\n\nThe main subject across all stickers is the same two-dimensional anime girl character: featuring pink twin tails, wearing a prominent black large bow and white lace-trimmed headband (the headpiece maintains correct structure and high consistency across all stickers), dressed in a blue-and-white sailor uniform with a red bow tie. Each sticker is accompanied by clearly legible black handwritten Simplified Chinese text, covering common chat phrases and internet memes. The specific stickers are as follows:\n\nRow 1:\nColumn 1: The girl smiles and waves hello, with the text '早上好！' (Good morning!)\nColumn 2: Her eyes turn into sparkling stars, hands clasped together full of anticipation, with the text '谢谢大佬！' (Thanks, boss!)\nColumn 3: Teary-eyed, biting a white handkerchief, with the text '呜呜呜...' (Waaah...)\nColumn 4: Arms crossed over chest, cheeks puffed up in an angry look, with the text '生气了！' (I'm angry!)\nColumn 5: Bowing her head, with a single giant blue sweat drop on her forehead, with the text '对不起嘛' (Sorry~)\nColumn 6: Head tilted, with a red three-dimensional large question mark appearing above her head, with the text '啊？' (Huh?)\n\nRow 2:\nColumn 1: Body melting like liquid, slumped over a desk, with a white semi-transparent soul escaping from her mouth, with the text '不想上班' (Don't wanna work)\nColumn 2: Both hands holding a cup of bubble milk tea, sucking hard on the straw, cheeks puffed out, with the text '吨吨吨' (Gulp gulp gulp)\nColumn 3: Eyes ablaze with roaring flames, hands with motion blur rapidly typing on a keyboard in front of her, with the text '开卷！' (Let's grind!)\nColumn 4: Lying down peacefully with eyes closed, a sleep bubble with 'Zzz' characters rising from the tip of her nose, with the text '晚安' (Good night)\nColumn 5: Both hands covering her face, eyes wide open, mouth exaggeratedly agape in an O-shape, with the text '震惊！' (Shocked!)\nColumn 6: Confidently winking with one eye closed, extending her right hand with a thumbs-up, with the text '包在我身上' (Leave it to me)\n\nRow 3:\nColumn 1: Looking down at a glowing phone screen, blushing and covering her mouth while giggling, with the text '磕到了' (I'm shipping it)\nColumn 2: Both hands holding up a protest wooden sign with a red X mark, expression cold and indifferent, with the text '退退退！' (Back off!)\nColumn 3: Eyes closed, mouth wide open, one hand slapping the desk forcefully, with vibration lines around it, with the text '哈哈哈哈哈' (Hahahahaha)\nColumn 4: Wearing black pixel-style sunglasses",
    "prompt_zh": "为我生成图中角色的绘制 Q 版的，LINE 风格的半身像表情包，注意头饰要正确 彩色手绘风格，使用 4x6 布局，涵盖各种各样的常用聊天语句，或是一些有关的娱乐 meme 其他需求：不要原图复制。所有标注为手写简体中文。 生成的图片需为 4K 分辨率 16:9"
