    "revised_prompt": "一张写实风格的特写人像照片，呈现出典型的一次性相机的复古胶片质感，采用竖向构图。画面中心是一个年轻女性，体态中等，镜头聚焦于她的面部、颈部和部分肩部。她闭着双眼，头部微微向后仰起，脸上绽放着充满狂喜与极度喜悦的灿烂微笑。她拥有一头长发，发丝质感自然而蓬松，正被一阵轻柔的微风拂过，发丝在半空中呈现出轻盈飘逸的动态美感。她身穿一件轻薄的浅色丝质吊带上衣，与画面氛围相得益彰。背景被严重虚化，营造出一种魔幻且空灵的氛围，呈现出梦幻般的浅紫、柔粉与淡蓝色交织的渐变色调，空气中隐约漂浮着柔和的发光微粒或星尘斑点。视觉上，照片带有一次性相机的低保真特征，包括明显的胶片颗粒感、轻微的暗角、以及画面边缘自然晕染开的温暖橙色漏光效果。光线仿佛是由轻微的正面闪光灯结合环境中的柔光构成，使得人物面部的皮肤质感真实且带有微光，整体色调既怀旧又充满超脱现实的空灵美感。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/item_1642_3.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "A realistic-style close-up portrait photo, exhibiting the typical vintage film aesthetic of a disposable camera, composed in portrait orientation. At the center of the frame is a young woman, of medium build, with the lens focused on her face, neck, and partial shoulders. Her eyes are closed, her head tilted slightly backward, and her face is beaming with a radiant smile full of ecstasy and extreme joy. She has long hair with a natural and voluminous texture, being swept by a gentle breeze, with strands suspended mid-air displaying a light and flowing dynamic beauty. She is wearing a thin, light-colored silk camisole top that complements the atmosphere of the image. The background is heavily blurred, creating a magical and ethereal ambiance, presenting dreamlike gradient tones of soft purple, gentle pink, and pale blue interwoven together, with softly glowing particles or stardust specks faintly floating in the air. Visually, the photo carries the lo-fi characteristics of a disposable camera, including noticeable film grain, slight vignetting, and a warm orange light leak effect that naturally bleeds in from the edges of the frame. The lighting appears to consist of a slight frontal flash combined with soft ambient light, rendering the skin texture on the subject's face realistic with a subtle luminosity, while the overall color tone is both nostalgic and imbued with an otherworldly, ethereal beauty.",
    "prompt_zh": "{\"imageDescription\":{\"style\":\"写实\",\"atmosphere\":\"魔幻且空灵\",\"subject\":{\"person\":{\"age\":\"年轻\",\"bodyType\":\"中等身材\",\"hair\":{\"length\":\"长发\",\"texture\":\"自然飘逸\",\"movement\":\"轻柔飘动，仿佛被风拂过\"},\"expression\":{\"emotion\":\"狂喜、愉悦\",\"eyes\":\"闭眼\",\"headPosition\":\"微微后仰\",\"smile\":\"微笑\"}}},\"photoType\":{\"camera\":\"一次性相机\",\"focus\":\"特写\",\"ratio\":\"9:16\"}}}"
