    "revised_prompt": "一张竖屏构图的摄影照片。画面捕捉了公交车内一个温馨的宠物瞬间。画面中央是一名年轻女子，她坐在公交车靠窗的座位上，侧着身子，脸上洋溢着自然、真诚的微笑，眼神温柔地看着怀里的一只金毛寻回犬。狗狗的两只前爪搭在车窗下沿，正好奇地望向窗外。女子穿着一件休闲的米色针织开衫，微卷的棕色头发在阳光下泛着光泽。环境设定在日落时分，透过宽大的公交车车窗，可以看到窗外迷人的夕阳风景。天空呈现出温暖的橙红色、粉色和紫色的渐变晚霞，远处的城市天际线和树木轮廓在暮色中显得柔和。车厢内部细节可见，包括女子身下的蓝色织物座椅、车窗边框以及画面上方隐约可见的金属扶手。光线呈现典型的黄金时刻特征，温暖柔和的侧逆光透过车窗洒进来，在女子的侧脸、发丝和狗狗金色的绒毛上勾勒出明亮的轮廓光。画面采用浅景深效果，窗外的日落风景和车厢背景被适度虚化，焦点清晰地集中在人物温暖的笑容和可爱的宠物上，整体色调温暖、治愈且充满生活气息。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/item_1667_1.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "A portrait-orientation photography shot. The frame captures a heartwarming pet moment inside a bus. At the center of the image is a young woman sitting in a window seat on the bus, turned sideways, with a natural, genuine smile on her face, gazing tenderly at a Golden Retriever in her arms. The dog's two front paws rest on the lower edge of the bus window as it curiously looks outside. The woman wears a casual beige knitted cardigan, and her slightly wavy brown hair gleams with a subtle sheen under the sunlight. The setting is at sunset; through the wide bus window, a captivating evening vista is visible. The sky displays a warm gradient of orange-red, pink, and purple sunset glow, while the distant city skyline and silhouettes of trees appear soft in the twilight. Interior details of the bus are visible, including the blue fabric seat beneath the woman, the window frame, and a metal handrail faintly visible at the top of the frame. The lighting exhibits classic golden hour characteristics—warm, soft rim light streaming through the window from a side-backlit angle, tracing bright contour highlights along the woman's profile, her hair strands, and the dog's golden fur. The image employs a shallow depth of field effect, with the sunset scenery outside and the bus interior moderately blurred, while the focal point remains sharply on the woman's warm smile and the adorable pet. The overall color tone is warm, healing, and full of everyday life atmosphere.",
    "prompt_zh": "一张风景照、一张公交车抓拍、一个宠物瞬间、一张日落照，以及一个自然的微笑抓拍。"
