    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/item_1713_3.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "This is a portrait photography shot with an outdoor fashion magazine editorial style, composed in a wide-format horizontal orientation, inspired by automotive and road trip (Petro) aesthetics and lifestyle. The main subject is a young girl standing beside a vintage red pickup truck, her body slightly tilted, naturally leaning against the edge of the driver's side window. The girl has a red bandana tied on her head and wears a thick white faux-fur coat over a minimalist-style white top. She has slightly curly, voluminous long hair, with strands displaying a natural sense of movement as if gently tousled by a breeze. The girl wears a confident, slightly dreamy expression with a relaxed gaze. The scene is set outdoors at dusk, with brilliant golden sunset afterglow illuminating the entire landscape from the side-rear, casting a warm rim light over the girl's face, the white fur coat, and the red body of the truck. The expansive background showcases a quintessential American wilderness highway landscape—behind the red truck, a straight road extends into the distance, flanked on both sides by arid sandy ground and low scrubland, with undulating low mountain ranges in the far distance. The sky displays a magnificent sunset palette transitioning from golden-yellow to orange-red. The overall image tone is warm and rich, with abundant light and shadow depth, perfectly combining the rugged outdoor scenery with refined high-fashion sensibility.",
    "prompt_zh": "一幅户外时尚杂志编辑风格的肖像照，灵感来源于 petro 的美学与生活方式。上传的图片展示一个年轻女孩站在一辆红色卡车旁，倚靠在车窗边，头上系着红色围巾，身穿白色蓬松皮草外套和极简白色上衣。她松散的波浪长发营造出自然感和动感。她自信而梦幻的表情在金色夕阳映照下更显迷人，阳光照亮了整个风景。背景"
