    "revised_prompt": "一张特写微距照片。画面中央横向放置着一根成熟的黄色香蕉，占据了画面的绝大部分空间。香蕉皮呈现出明亮的黄色，带有自然的细微纹理和几处浅棕色的斑点。在香蕉皮平滑的弯曲面上，用黑色马克笔密密麻麻地手写着一段长篇的秘密信息。黑色字迹略带连笔风格，顺着香蕉的弧度紧密排列，清晰可见。文字内容为：'Agent K, the rendezvous point has been compromised. Move to sector 4 immediately. The package is hidden inside the false bottom of the blue suitcase at the station lockers. Locker number 402. The combination is 8-1-5-9. Do not trust the courier. Destroy this message after reading. We are running out of time.' 背景被极浅的景深进行了深度的模糊处理，隐约显现出深色暗调的木质桌面质感，深邃的背景与亮黄色的香蕉主体形成了强烈的明暗与色彩对比。柔和的侧顶光均匀地照射在香蕉表面，不仅突显了果皮的立体感和光泽，还照亮了黑色墨水附着在果皮上产生的微弱反光。画面构图紧凑，焦点完全集中在带有文字的香蕉局部，呈现出极高的清晰度和写实的摄影质感。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/item_1750_2.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "A close-up macro photograph. At the center of the frame, a ripe yellow banana is placed horizontally, occupying the vast majority of the image space. The banana peel exhibits a bright yellow color with natural subtle textures and a few light brown speckles. On the smooth curved surface of the banana peel, a lengthy secret message is densely handwritten in black marker. The black lettering has a slightly cursive style, closely arranged following the curvature of the banana, and is clearly legible. The text reads: 'Agent K, the rendezvous point has been compromised. Move to sector 4 immediately. The package is hidden inside the false bottom of the blue suitcase at the station lockers. Locker number 402. The combination is 8-1-5-9. Do not trust the courier. Destroy this message after reading. We are running out of time.' The background is deeply blurred by an extremely shallow depth of field, faintly revealing the texture of a dark-toned wooden tabletop surface. The deep background creates a strong contrast in both luminance and color against the bright yellow banana subject. Soft, overhead side lighting illuminates the banana surface evenly, not only accentuating the three-dimensionality and sheen of the peel but also highlighting the faint reflections produced by the black ink adhering to the fruit skin. The composition is tight, with the focal point entirely concentrated on the section of the banana bearing the text, presenting an extremely high level of sharpness and realistic photographic quality.",
    "prompt_zh": "一张 16:9 的香蕉特写照片，香蕉皮上手写着一段长长的秘密信息。"
