    "title": "XKCD风格AI邮件漫画",
    "title_en": "XKCD-Style AI Email Comic",
    "prompt": "create a novel xkcd style comic, with a clever new insight",
    "prompt_en": "create a novel xkcd style comic, with a clever new insight",
    "source": "https://twitter.com/multimodalart/status/1991605181830824106",
    "type": "t2i",
    "author": "@javilopen",
    "author_link": "https://twitter.com/multimodalart/status/1991605181830824106",
    "revised_prompt": "一张横向排版的xkcd风格黑白简笔画漫画，背景为纯白色，线条为黑色且具有手绘感。画面分为三个从左至右排列的画格，没有死板的边框线，整体风格极简，人物为经典的火柴人形象。左侧画格的左上角有一行手写英文：'ME, WRITING AN EMAIL:'。下方画着一个火柴人坐在简单的方块椅子上，双手放在一张代表办公桌的横线上，面临一台笔记本电脑。火柴人头上有一个思考气泡，气泡内写着：'AI, make this short bullet point sound professional and polite.'。电脑屏幕伸出一条向下的箭头，指向一团代表长篇大论的密集波浪线。中间画格的顶部写着：'MY COWORKER, RECEIVING IT:'。另一个火柴人坐在类似的办公桌前看着电脑屏幕，头上有一个思考气泡，里面写着：'AI, summarize this long email into one short bullet point.'。右侧画格占据较大的宽度，顶部标题为：'THE MODERN COMMUNICATION PIPELINE'。标题下方是一个流程图：最左侧有一个小圆点，标注文字 'Raw Idea'；一条细线向右连接到一个巨大的服务器机架方块（表面画着简单的指示灯和散热缝隙），方块上方标注 'MASSIVE GPU CLUSTER EXPANDING TEXT'；从该方块向右伸出一个极其粗大的管状箭头，箭头内部写着 'Corporate Filler Words'；粗箭头连接到第二个巨大的服务器机架方块，上方标注 'MASSIVE GPU CLUSTER SUMMARIZING TEXT'；最后，一条细线从第二个方块向右引出，连接到一个小圆点，标注 'Same Raw Idea'。在整张漫画的最下方居中位置，有一行较小的手写体英文作为幽默脚注：'We are burning gigawatts of electricity just to add and remove the words \"I hope this email finds you well.\"'。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/item_1774_1.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "A horizontally laid-out xkcd-style black-and-white line-drawing comic, with a pure white background and black lines that have a hand-drawn feel. The image is divided into three panels arranged from left to right, without rigid border lines; the overall style is minimalist, and the characters are classic stick figures. In the upper left corner of the left panel is a line of handwritten English: 'ME, WRITING AN EMAIL:'. Below it, a stick figure is sitting on a simple block chair with both hands on a horizontal line representing an office desk, facing a laptop computer. Above the stick figure's head is a thought bubble containing the text: 'AI, make this short bullet point sound professional and polite.'. An arrow extends downward from the computer screen, pointing to a dense cluster of wavy lines representing a lengthy block of text. At the top of the middle panel is written: 'MY COWORKER, RECEIVING IT:'. Another stick figure is sitting at a similar desk looking at a computer screen, with a thought bubble above their head containing the text: 'AI, summarize this long email into one short bullet point.'. The right panel occupies a larger width, with the title at the top reading: 'THE MODERN COMMUNICATION PIPELINE'. Below the title is a flowchart: on the far left is a small dot, labeled 'Raw Idea'; a thin line extends to the right connecting to a huge server rack block (with simple indicator lights and ventilation slits drawn on its surface), labeled above as 'MASSIVE GPU CLUSTER EXPANDING TEXT'; from that block extends to the right an extremely thick tubular arrow with 'Corporate Filler Words' written inside the arrow; the thick arrow connects to a second huge server rack block, labeled above as 'MASSIVE GPU CLUSTER SUMMARIZING TEXT'; finally, a thin line extends to the right from the second block, connecting to a small dot labeled 'Same Raw Idea'. At the very bottom center of the entire comic, there is a line of smaller handwritten English serving as a humorous footnote: 'We are b",
    "prompt_zh": "创作一幅新颖的 xkcd 风格漫画，包含一个巧妙的全新洞见。"
