    "revised_prompt": "一张现代风格的天气预报应用界面设计图，采用横向比例。背景是一幅轻微高斯模糊的旧金山风景摄影图，展示了壮丽的金门大桥（Golden Gate Bridge），红色的悬索桥塔矗立在标志性的海湾晨雾中，天空呈现柔和的蓝橙渐变色。界面主体由磨砂玻璃质感（Glassmorphism）的半透明面板组成，带有柔和的白色边缘高光和轻微的阴影。画面左上角是一个大型的主天气信息区：顶部用粗体白色无衬线字体显示地点 'San Francisco, CA'；其下方是特大号数字 '62°F' 和一个黄白相间的“多云”图标（一个太阳被白云部分遮挡）；温度下方标有状态文字 'Partly Cloudy'；右侧水平排列着三项补充数据文字：'Humidity: 65%'、'Wind: 12 mph' 和 'Precipitation: 0%'。画面的下半部分是一个占据大部分宽度的横向半透明玻璃面板，左上角标有小标题 '5-Day Forecast'。面板内部横向均分为五个列卡片，每列从上到下依次包含星期、天气图标和高低温度：第一列文字为 'Mon'，下方是一个带有水平雾气线条的云朵图标，底部文字为 '64° / 52°'；第二列文字为 'Tue'，下方是一个明亮的黄色太阳图标，底部文字为 '66° / 53°'；第三列文字为 'Wed'，下方是一个白云遮挡半个太阳的图标，底部文字为 '63° / 51°'；第四列文字为 'Thu'，下方是一个带有蓝色雨滴的灰云图标，底部文字为 '60° / 50°'；第五列文字为 'Fri'，下方是两朵重叠的灰色云朵图标，底部文字为 '62° / 51°'。整体画面构图平衡，UI元素排布整齐，光线明亮柔和，文字全部为纯白色，信息清晰易读，具有极高的商业设计完成度。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/item_1777_2.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "A modern-style weather forecast app interface design mockup in a horizontal aspect ratio. The background is a slightly Gaussian-blurred photograph of San Francisco's scenery, showcasing the magnificent Golden Gate Bridge, with its red suspension bridge towers standing amid the iconic bay morning fog, and the sky displaying a soft blue-to-orange gradient. The main interface is composed of semi-transparent panels with a frosted glass texture (Glassmorphism), featuring soft white edge highlights and subtle shadows. In the upper left of the image is a large primary weather information area: the top displays the location 'San Francisco, CA' in bold white sans-serif font; below it is an extra-large numeral '62°F' alongside a yellow-and-white \"partly cloudy\" icon (a sun partially obscured by a white cloud); beneath the temperature is the status text 'Partly Cloudy'; to the right, three supplementary data items are arranged horizontally: 'Humidity: 65%', 'Wind: 12 mph', and 'Precipitation: 0%'. The lower half of the image features a horizontal semi-transparent glass panel spanning most of the width, with a small subtitle '5-Day Forecast' in its upper left corner. Inside the panel, five column cards are evenly distributed horizontally, each containing from top to bottom the day of the week, a weather icon, and high/low temperatures: the first column text reads 'Mon', below it is a cloud icon with horizontal fog lines, and the bottom text reads '64° / 52°'; the second column text reads 'Tue', below it is a bright yellow sun icon, and the bottom text reads '66° / 53°'; the third column text reads 'Wed', below it is an icon of a white cloud partially covering a sun, and the bottom text reads '63° / 51°'; the fourth column text reads 'Thu', below it is a gray cloud icon with blue raindrops, and the bottom text reads '60° / 50°'; the fifth column text reads 'Fri', below it is an icon of two overlapping gray clouds, and the bottom text reads '62° / 51°'. The overall composition of the image is balanced, UI elements are neatly arranged, the lighting is bright and soft, all text is in pure white, the information is clear and legible, and it exhibits a very high level of commercial design polish.",
