    "type": "t2i",
    "author": "@FedericoLKG",
    "author_link": "https://twitter.com/YiTayML/status/1991591875934056554",
    "revised_prompt": "垂直画幅的四格漫画（黑白加网点风格，带有部分高光色彩点缀），页面整体自上而下排布着四个等大的矩形画格，讲述起承转合的剧情。页面最上方居中位置有大号的英文手写体粗体标题：'I was reincarnated into another world as an ai researcher'，标题背景融合了绿色的二进制数字代码与金色的魔法星光点缀。\n\n第一格（起）：背景是长满草的奇幻野外环境，远处有中世纪风格的城堡轮廓。画面中心是一名年轻的男性主角，他穿着白色的研究员大褂，内搭黑色T恤，戴着圆框眼镜，双手端着一台打开的银色笔记本电脑。他正惊讶地看着前方地上的一只蓝色水滴状史莱姆。主角头部上方有一个椭圆形对话框，里面的文字是：'Wait, I got reincarnated? And I still have my laptop?'。史莱姆上方悬浮着一个半透明的系统提示框，写着：'Slime encountered!'。\n\n第二格（承）：主角的面部近景特写。他用中指推了一下反光的眼镜，嘴角上扬露出自信的微笑，双手在键盘上飞速敲击（带有残影和速度线）。笔记本屏幕上方投射出一个发光的立体魔法阵，魔法阵的纹路不是传统符文，而是由密集的Python代码片段和神经网络节点（相互连接的发光圆点）构成。旁边有一个带有锯齿边缘的对话框，显示主角的激昂台词：'No need for a sword. I'll just train a reinforcement learning model to defeat it! Initializing Neural Network!'。\n\n第三格（转）：从代码魔法阵中召唤出了一个小巧、笨重的方形机器人（代表AI智能体）。机器人走到史莱姆面前，却开始原地漫无目的地打转，被史莱姆轻轻撞得东倒西歪，头顶冒出代表混乱的圈圈符号。机器人上方弹出一个带有红色边框的全息警告屏幕，上面清晰地写着：'Warning: Model not converged. Insufficient dataset.'。画面一角，主角目瞪口呆，额头上画着三根巨大的蓝色汗滴线，下巴夸张地掉下来。\n\n第四格（结）：夸张的喜剧逃跑场景。主角正惊恐地流着两条宽阔的漫画眼泪，死死抱着他的笔记本电脑向画面左侧狂奔。他的身后跟着铺天盖地的一大群（约二十只）蓝色史莱姆，正蹦跳着追赶他，背景布满了密集的横向速度线以增强动感。主角张大嘴巴尖叫，上方巨大的爆裂形对话框里写着：'I need at least 10,000 more epochs and a cluster of H100 GPUs! This world's compute is terrible!'。画格最底部居中有一个黑底白字的矩形旁白框，里面写着总结语：'The path to AGI in a fantasy world is long.'。\n\n整体构图紧凑，画风为日系二次元喜剧风格，线条清晰锐利，充分利用了漫画特有的符号表达与网状阴影过渡。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/item_1793_2.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "A vertical four-panel comic strip (black-and-white with screentone style, accented with partial highlight colors), with the page arranged top to bottom in four equally sized rectangular panels, narrating a setup-development-twist-conclusion storyline. At the topmost center of the page is a large handwritten-style bold English title: 'I was reincarnated into another world as an ai researcher', with the title background blending green binary code digits and golden magical starlight accents.\n\nFirst panel (Setup): The background is a grassy fantasy outdoor environment with the silhouette of a medieval-style castle in the distance. At the center of the frame is a young male protagonist wearing a white lab coat over a black T-shirt, with round-framed glasses, holding an open silver laptop with both hands. He is staring in surprise at a blue teardrop-shaped slime on the ground in front of him. Above the protagonist's head is an oval speech bubble with the text: 'Wait, I got reincarnated? And I still have my laptop?'. Floating above the slime is a semi-transparent system prompt box reading: 'Slime encountered!'.\n\nSecond panel (Development): A close-up of the protagonist's face. He pushes up his reflective glasses with his middle finger, the corner of his mouth curling into a confident smile, his hands typing rapidly on the keyboard (with motion blur and speed lines). Above the laptop screen, a glowing three-dimensional magic circle is projected, its patterns composed not of traditional runes but of dense Python code snippets and neural network nodes (interconnected glowing dots). Beside it is a jagged-edged speech bubble displaying the protagonist's impassioned dialogue: 'No need for a sword. I'll just train a reinforcement learning model to defeat it! Initializing Neural Network!'.\n\nThird panel (Twist): From the code magic circle, a small, clunky, boxy robot (representing an AI agent) has been summoned. The robot walks up to the slime but begins spinning aimlessly in place, getting knocked around and toppling over from the slime's gentle bumps, with confusion circle symbols emerging above its head. Above the robot pops up a full",
    "prompt_zh": "创作一部4格漫画，标题为\"我转生到异世界成为了一名 AI 研究员\"。"
