    "revised_prompt": "狗仔队抓拍风格的街头人像摄影。宽幅画面中采用略微仰拍的特写视角，紧密聚焦于一名男子的脸部和肩部。男子拥有极其立体且引人注目的面部轮廓，他正越过自己的肩膀回头凝视镜头，嘴角挂着一抹自信且略带戏谑的微笑。他身穿一件质感厚实的深色高领毛衣，脸庞上佩戴着一副造型前卫的黑色时尚墨镜，散发出随性洒脱的街头时尚气息。男子的身后是横向延伸且被重度景深虚化的背景，展现出熙熙攘攘的人群；隐约可见背景中其他穿着时髦的模糊人影、错落的街灯以及交织的光斑，营造出宛如巴黎时装周场外那种喧闹、拥挤且充满活力的氛围。画面的光效模拟了强烈的机顶闪光灯直打效果（Harsh flash），在人物的下颌边缘和高领毛衣的褶皱处形成了高反差的硬朗阴影。整体照片呈现出明显的高ISO噪点与粗糙的胶片颗粒感，没有任何过度修饰，极大地强化了这种未经彩排、瞬间定格的原始张力与纪实感。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/item_1804_2.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "Paparazzi-style candid street portrait photography. The wide-format image employs a slightly low-angle close-up perspective, tightly focused on a man's face and shoulders. The man possesses an exceptionally sculpted and striking facial structure, and he is glancing back over his shoulder to gaze at the camera, with a confident and slightly playful smirk on his lips. He wears a thick-textured dark turtleneck sweater, and on his face sits a pair of avant-garde black fashion sunglasses, exuding an effortlessly cool street-fashion aura. Behind the man, the horizontally extending background is heavily blurred by depth of field, revealing bustling crowds; vaguely visible are other fashionably dressed blurred figures, staggered streetlights, and interwoven bokeh spots, creating an atmosphere reminiscent of the noisy, crowded, and vibrant scene outside Paris Fashion Week. The lighting simulates a harsh on-camera flash effect (harsh flash), casting high-contrast hard shadows along the edges of the subject's jawline and in the folds of his turtleneck sweater. The overall photograph exhibits pronounced high-ISO noise and coarse film grain, with no excessive retouching whatsoever, greatly intensifying the raw tension and documentary feel of this unrehearsed, frozen-in-the-moment capture.",
    "prompt_zh": "非摆拍狗仔队风格肖像，一个紧张的、特写的瞬间，捕捉到一位五官突出的男子[回头看并带着自信的微笑]。从略微低角度拍摄，在模糊的、熙熙攘攘的人群中只展现他的面部和肩膀。画面感觉原始而自发，由刺眼的闪光灯照亮，具有高ISO纹理质感。他穿着[深色高领毛衣并佩戴时尚太阳镜]，体现出毫不费力的街头时尚风格，其能量和氛围令人联想到巴黎时装周的混乱场面。"
