    "prompt": "將這張照片重繪為吉卜力（Ghibli）風格。﻿",
    "prompt_en": "Redraw this photo in Ghibli style.",
    "source": "https://www.fotor.com/tw/blog/nano-banana-model-prompts/",
    "type": "t2i",
    "author": "from fotor",
    "author_link": "https://www.fotor.com/tw/blog/nano-banana-model-prompts/",
    "revised_prompt": "一幅竖版构图的动画插画，呈现出经典的吉卜力（Ghibli）工作室美术风格。画面中央是一条向上蜿蜒的古老石阶，石阶表面斑驳且覆盖着厚厚的翠绿色青苔与几朵白色的野花。一位年轻的黑色短发少女正站在石阶中段，她穿着一件带有白色翻领的浅蓝色复古连衣裙，斜挎着一个做旧的棕色皮革小包。少女微微仰着头，神情中透着好奇与惊叹，注视着上方的森林。在少女左侧近景的草丛中，隐藏着一只圆滚滚、通体雪白、长着两只长耳朵的神秘奇幻小生物，它正顶着一片巨大的绿色芋头叶作为雨伞。背景是一片繁茂且充满生机的古老森林。几棵需要数人合抱的巨大古树拔地而起，树皮纹理清晰，表面攀附着粗壮的藤蔓和蕨类植物。背景的树叶层次分明，呈现出传统水彩画般的清透质感与极其丰富的绿色调。画面上方，明媚的阳光穿透茂密的树冠层，形成几道明显的金色丁达尔光束，柔和地洒在少女的裙摆和长满青苔的石阶上，营造出斑驳生动的光影效果。透过画面顶端树叶的缝隙，隐约可见极高处湛蓝的天空和一朵像棉花糖般巨大、立体感强烈的盛夏白云。整体画风具有浓郁的夏日治愈感和奇幻童话氛围，人物和生物采用细腻的赛璐璐平涂技法，边缘线条柔和，与手绘水彩质感的高精度背景完美融合。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/item_1825_3.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "A portrait-oriented animation illustration rendered in the classic Studio Ghibli art style. At the center of the scene, an ancient stone stairway winds upward, its surface weathered and covered with thick emerald-green moss and a few small white wildflowers. A young girl with short black hair stands midway up the stone steps, wearing a light blue vintage dress with a white Peter Pan collar and carrying a worn brown leather satchel on a cross-body strap. She tilts her head slightly upward, her expression conveying curiosity and wonder as she gazes at the forest above. In the foreground grass to the girl's left, a mysterious fantastical small creature hides—round and plump, entirely snow-white, with two long ears—holding up a giant green taro leaf as an umbrella. The background is a lush, vibrant ancient forest. Several enormous old-growth trees, so wide they would require several people to encircle, rise from the ground with clearly defined bark textures, their surfaces draped with thick vines and fern plants. The background foliage is rendered in distinct layers, exhibiting the translucent quality of traditional watercolor painting with an extraordinarily rich range of green tones. In the upper portion of the image, bright sunlight penetrates the dense canopy, forming several distinct golden Tyndall beams that gently fall upon the girl's skirt hem and the moss-covered stone steps, creating vivid dappled lighting effects. Through gaps in the leaves at the very top of the frame, a deep blue sky is faintly visible at a great height, along with a single massive, cotton-candy-like midsummer cumulus cloud with a strong sense of volume. The overall art style conveys a rich sense of summer healing and a fantastical fairy-tale atmosphere. The characters and creatures are rendered using delicate cel-shading flat coloring techniques with soft edge lines, seamlessly blending with the hand-painted watercolor-textured, high-detail background.",
    "prompt_zh": "將這張照片重繪為吉卜力（Ghibli）風格。﻿"
