    "title": "年轻情侣拍立得合照",
    "title_en": "Young Couple Polaroid Photo",
    "prompt": "讓照片呈現拍立得效果：看起來像一張普通的快照，沒有明顯的道具或特定主題。畫面應帶有輕微的模糊感與一致的光源，好比在黑暗房間裡的閃光燈，光線均勻散佈全景。保持人臉不變，將兩個人身後的背景換成白色窗簾，並讓照片看起來像是參考圖中的兩人正在彼此擁抱。﻿\n\n﻿Take a photo taken with a Polaroid camera. The photo should look like an ordinary photograph, without an explicit subject or property. The photo should have a slight blur and a consistent light source, like a flash from a dark room, scattered throughout the photo. Don’t change the face. Change the background behind those two people with white curtains. Make it look like both people in the reference picture are hugging each other.",
    "prompt_en": "Make the photo look like a Polaroid effect: it should look like an ordinary snapshot, without obvious props or a specific theme. The image should have a slight blur and a consistent light source, like a flash in a dark room, with light evenly scattered throughout the scene. Keep the faces unchanged, replace the background behind the two people with white curtains, and make the photo look as if the two people in the reference image are embracing each other.\n\nTake a photo taken with a Polaroid camera. The photo should look like an ordinary photograph, without an explicit subject or property. The photo should have a slight blur and a consistent light source, like a flash from a dark room, scattered throughout the photo. Don't change the face. Change the background behind those two people with white curtains. Make it look like b",
    "source": "https://www.fotor.com/tw/blog/nano-banana-model-prompts/",
    "type": "t2i",
