    "author_link": "https://www.fotor.com/tw/blog/nano-banana-model-prompts/",
    "revised_prompt": "一张复古拍立得风格的室内摄影快照。画面主体是一位年轻男子和一位年轻女子，两人正处于画面中央，紧紧相拥。男子身穿简单的深色休闲T恤，女子身着浅色针织衫，两人的手臂环绕着彼此的肩膀和后背，姿态亲密而自然。他们微微侧头贴近，面朝镜头，脸上带着轻松随意的微笑，面部特征清晰可见。这是一张充满生活气息的普通快照，画面中没有任何刻意摆放的道具或复杂的装饰。两人身后的背景是一整面干净的白色窗帘，窗帘带有垂直下垂的自然布料褶皱。画面的光影效果生动模拟了在黑暗房间中使用相机闪光灯直打的效果，强烈且一致的单一人造光源从正前方均匀散布打在两人身上，使得人物的面部肤色和衣物曝光充分，高光略微溢出，同时在他们身后的白色窗帘上投射出清晰、生硬且带有边缘的黑色阴影。整体画质带有拍立得相机的典型物理特征，呈现出轻微的失焦模糊感与明显的胶片颗粒质感。画面色彩具有复古的褪色感和轻微的偏色，边缘略带暗角，完美还原了未经修饰的老式抓拍快照氛围。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/item_1852_1.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "A vintage Polaroid-style indoor photography snapshot. The main subjects are a young man and a young woman, positioned at the center of the frame, embracing each other closely. The man wears a simple dark casual T-shirt, and the woman wears a light-colored knit top. Their arms wrap around each other's shoulders and backs in an intimate yet natural pose. They tilt their heads slightly toward one another, facing the camera with relaxed, casual smiles, their facial features clearly visible. This is an ordinary snapshot full of everyday life atmosphere, with no deliberately arranged props or elaborate decorations in the frame. Behind the two, the background is an entire clean white curtain with naturally draping vertical fabric folds. The lighting vividly simulates the effect of a camera flash fired directly in a dark room—a strong, uniform single artificial light source spreads evenly from directly in front onto the two subjects, rendering their facial skin tones and clothing fully exposed with highlights slightly blown out, while casting sharp, hard-edged black shadows onto the white curtain behind them. The overall image quality carries the typical physical characteristics of a Polaroid camera, exhibiting a slight soft-focus blur and noticeable film grain texture. The color palette has a vintage faded quality with a slight color cast, and the edges show mild vignetting, perfectly recreating the atmosphere of an unretouched, old-fashioned candid snapshot.",
    "prompt_zh": "讓照片呈現拍立得效果：看起來像一張普通的快照，沒有明顯的道具或特定主題。畫面應帶有輕微的模糊感與一致的光源，好比在黑暗房間裡的閃光燈，光線均勻散佈全景。保持人臉不變，將兩個人身後的背景換成白色窗簾，並讓照片看起來像是參考圖中的兩人正在彼此擁抱。﻿\n\n﻿Take a photo taken with a Polaroid camera. The photo should look like an ordinary photograph, without an explicit subject or property. The photo should have a slight blur and a consistent light source, like a flash from a dark room, scattered throughout the photo. Don’t change the face. Change the background behind those two people with white curtains. Make it look like both people in the reference picture are hugging each other."
