    "title": "营养对比信息图",
    "title_en": "Nutrition Comparison Infographic",
    "prompt": "制作可打印的营养对比信息图：可乐 vs 气泡水，采用对半布局，左侧红色调右侧蓝色调。",
    "prompt_en": "Create a printable nutritional comparison infographic: Cola vs Sparkling Water, using a split layout with a red color scheme on the left and a blue color scheme on the right.",
    "source": "https://www.bilibili.com/read/cv43897854/",
    "type": "t2i",
    "author": "@whataicc",
    "author_link": "https://space.bilibili.com/3632314974210332",
    "revised_prompt": "垂直排版的打印级营养对比信息图海报，采用严格的垂直对半布局，画面从正中央被一条直线分为左右两个区域。画面顶部居中横跨左右两半有一行醒目的大写加粗无衬线字体大标题 'COLA VS SPARKLING WATER'，其下方有一行较小字号的副标题 'NUTRITION FACTS BATTLE'。画面左半部分以深红色至亮红色的渐变为背景。左侧上方居中绘制了一幅扁平风格的插画，内容为一个经典的红色易拉罐，旁边是一杯装满冰块和深色可乐的玻璃杯，杯子里插着一根吸管。插画下方有白色粗体文字 'COLA'。文字下方纵向排列着详细的营养数据，每一项配有极简的白色线条图标：带有火焰图标的文字 'Calories: 140 kcal'，带有方糖堆积图标的文字 'Sugar: 39g'，以及一段较小的成分说明文字 'Ingredients: Carbonated water, high fructose corn syrup, caramel color, phosphoric acid, caffeine.'。左半部分的底端有三个带有白色边框的标签，分别写有 'High Sugar'、'Artificial Additives' 和 'Energy Spike'。画面右半部分以深蓝色至浅蓝色的渐变为背景。右侧上方居中绘制了一幅呼应左侧的扁平风格插画，内容为一个流线型的透明玻璃瓶，旁边是一杯装有清澈水、密集气泡、新鲜柠檬片和绿色薄荷叶的玻璃杯。插画下方有白色粗体文字 'SPARKLING WATER'。文字下方对齐左侧高度纵向排列着营养数据：带有空心圆圈图标的文字 'Calories: 0 kcal'，带有单片绿叶图标的文字 'Sugar: 0g'，以及成分说明文字 'Ingredients: Carbonated mineral water, natural lemon essence.'。右半部分的底端同样有三个带有白色边框的标签，分别写有 'Zero Sugar'、'Hydrating' 和 'No Artificial Colors'。画面的最底部横跨左右有一个深灰色的矩形条幅，内部居中写有白色的警示语文字 'CHOOSE YOUR DRINK WISELY'。整体设计风格现代、清晰、排版整齐，色彩对比强烈，非常适合作为健康宣传海报打印输出。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/item_1863_4.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "A vertically formatted, print-grade nutritional comparison infographic poster with a strict vertical half-and-half layout, where the canvas is divided into left and right sections by a straight line running down the exact center. At the top of the canvas, centered and spanning both halves, is a prominent large uppercase bold sans-serif headline reading 'COLA VS SPARKLING WATER,' with a smaller subtitle beneath it reading 'NUTRITION FACTS BATTLE.' The left half features a gradient background from dark red to bright red. In the upper-center of the left side is a flat-style illustration depicting a classic red aluminum can alongside a glass filled with ice cubes and dark cola, with a straw inserted in the glass. Below the illustration is white bold text reading 'COLA.' Beneath the text, detailed nutritional data is arranged vertically, each item accompanied by a minimalist white line icon: text reading 'Calories: 140 kcal' with a flame icon, text reading 'Sugar: 39g' with a stacked sugar cubes icon, and a smaller ingredient description reading 'Ingredients: Carbonated water, high fructose corn syrup, caramel color, phosphoric acid, caffeine.' At the bottom of the left half are three white-bordered tags reading 'High Sugar,' 'Artificial Additives,' and 'Energy Spike.' The right half features a gradient background from dark blue to light blue. In the upper-center of the right side is a flat-style illustration echoing the left side, depicting a streamlined transparent glass bottle alongside a glass containing clear water, dense bubbles, fresh lemon slices, and green mint leaves. Below the illustration is white bold text reading 'SPARKLING WATER.' Beneath the text, nutritional data is arranged vertically, aligned to match the height of the left side: text reading 'Calories: 0 kcal' with a hollow circle icon, text reading 'Sugar: 0g' with a single green leaf icon, and an ingredient description reading 'Ingredients: Carbonated mineral water, natural lemon essence.'",
    "prompt_zh": "制作可打印的营养对比信息图：可乐 vs 气泡水，采用对半布局，左侧红色调右侧蓝色调。"
