    "filename": "item_1875_3.png",
    "index": 1875,
    "title": "温馨客厅群像画",
    "title_en": "Cozy Living Room Group Portrait Painting",
    "prompt": "“生成一张 16:9 的可爱群像图：14 个毛绒角色挤在一张旧布艺沙发上看复古电视。室内有温暖的窗光和电视光，整体氛围温馨、细节丰富。”",
    "prompt_en": "\"Generate a 16:9 cute group portrait: 14 plush characters squeezed together on an old fabric sofa watching a retro TV. The interior has warm window light and TV glow, with an overall cozy atmosphere and rich details.\"",
    "source": "https://www.bilibili.com/read/cv43897854/",
    "type": "t2i",
    "author": "@whataicc",
    "author_link": "https://space.bilibili.com/3632314974210332",
    "revised_prompt": "一张高质量的3D童话风格毛绒插画，采用宽屏构图。画面中央摆放着一张宽大的黄棕色旧布艺沙发，沙发表面呈现出复古的磨损质感和灯芯绒纹理，边缘带有几处明显的针脚补丁和流苏，上面散落着带有波西米亚几何图案的抱枕。14个形态各异、质感逼真的毛绒角色紧密地挤在沙发及其周围。沙发正中央坐着一只体型最大的蓬松大橘猫；橘猫左侧依偎着一只穿着蓝色牛仔背带裤的米白色长耳兔，怀抱半根胡萝卜；兔子头上趴着一只戴着圆框眼镜的灰色小猫；橘猫右侧靠着一只戴着红色针织帽的胖乎乎棕熊，棕熊怀里搂着一只粉色的圆球状小猪；沙发靠背左侧边缘，两只绿色小青蛙并排趴着；靠背右侧边缘，一只红色小狐狸探出身子往下看；沙发坐垫右边缘坐着一只戴黄色围巾的小企鹅和一只黑白相间的小边牧犬；左侧扶手上站着一只穿水手服的小黄狗。沙发前方的复古花纹地毯上，坐着一只背着红蘑菇的棕色小松鼠和一只蓝色小象，小象正用鼻子卷着一块饼干；沙发底部的缝隙中，一只小刺猬探出半个身子。所有角色都聚精会神地盯着画面右前方的胡桃木外壳老式CRT复古电视，电视顶部带有V字形金属天线和侧面旋钮。画面采用冷暖双光源：左侧格子窗透入一束温暖金黄的夕阳，照亮空气中漂浮的微尘并在木地板上投下窗格光斑；复古电视屏幕则散发出幽蓝偏白的冷光，打在毛绒角色们专注的面部和柔软的绒毛上，形成细腻的边缘轮廓光。室内背景墙纸贴有淡淡的碎花图案，整体色彩丰富柔和，充满温馨治愈的怀旧氛围。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/item_1875_3.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "A high-quality 3D fairy-tale-style plush illustration in widescreen composition. At the center of the scene sits a wide, yellow-brown vintage fabric sofa with a worn retro texture and corduroy ridges, its edges featuring several visible stitched patches and fringe, with scattered throw pillows bearing bohemian geometric patterns. Fourteen plush characters of varying shapes and lifelike textures are crammed tightly onto and around the sofa. Seated right in the center of the sofa is the largest character—a fluffy big orange tabby cat. Nestled to the left of the orange cat is a cream-colored long-eared rabbit wearing blue denim overalls, cradling half a carrot. Perched on the rabbit's head is a small gray cat wearing round-framed glasses. To the right of the orange cat leans a chubby brown bear wearing a red knitted beanie, cuddling a pink spherical piglet in its arms. On the left edge of the sofa backrest, two small green frogs lie side by side. On the right edge of the backrest, a small red fox leans forward and peers downward. On the right edge of the seat cushion sit a small penguin wearing a yellow scarf and a small black-and-white Border Collie. Standing on the left armrest is a small yellow dog wearing a sailor suit. On the vintage floral-patterned rug in front of the sofa sit a small brown squirrel carrying a red mushroom on its back and a small blue elephant curling a cookie with its trunk. From the gap beneath the sofa, a small hedgehog pokes out half its body. All characters are gazing intently at an old-fashioned CRT retro television with a walnut shell casing positioned in the right foreground, topped with V-shaped metal rabbit-ear antennas and side-mounted knobs. The scene employs dual cool and warm lighting sources: through a mullioned window on the left, a beam of warm golden sunset light streams in, illuminating floating dust motes in the air and casting windowpane-shaped light patches on the wooden floor; the retro TV screen emits a cool bluish-white glow that falls upon the focused faces and soft fur of the plush characters, creating delicate rim lighting along their edges. The interior background wallpaper features a faint floral pattern. The overall color palette is rich yet soft, filled with a warm, healing, and nostalgic atmosphere.",
    "prompt_zh": "“生成一张 16:9 的可爱群像图：14 个毛绒角色挤在一张旧布艺沙发上看复古电视。室内有温暖的窗光和电视光，整体氛围温馨、细节丰富。”"
