    "author_link": "https://space.bilibili.com/3632314974210332",
    "revised_prompt": "一张80年代复古风格的平面设计排版海报，采用横向宽幅构图。画面正中央醒目地横向排布着巨大的英文单词 'TYPOGRAPHY'，占据了绝大部分的视觉空间。该单词使用极其厚重、紧凑的无衬线大写粗体字，字母笔画粗壮，字间距极小，展现出强烈的几何块面感。字母主体为深黑色，带有经典的复古印刷色差错位效果：字母向左下侧投射出亮粉色（洋红色）的阴影，向右上侧投射出荧光蓝色（青色）的阴影，两种颜色的阴影在字母重叠的边缘处产生交错与混合。整个画面深度融合了80年代的网点半色调（Halftone）风格，文字的彩色阴影部分并非纯色，而是由大小渐变、排列密集的波普风格圆状网点构成，呈现出清晰的复古印刷颗粒感与网花纹理。海报的背景底色为带有轻微做旧泛黄痕迹的米白色纸张质感，画面四周的负空间点缀着少量零星的粉色半色调网点块、蓝色细线条以及细碎的印刷对位十字线作为排版装饰。画面光线平直，色彩对比强烈且鲜明，完美复刻了传统油墨印刷的视觉特征。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/item_1878_3.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "An 80s retro-style graphic design typography poster in a horizontal wide-format composition. Prominently arranged horizontally across the exact center of the canvas is the enormous English word 'TYPOGRAPHY,' occupying the vast majority of the visual space. The word is set in an extremely heavy, tightly packed sans-serif uppercase bold typeface with thick letterform strokes and minimal letter-spacing, conveying a strong geometric block-like presence. The letter bodies are deep black with a classic retro print chromatic aberration offset effect: the letters cast a hot pink (magenta) shadow toward the lower left and a fluorescent blue (cyan) shadow toward the upper right, with the two colored shadows producing intersections and blending where they overlap at the letter edges. The entire canvas deeply incorporates an 80s halftone dot style—the colored shadow areas of the text are not solid colors but are composed of densely arranged, gradually scaled pop-art-style circular halftone dots, presenting a distinct retro print granularity and moiré texture. The poster's background base color is an off-white paper texture with slight aged yellowing traces. The negative space around the edges of the canvas is accented with sparse scattered pink halftone dot clusters, blue fine lines, and small print registration crosshair marks as typographic decoration. The lighting across the canvas is flat and even, with strong and vivid color contrasts, perfectly replicating the visual characteristics of traditional ink printing.",
    "prompt_zh": "“生成一张带有 80 年代网点半色调风格的排版海报。文字内容是‘TYPOGRAPHY’，使用厚重、紧凑的字体，带有蓝色与粉色重叠阴影效果。”"
