    "prompt": "“在柏林街景中，将房屋外形巧妙地设计成‘BERLIN’字母的形状，但仍保持真实建筑感。阳光明亮，阴影清晰，16:9。”",
    "prompt_en": "\"In a Berlin street scene, cleverly design the building shapes to form the letters 'BERLIN' while still maintaining a realistic architectural feel. Bright sunlight, crisp shadows, 16:9.\"",
    "source": "https://www.bilibili.com/read/cv43897854/",
    "type": "t2i",
    "author": "@whataicc",
    "author_link": "https://space.bilibili.com/3632314974210332",
    "revised_prompt": "一张高度写实的柏林街景摄影照片，采用竖屏构图。天气晴朗，明亮的阳光从画面左上角斜射下来，在建筑物和街道上投下深邃且边缘清晰锐利的阴影，赋予画面极强的立体感。画面的核心是一排沿着宽阔街道并列矗立的六栋特色建筑，它们的外立面轮廓、阳台、屋顶和承重结构巧妙地构成了巨大的大写字母 ‘BERLIN’，同时保持着极度逼真的建筑物理细节。\n\n从左至右，第一栋建筑（B）是一栋经典的暖黄色石材老公寓，左侧是笔直的实墙，右侧上下排列着两个巨大的半圆形凸窗与环形露台，完美勾勒出‘B’的形状。第二栋（E）是一栋白色的现代主义公寓楼，左侧为主承重墙，右侧悬挑出三层厚重的水平混凝土阳台，形成‘E’的三横。第三栋（R）是红砖复古建筑，上半部分拥有一个半圆形的拱门大窗户，右下方则由一条粗壮的斜向外部砖砌楼梯和飞扶壁作为支撑，构成‘R’的斜腿。第四栋（L）左侧是一座高耸的深灰色古典塔楼，底层的沿街商铺带有一个平坦且向右远远延伸的深色金属遮阳雨棚，构成‘L’的底边。第五栋（I）是一座极窄的垂直高塔建筑，立面由笔直的玻璃幕墙和深色钢框组成，反射着阳光，犹如一根矗立的柱子。第六栋（N）由两座相同的细长垂直副楼组成，两楼之间通过一条从左上角倾斜贯穿至右下角的封闭式玻璃天桥连廊相连，形成‘N’的形态。\n\n画面上方留有三分之一的蔚蓝天空，点缀着几片薄云。建筑的底层充满了真实的生活气息：有常春藤攀附的墙角、拉开遮阳伞的街角咖啡馆、清晰可见的玻璃橱窗。画面下方的街道前景铺设着典型的柏林石板路，地面上有着斑马线、几辆停靠在铁栏杆旁的自行车、黑色的复古街灯，以及几名正在步行的行人。行人和路灯在明亮的阳光下在地面拉出长长的高对比度阴影。整体色调饱满，材质纹理清晰可见，巧妙地将排版艺术融入真实的城市街景摄影中。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/item_1879_3.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "A highly realistic photograph of a Berlin street scene, composed in portrait orientation. The weather is clear and sunny, with bright sunlight streaming diagonally from the upper left of the frame, casting deep shadows with crisp, sharp edges onto the buildings and street, lending the image a strong sense of three-dimensionality. The core of the image is a row of six distinctive buildings standing side by side along a wide street, whose façade contours, balconies, rooftops, and load-bearing structures ingeniously form the giant uppercase letters 'BERLIN,' while maintaining extremely realistic architectural physical details.\n\nFrom left to right, the first building (B) is a classic warm-yellow stone old apartment building; its left side is a straight solid wall, while the right side features two large semicircular bay windows with circular balconies arranged vertically, perfectly outlining the shape of 'B.' The second building (E) is a white Modernist apartment block; the left side serves as the main load-bearing wall, while three tiers of heavy cantilevered horizontal concrete balconies project from the right side, forming the three horizontal strokes of 'E.' The third building (R) is a red-brick vintage structure; its upper half features a large semicircular arched window, and its lower right is supported by a stout diagonal external brick staircase and flying buttress, forming the diagonal leg of 'R.' The fourth building (L) has a tall dark-gray classical tower on its left side, with a ground-floor street-level shop fitted with a flat, dark metal awning that extends far to the right, forming the base stroke of 'L.' The fifth building (I) is an extremely narrow vertical tower, its façade composed of straight curtain-wall glass and dark steel framing that reflects sunlight, resembling an upright column. The sixth building (N) consists of two identical slender vertical sub-towers connected by an enclosed glass skybridge corridor that slants diagonally from the upper left to the lower right, forming the shape of 'N.'\n\nThe upper third of the frame is reserved for an azure sky dotted with a few wispy clouds. The ground floors of the buildings are filled with authentic signs of life: ivy-clad wall corners, a sidewalk café with open parasols, and clearly visible glass shopfront windows. The street foreground at the bottom of the frame is paved with typical Berlin cobblestones, featuring a zebra crossing, several bicycles parked against iron railings, black vintage streetlamps, and a few pedestrians walking by. The pedestrians and streetlamps cast long, high-contrast shadows on the ground under the bright sunlight. The overall color palette is rich and saturated, material textures are clearly visible, and the image skillfully integrates typographic art into authentic urban street photography.",
    "prompt_zh": "“在柏林街景中，将房屋外形巧妙地设计成‘BERLIN’字母的形状，但仍保持真实建筑感。阳光明亮，阴影清晰，16:9。”"
