    "title": "美食摄影",
    "title_en": "Food Photography",
    "prompt": "“制作一张写实程度极高的美食特写：寿司配木质托盘、自然柔光、景深突出食材纹理。仿专业美食摄影棚拍摄。”",
    "prompt_en": "\"Create an extremely realistic food close-up: sushi on a wooden tray, natural soft light, with depth of field highlighting the texture of the ingredients. Mimicking a professional food photography studio shoot.\"",
    "source": "https://www.bilibili.com/read/cv43897854/",
    "type": "t2i",
    "author": "@whataicc",
    "author_link": "https://space.bilibili.com/3632314974210332",
    "revised_prompt": "一张极高写实度的专业美食摄影照片，采用竖屏构图。画面中央偏下位置特写展示着一枚精致的三文鱼握寿司，放置在一块带有自然深刻木纹的原木色长条托盘上。寿司由晶莹剔透、颗粒分明且微微反光的醋米饭托底，上方覆盖着一片厚切的三文鱼刺身。三文鱼肉呈现出鲜亮诱人的橙红色，表面带有清晰平行的白色脂肪纹理，泛着新鲜食材特有的水润与微亮的油光。三文鱼顶部精心点缀着几颗晶莹剔透的橙色鲑鱼籽和一小撮翠绿的现磨山葵，鲑鱼籽表面有着高光反射。特写镜头配合极浅的景深，使得前景的寿司和其下方的木质托盘纹理极其清晰锐利，而背景则被强烈的景深效果完全虚化，呈现为柔和的深棕色和暖黄色调，隐约可见虚化的日式茶杯边缘和点状的温暖环境光斑。画面采用自然柔和的侧逆光照明，仿佛是透过窗户洒入的柔光，完美勾勒出食材的立体感、水润感以及木托盘的边缘轮廓。整体色调温暖、高级，极具专业美食摄影棚的打光质感，将观者的视觉焦点牢牢锁定在极其写实的食材微观肌理上。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/item_1881_3.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "An extremely photorealistic professional food photography shot, composed in portrait orientation. Slightly below the center of the frame, a close-up showcases an exquisite salmon nigiri sushi, placed on a natural-wood-toned rectangular serving board with deep, pronounced wood grain. The sushi is based on a bed of translucent, distinctly grained, slightly glistening vinegared rice, topped with a thick-cut slice of salmon sashimi. The salmon flesh exhibits a vivid, appetizing orange-red hue with clearly defined parallel white fat marbling lines, glistening with the moist sheen and subtle oily luster characteristic of fresh ingredients. The top of the salmon is meticulously garnished with several glistening, translucent orange salmon roe and a small mound of verdant freshly grated wasabi; the surfaces of the salmon roe display specular highlight reflections. The close-up lens paired with an extremely shallow depth of field renders the foreground sushi and the wood grain texture of the serving board beneath it exceptionally sharp and crisp, while the background is completely dissolved by the strong bokeh effect into soft dark-brown and warm-yellow tones, with faintly discernible blurred edges of a Japanese teacup and warm, diffused circular ambient light spots. The image employs natural, soft side-backlighting, as if gentle light were filtering through a window, perfectly delineating the three-dimensionality and moist sheen of the ingredients as well as the edge contours of the wooden serving board. The overall color tone is warm and refined, possessing the lighting quality of a professional food photography studio, firmly locking the viewer's visual focus onto the extraordinarily realistic micro-textures of the ingredients.",
    "prompt_zh": "“制作一张写实程度极高的美食特写：寿司配木质托盘、自然柔光、景深突出食材纹理。仿专业美食摄影棚拍摄。”"
}, {
    "filename": "item_1892_2.png",
    "index": 1892,
    "title": "文字构成的蓝鲸插画",
    "title_en": "Blue Whale Illustration Made of Text",
    "prompt": "创建一个[OBJECT]形状的文字插画,文字本身构成该形状。字体风格为粗体且活泼,填满整个轮廓,文字沿对象的曲线和轮廓自然排列。色彩选择鲜明对比且契合主题的。背景为纯色,以突出主体形状。风格采用矢量风格,干净整洁。分辨率高,适合海报格式。",
    "prompt_en": "Create a text illustration in the shape of a [OBJECT], where the text itself forms the shape. The font style should be bold and playful, filling the entire outline, with text naturally arranged along the curves and contours of the object. Choose colors that are vividly contrasting and thematically appropriate. The background should be a solid color to make the main shape stand out. Use a vector style that is clean and neat. High resolution, suitable for poster format.",
    "source": "https://adg.csdn.net/694e3f255b9f5f31781b0c9e.html",
    "type": "t2i",
    "author": "@木梯子",
    "author_link": "https://devpress.csdn.net/user/2501_94528627",
    "revised_prompt": "一张横幅宽比例的矢量文字插画。画面主体是一只向左游动的巨大蓝鲸，整个鲸鱼的轮廓完全由紧密排列的粗体、活泼的英文单词构成，文字本身代替了实体线条和色块，塑造出鲸鱼的物理形态。文字沿着鲸鱼流线型的身体曲线自然弯曲、拉伸和缩放，严丝合缝地填满了整个外轮廓。鲸鱼的头部由巨大的深蓝色单词 'WHALE' 和亮蓝色单词 'GIANT' 构成；流线型的躯干部分由交错排列的青色和深蓝色单词 'OCEAN'、'DEEP BLUE'、'MAJESTIC'、'SEA' 和 'WATER' 紧凑填充；下方的胸鳍由弯曲的单词 'SWIM' 构成；分叉的尾鳍部分则由向两侧延展的单词 'WAVES' 和 'NATURE' 组成。所有的文字内容均清晰可见。画面色彩对比鲜明，构成鲸鱼的文字以深海蓝、青色和亮蓝色的冷色调为主，而背景则是大面积纯净的明黄色暖色调。纯色背景没有任何渐变、杂色或多余装饰，极大地突出了蓝鲸的形状。整体呈现干净整洁的矢量图质感，边缘平滑锐利，排版充满活力与创意，契合海洋与自然的主题。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/item_1892_2.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "A wide-aspect-ratio vector typographic illustration. The main subject is a large blue whale swimming to the left, whose entire silhouette is composed entirely of tightly arranged bold, lively English words—the text itself replaces solid lines and color fills to sculpt the whale's physical form. The words naturally curve, stretch, and scale along the streamlined body contours of the whale, seamlessly filling the entire outer silhouette. The whale's head is formed by the large dark-blue word 'WHALE' and the bright-blue word 'GIANT'; the streamlined torso section is densely packed with alternating cyan and dark-blue words 'OCEAN,' 'DEEP BLUE,' 'MAJESTIC,' 'SEA,' and 'WATER'; the pectoral fin below is formed by the curved word 'SWIM'; and the forked tail flukes are composed of the words 'WAVES' and 'NATURE' extending outward to both sides. All textual content is clearly legible. The image features vivid color contrast: the words constituting the whale are predominantly in cool tones of deep-sea blue, cyan, and bright blue, while the background is a large expanse of pure, clean bright yellow in a warm tone. The solid-color background contains no gradients, noise, or superfluous decoration, dramatically highlighting the shape of the blue whale. The overall aesthetic is that of a clean, crisp vector graphic with smooth, sharp edges; the typography is dynamic and creative, in keeping with the themes of ocean and nature.",
    "prompt_zh": "创建一个[OBJECT]形状的文字插画,文字本身构成该形状。字体风格为粗体且活泼,填满整个轮廓,文字沿对象的曲线和轮廓自然排列。色彩选择鲜明对比且契合主题的。背景为纯色,以突出主体形状。风格采用矢量风格,干净整洁。分辨率高,适合海报格式。"
}, {
    "filename": "item_1896_3.png",
    "index": 1896,
    "title": "富士山下的狐狸画师",
    "title_en": "Fox Painter Under Mount Fuji",
    "prompt": "一组具有[日本浮世绘电影感的和风物语三宫格写真。整体为靛蓝、赭石与樱粉色调，充满侘寂与诗意的情绪。统一使用毛笔笔触字体添加字幕。画面中【狐狸画师】与参考图一致，衣着为简单的和服与斗笠。第一个宫格，中景：狐狸坐在能望见富士山的廊下，用尾巴卷着画笔，蘸取盘中的青黛色，为一把素白的团扇勾勒山峦线条，环境是庭院里枯山水静默，远处富士山积雪，天空有淡淡的云，画面强调画师的专业姿态与画面的留白美学。中文“将山河，收于方寸”，英文“Capturing mountainsona fan.”第二个宫格，特写：它用笔尖轻轻点染，将研磨好的樱花瓣粉末，化作画中富士山脚下的片片落英，环境是真实的樱花树在背景中摇曳，花瓣飘落，与画作交相辉映，画面强调创作的魔法瞬间与色彩的晕染。中文“让四季，在笔下轮回”，英文“Seasons turn at my brush tip.”第三个宫格，全景：夕阳西下，狐狸画师的作品挂满了整个廊下——团扇、灯笼、和伞。它满意地捧着一杯茶，看着这些作品在暮光中成为风景的一部分，环境是暖黄的夕光将一切镀上金边，富士山静静伫立，画面强调艺术与生活融合的圆满感。中文“此间风物，即成永恒”，英文“This moment, forever.”",
    "prompt_en": "A set of three-panel photo series with a [Japanese ukiyo-e cinematic Japanese-style monogatari aesthetic. The overall palette uses indigo, ochre, and cherry-blossom pink tones, filled with wabi-sabi and poetic emotion. Uniformly use brush-stroke calligraphy font for subtitles. The [fox painter] in the image matches the reference image, wearing a simple kimono and straw hat. First panel, mid-shot: The fox sits on a veranda overlooking Mount Fuji, curling its tail around a paintbrush, dipping it into a dish of indigo-blue pigment, sketching mountain contours onto a plain white round fan. The environment features a karesansui dry garden in quiet stillness, snow-capped Mount Fuji in the distance, and faint clouds in the sky. The composition emphasizes the painter's professional posture and the beauty of negative space. Chinese: \"将山河，收于方寸\", English: \"Capturing mountains on a fan.\" Second panel, close-up: It gently dabs with the brush tip, transforming ground cherry blossom petal powder into scattered falling petals at the foot of Mount Fuji in the painting. The environment shows real cherry blossom trees swaying in the background, petals drifting down, echoing the artwork in harmony. The composition emphasizes the magical moment of creation and the blending of colors. Chinese: \"让四季，在笔下轮回\", English: \"Seasons turn at my brush tip.\" Third panel, wide shot: At sunset, the fox painter's works hang all along the veranda—round fans, lanterns, and traditional umbrellas. It contentedly holds a cup of tea, watching these artworks become part of the scenery in the twilight. The environment has warm golden evening light gilding everything, Mount Fuji standing quietly. The composition emphasizes the sense of fulfillment where art and life merge. Chinese: \"此间风物，即成永恒\", English:",
    "source": "知乎文章",
    "type": "t2i",
    "author": "@知乎",
    "author_link": "",
    "revised_prompt": "一组垂直排版的日本浮世绘电影感的和风物语三宫格插画，整体分为上、中、下三个宫格。画面色调以靛蓝、赭石与樱粉色为主，呈现出侘寂与诗意的情绪，每个宫格底部均配有白色的毛笔笔触字体字幕。\n第一个宫格（上方）：中景构图。一只狐狸画师坐在能望见富士山的木制廊下，它身穿素简的赭石色和服，头戴竹编斗笠。狐狸正用毛茸茸的尾巴卷着一支画笔，笔尖蘸取瓷盘中的青黛色颜料，在前方的一把素白团扇上勾勒连绵的山峦线条。环境是庭院里铺满白砂与景石的枯山水，远处是山顶积雪的富士山，天空中漂浮着淡淡的薄云，画面留白广阔，强调画师的专业姿态。底部字幕为中文‘将山河，收于方寸’以及英文‘Capturing mountains on a fan.’\n第二个宫格（中间）：特写镜头。聚焦于狐狸画师的画笔笔尖。笔尖正轻轻点染研磨好的樱花瓣粉末，粉红色的颜料在画作上晕染开来，化作画中富士山脚下的片片落英。背景是虚化的真实樱树，粉色枝条摇曳，真实的樱花花瓣在空中飘落，与画纸上的色彩交相辉映，强调创作的魔法瞬间与色彩的晕染。底部字幕为中文‘让四季，在笔下轮回’以及英文‘Seasons turn at my brush tip.’\n第三个宫格（下方）：全景构图。夕阳西下的黄昏时分。狐狸画师满意地双手捧着一杯冒着热气的茶，坐在廊下眺望。木制廊下的屋檐和柱子之间挂满了它创作的作品——绘有风景的团扇、和纸灯笼以及撑开的和伞。暖黄色的夕阳余晖将整个庭院、挂件和狐狸镀上了一层金边，远处的富士山在暮色中静静伫立，场景宁静而充满艺术与生活融合的圆满感。底部字幕为中文‘此间风物，即成永恒’以及英文‘This moment, forever.’",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/item_1896_3.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "A set of vertically formatted Japanese ukiyo-e cinematic wa-fū monogatari three-panel illustrations, divided into upper, middle, and lower panels. The overall color palette centers on indigo, ochre, and cherry-blossom pink, evoking a mood of wabi-sabi and poetic sentiment. Each panel features white calligraphic brush-stroke subtitles at the bottom.\nFirst panel (top): Mid-shot composition. A fox painter sits on a wooden engawa veranda overlooking Mount Fuji, wearing a plain ochre-colored kimono and a woven bamboo kasa hat. The fox curls its fluffy tail around a painting brush, the tip dipped in indigo-blue pigment from a porcelain dish, tracing continuous mountain ridge lines on a plain white round fan (uchiwa) in front of it. The setting is a karesansui dry landscape garden of raked white sand and accent stones; in the distance stands snow-capped Mount Fuji beneath a sky with faintly drifting thin clouds. Generous negative space emphasizes the painter's professional posture. Bottom subtitle in Chinese: '将山河，收于方寸' and in English: 'Capturing mountains on a fan.'\nSecond panel (middle): Close-up shot. Focus on the tip of the fox painter's brush. The brush tip gently picks up ground cherry-blossom petal powder; pink pigment bleeds and diffuses across the painting, transforming into scattered falling petals at the foot of Mount Fuji within the artwork. The background features a bokeh-blurred real cherry tree with pink branches swaying, real cherry-blossom petals drifting through the air, echoing and complementing the colors on the paper—emphasizing the magical moment of creation and the diffusion of color. Bottom subtitle in Chinese: '让四季，在笔下轮回' and in English: 'Seasons turn at my brush tip.'\nThird panel (bottom): Wide-shot composition. Dusk as the sun sets. The fox painter contentedly holds a steaming cup of tea in both hands, sitting on the engawa gazing outward. Between the wooden eaves and pillars hang its completed works—landscape-painted round fans, washi paper lanterns, and opened wagasa parasols. Warm golden sunset light gilds the entire garden, the hanging pieces, and the fox with a golden rim; in the distance Mount Fuji stands quietly in the twilight. The scene is serene and filled with a sense of fulfillment where art and life merge. Bottom subtitle in Chinese: '此间风物，即成永恒' and in English: 'This moment, forever.'",
    "prompt_zh": "一组具有[日本浮世绘电影感的和风物语三宫格写真。整体为靛蓝、赭石与樱粉色调，充满侘寂与诗意的情绪。统一使用毛笔笔触字体添加字幕。画面中【狐狸画师】与参考图一致，衣着为简单的和服与斗笠。第一个宫格，中景：狐狸坐在能望见富士山的廊下，用尾巴卷着画笔，蘸取盘中的青黛色，为一把素白的团扇勾勒山峦线条，环境是庭院里枯山水静默，远处富士山积雪，天空有淡淡的云，画面强调画师的专业姿态与画面的留白美学。中文“将山河，收于方寸”，英文“Capturing mountainsona fan.”第二个宫格，特写：它用笔尖轻轻点染，将研磨好的樱花瓣粉末，化作画中富士山脚下的片片落英，环境是真实的樱花树在背景中摇曳，花瓣飘落，与画作交相辉映，画面强调创作的魔法瞬间与色彩的晕染。中文“让四季，在笔下轮回”，英文“Seasons turn at my brush tip.”第三个宫格，全景：夕阳西下，狐狸画师的作品挂满了整个廊下——团扇、灯笼、和伞。它满意地捧着一杯茶，看着这些作品在暮光中成为风景的一部分，环境是暖黄的夕光将一切镀上金边，富士山静静伫立，画面强调艺术与生活融合的圆满感。中文“此间风物，即成永恒”，英文“This moment, forever.”"
}, {
    "filename": "item_1905_2.png",
    "index": 1905,
    "title": "宝矿力水特夏日海滩海报",
    "title_en": "Pocari Sweat Summer Beach Poster",
    "prompt": "参考这个图片的风格，帮我生成一个宝矿力水特的产品海报\n\n在海报里加上英文“Pocari Sweat”，要和海报风格相融合",
    "prompt_en": "Typography engine uses a Bento Box grid system, organizing content in modular rounded-rectangle containers. Container material must be frosted glass with blur effect, featuring delicate white borders and soft drop shadows, with mandatory generous internal padding to avoid crowding.",
    "source": "https://my.feishu.cn/docx/IKO3dWCeyobZ5CxWE18cV40xnth",
    "type": "t2i",
    "author": "@Xuan酱",
    "author_link": "https://my.feishu.cn/docx/IKO3dWCeyobZ5CxWE18cV40xnth",
    "revised_prompt": "一张日系清新风格的宝矿力水特夏日产品海报。采用横向构图。画面中央偏右的前景位置，放置着一瓶经典的宝矿力水特透明塑料瓶。瓶身上贴着标志性的宝蓝色标签，带有白色的波浪线条设计，顶部是白色的塑料瓶盖。透明的瓶身内部装满半透明的浑浊液体，瓶子外壁布满了密集的冷凝水珠，几滴水珠正顺着瓶身滑落，折射着明亮的阳光。瓶子稳稳地立在洁白细腻的沙滩上，瓶底周围的细沙有些湿润，旁边散落着两枚小巧的纯白色海贝。背景是开阔的夏日海景。清澈蔚蓝的海水在阳光下波光粼粼，一道白色的海浪正翻滚着涌向沙滩。海平线上方是澄澈的浅蓝色天空，飘浮着几团蓬松巨大的白色积雨云。画面左侧的海水边缘，有一个穿着白色吊带夏装的模糊少女背影，正轻盈地向海里走去，人物呈现景深虚化效果，不抢夺产品焦点。画面的左上方的蓝天留白区域，排版着醒目的白色无衬线英文字母'Pocari Sweat'。字体设计清爽现代，带有轻微的半透明水波纹理质感，与整个蓝白调的夏日背景完美融合。整体画面色调以高明度的宝蓝色、纯白色和浅青色为主，光线通透刺眼，充满清凉、解渴与青春活力的氛围。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/item_1905_2.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "A Japanese fresh-style Pocari Sweat summer product poster. Horizontal composition. In the center-right foreground, a classic Pocari Sweat transparent plastic bottle is placed on the scene. The bottle bears its iconic royal-blue label with white wavy line design, topped with a white plastic cap. The transparent body is filled with semi-translucent, slightly cloudy liquid. The outer surface is covered with dense condensation droplets, several of which are sliding down the bottle, refracting bright sunlight. The bottle stands firmly on fine, pristine white sand; the sand around the bottle's base is slightly damp, and two small pure-white seashells are scattered nearby. The background is an expansive summer seascape. Crystal-clear azure water sparkles under the sunlight, and a white wave is rolling toward the shore. Above the horizon stretches a limpid pale-blue sky with several large, fluffy white cumulonimbus clouds. At the left edge of the water, there is the blurred silhouette of a girl seen from behind wearing a white camisole summer dress, stepping lightly into the sea; the figure is rendered with depth-of-field bokeh so as not to compete with the product focus. In the upper-left blue-sky negative-space area, prominent white sans-serif English lettering reads 'Pocari Sweat.' The typeface is clean and modern with a subtle semi-transparent water-ripple texture, blending seamlessly with the overall blue-and-white summer backdrop. The overall color palette is dominated by high-brightness royal blue, pure white, and light cyan; the lighting is transparent and dazzling, brimming with an atmosphere of coolness, thirst-quenching refreshment, and youthful vitality.",
    "prompt_zh": "参考这个图片的风格，帮我生成一个宝矿力水特的产品海报\n\n在海报里加上英文“Pocari Sweat”，要和海报风格相融合"
}, {
    "filename": "item_1918_1.png",
    "index": 1918,
    "title": "极简风咖啡产品棚拍摄影",
    "title_en": "Minimalist Coffee Product Studio Photography",
    "prompt": "多元素组合\n展台：商业棚拍摄影：概念产品展台。极简布景设计，由不同高度的几何讲台（圆柱、立方体和阶梯）组成。材质为光滑哑光米色微水泥与深色抛光胡桃木混合。背景为干净的曲面棚拍墙（环幕），柔和暖灰色。光源为高端棚拍品质：左上方柔光箱照明，产生柔和渐变阴影。8K 分辨率，建筑美学风格\n植物：极简风格的花瓶和植物，白底图。\n书堆：高级感的极简风格装饰画和书堆，白底图。\n毯子：精致纹理的装饰性地毯，白底图。\n组合：将这些图像组合成一个合适排列的电影感产品摄影画面，咖啡产品系列在各层级上艺术性摆放。主角为哑光深炭黑咖啡豆包装袋，置于最高中央讲台上；米色帆布托特包随意靠在较低的立方体上，或挂在极简风支架上；石器陶瓷咖啡杯与烟灰色玻璃香氛蜡烛放在前景阶梯上，增加层次感；其他毯子、书堆和植物都是场景点缀，不要喧宾夺主。",
    "prompt_en": "Insert gift-quality 3D objects, rendering unique high-end abstract 3D artifacts as visual anchors. Their appearance should resemble tangible expensive gifts or collectibles, with materials such as polished metal, iridescent acrylic, clear glass, or soft silicone, in shapes like floating capsules, spheres, shields, Möbius strips, or fluid waves.",
    "source": "https://my.feishu.cn/docx/IKO3dWCeyobZ5CxWE18cV40xnth",
    "type": "t2i",
    "author": "@Xuan酱",
    "author_link": "https://my.feishu.cn/docx/IKO3dWCeyobZ5CxWE18cV40xnth",
    "revised_prompt": "一幅商业棚拍风格的电影感概念产品摄影图。整体呈现极简主义与建筑美学风格，画幅比例宽阔。背景是一面干净的暖灰色曲面棚拍墙（无缝环幕）。左上方设有高端柔光箱照明，在背景墙和物体表面投射出柔和、细腻的渐变阴影，整体色调温暖、克制且富有高级质感。\n\n画面的核心是由不同高度的几何讲台组合而成的展台，材质交替使用了光滑的哑光米色微水泥与深色抛光胡桃木。展台的底部边缘铺垫着一块带有低调精致几何编织纹理的浅灰色装饰性地毯，作为场景的基础点缀。\n\n在视觉中央的最高处，矗立着一个深色抛光胡桃木材质的圆柱形讲台。圆柱顶端摆放着画面的主角：一袋哑光深炭黑色的咖啡豆包装袋，包装袋正面印有极简的白色英文字母'COFFEE ROASTERS'和稍小的'DARK BLEND'。在中央圆柱的左侧，是一个较低的哑光米色微水泥立方体讲台，一个米色帆布托特包以自然的褶皱形态随意地倚靠在立方体边缘，包身印有简约的黑色英文字母'EVERYDAY ESSENTIALS'。展台的最前方延伸出两级米色微水泥阶梯，阶梯台面上放置着一个质感粗朴的石器陶瓷咖啡杯，紧挨着咖啡杯的是一个装在烟灰色半透明玻璃罐中的香氛蜡烛，增加了前景的视觉层次。\n\n场景的四周精心布置了不喧宾夺主的极简装饰物。在画面的右后方，摆放着一个纯白色的极简磨砂花瓶，瓶中插着几支纤细挺拔的尤加利叶干枝，在暖灰色的墙面上映出淡淡的阴影。在画面的左侧中景位置，整齐叠放着三本极简风格的精装书籍，白色与灰色的书脊上清晰可见黑色的英文单字'ART'和'DESIGN'；在书堆的后方，斜靠着一幅带有大面积留白与抽象黑白线条的高级感装饰画框。整个画面构图严谨，主次分明，咖啡产品系列在各层级上呈现艺术性排列，细节达到了8K超高清的分辨率质感。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/item_1918_1.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "A cinematic concept product photography image in a commercial studio-shot style. The overall aesthetic is minimalist with architectural design sensibility and a wide aspect ratio. The background is a clean warm-gray curved cyclorama wall (seamless infinity cove). A high-end softbox light is positioned at the upper left, casting soft, delicate gradient shadows on the backdrop and object surfaces; the overall tone is warm, restrained, and exudes a premium feel.\n\nThe core of the composition is a display formed by geometric podiums of varying heights, alternating in material between smooth matte beige micro-cement and dark polished walnut wood. Along the base edge of the display, a light-gray decorative rug with a subtly refined geometric woven texture serves as a foundational accent for the scene.\n\nAt the highest point in the visual center stands a cylindrical podium of dark polished walnut wood. Atop the cylinder sits the hero product: a bag of matte dark charcoal-black coffee bean packaging, its front printed with minimalist white English lettering reading 'COFFEE ROASTERS' and the slightly smaller text 'DARK BLEND.' To the left of the central cylinder is a shorter matte beige micro-cement cubic podium; a beige canvas tote bag leans casually against the edge of the cube in a natural, creased form, printed with simple black English lettering reading 'EVERYDAY ESSENTIALS.' Extending from the very front of the display are two beige micro-cement steps; on the step surface sits a rough, rustic stoneware ceramic coffee cup, and right beside it is a scented candle in a smoky-gray semi-transparent glass jar, adding visual layering to the foreground.\n\nCarefully arranged minimalist decorative objects surround the scene without competing for attention. At the right rear, a pure-white minimalist matte-finish vase holds several slender, upright dried eucalyptus branches, casting faint shadows on the warm-gray wall. At the left mid-ground, three minimalist hardcover books are neatly stacked; the white and gray spines clearly display black English words 'ART' and 'DESIGN.' Behind the stack of books, a premium decorative framed print featuring generous negative space and abstract black-and-white linework leans at an angle. The entire composition is rigorously structured with clear visual hierarchy; the coffee product collection is artistically arranged across multiple levels, with detail quality achieving 8K ultra-high-definition resolution.",
    "prompt_zh": "多元素组合\n展台：商业棚拍摄影：概念产品展台。极简布景设计，由不同高度的几何讲台（圆柱、立方体和阶梯）组成。材质为光滑哑光米色微水泥与深色抛光胡桃木混合。背景为干净的曲面棚拍墙（环幕），柔和暖灰色。光源为高端棚拍品质：左上方柔光箱照明，产生柔和渐变阴影。8K 分辨率，建筑美学风格\n植物：极简风格的花瓶和植物，白底图。\n书堆：高级感的极简风格装饰画和书堆，白底图。\n毯子：精致纹理的装饰性地毯，白底图。\n组合：将这些图像组合成一个合适排列的电影感产品摄影画面，咖啡产品系列在各层级上艺术性摆放。主角为哑光深炭黑咖啡豆包装袋，置于最高中央讲台上；米色帆布托特包随意靠在较低的立方体上，或挂在极简风支架上；石器陶瓷咖啡杯与烟灰色玻璃香氛蜡烛放在前景阶梯上，增加层次感；其他毯子、书堆和植物都是场景点缀，不要喧宾夺主。"
