    "revised_prompt": "一张横幅网页广告图，呈现高端暗黑美学风格和专业影棚布光效果。整体背景为深邃的暗黑色，带有细腻的暗调氛围感。画面最左侧排布着粗体白色的文字，上方为英文 'SUMMER MATCHA 2026'，下方紧跟中文字符 '限定发售'。在这两行文字的正下方，设有一个极简风格的 UI 按钮，按钮内部清晰地显示着文字 'Order Now'。向右过渡到画面的中左侧，一道发光的霓虹绿色几何光线优雅地穿透深色的背景空间。正中间的位置，一个精致的黑色陶瓷浅盘被柔和的光线局部打亮，盘中堆满了一堆质感细腻、颜色鲜亮翠绿的宇治抹茶粉。在画面的中右侧，呈现出高速摄影的动态定格效果，几块晶莹剔透的冰块悬浮在半空中，伴随着飞溅而起的纯白色奶油与牛奶液体，动感十足。画面的最右侧是视觉主体——一杯盛装在透明玻璃杯中的冰抹茶饮品。玻璃杯外壁覆着一层冰霜，展现出超精细的水珠冷凝效果，在暗色调的光影下折射出冰冷清透的微光，杯中是浓郁的绿色抹茶与牛奶混合的液体。构图呈完美的横向延展，各元素分布均衡，视觉焦点清晰。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/item_1922_3.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "A horizontal banner web advertisement image, presenting a high-end dark aesthetic style with professional studio lighting effects. The overall background is a deep, dark black with a subtle, moody atmosphere. On the far left of the composition, bold white text is arranged vertically—the upper line reads 'SUMMER MATCHA 2026' in English, immediately followed below by the Chinese characters '限定发售'. Directly beneath these two lines of text, there is a minimalist-style UI button with the text 'Order Now' clearly displayed inside it. Transitioning to the center-left of the frame, a glowing neon-green geometric light ray elegantly pierces through the dark background space. At the exact center, an exquisite black ceramic shallow dish is partially illuminated by soft lighting, piled with a mound of finely textured, vivid emerald-green Uji matcha powder. On the center-right of the frame, a high-speed photography freeze-frame effect is presented, with several crystal-clear ice cubes suspended in mid-air, accompanied by dynamic splashes of pure white cream and milk liquid, full of kinetic energy. On the far right is the visual hero—a glass of iced matcha beverage served in a transparent glass cup. The exterior wall of the glass is coated with a layer of frost, showcasing ultra-fine water droplet condensation effects that refract cold, crisp glimmers of light against the dark-toned lighting. Inside the cup is a rich green matcha and milk blended liquid. The composition extends perfectly in the horizontal direction, with all elements distributed in a balanced manner and a clear visual focal point.",
    "prompt_zh": "提示词\n8:1 超宽网页横幅版式。高端暗黑美学，影棚布光。最左侧：粗体白色文字「SUMMER MATCHA 2026」与「限定发售」。文字下方是一个简洁极简 UI 按钮，文字为「Order Now（立即订购）」。中左侧：一道发光霓虹绿几何光线优雅地穿过深色背景。正中间：一堆鲜亮绿色的宇治抹茶粉，置于精致黑色陶瓷盘上，光线柔和打亮。中右侧：悬浮的冰块与飞溅的奶油牛奶，定格在半空中。最右侧：主体 —— 一杯覆霜的冰抹茶玻璃杯，超精细水珠冷凝效果，暗调氛围感布光。杰作级，完美构图。—— 比例 8:1"
