    "title_en": "Outdoor Life Vector Sticker Set",
    "prompt": "[BRAND NAME]. Act as a vector illustrator designing a trendy, high-end \"Sticker Sheet\" set.\nTHE TASK:\nDeconstruct the brand identity of [BRAND NAME] into a playful, cohesive set of approximately 8-10 unique sticker designs arranged on a single sheet.\nContent Generation: Do not just make logos. Autonomously invent a mix of:\nMascots/Characters: Stylized busts of people wearing brand-relevant accessories or expressing emotions.\nKey Products: Iconic items associated with the brand.\nSymbols/Objects: Abstract shapes or tools relevant to the brand's lifestyle.\n\nVISUAL STYLE (MONOLINE VECTOR):\nThe art style must strictly match \"Modern Trendy Line Art.\"\nLine Work: Use a THICK, UNIFORM line weight (monoline) for all internal details. The lines should be smooth, rounded, and confident.\nColoring: The stickers must be filled with Solid Off-White or Cream, utilizing the line color for details. NO gradients, NO shading, NO 3D effects. Flat 2D vector look.\nThe \"Sticker\" Effect: Every element must have a thick, distinct White (or Cream) Die-Cut Border surrounding it, separating it from the background.\nCOLOR PALETTE (HIGH CONTRAST):\nBackground: A solid, deep, saturated color to create maximum contrast.\nStickers: High-brightness Cream or White fill with Dark (Black or Dark Brown) outlines.\nCOMPOSITION:\nThe stickers are scattered naturally across the sheet (knolling layout) with even spacing. No overlapping.",
    "prompt_en": "[BRAND NAME]. Act as a vector illustrator designing a trendy, high-end \"Sticker Sheet\" set.\nTHE TASK:\nDeconstruct the brand identity of [BRAND NAME] into a playful, cohesive set of approximately 8-10 unique sticker designs arranged on a single sheet.\nContent Generation: Do not just make logos. Autonomously invent a mix of:\nMascots/Characters: Stylized busts of people wearing brand-relevant accessories or expressing emotions.\nKey Products: Iconic items associated with the brand.\nSymbols/Objects: Abstract shapes or tools relevant to the brand's lifestyle.\n\nVISUAL STYLE (MONOLINE VECTOR):\nThe art style must strictly match \"Modern Trendy Line Art.\"\nLine Work: Use a THICK, UNIFORM line weight (monoline) for all internal details. The lines should be smooth, rounded, and confident.\nColoring: The stickers must be filled with Solid Off-White or Cream, utilizing the line color for details. NO gradients, NO shading, NO 3D effects. Flat 2D vector look.\nThe \"Sticker\" Effect: Every element must have a thick, distinct White (or Cream) Die-Cut Border surrounding it, separating it from the background.\nCOLOR PALETTE (HIGH CONTRAST):\nBackground: A solid, deep, saturated color to create maximum contrast.\nStickers: High-brightness Cream or White fill with Dark (Black or Dark Brown) outlines.\nCOMPOSITION:\nThe stickers are scattered naturally across the sheet (knolling layout) with even spacing. No overlapping.",
    "source": "https://x.com/AmirMushich/status/2010070395974504565",
    "type": "t2i",
    "author": "@AmirMushich",
    "author_link": "https://x.com/AmirMushich/status/2010070395974504565",
    "revised_prompt": "现代潮流矢量插画风格的贴纸排版图。画面比例为横向，背景为纯色、高饱和度的深午夜蓝色，提供极高的色彩对比度。画面中均匀散落着9枚独立且互不重叠的贴纸，采用整齐的平铺布局（knolling layout）。整体视觉风格严格遵循现代单线艺术。所有贴纸的内部图案均由粗细完全一致的深棕色线条勾勒，线条平滑、圆润且流畅。贴纸的内部填充色均为纯平面的米白色，没有任何渐变、阴影或3D效果，呈现出纯粹的二维矢量外观。每一枚贴纸的最外围都带有一圈厚实且轮廓分明的纯白色模切白边（Die-Cut Border），将其与深色的背景物理隔离。贴纸的具体内容包含了一系列与现代户外生活方式品牌相关的元素：1. 人物吉祥物：一个戴着针织冷帽和圆形复古眼镜的年轻女孩半身像，带着俏皮的微笑。2. 动物吉祥物：一只脖子上系着户外探险三角巾的宠物狗头部特写。3. 核心产品：一个现代简约风格的随行保温杯，杯身带有流线型的纹理。4. 核心产品：一台经典的复古胶片相机，细节包含圆形镜头、闪光灯和快门按钮。5. 抽象符号：一簇风格化的篝火，火焰由流畅的几何水滴形状构成。6. 抽象符号：一棵几何风格的松树，由三层圆润的折线堆叠而成。7. 生活物件：一个复古指南针，内部带有简约的十字方向指针。8. 品牌名称贴纸：以粗体现代无衬线字体呈现的英文品牌名，内容为 'OAK & ECHO'。9. 标语贴纸：一个带有折叠效果的丝带横幅，上面写着大写的英文标语 'EXPLORE MORE'。画面色彩高度统一，米白色的主体、深棕色的单线与深蓝色的背景构成了高对比度的视觉效果，排版整洁有序。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/item_1992_3.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "A sticker layout image in a modern trendy vector illustration style. The image is in landscape orientation, with a solid, highly saturated deep midnight blue background providing extremely high color contrast. Nine independent, non-overlapping stickers are evenly scattered across the frame, arranged in a neat knolling layout. The overall visual style strictly adheres to modern mono-line art. The internal illustrations of all stickers are outlined with dark brown lines of completely uniform stroke weight—smooth, rounded, and fluid. The interior fill color of each sticker is a flat, solid cream white with no gradients, shadows, or 3D effects whatsoever, presenting a purely two-dimensional vector appearance. The outermost edge of every sticker features a thick, well-defined pure white die-cut border, physically separating it from the dark background. The specific contents of the stickers include a series of elements related to a modern outdoor lifestyle brand: 1. Character Mascot: A bust portrait of a young girl wearing a knitted beanie and round retro glasses, with a playful smile. 2. Animal Mascot: A close-up of a pet dog's head with an outdoor adventure bandana tied around its neck. 3. Core Product: A modern minimalist travel tumbler with streamlined textures on the body. 4. Core Product: A classic vintage film camera, with details including a circular lens, flash, and shutter button. 5. Abstract Symbol: A cluster of stylized campfire, with flames composed of smooth geometric teardrop shapes. 6. Abstract Symbol: A geometric-style pine tree, formed by three stacked layers of rounded chevron lines. 7. Lifestyle Object: A vintage compass with a simplified cross-shaped directional needle inside. 8. Brand Name Sticker: The English brand name rendered in bold modern sans-serif typeface, reading 'OAK & ECHO'. 9. Tagline Sticker: A ribbon banner with a fold effect, bearing the uppercase English tagline 'EXPLORE MORE'. The color palette is highly unified—the cream white subjects, dark brown mono-lines, and deep blue background create a high-contrast visual effect, with a clean and orderly layout.",
    "prompt_zh": "[BRAND NAME]。作为一名矢量插画师，设计一套时尚、高端的\"贴纸合集\"套装。\n任务：\n将[BRAND NAME]的品牌形象解构为一组有趣且风格统一的贴纸设计，约8-10个独特贴纸设计排列在一张纸上。\n内容生成：不要只做logo。自主创造以下混合内容：\n吉祥物/角色：佩戴品牌相关配饰或表达情绪的风格化人物半身像。\n核心产品：与品牌相关的标志性物品。\n符号/物件：与品牌生活方式相关的抽象形状或工具。\n\n视觉风格（单线矢量）：\n该艺术风格"
