    "revised_prompt": "高端奢侈产品广告摄影图，采用横向构图和浅景深效果。正俯视视角下，一瓶高端香水平放于带有细腻纹理的米白色细沙表面上。香水瓶身为厚实的透明矩形玻璃，内部盛有淡金色的液体，顶部配有光滑的金色金属圆柱形瓶盖。香水瓶正面完全可见且端正正立，中央贴有简约的白色方形标签，标签上印有清晰的黑色衬线体文字‘L'Éternité’，其下方印有两行较小的黑色无衬线字体，分别是‘EAU DE PARFUM’和‘100 ml - 3.4 FL.OZ.’。\n\n香水周围的米白色细沙表面呈现出被轻轻拨弄过的波浪状起伏痕迹，暗示着近期的微风或人工互动。香水被置于画面的视觉中心，四周刻意留出宽敞的空白区域。在右下角的空白处，优雅地放置着一小段带有两朵半开白色木兰花和几片翠绿叶片的干树枝；左上角则零星散落着三片洁白的木兰花瓣，作为视觉补充元素，自然地增强了场景的丰富度。\n\n一束温暖明亮的自然阳光从画面左上角斜射而下，在细沙的起伏处、香水瓶以及木兰花的右下方投射出清晰且真实的暖调阴影。透明的玻璃瓶身在阳光照射下，于沙面上形成了明亮的金色焦散光斑。画面整体呈现出3D渲染级别的极高写实度，焦点清晰地集中在香水瓶正面，而边缘散落的花瓣和沙面纹理则有着细腻的虚化过渡，整体光影高级、温暖且宁静。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/item_2019_4.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "A high-end luxury product advertising photograph, utilizing a horizontal composition and shallow depth of field. From a direct top-down overhead perspective, a premium perfume bottle lies flat on a cream-colored fine sand surface with delicate texture. The perfume bottle features a thick, transparent rectangular glass body containing a pale golden liquid, topped with a smooth gold metallic cylindrical cap. The front of the perfume bottle is fully visible and positioned upright, with a minimalist white square label affixed to the center. The label bears clearly printed black serif text reading 'L'Éternité', beneath which are two smaller lines of black sans-serif text reading 'EAU DE PARFUM' and '100 ml - 3.4 FL.OZ.' respectively.\n\nThe cream-colored fine sand surface surrounding the perfume displays gentle, undulating wave-like traces suggesting recent breeze or manual interaction. The perfume is placed at the visual center of the frame, with generous blank space intentionally left around it. In the blank area of the lower right corner, a small dry branch bearing two half-open white magnolia blossoms and several emerald-green leaves is elegantly placed; in the upper left corner, three pristine white magnolia petals are sparsely scattered as supplementary visual elements, naturally enhancing the richness of the scene.\n\nA warm, bright beam of natural sunlight streams diagonally from the upper left corner of the frame, casting clear and realistic warm-toned shadows on the lower right side of the sand undulations, the perfume bottle, and the magnolia flowers. Under the sunlight, the transparent glass bottle body creates bright golden caustic light patterns on the sand surface. The overall image presents an extremely high degree of photorealism at a 3D rendering level, with the focal point sharply concentrated on the front of the perfume bottle, while the scattered petals at the edges and sand surface textures exhibit a delicate bokeh transition. The overall lighting is sophisticated, warm, and serene.",
    "prompt_zh": "一张高端编辑风格照片，[PRODUCT]平放在[TEXTURED SURFACE]上，从正上方俯视角度拍摄。表面被轻微扰动，暗示近期有过动作或互动。产品正面完全可见且方向正确朝上。产品周围区域刻意留白，可选择性放置[COMPLEMENTARY OBJECTS]以在视觉上增强场景效果。来自左上方的自然阳光投射出温暖、逼真的阴影。3D写实风格，奢侈品产品摄影，浅景深，1:1画幅。"
