    "revised_prompt": "一张垂直排版的五宫格美食动作摄影海报，画面从上到下均分为五个横向的矩形区域，整体采用超高细节的微距镜头和较浅的景深，背景虚化，聚焦于双手撕开食物的诱人瞬间，色调统一偏向温暖的电影感。\n\n第一个区域（顶部）：画面中心是一双正在拉开一片刚出炉披萨的手。披萨切片与主饼盘之间拉出长长且富有弹性的马苏里拉奶酪丝。披萨饼皮边缘带有烘烤后的焦脆起泡纹理，表面散发着明显的白色热气，细碎的饼屑在半空中掉落。光线为温暖的烤箱电影感灯光。画面左上角带有白色的文字‘1/5’，右下角印有清晰的标签文字‘CHEESE PULL’。\n\n第二个区域：双手正在掰开一块浸透糖浆的果仁蜜饼（Baklava）。薄如蝉翼的酥皮层在拉扯中清晰断裂，露出内部填满的翠绿色开心果碎馅料。浓稠的蜂蜜糖浆在掰开的缝隙间形成拉丝，并有糖浆悬浮在半空中准备滴落。光线为金色的暖光。画面左上角带有文字‘2/5’，右下角印有标签文字‘SYRUP & CRUNCH’。\n\n第三个区域：双手将一个巧克力熔岩蛋糕从中间掰成两半。蛋糕中心正涌出光滑、浓郁、富有光泽的黑巧克力熔浆，热气缓慢上升，细小的深色蛋糕碎屑悬停在半空中。光影呈现为柔和的暖色聚光灯效果。画面左上角带有文字‘3/5’，右下角印有标签文字‘MOLTEN CHOCOLATE’。\n\n第四个区域：双手正在撕开一个裹着糖霜的肉桂卷。粘稠的肉桂糖馅料在拉开的半空中拉出闪亮且带有光泽的丝线，白色的糖霜顺着面团边缘缓慢滴落，内部蓬松柔软的面团纤维纹理极其清晰可见。光线为温暖舒适的烘焙室灯光。画面左上角带有文字‘4/5’，右下角印有标签文字‘STICKY PULL’。\n\n第五个区域（底部）：双手正在分离一块经典的纽约芝士蛋糕切片。蛋糕内部展现出极致绵密的质感并在拉开时缓慢分离，底部酥脆的棕色饼干底座从中间碎裂开来，切面处带有细微的奶油拉扯质感。光线为柔和的暖色影棚光。画面左上角带有文字‘5/5’，右下角印有标签文字‘CREAMY SEPARATION’。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/item_2062_3.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "A vertically composed five-panel food action photography poster. The frame is evenly divided from top to bottom into five horizontal rectangular zones. The entire composition employs ultra-high-detail macro lenses with a shallow depth of field, blurred backgrounds, and focuses on the appetizing moment of two hands tearing food apart. The color tone is uniformly warm with a cinematic feel.\n\nFirst zone (top): At the center of the frame, a pair of hands is pulling a freshly baked pizza slice away from the main pie. Long, elastic strings of mozzarella cheese stretch between the slice and the pie. The pizza crust edges feature a blistered, charred, crispy texture from baking; the surface emits visible white steam, and fine crumbs are falling through mid-air. The lighting is warm, oven-inspired cinematic lighting. The upper-left corner of the frame bears the white text '1/5,' and the lower-right corner displays a clear label reading 'CHEESE PULL.'\n\nSecond zone: Two hands are breaking open a syrup-soaked piece of Baklava. The paper-thin phyllo pastry layers crack and fracture clearly as they are pulled apart, revealing the interior filled with crushed emerald-green pistachio filling. Thick honey syrup forms glistening threads across the gap, with droplets of syrup suspended in mid-air about to drip. The lighting is a golden warm light. The upper-left corner bears the text '2/5,' and the lower-right corner displays the label 'SYRUP & CRUNCH.'\n\nThird zone: Two hands are breaking a chocolate lava cake in half from the center. A smooth, rich, glossy dark chocolate molten lava is surging from the cake's core; steam rises slowly, and tiny dark cake crumbs hover suspended in mid-air. The lighting presents a soft, warm-toned spotlight effect. The upper-left corner bears the text '3/5,' and the lower-right corner displays the label 'MOLTEN CHOCOLATE.'\n\nFourth zone: Two hands are tearing apart a frosted cinnamon roll. The sticky cinnamon-sugar filling stretches into shiny, glossy threads across mid-air as it is pulled apart; white frosting slowly drips along the edges of the dough, and the internal fluffy, soft dough fiber texture is extremely clearly visible. The lighting is warm, cozy bakery-room lighting. The upper-left corner bears the text '4/5,' and the lower-right corner displays the label 'STICKY PULL.'\n\nFifth zone (bottom): Two hands are separating a slice of classic New York cheesecake. The interior of the cake reveals an ultra-dense, creamy texture that slowly parts as it is pulled apart; the crispy brown graham cracker crust base fractures from the center, and the cross-section shows a subtle creamy stretching texture. The lighting is soft, warm-toned studio light. The upper-left corner bears the text '5/5.'",
