    "revised_prompt": "一张微距摄影风格的3D微缩景观图。画面中央是一张平铺在深色粗糙原木桌面上的复古风格东京街道地图，从这张二维平面的地图上，向上立体地生长、隆起一个照片级逼真的3D微缩东京城市景观，宛如一个精致的城市沙盘模型。微缩景观中包含极其精细的实体建筑：一座红白相间的微缩东京塔高耸入云，钢架结构清晰可见；涩谷十字路口地面的白色斑马线交织，路口周围矗立着微小的发光LED广告牌；古色古香的浅草寺雷门建筑模型坐落在一侧，正中悬挂着微缩的红灯笼。城市的街区和公园区域点缀着多棵粉色盛开的微型樱花树，为钢铁森林增添了自然气息。在密集的现代高楼大厦之间，隐约可见极其微小的行人与车辆轮廓，一条白色的微缩高架轨道跨越街区，上面正行驶着一列白色的新干线子弹头列车。街角深处，几家精致的微型日式拉面店挂着传统的布帘，窗户里透出温馨的暖黄色灯光。平铺在底部的地图图纸上，清晰地印着黑色的英文地名：'TOKYO'、'Shibuya' 和 'Minato City'。画面采用竖向构图，影棚级别的柔和顶光从侧上方倾洒，在地图表面投下微缩建筑的逼真阴影。极浅的电影级景深使画面的前景桌面以及远处的背景呈现出柔美的光学虚化散景，视觉焦点牢牢锁定在中心立体生长的微缩城市上，整体色彩丰富，冷色调的城市霓虹与暖色调的街角灯光形成鲜明对比。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/item_2107_1.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "A macro photography–style 3D miniature landscape image. At the center of the frame is a vintage-style Tokyo street map laid flat on a dark, rough-hewn wooden tabletop. Rising upward from this two-dimensional flat map, a photorealistic 3D miniature Tokyo cityscape grows and emerges in three dimensions, resembling an exquisite city sandbox model. The miniature landscape contains extremely fine physical structures: a red-and-white miniature Tokyo Tower soars skyward with its steel lattice framework clearly visible; the white zebra-crossing stripes of the Shibuya Crossing crisscross on the ground, surrounded by tiny glowing LED billboards; an antique-styled architectural model of Senso-ji Temple's Kaminarimon gate is situated on one side, with a miniature red lantern hanging at its center. The city blocks and park areas are dotted with multiple miniature cherry blossom trees in full pink bloom, adding a touch of nature to the steel jungle. Among the densely packed modern skyscrapers, extremely tiny silhouettes of pedestrians and vehicles are faintly visible; a white miniature elevated rail track spans across city blocks, with a white Shinkansen bullet train running on it. Deep in a street corner, several exquisite miniature Japanese ramen shops hang traditional noren curtains, with warm yellow light glowing from their windows. On the map paper laid flat at the base, black English place names are clearly printed: 'TOKYO,' 'Shibuya,' and 'Minato City.' The image uses a vertical composition, with studio-grade soft top lighting cascading from the upper side, casting realistic shadows of the miniature buildings onto the map surface. An extremely shallow cinematic depth of field renders both the foreground tabletop and the distant background in soft optical bokeh, while the visual focal point is firmly locked onto the miniature city growing three-dimensionally at the center. The overall colors are rich, with cool-toned urban neon forming a striking contrast against the warm-toned street-corner lighting.",
    "prompt_zh": "一张 {CITY_NAME} 的街头风格地图，放置在 {MAP_SURFACE} 上，地图中涌现出一个照片级写实的 {CITY_NAME} 微缩版本，包含 {LANDMARK_1}、{LANDMARK_2}、{LANDMARK_3}、{NATURE_ELEMENT}、{URBAN_LIFE_ELEMENT}、{ICONIC_TRANSPORT} 以及 {EXTRA_DETAIL}。所有元素如同 3D 城市微缩景观一般从地图中生长而出。工作室柔光照明，电影级景深，2:3 画幅。"
