    "revised_prompt": "这是一张带有强烈复古胶片质感的摄影照片，采用宽屏横向构图。画面主体是一位极具魅力的年轻女孩的侧影，她身穿一件高领、紧身的黑色长袖连衣裙，怀抱一束橙粉色的花朵。女孩的皮肤白皙细腻、略带剔透感。她的长发在温暖的逆光下散发出柔和的光晕，几缕凌乱的发丝在她的下颌线处狂野地飞舞。由于相机的平移跟拍与人物可爱的动态，女孩的精致面容和身体轮廓产生了明显的运动模糊与摇曳感，并伴有奇幻的重影效果。\n\n在女孩身旁，隐约可见一个陈旧的旧报刊亭，报刊亭的旁边堆放着一簇枯木，几株同样是橙粉色的花朵在枯木间绽放，与女孩手中的花束形成视觉上的呼应。\n\n整个画面覆盖着浓郁的复古胶片颗粒，背景被强烈的运动模糊和明显的拖影效果所吞没。柔焦镜头搭配暖色调、低饱和度的滤镜，使图像显得朦胧而慵懒。这种将动态模糊与胶片颗粒相融合的处理方式，营造出一种充满故事感和电影感的奇幻氛围，在展现女孩甜美生动的同时，又透露出一丝迷人且危险的独特气质，呈现出极具时尚社交媒体风格的视觉效果。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/item_2151_4.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "This is a photograph with a strong vintage film texture, composed in a widescreen landscape format. The main subject is the silhouette of a remarkably charming young girl, wearing a high-necked, form-fitting black long-sleeved dress and cradling a bouquet of orange-pink flowers. The girl's skin is fair, delicate, and slightly translucent. Her long hair emits a soft halo under warm backlight, with several disheveled strands dancing wildly around her jawline. Due to the camera's panning motion and the girl's adorable dynamic movement, her delicate facial features and body contours exhibit noticeable motion blur and a swaying quality, accompanied by fantastical ghosting effects.\n\nBeside the girl, a weathered old newsstand is faintly visible, with a cluster of dead wood piled next to it. Several flowers, also orange-pink in color, bloom among the dead branches, creating a visual echo with the bouquet in the girl's arms.\n\nThe entire image is covered with rich vintage film grain, and the background is engulfed by intense motion blur and pronounced trailing effects. A soft-focus lens paired with warm-toned, low-saturation filters renders the image hazy and languid. This treatment, which blends dynamic motion blur with film grain, creates a fantastical atmosphere full of narrative and cinematic quality. While showcasing the girl's sweet and vivid presence, it also exudes a hint of alluring yet dangerous unique temperament, presenting a highly fashion-forward social media–style visual effect.",
    "prompt_zh": "生成的图像以上传的图片作为角色参考，身穿高领紧身黑色长袖连衣裙。一簇枯木与橙粉色花朵散落在一座旧报亭旁，复古胶片的颗粒质感交织其中，模糊的背景带有明显的拖影，双重曝光效果营造出奇幻氛围。一位妖冶美丽的女孩，手捧鲜花，以侧面示人，白皙的肌肤细腻而通透。她精致的面庞在运动中模糊，身形轮廓随摇镜（panning）微微摇曳。"
