    "revised_prompt": "一张北欧极简风格的生活方式插画，采用竖构图。画面中央，一位留着红棕色短发的女孩正惬意地坐在芥末黄色的现代简约单人沙发上阅读。她微微低头，双手捧着一本打开的淡蓝色封面的书。女孩身穿米白色的高领宽松毛衣和浅灰色的直筒亚麻长裤，脚穿米色毛线袜。沙发的右侧放置着一个原木色的圆形极简边桌，桌面上有一个白色的陶瓷马克杯，杯口飘出两缕柔和弯曲的白色热气线条。画面的左下角是一株生长茂盛的龟背竹，宽大圆润的低饱和度绿色叶片错落有致。沙发和边桌下方铺着一张带有简单白色线条的鼠尾草绿色圆形地毯。背景呈现扁平化的几何色块组合，主墙面为低饱和度的灰粉色，女孩身后有一个巨大的米色拱形色块，一直向上延伸至画面顶部，充分利用了竖长画幅的空间。整体画面采用低饱和度的柔彩色调，运用扁平化设计，但在几何形状的边缘和背景中带有极其柔和的色彩渐变，边缘轮廓干净利落，没有黑色描边，完美营造出一种温馨舒适且充满现代感的视觉美学。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/item_2222_1.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "A Nordic minimalist lifestyle illustration in a vertical composition. At the center of the image, a girl with reddish-brown short hair is comfortably sitting on a mustard-yellow modern minimalist single-seat sofa, reading. She tilts her head slightly downward, holding an open book with a light blue cover in both hands. The girl wears an off-white turtleneck oversized sweater and light gray straight-cut linen trousers, with beige knitted socks on her feet. To the right of the sofa is a natural wood-toned round minimalist side table, on which sits a white ceramic mug with two soft, curving white steam lines rising from its rim. In the lower left corner of the image is a lush Monstera deliciosa plant, with large, rounded, low-saturation green leaves arranged in a staggered layout. Beneath the sofa and side table lies a sage-green circular rug with simple white line patterns. The background presents a flat geometric color-block combination: the main wall is a low-saturation grayish-pink, and behind the girl is a large beige arch-shaped color block extending upward to the top of the image, fully utilizing the vertical format's space. The overall image employs a low-saturation soft pastel color palette with flat design, yet incorporates extremely gentle color gradients along the edges of geometric shapes and in the background. Edge outlines are clean and crisp with no black strokes, perfectly creating a warm, cozy, and modern visual aesthetic.",
