    "revised_prompt": "纯白色背景的竖版构图中，展现一幅精细的黑白墨水线稿人物特写插画，融合了现代图画小说与高级时尚插画的审美风格。画面主体是一位年轻女性，呈四分之三侧面，目光微微向左倾斜。她的面部特征柔和逼真，双眼大而富有表现力，睫毛根根分明，鼻梁轮廓清晰，双唇微启，嘴唇上涂有柔和的珊瑚红色口红。她头戴一顶顶部带有毛线球的冬季针织帽，帽子上布满了由蓝色、黄色、粉色、红色和青色小矩形色块组成的彩色马赛克图案。除了这顶彩色的帽子和珊瑚红色的嘴唇，画面其余部分均保持高对比度的黑白单色调。女性留着飘逸的长发，几缕松散的发丝自然垂落，头发的质感通过极细的素描线条和交叉排线（cross-hatching）技法细腻勾勒。她身穿无袖上衣，裸露的肩膀和手臂上布满了抽象的几何图形和类似印刷排版的纹身图案，这些图案由极细的技术线条构成，带有一种建筑图纸和机械原理图的视觉感，手臂纹身中清晰可见‘SYS-09’、‘L-AXIS’和‘VOL. 4’等排版文字，并伴有坐标刻度和连接线。整体画面采用极简的阴影处理，线条超锐利，墨水线稿与数字精修结合，呈现出优雅、时尚且具有高清晰度的视觉效果。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/item_2252_4.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "In a vertical composition against a pure white background, a detailed black-and-white ink line-art character close-up illustration is presented, blending the aesthetic styles of modern graphic novels and high-fashion illustration. The main subject is a young woman shown in a three-quarter profile view, her gaze slightly tilted to the left. Her facial features are soft and realistic, with large, expressive eyes, individually defined eyelashes, a clearly outlined nose bridge, and slightly parted lips wearing soft coral-red lipstick. She wears a winter knitted beanie with a pom-pom on top, covered in a colorful mosaic pattern composed of small rectangular color blocks in blue, yellow, pink, red, and cyan. Apart from this colorful hat and the coral-red lips, the rest of the image remains in high-contrast black-and-white monochrome. The woman has flowing long hair, with a few loose strands falling naturally; the hair texture is delicately rendered through ultra-fine sketch lines and cross-hatching techniques. She wears a sleeveless top, and her exposed shoulders and arms are covered with abstract geometric shapes and typographic-style tattoo designs composed of ultra-fine technical lines, evoking a visual quality of architectural blueprints and mechanical schematics. Clearly visible within the arm tattoos are typographic texts such as 'SYS-09', 'L-AXIS', and 'VOL. 4', accompanied by coordinate scales and connecting lines. The overall image features minimal shadow treatment with ultra-sharp lines, combining ink line art with digital refinement to deliver an elegant, fashionable, and high-definition visual effect.",
