    "revised_prompt": "这是一张宽屏比例的品牌视觉识别（VI）系统设计样机展示图，采用3x3的九宫格布局，展示了一个名为“AURA”的高级护肤品牌的完整一致的视觉系统。整体画面铺设在浅灰色的无缝背景上，采用柔和的漫反射影棚光照，带有微妙细腻的阴影，呈现出干净、现代、极简的高端质感。品牌的统一配色方案由鼠尾草绿、暖米色和炭灰色组成。画面中没有人物，也没有任何真实世界的品牌名或水印。\n\n各个网格的具体内容如下：\n网格1（左上）：展示主要品牌Logo的纸卡样机。一张带有微小压纹质感的暖米色卡片居中放置，正面印有清晰的炭灰色主Logo文字 'AURA' 以及下方小字副标题 'BOTANICAL SKINCARE'。\n网格2（中上）：辅助标志和字母组合变体展示。画面背景为鼠尾草绿，中央展示了一个由极简几何线条构成的大写字母 'A' 标志，旁边排列着由该字母演变而成的图案阵列。\n网格3（右上）：色彩样本和字体排版海报。海报上方整齐排列着三个正方形色块（鼠尾草绿、暖米色、炭灰色），下方展示了字体排版样本，包含黑色大标题 'Typography'，副标题 'Helvetica Now Display'，以及一段清晰的示例文本 'The essence of pure, natural beauty.'。\n网格4（左中）：精华产品的包装盒样机。一个鼠尾草绿色的纸盒直立放置，包装正面印有白色的 'AURA' 标志，下方写着 'Glow Serum'，底部印有容量信息 '30ml / 1 fl oz'。\n网格5（正中）：面霜产品的主视觉摄影图。一个暖米色的哑光陶瓷面霜罐放置在极简的几何底座上，罐身印有炭灰色的 'AURA' 和 'Daily Moisture' 字样。\n网格6（右中）：一组三个不同尺寸的身体乳泵瓶。三个鼠尾草绿色的磨砂质感泵瓶按从低到高的顺序并排站立，瓶身统一印有 'AURA' 和 'Body Lotion'，并在底部带有对应的容量标识 '250ml'、'500ml'、'750ml'。\n网格7（左下）：品牌文具样机组合。画面中错落摆放着名片、信纸和信封。名片上印有 'AURA'、'Jane Doe'、'Creative Director' 以及邮箱 'hello@auraskincare.com'；信纸顶部居中印有主Logo；信封左上角印有小巧的字母 'A' 标志。\n网格8（中下）：社交媒体帖子和手机屏幕UI预览。一台平放的智能手机，屏幕点亮，显示着品牌的社交主页，顶部应用名称位置显示 'AURA'，下方呈现极简排版的网格图片流，图片内容均为色调一致的护肤品和植物元素。\n网格9（右下）：带有道具的生活方式场景图。浅色大理石台面上放置着一瓶 'AURA' 品牌的玻璃滴管精华液，旁边巧妙搭配了一片鼠尾草绿色的尤加利叶和一块天然浅色石块作为拍摄道具，自然光影斑驳地投射在产品上。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/item_2259_3.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "This is a widescreen brand Visual Identity (VI) system design mockup presentation, arranged in a 3×3 grid layout, showcasing the complete and consistent visual system of a premium skincare brand named \"AURA.\" The overall scene is set against a light gray seamless background, lit with soft diffused studio lighting and subtle, delicate shadows, conveying a clean, modern, minimalist, and high-end aesthetic. The brand's unified color palette consists of sage green, warm beige, and charcoal gray. There are no human figures in the image, nor any real-world brand names or watermarks.\n\nThe specific contents of each grid are as follows:\nGrid 1 (top-left): A paper card mockup displaying the primary brand logo. A warm beige card with a subtle embossed texture is centered, with the main logo text 'AURA' printed in charcoal gray on the front, along with the smaller subtitle 'BOTANICAL SKINCARE' below.\nGrid 2 (top-center): Secondary marks and monogram variants. The background is sage green, with a minimalist geometric uppercase letter 'A' mark displayed in the center, accompanied by an array of patterns derived from the letter arranged alongside it.\nGrid 3 (top-right): Color swatches and typography poster. Three square color swatches (sage green, warm beige, charcoal gray) are neatly arranged at the top of the poster, with typography samples displayed below, including a black headline 'Typography,' a subtitle 'Helvetica Now Display,' and a clear sample text reading 'The essence of pure, natural beauty.'\nGrid 4 (middle-left): A packaging box mockup for a serum product. A sage green paper box stands upright, with the white 'AURA' logo printed on the front, 'Glow Serum' written below, and the volume information '30ml / 1 fl oz' printed at the bottom.\nGrid 5 (center): A hero visual photograph of a moisturizer product. A warm beige matte ceramic cream jar is placed on a minimalist geometric pedestal, with 'AURA' and 'Daily Moisture' printed in charcoal gray on the jar body.\nGrid 6 (middle-right): A set of three body lotion pump bottles in different sizes. Three sage green frosted-finish pump bottles stand side by side in ascending height order, uniformly printed with 'AURA' and 'Body Loti",
