    "type": "t2i",
    "author": "@aleenaamiir",
    "author_link": "https://x.com/aleenaamiir/status/2008826083282686133",
    "revised_prompt": "高质量数字插画，采用垂直构图。画面中央以粗体、大写字母竖向错落堆叠拼写出英文单词 'ITALY'。字体具有明显的立体雕塑感，字母之间相互重叠，增强了画面的空间深度与视觉流动性。每个字母内部都由极具代表性的意大利传统美食和食材精细填充，食材的排列完美贴合字母的轮廓：字母 'I' 由缠绕的细长意大利面构成，面条间点缀着鲜艳的圣女果和翠绿的罗勒叶；字母 'T' 的顶部由一块边缘微焦、覆盖着马苏里拉奶酪的那不勒斯披萨构成，垂直部分是层叠的意大利薄切熏香肠和帕尔马火腿；字母 'A' 由质地粗糙的夏巴塔面包组成，表面镶嵌着黑橄榄和油浸小番茄；字母 'L' 是由金黄色的炸鱿鱼圈和炸玉米面块堆积而成，旁边挤放着新鲜的柠檬角；字母 'Y' 由层层叠叠的千层面和浓郁的红肉酱塑造，表面撒满白色的帕马森干酪碎。画面背景为深炭灰色，烘托出食材的温暖色调。字母周围及画面空白处自然散落着带皮大蒜、新鲜的迷迭香枝条、黑胡椒粒、少许白色面粉，以及一小碗装有初榨橄榄油与黑醋混合物的陶瓷调料碟。食物元素以美食摄影的编辑风格呈现，具有极高的清晰度和丰富的纹理细节。柔和的漫反射光线打在食材表面，展现出油脂的细腻光泽和食物的自然凹凸感。整体对比度高，色彩饱满，呈现出一种温暖、诱人且高级的视觉美学。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/item_2261_1.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "High-quality digital illustration in a vertical composition. At the center of the image, the English word 'ITALY' is spelled out in bold, uppercase letters stacked vertically in a staggered arrangement. The typography has a pronounced three-dimensional sculptural quality, with the letters overlapping one another to enhance spatial depth and visual flow. Each letter is intricately filled with highly representative traditional Italian foods and ingredients, with the food elements perfectly conforming to the contours of the letters: the letter 'I' is composed of intertwined thin spaghetti strands, interspersed with vibrant cherry tomatoes and bright green basil leaves; the top of the letter 'T' is formed by a Neapolitan pizza with slightly charred edges covered in mozzarella cheese, while its vertical stroke consists of layered Italian thinly sliced salami and Parma ham; the letter 'A' is made of coarse-textured ciabatta bread, studded with black olives and oil-marinated small tomatoes; the letter 'L' is built from golden fried calamari rings and fried polenta pieces stacked together, with fresh lemon wedges squeezed in alongside; the letter 'Y' is sculpted from layers upon layers of lasagna and rich red meat ragù, its surface generously sprinkled with white Parmesan cheese shavings. The background is deep charcoal gray, accentuating the warm tones of the ingredients. Scattered naturally around the letters and in the blank spaces of the composition are unpeeled garlic cloves, fresh rosemary sprigs, black peppercorns, a light dusting of white flour, and a small ceramic condiment dish containing a mixture of extra virgin olive oil and balsamic vinegar. The food elements are rendered in an editorial food photography style with extremely high clarity and rich textural detail. Soft diffused light falls across the surface of the ingredients, revealing the delicate sheen of oils and the natural contours and textures of the food. The overall contrast is high, the colors are saturated, presenting a warm, inviting, and sophisticated visual aesthetic.",
    "prompt_zh": "一幅高品质数字插画，以粗体大写字母拼出 [COUNTRY NAME] 一词。字体具有雕塑感和立体感，每个字母微妙地重叠或层叠排列以增强纵深感和视觉流动感。背景为浓郁的深色调，与食材的色彩相互映衬。\n\n每个字母内部精细地填充来自 [COUNTRY] 的标志性传统食物，例如 [SIGNATURE BREADS / FRUITS / SPICES / DISH ELEMENTS]，精心排列以贴合字体的轮廓。盛有 [TRADITIONAL SAUCES / CONDIMENTS] 的小碗和散落的食材"
}, {
