    "revised_prompt": "这是一幅超高清电影级的奢华护肤品广告摄影图，采用竖屏画幅。画面中心直立放置着一个半透明的琥珀色精华液按压泵头玻璃瓶。瓶身表面布满细微的凝结水滴，质感逼真。瓶身正中贴有极简风格的标签，上面印有清晰的黑色英文排版文字：顶部为品牌名 'LUMIÈRE'，中间是产品名 'AMBER RADIANCE SERUM'，底部标注容量 '50 ML / 1.7 FL OZ'。瓶子平稳地安放在一块弯曲且纹理粗糙的天然浮木上。在浮木两侧，对称地点缀着盛开的乳白色热带花朵以及一朵未开放的花蕾，呈现出雕塑般的视觉平衡。画面的前景处静静地散落着几根细长的深褐色香草豆荚。\n\n背景设定在一个温暖的沙漠色调工作室环境中，后方是一块柔软的沙色背景板，上面投射出大面积、具有流线感的阴影图案，营造出强烈的空间深度和戏剧性光影效果。光线采用高对比度的电影级照明，一束强烈的定向主光源从画面左侧打入，穿透瓶中的琥珀色液体，使其内部散发出耀眼的光芒；同时在玻璃瓶边缘勾勒出锐利的轮廓光。光线向右侧自然过渡为深邃的阴影，带来充满情绪张力的高级时尚大片质感。\n\n整体色调丰富且充满感官诱惑，由闪耀的金琥珀色、温暖的焦糖色、柔和的象牙白和深沉的大地棕色交织而成。构图采用略带低角度透视的居中特写方式。画面运用了极浅的景深效果，焦点处的精华瓶、水滴和标签文字如刀锋般锐利清晰，而背景的阴影与远处的元素则融化为如奶油般柔和细腻的散景。画面氛围优雅、神秘且极具奢华感，具备8K超高分辨率的逼真纹理细节。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/item_2262_4.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "This is an ultra-high-definition cinematic luxury skincare advertising photograph in a vertical portrait format. At the center of the frame stands an upright translucent amber-colored glass serum bottle with a press-pump dispenser. The bottle surface is covered with fine condensation droplets, rendered with lifelike realism. A minimalist-style label is affixed to the center of the bottle, printed with clear black English typographic text: the brand name 'LUMIÈRE' at the top, the product name 'AMBER RADIANCE SERUM' in the middle, and the volume '50 ML / 1.7 FL OZ' noted at the bottom. The bottle rests steadily on a curved, rough-textured piece of natural driftwood. On both sides of the driftwood, creamy white tropical flowers in full bloom and an unopened bud are symmetrically arranged, creating a sculptural visual balance. In the foreground, several slender dark brown vanilla bean pods are scattered casually.\n\nThe background is set in a warm desert-toned studio environment, with a soft sand-colored backdrop behind, onto which large, flowing shadow patterns are projected, creating a strong sense of spatial depth and dramatic chiaroscuro effect. The lighting employs high-contrast cinematic illumination, with a strong directional key light entering from the left side of the frame, penetrating the amber liquid inside the bottle and causing it to radiate a brilliant inner glow; simultaneously, it traces a sharp rim light along the edges of the glass bottle. The light naturally transitions to deep shadows on the right side, delivering a moody, high-fashion editorial quality charged with emotional tension.\n\nThe overall color palette is rich and sensually evocative, woven from gleaming golden amber, warm caramel, soft ivory, and deep earthy brown tones. The composition employs a slightly low-angle perspective with a centered close-up framing. An extremely shallow depth of field is utilized—the serum bottle, water droplets, and label text at the focal point are razor-sharp, while the background shadows and distant elements dissolve into creamy, velvety smooth bokeh. The atmosphere is elegant, mysterious, and exquisitely luxurious, with lifelike textural detail at 8K ultra-high resolution.",
    "prompt_zh": "超电影感奢华护肤品产品摄影，一瓶半透明琥珀色精华液按压瓶直立于画面中央，置于一块弧形纹理浮木之上，瓶身贴有极简标签，印有清晰的黑色字体排版，玻璃表面凝有细密的水珠；瓶身两侧对称排列着盛开的奶白色热带花朵和一枚未开的花苞，沿浮木布置，营造雕塑般的平衡感，前景中搁置着纤细的香草荚；背景为暖色调沙漠风格的摄影棚环境，大面积流动的光影图案投射在一块光滑的表面上"
