    "revised_prompt": "超写实电影级人像摄影。画面采用宽幅横向构图，聚焦一位年轻女性的肩部以上特写。她头部微侧，目光望向画外，神情柔和沉思。人物面部比例自然，皮肤纹理真实，雀斑等细节清晰可见，几缕略显凌乱的发丝自然垂于面庞。她身穿黑色细吊带上衣，造型极简，无配饰。光影极具戏剧张力，温暖的侧面定向光照亮脸部一侧，另一侧陷入深邃阴影，形成强烈对比与情感深度。背景为暗色调，经过柔和模糊处理，模拟85mm人像镜头的浅景深与奶油状散景效果。整体画面具备高动态范围与自然逼真的编辑级调色，肤色真实且无人工光晕。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/item_2268_4.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "Hyper-realistic, cinematic-grade portrait photography. The image employs a wide horizontal composition, focusing on a close-up of a young woman from the shoulders up. Her head is slightly tilted, her gaze directed off-camera, with a soft, contemplative expression. The facial proportions are natural, the skin texture is authentic, and fine details such as freckles are clearly visible, with a few slightly tousled strands of hair falling naturally across her face. She wears a black thin spaghetti-strap top, with minimalist styling and no accessories. The lighting carries intense dramatic tension—warm, directional side light illuminates one side of the face while the other side falls into deep shadow, creating strong contrast and emotional depth. The background is dark-toned, treated with soft blur to simulate the shallow depth of field and creamy bokeh effect of an 85mm portrait lens. The overall image features high dynamic range and naturally realistic editorial-grade color grading, with true-to-life skin tones and no artificial haloing.",
    "prompt_zh": "超写实电影感近景肖像，将拍摄主体替换为我的参考图像。\n\n一位年轻女性肩部以上特写，头部微微侧转，目光望向画面外，带有柔和而沉思的表情。自然的面部比例，可见的皮肤纹理，细微的雀斑和精细细节均予以保留。\n\n松散、略显凌乱的发丝垂落在脸颊前，营造自然而亲密的氛围，身穿细肩带黑色上衣，造型极简，无厚重配饰。灯光具有戏剧性和电影感：温暖的定向光从一侧照射面部，对侧形成深邃的阴影，营造出"
