    "author_link": "https://x.com/Taaruk_/status/2018252656574185981",
    "revised_prompt": "一张采用垂直构图的超写实印尼传统美食信息图海报。整体风格为现代烹饪编辑排版，背景为干净且具有戏剧性光影对比的深炭灰色。\n\n画面顶部居中位置印有粗体醒目的标题文字，大标题为 'KARI AYAM'，其下方紧跟说明菜品起源的副标题 'ASAL: INDONESIA'。\n\n画面下半部分放置着一个质感高级的深色陶瓷碗，碗中盛满诱人的印尼咖喱鸡，浓郁金黄的汤汁表面泛着高光，真实的白色蒸汽正从碗中袅袅升起。\n\n在碗的正上方，呈现出极具电影感的食材悬浮定格画面：一块纹理清晰的新鲜鸡肉、鲜艳的红辣椒、切开的亮黄色姜黄根、翠绿的柠檬叶、一根香茅草以及几枚八角，正以失重的状态漂浮在半空中。穿插在这些香草与香料之间的，是充满光泽感的金黄色咖喱汁与乳白色椰奶在空中飞溅、交织的动态水花，质感超写实且令人垂涎。\n\n海报画面中分布着干净现代的印尼语文本标签，通过带有弧度的白色细线箭头精准连接并指向对应的悬浮食材。具体的标签文字包括：指向鸡肉的 'Daging Ayam Segar'，指向红辣椒的 'Cabai Merah Besar'，指向香茅的 'Serai Wangi'，指向姜黄的 'Kunyit Segar'，以及指向飞溅汤汁的 'Kuah Kari Kental' 和 'Santan Kelapa'。\n\n整幅画面呈现出 8K 单反级专业美食摄影的画质。摄影采用浅景深效果，焦点集中在漂浮的食材和飞溅的咖喱上。丰富的金色工作室灯光从侧面打入，勾勒出食材的边缘轮廓，营造出专业、高端且极具食欲的视觉氛围。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/item_2286_3.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "A vertically composed, hyper-realistic Indonesian traditional cuisine infographic poster. The overall style follows modern culinary editorial typography, set against a clean, dramatically lit deep charcoal-gray background.\n\nAt the top center of the image, bold and eye-catching title text is printed, with the main heading reading 'KARI AYAM', immediately followed below by the subtitle indicating the dish's origin: 'ASAL: INDONESIA'.\n\nIn the lower half of the image sits a premium-textured dark ceramic bowl filled with appetizing Indonesian chicken curry, the rich golden broth glistening with specular highlights on its surface, while realistic white steam wisps rise gently from the bowl.\n\nDirectly above the bowl, a cinematic freeze-frame scene of levitating ingredients is presented: a piece of fresh chicken with clearly defined texture, vibrant red chilies, a sliced bright-yellow turmeric root, verdant kaffir lime leaves, a stalk of lemongrass, and several star anise pods, all floating in mid-air in a weightless state. Interspersed among these herbs and spices are glossy, dynamic splashes of golden curry sauce and milky-white coconut milk swirling and intertwining in the air, rendered with hyper-realistic texture that is utterly mouth-watering.\n\nDistributed across the poster are clean, modern Indonesian-language text labels, precisely connected to their corresponding levitating ingredients via curved white thin-line arrows. The specific label texts include: 'Daging Ayam Segar' pointing to the chicken, 'Cabai Merah Besar' pointing to the red chilies, 'Serai Wangi' pointing to the lemongrass, 'Kunyit Segar' pointing to the turmeric, as well as 'Kuah Kari Kental' and 'Santan Kelapa' pointing to the splashing broth.\n\nThe entire image presents 8K DSLR-grade professional food photography quality. The photography employs a shallow depth of field effect, with the focal point concentrated on the levitating ingredients and splashing curry. Rich golden studio lighting enters from the side, tracing the edge contours of the ingredients and creating a professional, high-end, and intensely appetite-inducing visual atmosphere.",
    "prompt_zh": "Nano Banana pro on Goggle Gemini.\n{\n  \"image_prompt\": {\n    \"type\": \"超写实印度尼西亚传统美食信息图海报\",\n    \"layout_and_composition\": {\n      \"orientation\": \"竖版构图\",\n      \"style\": \"现代美食信息图设计，编辑排版风格\",\n      \"background\": \"富有戏剧性但干净整洁的背景\"\n    },\n    \"typography_elements\": {\n      \"headline\": {\n        \"position\": \"顶部\",\n        \"style\": \"粗体文字显示菜品名称和产地（ASAL）\"\n      },\n      \"labels\": {\n        \"style\": \"简洁的印度尼西亚语字体排版\",\n        \"connectors\": \"弧形标签指引箭头"
