    "revised_prompt": "一张高端写实的商业护肤品摄影图，采用竖版构图。画面中央直立着一个哑光白色的塑料按压式护肤品瓶。瓶身正面印有清晰极简的黑色无衬线英文字母，最上方是品牌名 'hella beauty'，紧接着下方以较小字体印着产品名称 'water bank moisture lotion'。在产品名下方，还印有几排细微的深灰色产品说明文字，依次为 'HYDRATING & SOOTHING FORMULA' 以及底部的容量标识 '150 ML / 5.0 FL. OZ.'。瓶子平稳放置在层叠的天然石材表面上。瓶身周围环绕着精心布置的自然有机道具，整体呈现出平衡且对称的构图。道具包括数块光滑的灰色河石、浅米色且带有粗糙多孔纹理的岩石块、几簇湿润柔软的绿色苔藓、几朵精致的白色绒球花、几朵奶油色的雏菊状花朵、几片浅绿色的蕨类植物叶片，以及一朵色彩柔和的鼠尾草绿玫瑰。画面的最前景被几朵柔和模糊、处于失焦状态的白色花朵部分包围，形成前景框架并营造出平滑的虚化光斑（Bokeh），极大地增强了空间景深感。背景是无缝的柔和暖米色影棚背景幕布，带有柔和的微渐变效果，无任何可见的物理边缘。光线模拟柔和漫射的自然日光，从左上方倾洒而下，在石块、植物和瓶身的右侧投下柔和的阴影，并在哑光塑料瓶身和天鹅绒般的花瓣上形成了自然细腻的高光。整体色调以温暖的中性色、柔和的白色、鼠尾草绿和低饱和度的大地色调为主。画面采用浅景深手法，焦点极其锐利地落在中景的产品标签、多孔石材和湿润苔藓的微观细节上，呈现出一种平静、轻盈、纯净的奢华植物护肤品广告美学与电影级超高逼真度。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/item_2288_2.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "A high-end, realistic commercial skincare product photography image in vertical/portrait orientation. At the center of the frame stands an upright matte-white plastic pump-dispenser skincare bottle. The front of the bottle features clean, minimalist black sans-serif English lettering: the brand name 'hella beauty' at the very top, followed directly below in smaller font by the product name 'water bank moisture lotion'. Beneath the product name, several lines of fine dark-gray product description text are printed, reading 'HYDRATING & SOOTHING FORMULA' and the volume designation '150 ML / 5.0 FL. OZ.' at the bottom. The bottle is placed steadily on layered natural stone surfaces. Carefully arranged natural, organic props surround the bottle, presenting an overall balanced and symmetrical composition. The props include several smooth gray river stones, light beige rock pieces with rough porous textures, clusters of moist soft green moss, several delicate white pom-pom flowers, a few cream-colored daisy-like blooms, several pale green fern fronds, and a softly colored sage-green rose. The very foreground is partially framed by several softly blurred, out-of-focus white flowers, forming a foreground frame and creating smooth bokeh that greatly enhances the sense of spatial depth. The background is a seamless, soft warm-beige studio backdrop with a gentle subtle gradient effect and no visible physical edges. The lighting simulates soft, diffused natural daylight cascading from the upper left, casting gentle shadows on the right side of the stones, plants, and bottle, while producing naturally delicate highlights on the matte plastic bottle surface and the velvety petals. The overall color palette is dominated by warm neutrals, soft whites, sage greens, and desaturated earth tones. The image employs a shallow depth of field technique, with the focal point tack-sharp on the mid-ground product label, the micro-detail of the porous stone, and the moist moss, presenting a serene, airy, pure luxury botanical skincare advertising aesthetic with cinematic ultra-high photorealism.",
    "prompt_zh": "超高端照片级写实商业护肤品产品摄影，画面中央直立放置一瓶哑光白色塑料按压瓶，瓶身标注\"hella beauty\"字样，采用简洁的黑色极简字体排版，下方较小文字写有\"water bank moisture lotion\"及细微产品信息，瓶身置于层叠的天然石材表面上，周围精心摆放着有机道具，包括光滑的灰色河石、浅米色纹理岩石造型、柔软的绿色苔藓簇团、精致的白色绒球花、奶油色雏菊状花朵、浅绿色蕨类叶片，以及一朵柔和的鼠尾草色玫瑰"
