    "revised_prompt": "一幅整洁、色彩丰富的蜡笔和彩色铅笔手绘插画。画面为竖版构图，背景是带有明显颗粒质感的白色纹理纸。画面的最上方，用大号、粗细不均且色彩斑斓的蜡笔手写着英文大写字母 'NEW YORK'，每个字母呈现不同的颜色（如红、蓝、黄、绿、橙、紫交替），充满童趣又与城市的活力氛围相匹配。文字下方描绘了纽约市的标志性景观。画面中央偏后矗立着帝国大厦和克莱斯勒大厦，建筑用干净但略显俏皮的线条勾勒，透视呈现出童话般的不均匀和轻微倾斜感；左侧是绿色的自由女神像，高举着黄色的火炬；右侧延伸出布鲁克林大桥的棕色桥塔和黑色悬索，桥下有几道蓝色和青色的曲线代表水波。建筑群前方点缀着几棵造型可爱的树木，树冠呈云朵状，涂满鲜艳的绿色，配有棕色的树干。底部灰色的街道上画着一辆造型圆润的经典黄色出租车。背景的天空十分明亮，右上角有一轮散发着短促线条光芒的黄色太阳，周围散布着几朵由淡蓝色线条勾勒的蓬松白云。整体画风比典型的儿童画更加精致，线条清晰流畅，但保留了手绘的迷人瑕疵与蜡笔、彩铅特有的涂抹肌理和笔触感。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/item_2309_1.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "A neat, colorful hand-drawn illustration in crayon and colored pencil. The composition is in portrait orientation, with a white textured paper background featuring noticeable grain texture. At the very top of the image, the uppercase English letters 'NEW YORK' are hand-written in large, unevenly thick, and colorful crayon strokes, with each letter rendered in a different color (such as red, blue, yellow, green, orange, and purple alternating), exuding a childlike charm that matches the vibrant atmosphere of the city. Below the text, iconic landmarks of New York City are depicted. Slightly behind the center of the image stand the Empire State Building and the Chrysler Building, outlined with clean yet somewhat playful lines, with perspective rendered in a fairy-tale-like unevenness and slight tilt; on the left is the green Statue of Liberty, holding aloft a yellow torch; extending to the right are the brown towers and black suspension cables of the Brooklyn Bridge, with several curved lines in blue and cyan beneath the bridge representing water ripples. In front of the cluster of buildings, a few adorably shaped trees are scattered, their canopies in cloud-like forms filled with vivid green, paired with brown trunks. On the gray street at the bottom, a rounded classic yellow taxi cab is drawn. The sky in the background is very bright, with a yellow sun emitting short radiating lines in the upper right corner, surrounded by a few fluffy white clouds outlined in light blue lines. The overall drawing style is more refined than a typical children's drawing, with clear and smooth lines, yet retaining the charming imperfections of hand-drawing along with the characteristic smudged texture and brushstroke feel of crayons and colored pencils.",
    "prompt_zh": "一幅整洁、色彩丰富的蜡笔和彩色铅笔画，描绘的是[CITY]，画面包含标志性地标建筑、树木和明亮的天空。风格比典型的儿童画稍显精致——线条干净但仍充满童趣，透视略有偏差，带有迷人的不完美感。页面顶部用大号多彩蜡笔字母写着\"CITY\"字样，色调与城市氛围相呼应。白色纹理纸张背景"
