    "title_en": "Retro Film Wildflower Portrait",
    "prompt": "cinematic, wide-angle portrait of her sitting in a wildflower field during the day. She leans slightly forward, extending one arm to hold a daisy toward the camera, gently blurring the flower in the foreground. Her expression is soft and charming, with messy hair adding to his relaxed, effortless look. She wears a sky-blue sweater adorned with white cloud patterns and light-wash denim jeans. The field around him is bursting with yellow wildflowers and daisies, set beneath a dramatic, partly cloudy sky. The lighting is natural and soft, with a warm, vibrant color grade and a hint of vintage film tones, enhancing the nostalgic, dreamy atmosphere. The shallow depth of field and editorial-style composition evoke a timeless, cinematic mood.\"",
    "prompt_en": "cinematic, wide-angle portrait of her sitting in a wildflower field during the day. She leans slightly forward, extending one arm to hold a daisy toward the camera, gently blurring the flower in the foreground. Her expression is soft and charming, with messy hair adding to his relaxed, effortless look. She wears a sky-blue sweater adorned with white cloud patterns and light-wash denim jeans. The field around him is bursting with yellow wildflowers and daisies, set beneath a dramatic, partly cloudy sky. The lighting is natural and soft, with a warm, vibrant color grade and a hint of vintage film tones, enhancing the nostalgic, dreamy atmosphere. The shallow depth of field and editorial-style composition evoke a timeless, cinematic mood.\"",
