    "revised_prompt": "一幅复古胶片风格的电影感广角人像摄影作品，采用竖直构图。画面中央，一位年轻女性坐在明媚的野花地里。她身体微微前倾，伸出一只手臂，将一朵洁白的雏菊递向镜头。这朵雏菊占据了画面的最前景，因极度靠近镜头而呈现出柔和的失焦模糊效果，增强了画面的空间纵深感。女性的面部表情柔和且迷人，发丝微微凌乱，展现出一种毫不费力、轻松自然的状态。她身穿一件天蓝色的针织毛衣，毛衣表面装饰着白云图案，下半身搭配一条浅色水洗牛仔裤。在她的周围，广阔的田野里盛开着大片明黄色的野花和星星点点的雏菊，生机盎然。画面的上半部分是一片充满戏剧张力的多云天空，云层丰富且富有层次。整个场景沐浴在自然柔和的光线中，色彩温暖而饱满，带有明显的复古胶片色调。浅景深的运用使得人物清晰而背景略微虚化，结合杂志大片般的编辑风格构图，营造出一种怀旧、梦幻且超越时间的电影氛围。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/item_2329_4.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "A cinematic wide-angle portrait photograph in vintage film style, composed in vertical orientation. At the center of the frame, a young woman sits in a bright field of wildflowers. She leans slightly forward, extending one arm to offer a pristine white daisy toward the camera. This daisy occupies the extreme foreground of the image, rendered in a soft, out-of-focus blur due to its extreme proximity to the lens, enhancing the spatial depth of the scene. The woman's facial expression is soft and captivating, with slightly tousled hair, conveying an effortless and naturally relaxed demeanor. She wears a sky-blue knitted sweater adorned with white cloud patterns on its surface, paired with light-colored washed denim jeans on her lower half. Around her, the expansive field is abloom with large swaths of bright yellow wildflowers and scattered daisies, brimming with vitality. The upper half of the frame features a dramatically charged cloudy sky, with rich and layered cloud formations. The entire scene is bathed in naturally soft light, with warm and saturated colors bearing a distinctly vintage film color tone. The use of shallow depth of field renders the subject sharp while the background is slightly blurred, combined with a magazine editorial-style composition, creating a nostalgic, dreamy, and timeless cinematic atmosphere.",
    "prompt_zh": "电影感广角人像，她白天坐在野花田中。她微微前倾，伸出一只手将一朵雏菊递向镜头，前景中的花朵轻微虚化。她的表情柔和迷人，凌乱的头发增添了她随性、不经意的气质。她穿着一件饰有白色云朵图案的天蓝色毛衣和浅色水洗牛仔裤。她周围的田野里开满了黄色野花和雏菊，背景是戏剧性的、多云的天空。光线自然柔和，色调温暖鲜艳，带有一丝复古胶片感。"
