    "revised_prompt": "超写实的高清黑白人物肖像照片。画面主体为乔治娜·罗德里格斯（Georgina Rodríguez）的头部和肩部半身特写，采用横向构图。她的身体微微侧倾，脸部面向前方，但视线若有所思地看向画面右侧画外，神情中性、沉思且略带迷人的慵懒感。面部细节刻画极尽真实：肤质白皙细腻，鼻梁和双颊上自然散布着明显的雀斑；深邃的杏仁眼画有上扬的飞燕眼线并涂有睫毛膏；深色的眉毛轮廓分明且微微上挑；双唇丰满润泽，微微张开；下颌线条柔和，面容年轻。她留着深色齐肩发，发型呈现具有层次感的凌乱波浪卷，八字刘海自然修饰脸庞，几缕松散的碎发在强光下尤为分明。她身穿一件质地简单的白色V领极细肩带吊带背心。画面采用模拟正面直射的闪光灯打光手法，营造出极致的高对比度黑白光影效果，人物的轮廓在平整的纯色背景上投射出清晰、边缘锐利的黑色硬阴影。整体画面充满90年代复古颓废美学与低保真的自然抓拍氛围，焦点极其锐利，完美展现出逼真的皮肤毛孔纹理与细腻的摄影胶片颗粒质感。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/item_2336_3.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "A hyper-realistic high-definition black-and-white portrait photograph. The main subject is a head-and-shoulders close-up of Georgina Rodríguez, composed in landscape orientation. Her body is slightly tilted to one side, with her face directed forward, but her gaze thoughtfully directed off-frame to the right, her expression neutral, contemplative, and carrying a hint of alluring languor. Facial details are rendered with extreme realism: fair and delicate skin with naturally scattered, prominent freckles across the bridge of the nose and both cheeks; deep-set almond eyes accentuated with upswept winged eyeliner and mascara; dark eyebrows with well-defined contours and a slight upward arch; full, moistened lips slightly parted; a soft jawline and youthful visage. She has dark shoulder-length hair styled in textured, tousled wavy curls, with curtain bangs naturally framing her face, and a few loose wisps of hair particularly distinct under the strong light. She wears a simple-textured white V-neck thin-strapped camisole top. The lighting simulates a direct frontal flash, creating an extreme high-contrast black-and-white chiaroscuro effect, with the subject's silhouette casting a sharp, hard-edged black shadow onto the flat, solid-colored background. The overall image is imbued with a 1990s vintage grunge aesthetic and lo-fi candid snapshot atmosphere, with an extremely sharp focal point that perfectly reveals lifelike skin pore texture and fine photographic film grain.",
    "prompt_zh": "{\n  \"image_analysis\": {\n    \"subject\": {\n      \"type\": \"Georgina Rodríguez\",\n      \"expression\": \"中性、略带性感、沉思、视线偏离镜头朝向右侧\",\n      \"pose\": \"肖像拍摄，头肩构图，身体微微倾斜\"\n    },\n    \"facial_features\": {\n      \"skin\": \"白皙，鼻梁和脸颊上点缀着明显的天然雀斑\",\n      \"eyes\": \"深色，杏仁形，侧目凝视，配以飞翼眼线和睫毛膏\",\n      \"eyebrows\": \"深色，轮廓清晰，略带弧度\",\n      \"lips\": \"丰满、饱满、有光泽、微微张开\",\n      \"structure\": \"柔和的下颌线"
}, {
