    "author": "@AmirMushich",
    "author_link": "https://x.com/AmirMushich/status/2024533642555371878",
    "revised_prompt": "一幅极简主义的二维矢量插画海报，采用1950至1960年代的复古线条艺术风格。画面为竖版比例，背景为纯粹的纯白色，居中构图展示着一家经典复古风格的咖啡馆建筑立面。画面顶端居中位置，用优雅的复古英文字体醒目地写着大型标题 'Coffee Roasters Society'。标题下方是咖啡馆的店面设计，店面顶部设有一个宽大的条纹雨篷，雨篷正面的中央清晰地印有品牌名称 'Starbucks'。在雨篷下方平整的门楣处，左侧写有创立年份 'EST. 1971'，右侧写着起源城市 'Seattle'。店面主体由带有方格玻璃的经典双开木门和一大扇明亮的展示橱窗组成。在店面正前方的区域，放置着一张极简的户外长椅。长椅上坐着一位穿着复古风衣与长裙的女士，她姿态从容，手中端着一个咖啡杯。女士的脚边趴着一只安静的宠物狗。整个画面的视觉风格严格遵循双色调调色板，仅使用了星巴克标志性的深绿色与纯白色。所有的轮廓线条、实心色块填充以及排版文字均由深绿色构成。画面完全扁平化，没有任何渐变色、高光或阴影效果，呈现出极致清晰的单色美学与复古氛围。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/item_2338_2.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "A minimalist two-dimensional vector illustration poster in a retro line art style from the 1950s to 1960s. The image is in portrait orientation with a pure white background, featuring a centered composition showcasing the façade of a classic retro-style café. At the top center of the image, a large title 'Coffee Roasters Society' is prominently displayed in an elegant vintage English typeface. Below the title is the café's storefront design, topped with a wide striped awning that has the brand name 'Starbucks' clearly printed at the center of its front face. On the flat lintel beneath the awning, the founding year 'EST. 1971' is inscribed on the left side, and the city of origin 'Seattle' on the right. The main storefront consists of classic double wooden doors with mullioned glass panes and a large bright display window. In the area directly in front of the storefront, a minimalist outdoor bench is placed. Seated on the bench is a woman dressed in a vintage trench coat and long skirt, poised in a relaxed posture, holding a coffee cup in her hand. At the woman's feet lies a quiet pet dog. The entire visual style strictly adheres to a two-tone color palette, using only Starbucks' iconic dark green and pure white. All outlines, solid color block fills, and typographic text are rendered in dark green. The image is completely flat, with no gradients, highlights, or shadow effects whatsoever, presenting an ultimate monochromatically crisp aesthetic and retro atmosphere.",
    "prompt_zh": "[BRAND NAME] | [SUBJECT_TOGGLE]。担任首席平面设计师。\n\n第一阶段：建筑场景设定。\n\n创建一幅极简主义2D矢量插画，表现代表[BRAND NAME]的复古风格店面。\n\n- 自主设计立面风格（现代主义、工业风或古典风），以匹配品牌的历史传承。\n\n第二阶段：主体逻辑（切换系统）。\n\n- 如果[SUBJECT_TOGGLE]为\"OFF\"：仅展示空店面。\n\n- 如果[SUBJECT_TOGGLE]为\"ON\"：自主添加1-2个人物角色或一只宠物，契合品牌的生活方式调性。\n\n第三阶段：动态字体排版（已修正）。\n\n- 标题：自主生成高端"
