    "revised_prompt": "一张竖版多面版时尚Lookbook拼贴海报，采用网格布局，背景为干净的灰白色。占据视觉中心的主画面是一名模特展现高冷时尚姿态，身穿一件重磅黑灰色复古水洗连帽卫衣，卫衣带有明显的做旧破坏边缘和高质量的龟裂丝网印花。画面旁分布着3个较小的矩形细节框：第一个展示龟裂印花的面料微距特写；第二个展示生锈做旧的金属拉链头五金件；第三个展示粗糙的接缝和磨损袖口。海报包含粗野主义无衬线字体的文字，带有斑驳的复印机磨损质感。醒目的品牌主标题为 'OBSCURA'，下方为副标题 'PROJECT: ECLIPSE'。底部排列着说明性小字 'ARCHIVE COLLECTION / HEAVYWEIGHT COTTON / DISTRESSED FINISH / TOKYO STUDIO'。整体呈现高端低保真美学，具有强烈的35mm胶片颗粒感、模拟噪点和轻微扫描线。光线为高对比度的时尚闪光灯效果，阴影深邃，色调暗哑忧郁。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/item_2367_3.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "A portrait-oriented, multi-panel fashion lookbook collage poster with a grid layout on a clean off-white background. The main image occupying the visual center features a model striking an aloof, high-fashion pose, wearing a heavyweight black-gray vintage washed hoodie with pronounced distressed raw edges and high-quality cracked screen-print graphics. Distributed alongside the main image are three smaller rectangular detail frames: the first showcasing a macro close-up of the cracked print fabric; the second displaying a rusted, aged metal zipper pull hardware; and the third showing rough seams and frayed cuffs. The poster contains text in brutalist sans-serif typography with a mottled photocopier-worn texture. The prominent brand main title reads 'OBSCURA', with the subtitle 'PROJECT: ECLIPSE' below. Across the bottom, descriptive small text is arranged: 'ARCHIVE COLLECTION / HEAVYWEIGHT COTTON / DISTRESSED FINISH / TOKYO STUDIO'. The overall presentation conveys a high-end lo-fi aesthetic with strong 35mm film grain, analog noise, and subtle scan lines. The lighting employs a high-contrast fashion flash effect with deep shadows and muted, moody tones.",
    "prompt_zh": "[BRAND NAME]。担任创意总监和品牌策略师。\n\n第一阶段：概念与构图。\n\n在干净的米白色背景上创建一组多面板时尚造型手册拼贴画（网格布局）。\n\n- 主图：模特穿着[BRAND NAME]标志性单品的全身编辑风格造型。\n\n- 细节图：3-4个较小的矩形画框，展示面料、五金配件和缝线的微距特写。\n\n- 根据品牌当前的热门单品自主确定服装类型。\n\n第二阶段：视觉风格与质感。\n\n\"高端Lo-fi\"美学。强烈的胶片颗粒感、模拟噪点和扫描线伪影。厚重的、"
