    "title": "工业离心泵信息图解",
    "title_en": "Industrial Centrifugal Pump Infographic",
    "prompt": "Industrial engineering-style infographic of an object (match exactly the object from the uploaded photo reference).\nUltra-precise technical rendering of the object placed at the center, with accurate proportions, textures, materials, and surface details identical to the reference photo.\nSurround the object with industrial–grade technical elements:\n• Blueprint-inspired dimension lines (length, width, height, radius, angle, tolerances).\n• Cross-section cutaway view revealing internal components with engineering hatching patterns.\n• Exploded-view assembly diagram showing bolts, brackets, joints, wiring, bearings, or internal mechanisms.\n• Material specification blocks (steel type, plastics, alloys, coatings, finishes).\n• Process flow arrows describing manufacturing steps (CNC, casting, welding, injection, stamping).\n• Load & stress indicator graphics with arrows, vector force diagrams, thermal flow, or torque direction.\n• Part numbering following industrial annotation style (Part A01, A02, etc).\n• Tech data panels like: weight, volume, tolerances, rated load, pressure, RPM, operating temperature.\n• QR-style data block or barcode element for extra industrial feel.\nDesign style:\n• clean, structured, engineering-oriented layout\n• color palette of steel grey, dark navy, orange/yellow safety accents\n• background like a technical drafting sheet or industrial metal texture (subtle, not distracting)\n• sharp sans-serif typeface using actual engineering annotation style\n• shadows minimal, prioritizing clarity and precision\nOverall vibe: serius, presisi, manufaktur-grade, seperti poster teknik pabrik atau katalog industrial tooling.\nAspect Ratio: 9:16",
    "prompt_en": "Industrial engineering-style infographic of an object (match exactly the object from the uploaded photo reference).\nUltra-precise technical rendering of the object placed at the center, with accurate proportions, textures, materials, and surface details identical to the reference photo.\nSurround the object with industrial–grade technical elements:\n• Blueprint-inspired dimension lines (length, width, height, radius, angle, tolerances).\n• Cross-section cutaway view revealing internal components with engineering hatching patterns.\n• Exploded-view assembly diagram showing bolts, brackets, joints, wiring, bearings, or internal mechanisms.\n• Material specification blocks (steel type, plastics, alloys, coatings, finishes).\n• Process flow arrows describing manufacturing steps (CNC, casting, welding, injection, stamping).\n• Load & stress indicator graphics with arrows, vector force diagrams, thermal flow, or torque direction.\n• Part numbering following industrial annotation style (Part A01, A02, etc).\n• Tech data panels like: weight, volume, tolerances, rated load, pressure, RPM, operating temperature.\n• QR-style data block or barcode element for extra industrial feel.\nDesign style:\n• clean, structured, engineering-oriented layout\n• color palette of steel grey, dark navy, orange/yellow safety accents\n• background like a technical drafting sheet or industrial metal texture (subtle, not distracting)\n• sharp sans-serif typeface using actual engineering annotation style\n• shadows minimal, prioritizing clarity and precision\nOverall vibe: serius, presisi, manufaktur-grade, seperti poster teknik pabrik atau katalog industrial tooling.\nAspect Ratio: 9:16",
    "source": "https://x.com/Strength04_X/status/2021082486294675765",
    "type": "t2i",
    "author": "@Strength04_X",
    "author_link": "https://x.com/Strength04_X/status/2021082486294675765",
    "revised_prompt": "一张工业工程风格的高级技术信息图海报，采用横向构图。画面背景为深海军蓝色的技术制图纸纹理，带有极浅的浅灰色网格线，整体色调以钢灰色和深海军蓝为主，并使用亮橙色和明黄色作为技术提示点缀。阴影处理极简，强调工业制造级别的极致清晰度与精度。画面正中央放置着一个超高精度的工业级多级离心泵转子组件技术渲染图。该物体具有逼真的金属质感，表面呈现出不锈钢的拉丝纹理、金属高光和抛光倒角细节。围绕着中心物体，密集且结构化地分布着大量工业技术元素：中心物体周围延伸出蓝图风格的细长尺寸线和引导线，标注着文字：'L=450.00±0.05 mm'、'Ø120.50 mm'、'R5.00'、'ANGLE: 45°'。画面的左上角展示了该转子组件的横截面剖视图，剖切面带有标准的斜向工程剖面线，揭示了内部流道结构。画面右侧区域是一个爆炸视图装配图，将部件沿中心轴向外展开，清晰展示了内部的螺母、密封圈、叶轮和轴承；部件旁带有引线和零件编号，文字为：'A01: MAIN SHAFT'、'A02: PRIMARY IMPELLER'、'A03: THRUST BEARING'、'A04: SEALING RING'、'A05: M8 HEX BOLT'。左下角是一个材料规格数据块，带有橙色边框，文字为：'MATERIAL SPECIFICATIONS'、'Shaft: Stainless Steel AISI 316L'、'Impeller: Cast Iron EN-GJL-250'、'Coating: Titanium Nitride (TiN)'、'Surface Finish: Ra 0.8'。中心物体的下方有一组指示制造步骤的橙色工艺流程箭头，文字依次为：'STEP 1: CNC TURNING'、'STEP 2: 5-AXIS MILLING'、'STEP 3: DYNAMIC BALANCING'。在转子主轴附近，附有载荷与应力指示图形，包含黄色的矢量力图箭头和表示热流分布的颜色渐变条，标注文字为：'ROTATION DIR.'、'AXIAL LOAD: 2.5 kN'、'MAX TORQUE: 500 Nm'。右下角设有一个结构化的技术数据面板，采用锐利的无衬线字体，文字为：'TECHNICAL DATA'、'Weight: 14.5 kg'、'Volume: 3.2 L'、'Max Operating Pressure: 250 Bar'、'Nominal Speed: 3600 RPM'、'Operating Temp: -20°C to 150°C'。在数据面板的最底端，放置着一个工业风格的 QR 码和一个条形码，旁边印有序列号：'PART NO. 883-992-B'。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/item_2370_2.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "An advanced technical infographic poster in an industrial engineering style, in landscape orientation. The background features a deep navy blue technical drafting paper texture with very faint light gray grid lines. The overall color palette is dominated by steel gray and deep navy blue, with bright orange and bright yellow used as technical accent highlights. Shadow treatment is minimal, emphasizing industrial manufacturing-grade extreme clarity and precision. Positioned at the center of the image is an ultra-high-precision technical rendering of an industrial-grade multi-stage centrifugal pump rotor assembly. The object exhibits realistic metallic texture, with the surface displaying stainless steel brushed grain, metallic highlights, and polished chamfer details. Surrounding the central object, a dense and structured array of industrial technical elements is distributed: blueprint-style elongated dimension lines and leader lines extend from the central object, annotated with text: 'L=450.00±0.05 mm', 'Ø120.50 mm', 'R5.00', 'ANGLE: 45°'. The upper-left corner of the image presents a cross-sectional cutaway view of the rotor assembly, with the cut plane featuring standard diagonal engineering section lines, revealing the internal flow channel structure. The right side of the image contains an exploded-view assembly diagram, with components expanded outward along the central axis, clearly displaying the internal nuts, sealing rings, impellers, and bearings; parts are accompanied by leader lines and part numbers, with text reading: 'A01: MAIN SHAFT', 'A02: PRIMARY IMPELLER', 'A03: THRUST BEARING', 'A04: SEALING RING', 'A05: M8 HEX BOLT'. The lower-left corner features a material specification data block with an orange border, with text reading: 'MATERIAL SPECIFICATIONS', 'Shaft: Stainless Steel AISI 316L', 'Impeller: Cast Iron EN-GJL-250', 'Coating: Titanium Nitride (TiN)', 'Surface Finish: Ra 0.8'. Below the central object is a set of orange process flow arrows indicating manufacturing steps, with text reading sequentially: 'STEP 1: CNC TURNING', 'STEP 2: 5-AXIS MILLING', 'STEP 3: DYNAMIC BALANCING'.",
    "prompt_zh": "工业工程风格信息图，展示一个物体（与上传的照片参考完全一致）。\n超精密技术渲染，物体置于中心位置，比例精确，纹理、材质和表面细节与参考照片完全一致。\n围绕物体布置工业级技术标注元素：\n• Blueprint风格的尺寸标注线（长度、宽度、高度、半径、角度、公差）。\n• 横截面剖视图，展示内部组件，配以工程剖面线图案。\n• 爆炸图装配示意，展示螺栓、支架、接头、"
