    "revised_prompt": "画面呈现一张超写实的竖版红毯活动时尚摄影照片。画面中心是著名女星梅根·福克斯（Megan Fox）。她正面站立，头部微微向左倾斜，双眼直视镜头，展现出沉着、自信且优雅的柔和凝视。她的发型是齐肩的层次波波头，发根呈深黑色，向下过渡为蜜金色的波浪卷，呈现出随性凌乱的质感。她的面部特征对称，蓝色的眼眸画有上挑的翼状眼线，眉毛修剪整齐，白皙的皮肤上保留着极其逼真的毛孔与肌肤纹理，嘴唇涂着闪耀的裸色唇彩，双颊带有柔和的玫瑰色腮红。\n\n在服装穿搭方面，她身穿一件夺目的红色定制缎面礼服。礼服采用高开叉的垂坠剪裁，露出一侧紧实健美的腿部以及腿上穿着的渔网袜。衣服细节极其丰富：肩部是极细的吊带，深垂褶的领口边缘点缀着璀璨的水晶；双臂自然放松垂于身体两侧，大臂上佩戴着露肩设计的水晶镶嵌臂环；上半身是贴合曲线的紧身胸衣剪裁，高光泽的红色丝绸缎面顺着身体自然垂落。配饰上，她佩戴着一条精致的钻石网球项链和一对硕大的钻石耳钉。\n\n环境与背景设定在一个红毯活动的媒体拍照墙前。背景是一面深黑色或暗海军蓝色的展示板，上面整齐交错地排列着白色的重复品牌标志，清晰可见的文字内容为'KeorUnreal'。背景呈现出大光圈镜头带来的浅景深和柔和光斑（bokeh）虚化效果，将焦点完全集中在人物主体上。\n\n光影与整体画风模拟了专业的红毯闪光灯摄影效果。正面明亮而强烈的布光营造出高对比度，使得红色的缎面布料和水晶饰品上闪烁着耀眼的镜面高光。人物双眼中有明亮清晰的眼神光，面部和身体阴影极少，皮肤展现出真实的次表面散射光泽。整体画面具有8K分辨率级别的极高清晰度，生动还原了电影级的光影质感与顶级时尚摄影的视觉冲击力。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/item_2415_1.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "The image presents a hyper-realistic vertical red carpet event fashion photography photo. At the center of the frame is renowned actress Megan Fox. She stands facing forward, her head tilted slightly to the left, eyes gazing directly into the camera, projecting a composed, confident, and elegantly soft gaze. Her hairstyle is a shoulder-length layered bob, with deep black roots transitioning downward into honey-blonde wavy curls, exhibiting a casually tousled texture. Her facial features are symmetrical, with blue eyes accentuated by upswept winged eyeliner, neatly groomed brows, and fair skin that retains extremely lifelike pores and skin texture. Her lips are coated in a shimmering nude lip gloss, and her cheeks carry a soft rose-toned blush.\n\nIn terms of outfit styling, she wears a striking red custom satin gown. The gown features a high-slit draped cut, revealing one toned and sculpted leg clad in fishnet stockings. The garment details are exceptionally rich: the shoulders have ultra-thin spaghetti straps, and the edges of the deep draping neckline are adorned with dazzling crystals. Her arms hang naturally relaxed at her sides, with crystal-encrusted off-shoulder arm cuffs on the upper arms. The upper body features a curve-hugging corset cut, with high-gloss red silk satin draping naturally along the body. For accessories, she wears a delicate diamond tennis necklace and a pair of oversized diamond stud earrings.\n\nThe environment and background are set in front of a media photo wall at a red carpet event. The backdrop is a deep black or dark navy blue display board, neatly arranged with alternating rows of repeating white brand logos, with the clearly visible text reading 'KeorUnreal.' The background exhibits the shallow depth of field and soft bokeh blur effect produced by a wide-aperture lens, concentrating focus entirely on the subject.\n\nThe lighting and overall visual style simulate professional red carpet flash photography. Bright and intense frontal lighting creates high contrast, producing dazzling specular highlights that shimmer across the red satin fabric and crystal accessories. The subject's eyes contain bright and clear catchlights, with minimal shadows on the face and body, and the skin exhibits realistic subsurface scattering luminosity. The overall image possesses an ultra-high clarity at an 8K resolution level, vividly reproducing cinematic lighting quality and the visual impact of top-tier fashion photography.",
    "prompt_zh": "{\n  \"image_prompt_structure\": {\n    \"subject\": {\n      \"demographics\": \"女性名人\n      \"hair\": \"齐肩纹理波波头，深黑发根渐变至蜜金色波浪，蓬松凌乱风格\",\n      \"face\": \"对称五官，蓝色眼眸搭配上挑眼线，精修眉形，白皙肌肤可见自然纹理与毛孔，裸色水润唇彩，柔和玫瑰色腮红\",\n      \"pose\": \"正面站立，头部微微转向左侧，直视镜头，双臂自然垂放于身体两侧\",\n      \"expression\": \"沉稳、自信、柔和凝视、优雅\"\n    },\n    \"fashion\": {\n      \"garment\": \"浅冰蓝色定制缎面"
