    "revised_prompt": "一张左右对照的高分辨率多媒材拼接海报，宽高比呈现宽屏布局。画面从正中间被一条细锐的垂直白线一分为二。画面左侧为一幅蓝图风格的中国长城技术制图。背景为经典的深蓝色，上面绘有精细的白色工程线条。图纸中包含了长城的侧立面图和俯视平面图。画面左上方用大号工程字体清晰印有标题文字：'THE GREAT WALL OF CHINA' 和副标题 'ARCHITECTURAL SPECIFICATIONS'。在侧立面图中，精细描绘了城墙段（wall segments）、敌楼（watchtowers）以及垛口等防御结构。图中标有精确的公制尺寸数据，用英文工程字体标注，包括城墙高度的虚线与数字：'Wall Height: 7.8m'，顶宽和底宽标注：'Top Width: 5.8m'、'Base Width: 6.5m'，以及两座塔楼之间的间距标注：'Tower Spacing: 200m'。敌楼旁边带有海拔标注：'Elevation: 850m'。各防御结构有引线标明名称：'Watchtower'、'Parapet Wall'、'Crenels'。图纸下半部分是沿着地形弯曲的俯视图，带目标签：'TOP DOWN LAYOUT'，旁边另有侧立面图的标签：'SIDE ELEVATION'。画面右侧是一张高清晰度的长城实景照片，展现了与之对应的壮阔真实场景。画面采用广角全景视角，一条古老蜿蜒的长城如同巨龙般横跨在连绵起伏的翠绿群山脊梁上。照片色彩逼真自然，处于明亮的自然日光下，天空是清澈的浅蓝色，飘着几朵轻薄的白云。长城的灰褐色砖石纹理、风化痕迹以及周围茂密的绿色植被清晰可见。左侧严谨的单色蓝图数据与右侧壮丽写实的自然人文景观形成强烈的视觉对比。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/item_2419_4.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "A high-resolution mixed-media composite poster in a left-right comparison layout, with an aspect ratio in a widescreen format. The image is divided in half from the exact center by a thin, sharp vertical white line. The left side of the image is a blueprint-style technical drawing of the Great Wall of China. The background is a classic deep blue, overlaid with finely detailed white engineering linework. The drawing includes a side elevation and a top-down plan view of the Great Wall. In the upper left of the image, the title text is clearly printed in large engineering typeface: 'THE GREAT WALL OF CHINA' with the subtitle 'ARCHITECTURAL SPECIFICATIONS.' In the side elevation, wall segments, watchtowers, and defensive structures such as crenels are meticulously depicted. Precise metric dimension data is annotated in English engineering typeface, including dashed lines and numerals for wall height: 'Wall Height: 7.8m,' top and base width annotations: 'Top Width: 5.8m,' 'Base Width: 6.5m,' and the spacing between two towers: 'Tower Spacing: 200m.' Next to the watchtower is an elevation annotation: 'Elevation: 850m.' Various defensive structures have leader lines indicating their names: 'Watchtower,' 'Parapet Wall,' 'Crenels.' The lower half of the drawing is a top-down view that follows the terrain's curvature, with a label reading: 'TOP DOWN LAYOUT,' alongside another label for the side elevation: 'SIDE ELEVATION.' The right side of the image is a high-definition real-life photograph of the Great Wall, presenting the corresponding grand and authentic scene. The shot employs a wide-angle panoramic perspective, with an ancient, winding Great Wall stretching like a giant dragon across the ridgelines of rolling, lush green mountains. The photo colors are vivid and natural, under bright natural daylight, with a clear light blue sky dotted with a few wispy white clouds. The grayish-brown masonry texture of the Great Wall, weathering marks, and the surrounding dense green vegetation are clearly visible. The rigorous monochromatic blueprint data on the left forms a striking visual contrast with the magnificent and realistic natural and cultural landscape on the right.",
    "prompt_zh": "草图到天际线——使用 Google Nano Banana Pro 在 @lovart_ai 上可视化中国长城\n\nPrompt - {\n  \"objective\": \"创建一张并排对比图像，包含中国长城的技术草图和真实照片\",\n  \"image_specifications\": {\n    \"style\": \"混合媒介（技术制图 + 真实照片）\",\n    \"layout\": \"水平分割——左侧：带尺寸标注的草图，右侧：真实照片\",\n    \"aspect_ratio\": \"3:2\"\n  },\n  \"left_side\": {\n    \"content_type\": \"中国长城的技术草图\",\n    \"features\": [\n      \"展示建筑结构的详细线条"
}, {
