    "revised_prompt": "一张超写实的微缩模型渲染图，呈现出一种梦幻般的微观城市街景，具有高级商业广告的质感。画面采用竖屏构图，视觉中心是一个被改造为迷人咖啡馆建筑的巨大复古意式浓缩咖啡机。咖啡机机身采用午夜蓝色的烤漆工艺与抛光黄铜材质相间，构成了建筑高耸的上半部分结构。咖啡机表面带有精密的金属旋钮、复古的指针式压力表和金属操作杆，机身正中央印有清晰的金色品牌文字 'L'ESPRESSO'。\n\n建筑的地面层被精巧地改造成一个温馨的咖啡馆店面，门面上方悬挂着一块小巧的黑底金字招牌，上面写着 'CAFE & ROASTERY'。店面装有宽大的透明玻璃落地窗，从内部透出温暖而诱人的琥珀色灯光。透过玻璃，可以清晰地看到微缩的咖啡馆内部结构，包括微型实木吧台、几张小巧的木制圆桌、吧台前的几把金属高脚凳以及墙上的迷你装饰画，展现出极致的工艺和比例感。\n\n建筑周围是一条干净整洁的鹅卵石铺就的微缩街道。街道两旁立着几盏精致的黑色铸铁复古路灯，散发着柔和的光晕。店门外点缀着几盆微型绿色阔叶盆栽和细致的路边石栏，营造出一种热情好客的社区氛围。\n\n画面的光影效果采用电影级的柔和布光，整体色调在温暖的室内光与周围略显幽蓝的暮色环境光之间形成对比。金属表面有着柔和的高光反射，投射出自然的阴影。画面呈现出超高的分辨率和极其丰富的细节，将产品设计与微缩建筑巧妙融合，展现出一种超现实却又无比真实的梦幻感。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/item_2428_1.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "A hyper-realistic miniature model render presenting a dreamlike micro urban street scene with the quality of a premium commercial advertisement. The image uses a vertical portrait composition, with the visual center being a giant vintage Italian espresso machine transformed into a charming café building. The espresso machine body features midnight blue baked enamel finish alternating with polished brass material, forming the towering upper structure of the building. The machine surface has precision metal knobs, vintage analog pressure gauges, and metal lever handles, with clear gold brand lettering 'L'ESPRESSO' printed at the center of the body.\n\nThe ground level of the building is ingeniously converted into a cozy café storefront, with a small black signboard with gold lettering hanging above the façade, reading 'CAFE & ROASTERY.' The storefront is fitted with expansive transparent floor-to-ceiling glass windows, emanating warm and inviting amber-toned light from within. Through the glass, the miniature café interior structure is clearly visible, including a tiny solid wood bar counter, several small wooden round tables, a few metal bar stools in front of the counter, and mini decorative paintings on the walls, showcasing exquisite craftsmanship and sense of scale.\n\nSurrounding the building is a clean and tidy cobblestone-paved miniature street. Lining both sides of the street are several exquisite black cast-iron vintage lampposts emitting soft halos of light. Outside the shop entrance, several miniature green broad-leaf potted plants and detailed curbside stone railings are placed as accents, creating a warm and hospitable neighborhood atmosphere.\n\nThe lighting effect of the image employs cinematic soft lighting, with the overall color tone contrasting between warm interior light and the slightly cool blue twilight ambient light of the surroundings. Metal surfaces have soft specular reflections, casting natural shadows. The image presents ultra-high resolution and extraordinarily rich detail, ingeniously merging product design with miniature architecture, conveying a surreal yet incredibly lifelike dreamlike quality.",
    "prompt_zh": "一个梦幻般的微缩城市场景，其中一个超大尺寸的 [BRAND PRODUCT] 被重新构想为一间迷人的咖啡馆，以俏皮而高端的方式将产品设计与建筑融为一体。\n\n该产品构成建筑的上部结构，而地面层则变身为一间温馨的咖啡馆店面，散发着温暖而诱人的光芒。\n\n透明玻璃窗展露出精致的微缩内部空间，可见小巧的桌椅、凳子和细腻的装饰，突出工艺感与比例感。\n\n周围的街道经过精心布置，配有精致的路灯、小型城市细节和整洁的路面，营造出"
}, {
