    "revised_prompt": "一张呈横宽比例的3D等距视角微缩模型（isometric miniature diorama）风格渲染图，采用景深移轴（tilt-shift）摄影效果和柔和的边缘散景，展现出极具细节的玩具屋微缩比例。画面呈现一个日式风格的温馨浴室角落，采用俯视的45度等距视角。浴室的墙面铺设着奶油色的陶瓷地铁砖，并带有温暖的木质装饰线条；地面铺设着米色与白色相间的棋盘格地砖。整体色调以温暖的陶土色和米色为主基调。空间角落里放置着一个复古的猫脚浴缸，浴缸内满是蓝色的丰富泡沫。浴缸上方横搭着一块木质浴缸托盘，上面放置着一台翻开的笔记本电脑、一个绿色的马克杯、一块香皂以及点燃的蜡烛。浴缸上方装有金色的黄铜弧形淋浴杆，挂着拉开的米色淋浴帘。浴室另一侧设有一个带木质储物柜的白色瓷质洗手台，配有黄铜水龙头；上方墙面挂着一面圆形的木框镜子，镜子两侧的金色壁灯散发着温暖柔和的光芒。洗手台旁是一个带有木质马桶圈的马桶。空间中散落着丰富的细节：一张小木凳上叠放着卷好的白色毛巾和几本书；地上放置着一个装满粉色、橙色衣物和彩色毛巾的柳条洗衣篮；地板中央铺着一张圆形的紫色毛绒洗浴地垫。墙面挂钩上挂着一条浅蓝色蓬松毛巾。浴室内还点缀着一瓶绿色葡萄酒瓶、一盆精致的微型盆景，以及分别装在白色花盆中的几株小绿植。整体光照表现为柔和的黄金时刻暖光与室内壁灯的温暖环境光相交织，投射出柔和的阴影，呈现出8k级别的超高清晰度纹理与温馨舒适的居家氛围。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/item_2473_3.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "A horizontal wide-aspect 3D isometric miniature diorama-style rendering with tilt-shift depth-of-field photography effects and soft edge bokeh, exhibiting highly detailed dollhouse miniature scale. The scene presents a cozy Japanese-style bathroom corner from an overhead 45-degree isometric perspective. The bathroom walls are clad in cream-colored ceramic subway tiles with warm wooden trim moldings; the floor is laid with beige and white checkerboard tiles. The overall color palette is dominated by warm terracotta and beige tones. In the corner of the space sits a vintage clawfoot bathtub filled with rich blue foam. A wooden bath caddy stretches across the top of the tub, holding an open laptop, a green mug, a bar of soap, and a lit candle. Above the bathtub, a gold brass curved shower rod is mounted, with a drawn-back beige shower curtain. On the other side of the bathroom is a white porcelain washbasin with a wooden storage cabinet, fitted with brass faucets; above it on the wall hangs a round wooden-framed mirror, flanked by gold wall sconces emitting warm, soft light. Next to the washbasin is a toilet with a wooden toilet seat. The space is scattered with rich details: a small wooden stool stacked with rolled white towels and several books; on the floor sits a wicker laundry basket filled with pink and orange garments and colorful towels; in the center of the floor lies a round purple plush bath mat. A light blue fluffy towel hangs from wall hooks. The bathroom is also accented with a green wine bottle, a delicate miniature bonsai, and several small green plants in white pots. The overall lighting blends soft golden-hour warm light with the warm ambient glow from the interior wall sconces, casting gentle shadows, presenting ultra-high 8K-level texture clarity and a cozy, comfortable homey atmosphere.",
