    "revised_prompt_en": "A 3D-rendered photorealistic-style image. The scene is captured from a direct top-down overhead perspective in a wide horizontal composition. Lying horizontally in the exact center of the frame are massive, three-dimensional bold English letters sculpted from pure white snow, clearly spelling out the word 'SNOW.' These snow-formed letters are extremely thick and voluminous with a strong sense of mass and rounded edges. They rest quietly on an expansive, flat snow surface, and due to their own weight, the bottoms of the letters slightly indent and sink into the snow layer beneath, with natural snow compression and transitional traces where the letter edges meet the surrounding snow. The material rendering across the entire scene is extremely realistic—the snow surface exhibits a soft granular texture accompanied by the appearance of tiny ice crystals. The lighting is expertly arranged, producing realistic highlights and soft shadows; gentle light creates glistening, bright highlights on the tops and light-facing surfaces of the snow letters, while casting soft pale blue-gray shadows on the shaded sides and in the recesses, perfectly accentuating the three-dimensional structure. The overall color palette is dominated by pure bright white and very pale ice blue, with extremely high image clarity and snow micro-textures rendered in exquisite detail.",
    "prompt_zh": "创建一个由白色雪制成的 [OBJECT] 3D 图像。体积感十足的物体放置在雪地表面上，略微陷入雪中。俯视视角。具有逼真高光和柔和阴影的照片。1080x1080 尺寸图片。"
