    "revised_prompt": "一张竖直构图的超写实人物肖像照片，呈现出原始时尚摄影和狗仔队闪光灯美学风格。画面主体是一位二十岁出头、极具吸引力且极其美丽的年轻女性。她非常靠近镜头站立，身体从腰部开始微微前倾，双肩自然向后微展，胸部自然挺起，下巴微收。她的面容对称且精致，拥有深邃的大眼睛，眼神直视镜头，展现出强烈的眼神交流与亲密感。眉毛自然放松，嘴唇柔软、带有光泽且微微张开，带着自然自信的微笑。她的浓密深棕色长发略带蓬松与微乱的质感，自然垂落在双肩前方，完美修饰着脸庞。\n\n她的右手举在脸颊高度，手中清晰地握着一个华丽的银黑相间威尼斯化装舞会面具，面具向外倾斜，完全展现出其表面精细复杂的金属丝镂空雕花工艺。她的左手轻轻搭在腰臀处以突显身体曲线。女子身穿一件银色亮片吊带连衣裙，细肩带搭配深邃优雅的领口，自然地展现出锁骨与乳沟轮廓。裙子的亮片在强烈的闪光灯照射下闪烁着耀眼的光芒。她的脖子上佩戴着一条极简风格的钻石项链，刚好位于领口上方。\n\n环境设定在夜晚的豪华屋顶或阳台，背景非常暗且呈现浅景深效果，仅有柔和模糊的城市夜景灯光光斑，没有任何分散注意力的元素。画面采用直接的正面闪光灯照明，光源位于视线稍上方，在女子的眼睛、颧骨、锁骨、领口肌肤以及面具上勾勒出锐利的高光和干净利落的阴影。画面的焦点极为锐利，精准对焦在女子的眼睛和面具上。皮肤质感极度逼真，毛孔清晰可见，亮片的反射光泽、面具的繁复细节以及每一根发丝都展现出极高的清晰度与电影般的写实感。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/item_2554_2.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "A vertical-composition hyperrealistic portrait photograph exhibiting raw fashion photography and paparazzi flash aesthetic. The main subject is an extremely attractive and strikingly beautiful young woman in her early twenties. She stands very close to the camera, her body leaning slightly forward from the waist, shoulders naturally drawn back slightly, chest naturally lifted, chin tucked subtly. Her face is symmetrical and refined, with deep, large eyes gazing directly into the lens, conveying intense eye contact and a sense of intimacy. Her eyebrows are naturally relaxed, her lips soft, glossy, and slightly parted, bearing a naturally confident smile. Her thick, dark brown long hair has a slightly tousled and voluminous texture, falling naturally in front of both shoulders, perfectly framing her face.\n\nHer right hand is raised to cheek height, clearly holding an ornate silver-and-black Venetian masquerade mask, tilted outward to fully reveal its intricate filigree metalwork openwork design on the surface. Her left hand rests gently on her waist-hip area to accentuate her body curves. The woman wears a silver sequined spaghetti-strap dress with thin straps and a deep, elegant neckline that naturally reveals the contours of her collarbones and décolletage. The sequins on the dress shimmer with dazzling brilliance under the intense flash lighting. Around her neck she wears a minimalist-style diamond necklace, positioned just above the neckline.\n\nThe setting is a luxurious rooftop or balcony at night, with a very dark background rendered in shallow depth of field, showing only soft, blurred city nightscape light bokeh with no distracting elements. The image employs direct frontal flash lighting, with the light source positioned slightly above eye level, sculpting sharp highlights and clean, crisp shadows on the woman's eyes, cheekbones, collarbones, neckline skin, and the mask. The focal point is extremely sharp, with precise focus on the woman's eyes and the mask. The skin texture is hyper-realistic with clearly visible pores, and the reflective sheen of the sequins, the elaborate details of the mask, and every individual strand of hair are rendered with exceptional clarity and cinematic realism.",
    "prompt_zh": "{\n  \"prompt_configuration\": {\n    \"type\": \"超写实编辑风格肖像\",\n    \"aspect_ratio\": \"3:4\",\n    \"style_model\": \"Raw Flash Photography\"\n  },\n  \"prompt_structure\": {\n    \"subject_description\": {\n      \"identity\": \"极其美丽的年轻女性，20岁出头，富有银幕魅力的存在感，毫不费力的自信。\",\n      \"hair\": \"长而浓密的深棕色头发，带有柔和蓬松感，微微凌乱，框住面部并从双肩前方垂落。\",\n      \"face\": \"引人注目的对称面容，富有表现力的大眼睛带有强烈的直视目光，眉毛自然放松，柔软光泽的嘴唇微微"
