    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/item_2613_3.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "A vertical-composition casual street-style portrait photo in a medium close-up shot, focusing on the face and upper body of a young woman. The subject is positioned at the center of the frame, wearing a natural, relaxed gentle smile, with friendly eyes looking directly into the camera. She has light green-gray eyes, neatly groomed natural brown eyebrows, and soft light-pink lips with minimal, natural makeup. Her skin is fair, radiating a healthy glow under the sunlight. She has shoulder-length platinum blonde wavy curly hair in a center-parted style, with a light and naturally textured appearance. On her left ear, she wears a white wireless earbud, and around her neck is a delicate gold choker. She is dressed in a fitted light yellow-green ribbed sleeveless tank top with a small blue-green triceratops motif on the chest. Black backpack straps are visible on both shoulders. The background is an outdoor European urban street scene; behind the subject is a blue-gray metal door with a sign clearly printed with the German text 'Notausgang freihalten.' On the left side of the frame, a portion of an orange-painted wall is visible. The lighting is natural golden-hour sunlight in the early evening, with warm sidelight falling on the subject and casting soft shadows on the wall behind her. The overall color tone is warm, imbued with an everyday, approachable sense of life.",
    "prompt_zh": "nano banana pro 🍌\n\n{\n  \"prompt\": \"休闲街头风格肖像，年轻女性，铂金白色金发及肩波浪卷发，面带柔和微笑看向镜头，浅绿灰色眼睛，自然淡妆搭配柔粉色嘴唇，耳中佩戴白色无线耳机，细金色choker项链，穿着浅黄绿色罗纹背心上面绣有小蓝色三角龙恐龙图案，黑色双肩包肩带可见于肩膀上，站在建筑外面，蓝灰色金属门上有德文标志写着 Notausgang freihalten，左侧可见橙色墙壁部分，温暖的黄金时段阳光"
