    "revised_prompt": "这是一张高端产品摄影海报图，竖直画幅，整体呈现极简、智能与科技奢华的视觉风格。画面中央展示了一台被重新定义为奢华科技艺术品的全透明浓缩咖啡机，以及配套的玻璃咖啡杯。它们被放置在一个极简的浅灰色基座上，背景是干净、无缝的纯白至浅灰色渐变背景（cyclorama）。咖啡机主体由带有微弱绿色透明光泽的精密模压光学玻璃制成，内部机械结构完全裸露且排列得一丝不苟。可以清晰看到顶部的玻璃咖啡豆仓内装有真实的深棕色烘焙咖啡豆；机身内部贯穿有拉丝钛金属和暖灰色的热水循环管及压力室，研磨和萃取机械结构充满干净的工程美学。机器内部的结构中嵌入了实体电脑主板风格的电路，电路走线为柔和的工业橙色，支撑元件为石墨色和钛色调；这些电路是物理实体结构，没有任何发光效果。咖啡机侧面的玻璃机身上雕刻有 'BAGEL LABS' 字样（无印刷和贴纸）。下方是一个配套的加底光学玻璃咖啡杯，杯底附近也精细雕刻着低调的 'BAGEL LABS' 标志。画面捕捉了一个极其精准的动态瞬间：新鲜的咖啡正从咖啡机流出，平滑地注入玻璃杯中；透过透明的杯体可以清晰看到咖啡液体的动态、色彩渐变以及表面那层金黄色的咖啡油脂（crema），展现了极致的液体流体力学之美。摄影采用柔和的演播室高调照明（High-key lighting），没有生硬的阴影，精确控制的反光完美凸显了玻璃的厚重感、真实的折射效果以及机器内部极具微距细节的金属与电路质感。画面表面附有极简的排版元素：在画面的左下角，有两行极简的黑色小字，第一行为 'Transparent Espresso System'，第二行为 'Engineered Glass / Integrated Circuitry'；在画面的右下角，有一个小巧、低调的单色 'BAGEL LABS' 标志。画面中无人物、无多余杂物、无包装盒、无复杂的厨房环境，焦点完全集中在这组完美的科技化日常物品上。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/item_2707_3.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "This is a high-end product photography poster image in a vertical format, presenting an overall visual style of minimalism, intelligence, and technological luxury. At the center of the frame is a fully transparent espresso machine reimagined as a luxurious tech art piece, along with a matching glass coffee cup. They are placed on a minimalist light-gray pedestal against a clean, seamless pure white to light-gray gradient background (cyclorama). The main body of the espresso machine is made of precision-molded optical glass with a faint green transparent sheen, with the internal mechanical structure fully exposed and arranged with meticulous precision. Clearly visible is the glass coffee bean hopper at the top containing real dark-brown roasted coffee beans; inside the body, brushed titanium and warm-gray hot water circulation pipes and pressure chambers run throughout, with grinding and extraction mechanical structures exuding a clean engineering aesthetic. Embedded within the machine's internal structure are physical motherboard-style circuits with soft industrial-orange trace lines and support components in graphite and titanium tones; these circuits are physical solid structures with no glowing effects whatsoever. On the side of the espresso machine, the glass body is engraved with the text 'BAGEL LABS' (no printing or stickers). Below is a matching glass coffee cup with an optically enhanced base, with a subtle 'BAGEL LABS' logo finely engraved near the bottom of the cup. The image captures an extremely precise dynamic moment: fresh coffee is flowing out of the espresso machine, smoothly pouring into the glass cup; through the transparent cup body, one can clearly see the coffee liquid's dynamics, color gradation, and the golden layer of crema on the surface, showcasing the ultimate beauty of liquid fluid dynamics. The photography employs soft studio high-key lighting with no harsh shadows, and precisely controlled reflections that perfectly highlight the heft of the glass, realistic refraction effects, and the macro-detailed metal and circuit textures inside the machine. Minimal typographic elements are overlaid on the image: in the lower-left corner, there are two lines of minimal small black text—the first line reading 'Transparent Espresso System' and the second line reading 'Engineered Glass / Integrated Circuitry'; in the lower-right corner, there is a small, understated monochrome 'BAGEL LABS' logo. The image contains no people, no extraneous objects, no packaging boxes, and no complex kitchen environment—the focus is entirely on this set of perfect tech-forward everyday objects.",
    "prompt_zh": "BAGEL LABS.\n担任创意总监，策划一系列涵盖广泛、风格不拘一格的\"重新语境化日常物品\"合集。\n\n多样化物品选择（必须保证多样性）：\n从以下不同类别中随机选择一件物品以确保多样性：\n模拟办公与桌面用品：\n运动与休闲：\n酒具与厨房用品：\n工具与器具：\n个人护理：\n旅行用品：\n\n已选类别：\n酒具与厨房用品\n\n选定物品：\n一台咖啡机和咖啡杯——辨识度极高，重新想象为奢华科技感工艺品。\n\n概念：\n将日常咖啡机重新语境化为一个透明的、高精度物体"
