    "revised_prompt": "极具电影感和戏剧张力的微距美食摄影照片，采用竖向构图。画面设定在一个暗调、质朴的深色乡村厨房环境中，背景呈现浅景深带来的强烈虚化效果。画面下半部分放置着一块充满风化痕迹、表面布满粗糙木纹与深邃裂纹的厚重木质砧板。砧板上堆叠着几个刚刚出锅、热气腾腾的尼泊尔饺子（Momo）。饺子面皮油润且富有光泽，表面泛着一层淡淡的诱人油光，顶端手工捏制的褶皱精致立体，细节清晰可见。浓郁且极具视觉冲击力的白色蒸汽正从饺子上袅袅升起，在空气中盘旋。画面上半部分展现了‘时间静止’般的解构爆炸视图。一张张半透明的生饺子皮、揉捏紧实且布满香料颗粒的肉馅球，以及零星散落的新鲜绿色香草叶（如香菜与葱段）正以分离、悬浮的姿态定格在半空中。整个画面充满强烈的动态冻结感：空气中弥漫着细密的悬浮面粉颗粒，红褐色的香料粉末在空中拖出凝固的运动轨迹，并伴有几滴极具张力的、慢动作般的汁液飞溅效果。飘落的绿色香草叶与下方升腾的厚重蒸汽在空间中完美交融。光影与色彩方面，采用电影级工作室布光，温暖且诱人的高光打在食材表面，与深邃浓重的阴影形成强烈的高对比度，呈现出专业美食杂志社论风格的高级质感。前景中的食材、飞溅的液体、悬浮的面粉颗粒以及木板的干裂纹理均保持着极其锐利的对焦与超高清晰度的微距细节表现，完美凸显了食物的结构与材质。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/item_2762_3.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "An extremely cinematic and dramatically compelling macro food photography shot in vertical composition. The scene is set in a dark-toned, rustic, deep-colored countryside kitchen environment, with the background exhibiting a strong bokeh effect produced by shallow depth of field. The lower half of the frame features a heavy wooden cutting board bearing weathered marks, its surface covered with coarse wood grain and deep cracks. Stacked on the cutting board are several freshly steamed, piping-hot Nepalese dumplings (Momo). The dumpling wrappers are oily and lustrous, their surfaces gleaming with a faint, appetizing sheen of oil, while the hand-pinched pleats at the top are exquisitely three-dimensional with clearly visible details. Rich, visually striking white steam rises and curls from the dumplings, swirling through the air. The upper half of the frame presents a 'time-frozen' deconstructed explosion view. Translucent raw dumpling wrappers, tightly kneaded meatballs studded with spice granules, and scattered fresh green herb leaves (such as cilantro and scallion segments) are captured in a separated, suspended state, frozen in mid-air. The entire frame is imbued with an intense sense of frozen motion: the air is filled with fine suspended flour particles, reddish-brown spice powder trails frozen mid-trajectory, accompanied by several highly dynamic, slow-motion-like droplet splashes. Falling green herb leaves and the thick rising steam from below merge seamlessly in the space. In terms of lighting and color, cinematic studio-grade lighting is employed, with warm, inviting highlights striking the surface of the ingredients, creating strong high contrast against deep, heavy shadows, presenting a premium aesthetic in the style of professional food magazine editorial photography. The ingredients in the foreground, splashing liquids, suspended flour particles, and the dry, cracked texture of the wooden board all maintain extremely sharp focus and ultra-high-definition macro detail rendering, perfectly highlighting the structure and texture of the food.",
    "prompt_zh": "{\n电影感Momo双重奏\n主体与场景\n * 成品菜肴：新鲜蒸制的饺子（momos）堆叠在质朴的木板上。\n * 细节：光泽面皮带有精致的手工褶纹，表面微微泛油光，浓厚的戏剧性蒸汽升腾而起。\n * 分解视图：并列或分割场景展示\"解构\"的momo。漂浮的饺子皮、调味肉馅球以及散落的新鲜香草。\n动态与动作\n * 凝固瞬间：悬浮在半空中的面粉颗粒、运动定格的香料，以及戏剧性的慢动作飞溅效果。\n * 氛围：缥缈旋绕的蒸汽和飘落的香草叶"
