    "revised_prompt_en": "A four-panel photo collage arranged in a 2x2 grid, simulating the authentic style of selfie snapshots taken with a phone's flash after a party. The overall frame is divided into four rectangular blocks—top-left, top-right, bottom-left, and bottom-right—separated by clean, thin-line borders. There is no text, icons, or watermarks anywhere in the frame.\n\nThe subject across all four panels is the same young woman. She has a head of thick, voluminous chestnut-brown wavy curls in a side-parted style, with hair exhibiting a natural, healthy sheen and no golden highlights. Her makeup is in a refined party style, featuring crisp, clean eyeliner and thick, curled lashes, warm-toned blush blended onto her cheeks, and soft matte red lipstick on her lips. She wears a pair of medium-sized metallic hoop earrings and a shiny, sparkling red strapless bodycon mini dress. The background is uniformly an indoor hallway or room corner, with walls covered in warm beige wallpaper bearing subtle dark floral patterns, in a minimal setting with no extraneous props.\n\nTop-left panel (first frame): Half-body composition, the woman in a three-quarter side-facing pose with her face turned toward the camera, lips slightly parted as if caught in the midst of laughter, eyes looking directly into the lens.\n\nTop-right panel (second frame): The woman makes a playful pout-kiss expression toward the camera, one hand gently touching her own cheek, both eyes gazing into the lens.\n\nBottom-left panel (third frame): A tighter close-up composition, with the woman's head slightly tilted, a soft smile at the corners of her mouth, eyes looking gently toward the camera.\n\nBottom-right panel (fourth frame): The woman presents a confident side-profile view, one hand lightly resting near her chin and jawline, eyes still directed toward the camera, exuding a post-party languidness and ease.\n\nIn terms of visual details and style, all four photos employ lighting that simulates an on-camera direct phone flash, with the subject appearing bright and clear while the light softly falls off toward the edges, casting gentle peripheral shadows on the wall behind the subject. Highlights are well-controlled with no overexposure. The overall frame conveys a warm-toned, dimly lit indoor ambiance. The image quality presents an unretouched, authentic texture, with the subject's skin retaining real texture without any beauty-filter smoothing effect. The lens exhibits slight wide-angle perspective distortion, and the frame is overlaid with subtle noise and film grain, producing a natural, vivid candid snapshot effect.",
