    "revised_prompt_en": "A hyper-realistic candid photograph taken at a nighttime party, composed in a widescreen format. At the center of the frame is a half-body shot of a man and a woman in an intimate interaction. The woman on the left faces the camera, displaying a happy and natural smile with her head tilted slightly to the right; the man on the right has turned his head and is gently kissing the woman's cheek with closed lips. The woman's arms are wrapped around the man's neck and shoulders, while the man's arms are tightly embracing the woman's waist and back.\n\nThe woman wears her hair in an elegant, sleek, and neatly swept-back updo. Both ears are adorned with striking oversized gold earrings in the shape of suns or stars, and a delicate gold bracelet graces her wrist; she is dressed in a solid-colored, opaque evening party dress, and her face is unobstructed by the man, fully clear and visible. The man has naturally slightly tousled short hair, realistic short stubble along his jawline, a gentle demeanor, and wears a light-colored solid shirt. The body language and hand structures of both individuals are natural and anatomically accurate.\n\nThe scene is set at a nighttime party event. The photograph employs the classic on-camera direct flash lighting effect, with the subjects' faces and upper bodies evenly illuminated by strong light, producing realistic and natural skin tones; the background appears very dim due to light falloff, exhibiting an extremely shallow depth of field. The dark-toned background extends to both sides, scattered with numerous warm orange-yellow out-of-focus circular light spots (bokeh) and extremely blurred silhouettes of crowds. The image possesses an exceptionally high degree of realism and sharp clarity, with a subtle natural film grain texture, an overall warm color tone, and contains no text, logos, or watermarks whatsoever.",
    "prompt_zh": "{\n  \"request_metadata\": {\n    \"model\": \"Nano Banana Pro\",\n    \"content_type\": \"照片级真实_派对_情侣_亲吻脸颊_闪光灯_男方亲吻女方\",\n    \"quality_preset\": \"超高画质\",\n    \"format_aspect_ratio\": \"3:4\",\n    \"output\": \"单张图片\"\n  },\n  \"references\": {\n    \"reference_images\": {\n      \"female_reference\": \"UPLOAD_FEMALE_REFERENCE_IMAGE（必需）\",\n      \"male_reference\": \"UPLOAD_MALE_REFERENCE_IMAGE（必需）\"\n    },\n    \"reference_rules\": {\n      \"exactly_two_references_only\": true,\n      \"preserve_identity_female\": true,\n      \"preserve_identity_male\": true,\n      \"identity_lock_strength"
