    "author_link": "https://x.com/meng_dagg695/status/2008133265492988148",
    "revised_prompt": "一张高品质的时尚编辑类肖像摄影照片。画面采用垂直画幅和紧凑的面部特写构图，镜头以轻微的低角度仰拍，主体居中，头顶略微被裁剪出画，面部和上半部颈部完整清晰可见。\n\n画面主体是一位年轻女性，肤色白皙，保留了真实的皮肤纹理与柔和的高光。她拥有鹅蛋脸，部分可见的额头被柔光照亮。棕色的眉毛呈现自然的形状与中等粗细；浅色（偏绿或淡褐色）的杏仁眼透出放松、中性的神情，视线略微向下凝视着镜头。她的鼻梁挺直且比例匀称，丰满的双唇微微张开，表面带有晶莹的光泽感。她的整体神态平静、从容。她的头发是带有暖色高光的浅棕色，松散的波浪卷发自然地修饰着脸庞，几缕发丝在半空中扬起，暗示着微风的吹拂或运动感，发顶没有明显的发缝。\n\n她穿着一件深红色与白色相间的紧身高领上衣，面料平滑挺括，表面印有华丽的花卉与巴洛克风格图案。画面中人物没有佩戴任何首饰、眼镜或头部配件。\n\n光线为自然阳光，强烈的侧光从左上方照射，在受光面与阴影之间形成了鲜明的明暗对比。颧骨、鼻梁和嘴唇上呈现出明显的明亮高光，而脸颊右侧则笼罩着柔和的过渡阴影。背景是户外的纯蓝色天空，呈现出完全平滑虚化的浅景深效果，没有任何可见的物体或纹理。整体色调自然温暖，饱和度适中，画面噪点极低，焦点精准落在人物的眼睛与嘴唇上，呈现出干净、极简且高度逼真的写实美感。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/item_2870_3.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "A high-quality fashion editorial portrait photograph. The image employs a vertical format with a tight facial close-up composition, shot from a slightly low angle looking upward, with the subject centered, the top of the head slightly cropped out of frame, and the face and upper portion of the neck fully and clearly visible.\n\nThe subject is a young woman with fair skin that retains realistic skin texture and soft highlights. She has an oval face, with her partially visible forehead illuminated by soft light. Her brown eyebrows exhibit a natural shape and medium thickness; her light-colored (greenish or light hazel) almond-shaped eyes convey a relaxed, neutral expression, with her gaze directed slightly downward toward the camera. Her nose bridge is straight and well-proportioned, and her full lips are slightly parted with a glossy, luminous sheen on their surface. Her overall demeanor is calm and composed. Her hair is a light brown with warm-toned highlights, and loose wavy curls naturally frame her face, with a few strands lifted in mid-air suggesting the presence of a gentle breeze or a sense of movement; there is no visible hair part at the top.\n\nShe wears a deep red and white form-fitting turtleneck top made of smooth, structured fabric, printed with ornate floral and Baroque-style patterns. The subject in the image is not wearing any jewelry, glasses, or head accessories.\n\nThe lighting is natural sunlight, with strong sidelight cast from the upper left, creating a pronounced chiaroscuro contrast between the lit areas and the shadows. Prominent bright highlights appear on the cheekbones, nose bridge, and lips, while the right side of the cheek is enveloped in softly transitioning shadows. The background is an outdoor pure blue sky, rendered in a completely smooth bokeh with a shallow depth of field effect, with no visible objects or textures. The overall color tone is naturally warm with moderate saturation, the image has extremely low noise, and the focus falls precisely on the subject's eyes and lips, presenting a clean, minimalist, and highly realistic aesthetic.",
    "prompt_zh": "{\n  \"image_type\": \"摄影肖像\",\n  \"composition\": {\n    \"framing\": \"紧凑特写肖像\",\n    \"crop\": \"头顶轻微裁切，面部及上颈部完全可见\",\n    \"orientation\": \"竖向\",\n    \"camera_angle\": \"略微低角度仰拍，向上看向拍摄对象\",\n    \"subject_position\": \"居中\",\n    \"depth_of_field\": \"浅景深，背景完全虚化\"\n  },\n  \"subject\": {\n    \"gender_presentation\": \"女性呈现\",\n    \"age_range_visible\": \"年轻成人\",\n    \"skin_tone\": \"白皙/浅肤色\",\n    \"skin_texture\": \"可见自然皮肤纹理"
