    "author_link": "https://x.com/saniaspeaks_/status/2004107821525422107",
    "revised_prompt": "具有复古美学与电影质感的人像摄影照片。横向构图中，画面主体是一位安静坐着的人物，以半身特写呈现。人物的面部表情深思且梦幻，眼神略带迷离，一只手轻轻靠在脸颊旁边，姿态自然放松。画面采用柔和且富有戏剧性的光影效果，一束温暖的金黄色阳光从侧面投射过来，照亮了人物的部分脸庞，而面部的另一侧和身体边缘则隐没在深邃的阴影中，形成了强烈的明暗对比与充满情绪张力的氛围。背景被柔和地虚化且色调暗沉，去除了多余的干扰元素，将视觉焦点完全集中在人物的面部。整体画面带有明显的胶片颗粒质感和柔焦效果，营造出一种静谧、舒适且极具艺术感的氛围。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/item_2885_3.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "A portrait photograph with vintage aesthetics and cinematic quality. In a horizontal composition, the subject is a figure sitting quietly, presented in a medium close-up. The subject's facial expression is contemplative and dreamy, with a slightly hazy gaze, and one hand resting gently near the cheek in a naturally relaxed pose. The image employs soft yet dramatic lighting effects, with a beam of warm golden sunlight cast from the side, illuminating part of the subject's face, while the other side of the face and the edges of the body recede into deep shadows, creating a strong chiaroscuro contrast and an atmosphere filled with emotional tension. The background is softly blurred with muted tones, eliminating extraneous distracting elements and focusing the viewer's attention entirely on the subject's face. The overall image carries a pronounced film grain texture and soft-focus effect, evoking a serene, comfortable, and highly artistic atmosphere.",
    "prompt_zh": "一张电影感的人物肖像，人物坐在柔和的戏剧性光线中。面部一侧被温暖的金色阳光部分照亮，营造出深邃的阴影和充满情绪感的氛围。表情若有所思且梦幻，手轻轻靠近面部。背景柔和虚化且偏暗，突出主体的面部。胶片颗粒效果，复古美学，柔焦，温馨且富有艺术感的氛围。"
