    "revised_prompt": "一张超写实电影感摄影照片，采用16:9宽画幅构图，展现了一个温馨舒适的厨房场景。画面中心是一位年轻女性，正坐在厨房的小圆桌旁。她留着自然微卷的长发，随意披散在双肩上，身穿一件淡彩色调（如柔和的莫兰迪浅粉色）的无袖连衣裙，面料柔软垂坠。她的姿态自然放松，双手正轻轻端着一只复古碎花图案的陶瓷茶杯，将其微微贴近唇边。她的表情平静、若有所思，面部皮肤纹理极其逼真细腻，保留了真实的质感而无过度修饰。小圆桌的桌面上铺着一块编织餐垫，上面放着一只与茶杯配套的复古碎花茶壶。背景是一个被浅景深柔和虚化的明亮厨房，隐约可以分辨出墙上悬挂着的金属平底锅和摆放着厨具的木质置物架。镜头采用中景拍摄和50mm焦段的真实透视，焦点精准锁定在女性面部和手中的茶杯上。柔和的自然日光从侧面的窗户倾洒进来，在她的侧脸、发丝和陶瓷茶杯边缘勾勒出细腻的光影。整体画面色调偏暖，带有电影胶片般的色彩分级和轻微的颗粒感，高动态范围保留了丰富的光泽与暗部细节，营造出一种宁静、真实且充满私密生活气息的故事氛围。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/item_3012_2.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "A hyper-realistic, cinematic-style photograph in 16:9 widescreen composition, depicting a warm and cozy kitchen scene. At the center of the frame is a young woman seated at a small round table in the kitchen. She has naturally slightly wavy long hair, casually draped over both shoulders, and is wearing a sleeveless dress in a soft, muted tone (such as a gentle Morandi pale pink) with a soft, draping fabric. Her posture is natural and relaxed, both hands gently holding a vintage floral-patterned ceramic teacup, bringing it slightly close to her lips. Her expression is calm and contemplative, with extremely realistic and delicate facial skin texture, preserving authentic detail without excessive retouching. The surface of the small round table is covered with a woven placemat, upon which sits a vintage floral teapot matching the teacup. The background is a bright kitchen softly blurred by shallow depth of field, where one can faintly make out metal pans hanging on the wall and a wooden shelf holding kitchen utensils. The shot is framed in a medium shot with the realistic perspective of a 50mm focal length, the focus precisely locked on the woman's face and the teacup in her hands. Soft natural daylight streams in from a window to the side, tracing delicate light and shadow along her profile, hair strands, and the rim of the ceramic teacup. The overall color tone of the image leans warm, with cinematic film-like color grading and a subtle grain texture. High dynamic range preserves rich highlights and shadow details, creating a serene, authentic atmosphere imbued with an intimate, slice-of-life narrative quality.",
    "prompt_zh": "{\"render_goal\": \"创建一张逼真的单幅图像，灵感来源于参考拼贴画的外观和氛围，柔和的自然光线，温暖舒适的厨房氛围，平静的叙事感。\",\"subject\": {\"type\": \"女性\",\"same_as_reference\": true,\"pose\": \"坐在一张小圆形厨房桌旁，轻轻将茶杯举到嘴边\",\"expression\": \"平静、若有所思、放松\",\"wardrobe\": \"简约无袖连衣裙，柔软面料，柔和的粉彩色调\",\"hair\": \"自然、微卷、垂落在肩上\"},\"scene\": {\"location\": \"明亮的厨房，日光照射"
