    "revised_prompt": "一张竖版比例的电影感写实静物摄影海报，画面采用极简主义的构图与象征手法。场景设定在户外一个干净、平滑的浅灰白色石材质感平面上，沐浴在柔和的自然漫反射光中。画面中央偏下位置，放置着两块原本完全相同的方形焦糖色太妃糖，呈现出强烈的视觉对比。右侧的太妃糖被整齐地包裹在闪亮的透明与金色相间的糖纸中，糖纸表面反射着细腻的高光，整体显得干净、独立且完好无损。左侧的太妃糖则是完全未包装的状态，焦糖色的糖块直接暴露在外。这块裸露的太妃糖表面和四周密密麻麻地爬满了黑色的蚂蚁，还有一队细小的蚂蚁正从画面左下角朝着它缓慢爬行聚集，将其层层包围；而右侧带有糖纸保护的太妃糖周围干干净净，完全没有蚂蚁靠近。画面采用微距镜头的视角，背景带有柔和的景深虚化效果，色调冷峻克制，光影过渡自然。在画面的上半部分较为空白的背景区域，居中排版着一行清晰的白色无衬线英文字体：'When you are too open, you can be used.'。在画面的最下方，同样居中排版着另一行清晰的白色现代英文字体：'Boundaries protect your value.'。整体画面完美融合了高品质微距摄影与电影字幕般的文本布局，氛围平静且充满哲理隐喻。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/item_3053_2.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "A vertical-ratio cinematic realistic still-life photography poster, employing minimalist composition and symbolic techniques. The scene is set outdoors on a clean, smooth, light grayish-white stone-textured flat surface, bathed in soft natural diffused light. Slightly below the center of the frame, two originally identical square caramel-colored toffee candies are placed, presenting a striking visual contrast. The toffee on the right is neatly wrapped in shiny transparent and gold-toned candy wrapper, its surface reflecting delicate highlights, appearing clean, self-contained, and perfectly intact. The toffee on the left is completely unwrapped, with the caramel-colored candy block directly exposed. The surface and sides of this bare toffee are densely covered with black ants, and a trail of tiny ants is slowly crawling and converging toward it from the lower-left corner of the frame, surrounding it layer by layer; meanwhile, the area around the wrapper-protected toffee on the right is perfectly clean, with no ants approaching at all. The image is shot from a macro lens perspective, with the background featuring a soft depth-of-field bokeh effect, the color tone cool and restrained, and the light-shadow transitions natural. In the relatively empty background area of the upper half of the frame, a line of clear white sans-serif English text is centered: 'When you are too open, you can be used.' At the very bottom of the frame, another line of clear white modern English text is likewise centered: 'Boundaries protect your value.' The overall image seamlessly blends high-quality macro photography with a cinematic subtitle-style text layout, exuding a calm atmosphere rich in philosophical metaphor.",
    "prompt_zh": "{\"style\": \"电影感、象征性、极简、写实\",\"aspect_ratio\": \"9:16\",\"scenes\": [{\"scene_number\": 1,\"description\": \"一个安静的户外场景，柔和自然光下有一个干净的平面。两颗相同的太妃糖并排放置。\",\"camera\": \"缓慢推进\",\"mood\": \"平静、中性\"},{\"scene_number\": 2,\"description\": \"一颗太妃糖整齐地包裹在光亮的糖纸中。另一颗太妃糖未包装，完全裸露。\",\"camera\": \"静态特写\",\"mood\": \"对比、期待\"},{\"scene_number\": 3,"
