    "revised_prompt": "超高精度的微距倾角摄影作品，在宽幅全景构图下展现了一个完全由法式美食食材构建的微缩巴黎城市景观（Diorama）。画面中心是标志性的埃菲尔铁塔，其塔身结构由精巧交织的烘焙法棍面包条、椒盐卷饼棒和硬质拉糖作为钢架搭建而成，节点处用融化的格吕耶尔奶酪作为黏合剂，表面泛着诱人的烘焙油脂光泽。铁塔左侧的凯旋门由一大块层次分明的法式千层酥（Mille-feuille）构建，酥皮之间夹着浓郁的香草奶油，表面的浮雕细节由精细挤压的糖霜雕刻。背景和街道两侧林立着奥斯曼风格的公寓楼，墙面由层叠的法式可丽饼和切片面包砌成，屋顶覆盖着深褐色的黑巧克力碎片和层叠的黑松露薄片，模仿经典的锌制屋顶；阳台栏杆是弯曲的巧克力刨花。画面前方，代表塞纳河的闪耀酒红色液体（红酒）蜿蜒流过，河面上横跨着由巨大的黄油牛角面包（Croissant）拼接而成的桥梁。街道的铺路石由致密排列的绿扁豆、酸豆和粗海盐粒构成，路边微缩的行道树是一簇簇新鲜的西蓝花和欧芹，表面撒着如霜的糖粉。右侧隐约可见卢浮宫金字塔，由半透明的薄片糖艺和切成几何形状的布里奶酪拼合而成。画面采用微距镜头的浅景深效果（f/2.8），前景的河流和远处的建筑呈现出柔和的边缘虚化，视觉焦点紧紧锁定在中景的建筑群上，营造出强烈的微缩比例模型感。柔和的微距布光打在食材上，产生令人垂涎的油润高光与环境光遮蔽（AO）阴影，呈现出8K分辨率下极致细腻的纹理与虚幻引擎5级别的渲染质感。整个场景完全由原汁原味的法国本土甜咸美食构筑，排除了任何真实金属、混凝土、塑料、餐具或人类元素的介入。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/item_3177_2.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "An ultra-high-precision macro tilt-shift photography work, presenting a miniature Paris cityscape (Diorama) constructed entirely from French culinary ingredients under a wide panoramic composition. At the center of the frame stands the iconic Eiffel Tower, its structural framework built from intricately interwoven baked baguette sticks, pretzel rods, and hard pulled-sugar pieces serving as steel girders, with melted Gruyère cheese used as adhesive at the joints, the surface gleaming with an appetizing sheen of baked oils and fats. To the left of the tower, the Arc de Triomphe is constructed from a large, distinctly layered Mille-feuille, with rich vanilla cream sandwiched between the puff pastry layers, and the relief details on its surface sculpted from finely piped royal icing. In the background and lining both sides of the streets stand Haussmann-style apartment buildings, their walls assembled from stacked French crêpes and sliced bread, rooftops covered with dark brown dark chocolate shavings and layered black truffle slices mimicking the classic zinc rooftops; the balcony railings are curved chocolate curls. In the foreground, a shimmering wine-red liquid (red wine) representing the Seine River winds through the scene, spanned by bridges assembled from large butter croissants. The cobblestones of the streets are composed of densely arranged green lentils, capers, and coarse sea salt grains, while the miniature roadside trees are clusters of fresh broccoli and parsley, dusted with frost-like powdered sugar. On the right side, the Louvre Pyramid is faintly visible, assembled from translucent thin sugar art pieces and geometrically cut Brie cheese. The image employs a shallow depth-of-field effect from a macro lens (f/2.8), with the river in the foreground and the buildings in the distance exhibiting soft edge bokeh, the visual focal point locked tightly on the building cluster in the middle ground, creating a strong miniature scale model sensation. Soft macro lighting falls upon the ingredients, producing mouth-watering oily highlights and ambient occlusion (AO) shadows, presenting extraordinarily delicate textures at 8K resolution with an Unreal Engine 5-level rendering quality. The entire scene is constructed exclusively from authentic French savory and sweet culinary ingredients, excluding any real metal, concrete, plastic, tableware, or human elements.",
