    "revised_prompt": "一张写实风格的夜景街头人像摄影照片。画面采用横向构图，主体是一名年轻女子，她站在夜晚的城市小巷中，身体微微背向前方，从肩膀上方回眸凝视着镜头。她的面部表情柔和且自然，一头略微凌乱的深色长发自然披散，几缕发丝垂落并贴合在脸颊两侧，修饰着面部轮廓。她身穿一件质感厚实的深色外套。\n\n由于采用了大光圈的浅景深效果，背景的城市小巷被深度虚化。背景中布满了色彩斑斓的圆形散景（bokeh），由远处的霓虹灯和街灯光晕形成。\n\n画面的光照呈现电影级别的质感，温暖的红色和黄色光线混合在一起，映照在女子的侧脸、鼻梁和发丝边缘，形成柔和的高光与清晰的轮廓光；而周围的背景环境光则透出清冷的色调，冷暖色彩在画面中相互交融，营造出一种幽暗且具有情绪感染力的夜景氛围。照片具有极高的清晰度与超写实的质感，女子的皮肤纹理、细微的面部起伏、眼球中的反光以及每一根发丝的光泽均清晰逼真，整体视觉效果如同35mm镜头下捕捉到的电影画面定格截帧。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/item_3191_2.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "A realistic-style nighttime street portrait photography shot. The image employs a horizontal composition, with the main subject being a young woman standing in a city alleyway at night, her body slightly turned away from the camera, glancing back over her shoulder to gaze into the lens. Her facial expression is soft and natural, with slightly tousled dark long hair cascading freely, a few strands falling and resting against both sides of her cheeks, framing her facial contours. She wears a thick, textured dark coat.\n\nDue to the shallow depth-of-field effect achieved with a wide aperture, the city alleyway in the background is deeply blurred. The background is filled with colorful circular bokeh, formed by distant neon lights and streetlamp halos.\n\nThe lighting in the image presents a cinematic quality, with warm red and yellow light blending together, illuminating the woman's profile, the bridge of her nose, and the edges of her hair, creating soft highlights and distinct rim lighting; meanwhile, the ambient light in the surrounding background carries cool tones, with warm and cool colors intermingling throughout the frame, creating a dim yet emotionally evocative nighttime atmosphere. The photograph possesses extremely high clarity and hyper-realistic quality—the woman's skin texture, subtle facial contours, reflections in her eyes, and the sheen of every individual strand of hair are all rendered with vivid realism, the overall visual effect resembling a cinematic still frame captured through a 35mm lens.",
