    "revised_prompt": "一张超细致、高动态范围的专业生活方式摄影照片。画面中央是一位年轻女性，她正随意且放松地靠坐在一张浅中性色的柔软布艺沙发上。她的一只手臂自然地搭在沙发靠背上，双腿舒展放松，呈现出一种毫不费力的现代街头生活态度。女性拥有一头自然蓬松的深棕色长卷发，肌肤呈现出真实的纹理，脸颊上带有细微的雀斑。她的妆容极简干净，主要为自然色调。她正用平静、自信的眼神直视镜头，流露出轻松自然的气场。在穿着方面，她上身穿着一件复古风格的短款印花T恤，T恤胸前印有褪色做旧的英文字母 'NEW YORK CITY'。下身搭配高腰宽松的蓝色牛仔裤，脚穿一双白色的休闲运动鞋。她的脖子上佩戴着多条叠搭的金色项链。画面清晰地展现了牛仔裤的丹宁颗粒感以及沙发的织物纹理。人物所处的环境是一个现代工业风的城市阁楼客厅。背景中，可见一面裸露的红砖墙，墙边靠着一幅装裱好的抽象艺术画，画中是简单的黑色线条与色块。旁边摆放着一盆叶片宽大、呈现柔和绿色的琴叶榕盆栽。房间一侧有巨大的黑色边框工业风落地窗，透过窗户可以隐约看到柔和的城市高楼天际线轮廓。整个空间显得空旷、现代且充满生活气息。摄影采用了35mm镜头，视平线视角构图，适合竖版的取景将人物的主体姿态完整纳入，景深适中，主体人物对焦清晰，而背景呈现出柔和的虚化效果。光线主要来自大窗户透入的柔和自然日光，为人物脸部勾勒出平缓、柔和的阴影。画面的主色调由沙发的米色和裤子的牛仔蓝构成，并以人物温暖的肤色、植物的绿色以及背景的砖红色作为点缀。整体调色自然真实，带有微妙的暖意，没有厚重的滤镜感，展现出极高的照片逼真度。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/item_3263_1.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "An ultra-detailed, high dynamic range professional lifestyle photograph. At the center of the frame is a young woman, casually and relaxedly leaning back on a soft fabric sofa in a light neutral tone. One of her arms rests naturally on the sofa backrest, her legs stretched out and relaxed, exuding an effortless modern streetwear attitude. The woman has naturally voluminous, long curly dark brown hair, with skin exhibiting realistic texture and subtle freckles on her cheeks. Her makeup is minimal and clean, primarily in natural tones. She gazes directly into the camera with a calm, confident expression, conveying a relaxed and natural aura. In terms of attire, she wears a vintage-style cropped graphic T-shirt with faded, distressed English lettering reading 'NEW YORK CITY' across the chest. On the bottom, she pairs it with high-waisted, loose-fit blue jeans and white casual sneakers. Around her neck, she wears multiple layered gold necklaces. The image clearly captures the denim grain texture of the jeans and the fabric texture of the sofa. The setting is a modern industrial-style urban loft living room. In the background, an exposed red brick wall is visible, with a framed abstract art piece leaning against it, featuring simple black lines and color blocks. Beside it stands a potted fiddle-leaf fig with broad leaves in a soft green hue. On one side of the room, there are large black-framed industrial floor-to-ceiling windows, through which a soft urban skyline silhouette is faintly visible. The entire space appears spacious, modern, and full of lived-in character. The photography employs a 35mm lens with an eye-level perspective composition; the vertical framing fully encompasses the subject's primary pose. The depth of field is moderate, with the subject in sharp focus while the background presents a soft bokeh effect. The lighting primarily comes from soft natural daylight streaming through the large windows, casting gentle, gradual shadows on the subject's face. The dominant color palette consists of the sofa's beige and the denim blue of the jeans, accented by the subject's warm skin tones, the green of the plant, and the brick red of the background. The overall color grading is natural and authentic with a subtle warmth, free of heavy filter effects, demonstrating an exceptionally high degree of photorealism.",
    "prompt_zh": "{\n  \"model\": \"Nano Banana Pro\",\n  \"scene\": \"带有大型工业风窗户的现代Loft客厅\",\n  \"subject\": {\n    \"type\": \"年轻女性\",\n    \"pose\": \"随意斜倚在布艺沙发上，一只手臂搭在靠背上，双腿放松\",\n    \"expression\": \"平静、自信、沉稳笃定\",\n    \"gaze\": \"与镜头直接对视\",\n    \"emotion\": \"从容、自信、自然的存在感\"\n  },\n  \"appearance\": {\n    \"hair\": {\n      \"color\": \"深棕色\",\n      \"style\": \"散落的长卷发，自然蓬松\"\n    },\n    \"skin\": \"自然肤色，带有细微雀斑和真实的"
