    "revised_prompt": "一幅垂直构图的儿童故事书手绘插画。画面呈现温馨、治愈且充满童趣的绘本风格，带有明显的彩铅手绘质感与略显粗糙、有机的柔软铅笔轮廓线。画面中央，在一棵粗壮的橡树旁，坐着一只巨大的浅棕色毛绒小熊。小熊体态圆润，具有半卡通的比例，面部特征极简且生动：只有两个黑色的豆豆眼和一条小巧弯曲的微笑线。在小熊毛茸茸的肚子上，舒舒服服地靠坐着一个可爱的小女孩。她留着棕色的短发，穿着柔和的浅粉色短袖和淡蓝色的背带裤。小女孩同样拥有简单的豆豆眼和浅浅的微笑，她双手捧着一本打开的精装绘本，似乎正念给小熊听；书的封皮上用稚嫩的彩色铅笔字体写着 'STORIES'。小熊和小女孩坐在浅绿色的草地上，草坪上可见一排排铅笔画出的细草纹理。画面右下角长着一朵红底白点的卡通大蘑菇，周围零星散布着几朵简单的黄色五瓣野花。橡树的树干位于画面左侧并向顶部延伸，繁茂的绿色树冠占据了画面左上方的空间，树枝上垂下一根细线，挂着一个黄色的小星星吊饰。背景的右上角是一片温暖的淡蓝色天空，飘浮着两朵边缘柔软、带有随意涂鸦感的白云。在艺术风格上，整幅画采用温暖、明亮且友好的粉彩色调。光影极其柔和，没有强烈的对比度或深沉的阴影，主要以平涂色彩搭配轻微的铅笔颗粒纹理和轻柔的过渡来表现，高光部分保留了温和的铅笔留白感。整体视觉干净简单，彻底摒弃了3D渲染与写实光影，完美契合舒适、欢乐的非写实类手绘儿童插画美学。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/item_3284_4.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "A vertically composed hand-drawn children's storybook illustration. The image presents a warm, healing, and whimsical picture book style, with a distinct colored pencil hand-drawn texture and slightly rough, organic soft pencil outlines. At the center of the image, beside a stout oak tree, sits an enormous light brown plush teddy bear. The bear has a rounded body with semi-cartoonish proportions, and minimalist yet expressive facial features: just two black bead eyes and a small, curved smile line. Nestled comfortably against the bear's fuzzy belly is an adorable little girl. She has short brown hair and wears a soft light pink short-sleeved top and pale blue overalls. The little girl likewise has simple bead eyes and a gentle smile; she holds an open hardcover picture book in both hands, as if reading aloud to the bear. On the book's cover, the word 'STORIES' is written in a childlike colored pencil font. The bear and the little girl sit on a light green meadow, where rows of fine grass textures drawn in pencil are visible. In the lower right corner of the image grows a large cartoon mushroom with a red cap and white polka dots, surrounded by a scattering of simple yellow five-petaled wildflowers. The oak tree trunk is positioned on the left side of the image and extends toward the top, its lush green canopy occupying the upper left area of the frame. A thin string hangs from a branch, bearing a small yellow star ornament. In the upper right corner of the background is a warm, pale blue sky with two soft-edged white clouds that have a casual doodle-like quality. In terms of artistic style, the entire illustration employs a warm, bright, and friendly pastel color palette. The lighting and shadows are extremely soft, with no strong contrasts or deep shadows, rendered primarily through flat color fills complemented by slight pencil grain texture and gentle transitions; highlights retain a warm pencil-white reserve quality. The overall visual is clean and simple, thoroughly eschewing 3D rendering and realistic lighting, perfectly aligned with a cozy, joyful, non-realistic hand-drawn children's illustration aesthetic.",
