    "revised_prompt": "一张具有35mm电影胶片质感的浪漫摄影静帧。画面采用横向构图和极浅的景深特写，聚焦于一男一女在户外草地上的亲密互动。两人面对面距离极近，眼神深情交汇，充满安静浪漫的张力。女士位于画面一侧，穿着简约的白色细带棉质上衣，露出放松的肩膀，身体微微向前倾斜；她留着深棕色长发，发丝自然柔和地垂落，面部表情平静温柔，嘴角带着淡淡的暖意。男士位于画面另一侧，穿着休闲的白色无袖背心，深色波浪卷发略显凌乱，下颌带有自然的短胡茬。他的手臂抬起，手腕上佩戴着一块简约低调的机械手表；他的手指骨骼分明且动作轻柔，正捏着一朵娇嫩的粉色波斯菊，细心地将其别在女士鬓角的发际线处。背景是乡村野花的绿地，呈现为大片柔和模糊的绿色植物与草丛，形成奶油般细腻的自然散景，没有任何人工建筑。此时正值傍晚的黄金时刻，柔和温暖的自然光洒在两人身上，在真实细腻的皮肤纹理上留下温暖的高光，光线过渡柔和，没有生硬的阴影。画面色彩以温暖的绿色和自然的肤色为主基调，粉色花朵形成视觉点缀；整体画面带有真实的胶片颗粒感和轻微的高光晕影，质感写实且极具怀旧诗意。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/item_3349_1.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "A romantic photographic still with the texture of 35mm cinema film. The frame employs a horizontal composition and an extremely shallow depth-of-field close-up, focusing on the intimate interaction between a man and a woman on an outdoor grassy field. The two face each other at very close range, their gazes meeting with deep affection, brimming with quiet romantic tension. The woman is positioned on one side of the frame, wearing a simple white thin-strapped cotton top that reveals her relaxed shoulders, her body leaning slightly forward; she has long dark brown hair falling naturally and softly, her facial expression calm and tender, the corners of her lips carrying a faint warmth. The man is on the other side of the frame, wearing a casual white sleeveless tank top, his dark wavy curly hair slightly tousled, with natural short stubble along his jawline. His arm is raised, a minimalist and understated mechanical watch adorning his wrist; his fingers are well-defined with gentle movements, pinching a delicate pink cosmos flower and carefully tucking it into the hairline at the woman's temple. The background is a countryside wildflower meadow, rendered as large swathes of softly blurred green vegetation and grass, forming a creamy, fine natural bokeh, devoid of any man-made structures. It is the golden hour of the late afternoon, and soft warm natural light bathes the two of them, leaving warm highlights on their realistically detailed skin textures, with gentle light transitions and no harsh shadows. The color palette is dominated by warm greens and natural skin tones, with the pink flower serving as a visual accent; the overall image carries authentic film grain and a slight highlight halation, realistic in texture yet deeply nostalgic and poetic.",
    "prompt_zh": "{\n  \"generation_request\": {\n    \"meta_data\": {\n      \"tool\": \"NanoBanana Pro\",\n      \"task_type\": \"photoreal_cinematic_romantic_closeup\",\n      \"version\": \"v1.0_GOLDEN_HOUR_FLOWER_TUCK_INTIMATE_FILM_STILL\",\n      \"priority\": \"highest\"\n    },\n\n    \"references\": {\n      \"reference_image_1\": {\n        \"source\": \"UPLOAD_REFERENCE_IMAGE\",\n        \"purpose\": \"POSE_INTIMACY_LIGHTING_TEXTURE_REFERENCE\",\n        \"strict_lock\": true,\n        \"match_reference_priority\": \"MAX\",\n        \"preserve_hand_to_face_gesture\": true,\n        \"preserve_distance_and_eye_lines\": true,\n        \"preserve_shallow_dof_and"
