    "type": "t2i",
    "author": "@Gdgtify",
    "author_link": "https://x.com/Gdgtify/status/2009084893897121982",
    "revised_prompt": "一张呈现2x2网格布局的高精度微缩建筑透视图。整体画面采用移轴摄影风格和宏观镜头（f/2.8）的浅景深效果，边缘模糊而中心极度清晰，展现出如虚幻引擎5（Unreal Engine 5）渲染般的8K级画质、逼真的物理材质纹理和全局光照下的环境光遮蔽效果。画面中没有人物，纯粹聚焦于四座中国小众城市的微缩地标，每座城市的天际线均由当地著名的特产材料拼装构建而成。\n\n左上角网格展示【潍坊】。城市天际线完全由“风筝”的材质构成。摩天大楼的骨架是精细绑扎的竹条，外墙是紧绷的半透明丝绸和宣纸，表面印有高饱和度的传统燕子、蝴蝶和彩色条纹图案。建筑顶部呈现出风筝翅膀的张力形态。光线穿透丝绸产生柔和的次表面散射效果，展现出轻盈的体积感。该面板底部居中印有黑色的清晰英文字母：'Weifang'。\n\n右上角网格展示【浏阳】。城市景观由“烟花”组件拼接而成。高楼大厦是成排绑定的圆柱形厚纸筒，外层包裹着带有细微褶皱的亮红色纸张和烫金纹理；高架桥和建筑间的连廊由粗糙的绿色和灰色火药引线交织而成，部分半球形的屋顶形似未发射的礼花弹外壳。材质呈现出哑光纸板、木屑和火药颗粒的粗糙物理纹理。该面板底部居中印有黑色的清晰英文字母：'Liuyang'。\n\n左下角网格展示【宜兴】。微缩城市由“紫砂”构建。建筑物呈现出紫砂壶的几何解构形态，表面是未挂釉的红棕色和深紫色陶土，带有细腻的砂砾质感和温润的漫反射光泽。弯曲的壶嘴化作连接楼宇的悬空拱桥，圆润的壶盖和提梁构成了建筑的穹顶和飞挑的屋檐。厚重的泥料逻辑贯穿整个建筑结构。该面板底部居中印有黑色的清晰英文字母：'Yixing'。\n\n右下角网格展示【东海】。整个城市天际线由“水晶”原石和刻面宝石拔地而起。主干摩天大楼是巨大的六棱柱状透明白水晶和紫水晶晶簇，切面极其平滑；低矮的附属结构则是多面切割的闪亮碎晶。光线在建筑群内部产生强烈的折射、色散和焦散现象，晶体内部的天然冰裂纹和棉絮状包裹体清晰可见，散发出梦幻的体积光晕。该面板底部居中印有黑色的清晰英文字母：'Donghai'。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/item_3393_1.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "A high-precision miniature architectural perspective presented in a 2x2 grid layout. The overall image adopts a tilt-shift photography style with a shallow depth-of-field effect from a macro lens (f/2.8), blurred at the edges yet extremely sharp at the center, showcasing 8K-level image quality akin to Unreal Engine 5 rendering, photorealistic physically-based material textures, and ambient occlusion under global illumination. There are no human figures in the scene; it focuses purely on miniature landmarks of four lesser-known Chinese cities, each city's skyline constructed and assembled entirely from materials of its locally renowned specialty products.\n\nThe upper-left grid showcases **Weifang**. The city skyline is composed entirely of \"kite\" materials. The skyscrapers' frameworks are finely bound bamboo strips, and the exterior walls are taut, semi-transparent silk and xuan paper, printed with highly saturated traditional patterns of swallows, butterflies, and colorful stripes. The building tops exhibit the tensile form of kite wings. Light penetrates the silk, producing a soft subsurface scattering effect that conveys a sense of lightweight volume. Centered at the bottom of this panel are clear black English letters: 'Weifang'.\n\nThe upper-right grid showcases **Liuyang**. The cityscape is assembled from \"firework\" components. The high-rise buildings are rows of bound cylindrical thick paper tubes, their outer layers wrapped in bright red paper with subtle creases and hot-stamped gold textures; the elevated bridges and corridors between buildings are woven from coarse green and gray gunpowder fuses, and some hemispherical rooftops resemble unfired firework shells. The materials exhibit the rough physical textures of matte cardboard, wood shavings, and gunpowder granules. Centered at the bottom of this panel are clear black English letters: 'Liuyang'.\n\nThe lower-left grid showcases **Yixing**. The miniature city is constructed from \"Zisha\" (purple clay). The buildings present geometrically deconstructed forms of Zisha teapots, their surfaces unglazed red-brown and deep purple clay with a fine sandy granular texture and a warm diffuse luster. Curved teapot spouts transform into suspended arch bridges connecting buildings, while rounded teapot lids and loop handles form the domes and cantilevered eaves of the structures. The logic of heavy clay material permeates the entire architectural composition. Centered at the bottom of this panel are clear black English letters: 'Yixing'.\n\nThe lower-right grid showcases **Donghai**. The entire city skyline rises from \"crystal\" raw stones and faceted gemstones. The main skyscrapers are massive hexagonal prismatic transparent clear quartz and amethyst crystal clusters with extremely smooth cut surfaces; the lower ancillary structures are multi-faceted, brilliantly cut crystal shards. Light produces intense refraction, dispersion, and caustic phenomena within the building cluster, and natural ice-crack inclusions inside the crystals—",
    "prompt_zh": "针对中国执行以下操作：<instructions>\n输入 = 国家\n扮演世界级视觉艺术家和地理专家。针对每个国家，找出4个较不知名的城市以及在当地非常流行的一种产品。请做好调研以确保此步骤准确。\n\n函数 Draw ($ 城市, $ 材料) 锚点：[地点] :: [材料概念]::4\n形态：[地点]的微缩建筑城市景观，整个天际线通过[材料概念]组件的集合构建而成，摩天大楼和建筑结构由[材料概念]的组成部分形成，主题化结构工程，超精细立体透视模型::3"
}, {
    "filename": "item_3396_2.png",
    "index": 3396,
    "title": "黄铜机械字母\"TIME\"装置",
    "title_en": "Brass Mechanical Letter \"TIME\" Installation",
    "prompt": "<instructions> \nInput word or concept\nAct as a Conceptual Sculptor. Generate a 3D typography render where the letters are constructed from materials that Physically Embody the Input Word.\n1. Material & Physics Inference (The DNA):\nAnalyze the Input Word to determine the Structural Material and Internal Physics:\nIf Ethereal (e.g., TIME, SOUL): Use Glass, Brass, and Light. Physics = Flowing, ticking, glowing.\nIf Elemental (e.g., FIRE, MAGMA): Use Black Iron cages. Physics = Burning, dripping, smoking.\nIf Organic (e.g., GROWTH, LIFE): Use Wooden frames or Terrarium glass. Physics = Growing, blooming, condensation.\nIf Industrial (e.g., FACTORY, STEEL): Use Rusted Steel beams. Physics = Grinding gears, steam vents.\n2.  Container  :\nThe Structure: The letters are massive, 3D structural frames.\nThe Transparency: The front face is open or transparent to reveal the Internal Mechanism.\nThe Logic: The frame must look like it was built to contain the specific substance inside (e.g., thick glass for gas; heavy iron for magma).\n3. The Internal Mechanism :\nContent: Fill the hollow letters with the active element of the concept.\nExample (TIME): Sand pouring from T to I; Pendulums swinging in M; Gears turning in E.\nExample (FIRE): Real flames licking up the inside of F; Coals glowing in I; Smoke venting from R.\nConnectivity: Pipes, wires, or vines connect the letters, transferring the energy from one to the next.\n4. The Narrative Scale :\nThe Figures: Tiny 1:87 scale figures interact with the letters.\nInference: If \"TIME,\" figures are winding clocks. If \"FIRE,\" figures are stokers shoveling coal. If \"GROWTH,\" figures are gardeners watering plants.\n5. Lighting & Atmosphere:\nSource: The light comes from the Material itself (e.g., Fire glow, Bioluminescence, Neon).\nEnvironment: The table/floor matches the theme (e.g., Burnt wood for FIRE; Mossy earth for GROWTH).\nOutput: ONE image, High Resolution 3D Render, Conceptual Art Aesthetic.\n</instructions>",
    "prompt_en": "<instructions> \nInput word or concept\nAct as a Conceptual Sculptor. Generate a 3D typography render where the letters are constructed from materials that Physically Embody the Input Word.\n1. Material & Physics Inference (The DNA):\nAnalyze the Input Word to determine the Structural Material and Internal Physics:\nIf Ethereal (e.g., TIME, SOUL): Use Glass, Brass, and Light. Physics = Flowing, ticking, glowing.\nIf Elemental (e.g., FIRE, MAGMA): Use Black Iron cages. Physics = Burning, dripping, smoking.\nIf Organic (e.g., GROWTH, LIFE): Use Wooden frames or Terrarium glass. Physics = Growing, blooming, condensation.\nIf Industrial (e.g., FACTORY, STEEL): Use Rusted Steel beams. Physics = Grinding gears, steam vents.\n2.  Container  :\nThe Structure: The letters are massive, 3D structural frames.\nThe Transparency: The front face is open or transparent to reveal the Internal Mechanism.\nThe Logic: The frame must look like it was built to contain the specific substance inside (e.g., thick glass for gas; heavy iron for magma).\n3. The Internal Mechanism :\nContent: Fill the hollow letters with the active element of the concept.\nExample (TIME): Sand pouring from T to I; Pendulums swinging in M; Gears turning in E.\nExample (FIRE): Real flames licking up the inside of F; Coals glowing in I; Smoke venting from R.\nConnectivity: Pipes, wires, or vines connect the letters, transferring the energy from one to the next.\n4. The Narrative Scale :\nThe Figures: Tiny 1:87 scale figures interact with the letters.\nInference: If \"TIME,\" figures are winding clocks. If \"FIRE,\" figures are stokers shoveling coal. If \"GROWTH,\" figures are gardeners watering plants.\n5. Lighting & Atmosphere:\nSource: The light comes from the Material itself (e.g., Fire glow, Bioluminescence, Neon).\nEnvironment: The table/floor matches the theme (e.g., Burnt wood for FIRE; Mossy earth for GROWTH).\nOutput: ONE image, High Resolution 3D Render, Conceptual Art Aesthetic.\n</instructions>",
    "source": "https://x.com/Gdgtify/status/2011736617174573428",
    "type": "t2i",
    "author": "@Gdgtify",
    "author_link": "https://x.com/Gdgtify/status/2011736617174573428",
    "revised_prompt": "宽幅的高分辨率3D排版渲染图与概念艺术作品。画面正中央矗立着四个巨大的3D立体建筑级字母，拼成了英文单词‘TIME’。这些字母被设计成宏伟的微观机械容器，外部框架由做旧的抛光黄铜构建，正面镶嵌着极厚的透明结构玻璃，暴露出内部用来具象化“时间”概念的复杂物理机制。\n\n字母‘T’内部被设计成一个巨大的沙漏，发光的金色细沙正从顶部横杠倾泻而下；金沙底部连接着粗壮的黄铜管道，将流动的沙粒引流至字母‘I’中，在‘I’的垂直透明玻璃腔体内形成一道耀眼的金色能量流；字母‘M’的双拱形空间内悬挂着数个沉重的黄铜钟摆，呈现出不同角度的动态摆动；字母‘E’的三个横杠内部塞满了精密咬合的大型黄铜齿轮和发条盒，正在缓慢运转。字母之间通过错综复杂的管道、带有压力表的黄铜阀门以及发光的导线紧密相连，金色的能量在管道网中穿梭传输。\n\n在这些巨大的字母框架周围、顶部和栈道上，分布着许多1:87比例的微缩小人。部分穿着工装的小人正站在‘M’的钟摆旁，用巨大的绞盘给发条上弦；几个小人架着微型脚手架在‘E’的齿轮间进行维护润滑；还有几个小人推着装满发光金沙的手推车，走在连接‘T’和‘I’的金属网格栈道上。\n\n画面的主光源来自‘TIME’内部金沙和能量散发的温暖金色辉光，在黄铜表面折射出细腻的金属光泽。整个庞大的结构放置在一张布满划痕的复古深色胡桃木工作台上。工作台表面铺着几张边缘泛黄的机械蓝图，蓝图角落清晰可见英文‘CHRONOS MK-IV’。台面周围散落着微小的怀表零件和做旧的独立齿轮。空气中漂浮着发光的尘埃微粒，景深效果强烈，背景隐没在柔和的暗色调中，呈现出极致的电影级光影质感与复古精工机械美学。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/item_3396_2.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "A wide-format, high-resolution 3D typographic render and concept art piece. Standing prominently at the center of the frame are four enormous 3D architectural-scale letters spelling out the English word 'TIME'. These letters are designed as grand micro-mechanical vessels; their external frameworks are constructed from aged polished brass, with extremely thick transparent structural glass inlaid on the front faces, exposing the complex physical mechanisms inside that physicalize the concept of \"time.\"\n\nThe interior of the letter 'T' is designed as a giant hourglass, with luminous fine golden sand cascading down from the top crossbar; thick brass pipes at the base of the golden sand channel the flowing grains into the letter 'I', forming a dazzling golden energy stream within the vertical transparent glass chamber of 'I'; within the double-arched spaces of the letter 'M', several heavy brass pendulums are suspended, exhibiting dynamic swinging at various angles; the three horizontal bars of the letter 'E' are packed with precisely interlocking large brass gears and mainspring barrels, slowly turning. The letters are tightly interconnected through an intricate network of pipes, brass valves fitted with pressure gauges, and glowing conduits, with golden energy shuttling through the pipe network.\n\nAround, atop, and on the walkways of these enormous letter frameworks, numerous 1:87 scale miniature figures are distributed. Some figures in work overalls stand beside the pendulums of 'M', using large winches to wind the mainsprings; several figures have erected miniature scaffolding among the gears of 'E' to perform maintenance and lubrication; still others push handcarts loaded with glowing golden sand along metal grate walkways connecting 'T' and 'I'.\n\nThe primary light source in the scene emanates from the warm golden glow of the golden sand and energy within 'TIME', refracting fine metallic luster across the brass surfaces. The entire massive structure is placed on a vintage dark walnut worktable covered with scratches. Several yellowed-edged mechanical blueprints are spread across the table surface, with the English text 'CHRONOS MK-IV' clearly visible in the corner of the blueprints. Tiny pocket watch parts and aged standalone gears are scattered around the tabletop. Luminous dust particles float in the air, the depth-of-field effect is strong, and the background recedes into soft dark tones, presenting an ultimate cinematic lighting quality and vintage precision mechanical aesthetic.",
    "prompt_zh": "<instructions>\n输入词语或概念\n扮演概念雕塑家。生成一幅3D字体渲染图，其中字母由能物理体现输入词语的材料构建而成。"
