    "title": "食材微缩还原冷门影视场景",
    "title_en": "Food Miniature Recreating Obscure Movie Scenes",
    "prompt": "<instructions>\ninput: movie, tv shoes, game\nanalyze every aspect, main characters, most iconic scenes\nfind 4 \"gems\" or less known titles in the same class (e..g game -> game, tv shows -> tv show)\n\ndo this for all 4 in a 2x2 grid: {\nInput A: movie, tv series or stories\nAnalyze every character, storylineline, interact and pick up iconic scenes from Input A\nPick the right food ingredients, sauces and spices to draw 3D iconic scenes.\nContainer:  elongated plate depicting the most iconic scene involving top characters in 3D. \n Draw: one image, include name\n</instructions>",
    "prompt_en": "<instructions>\ninput: movie, tv shoes, game\nanalyze every aspect, main characters, most iconic scenes\nfind 4 \"gems\" or less known titles in the same class (e..g game -> game, tv shows -> tv show)\n\ndo this for all 4 in a 2x2 grid: {\nInput A: movie, tv series or stories\nAnalyze every character, storylineline, interact and pick up iconic scenes from Input A\nPick the right food ingredients, sauces and spices to draw 3D iconic scenes.\nContainer:  elongated plate depicting the most iconic scene involving top characters in 3D. \n Draw: one image, include name\n</instructions>",
    "source": "https://x.com/Gdgtify/status/2011039146274664956",
    "type": "t2i",
    "author": "@Gdgtify",
    "author_link": "https://x.com/Gdgtify/status/2011039146274664956",
    "revised_prompt": "一张2x2网格排版的食物艺术与流行文化微缩景观摄影图。画面被等分为四个象限，每个象限的深色木质桌面上都放置着一个细长的白色陶瓷餐盘。盘中利用真实的3D立体食材、酱汁和香料构建了四部冷门佳作（电影、剧集、游戏）的标志性场景微缩模型。左上角象限（电影）：盘子边缘用黑色芝麻酱清晰写着 'MOON'。盘中用凹凸不平的土豆泥铺成月球表面，表面撒着黑胡椒粉以模拟陨石坑。土豆泥上停着一辆用白萝卜和胡萝卜片精雕而成的微型月球探测车。车旁站着一个用米饭捏成、贴着极小海苔片作为细节的立体小人（主角Sam）。背景是浓稠黑芝麻糊涂抹成的深邃太空，一滴纯白酸奶作为远处的星星。右上角象限（剧集）：盘子边缘用鲜黄色的芥末酱写着 'UTOPIA'。盘底铺垫着一层用藏红花染色的明黄色烩饭，代表剧集高饱和度的色调。中央放置着一块雕刻成翻开漫画书形状的玉子烧煎蛋卷，书页上的图案用牙签蘸取黑色意大利黑醋精细描绘。旁边斜放着一把银色糖霜包裹的长条形巧克力（模拟剧中的勺子道具），边缘散落着几颗红色的石榴籽。左下角象限（游戏）：盘子边缘用白色奶油细管挤出尖锐字体的 'HOLLOW KNIGHT'。盘子主要以盘绕堆叠的墨鱼汁黑色意大利面为基底，营造出深邃的废墟氛围。主角模型用切割完美的白蘑菇头（面具）和海苔米饭团（黑色披风）立体拼接而成，安静地坐在由两根焦黄法式薯条搭成的长椅上。周围点缀着几滴发光的蓝色螺旋藻糖浆。右下角象限（游戏）：盘子边缘用红棕色的番茄沙司流畅写出 'JOURNEY'。餐盘上铺满了细腻的古斯古斯面和全麦饼干屑，堆砌出起伏的3D沙漠沙丘。沙丘顶部站着一个用三文鱼生鱼片折叠卷曲而成的立体红袍旅者，细长的红色辣椒丝作为飘扬的围巾。餐盘尽头是一座由立体玉米面糕雕刻而成的高山，山顶淋有闪亮的金色芒果泥以模拟神圣的光束。整体光线采用聚光灯效果，突显出食物的质感、纹理和立体微缩模型的精细度，色调丰富，具有高清微距摄影的清晰度。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/item_3411_4.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "A food art and pop culture miniature landscape photography image in a 2x2 grid layout. The frame is equally divided into four quadrants, each featuring a dark wooden tabletop with a slender white ceramic dinner plate. Within each plate, real 3D food ingredients, sauces, and spices are used to construct miniature models of iconic scenes from four underrated masterpieces (films, series, games). Upper-left quadrant (film): The plate's rim has 'MOON' clearly written in black sesame paste. The plate's surface is covered with uneven mashed potato to form the lunar surface, sprinkled with black pepper to simulate craters. On the mashed potato sits a miniature lunar rover intricately carved from white radish and carrot slices. Beside the rover stands a small 3D figure (protagonist Sam) shaped from rice and detailed with tiny pieces of nori seaweed. The background is a deep space created by smearing thick black sesame paste, with a drop of pure white yogurt serving as a distant star. Upper-right quadrant (series): The plate's rim has 'UTOPIA' written in bright yellow mustard sauce. The plate's base is lined with a layer of saffron-tinted bright yellow risotto, representing the show's highly saturated color palette. At the center sits a tamagoyaki egg roll carved into the shape of an open comic book, with patterns on the pages finely drawn using a toothpick dipped in black Italian balsamic vinegar. Beside it, placed at an angle, is an elongated chocolate bar coated in silver icing (simulating the spoon prop from the series), with a few red pomegranate seeds scattered around the edges. Lower-left quadrant (game): The plate's rim has 'HOLLOW KNIGHT' piped in sharp-edged font using a white cream tube. The plate's base primarily consists of coiled and stacked squid ink black pasta, creating a deep, ruinous atmosphere. The protagonist model is three-dimensionally assembled from a perfectly cut white mushroom cap (mask) and a nori-wrapped rice ball (black cloak), sitting quietly on a bench made from two golden-brown French fries. Surrounding it are a few glowing drops of blue spirulina syrup. Lower-right quadrant (game): The plate's rim has 'JOURNEY' fluidly written in reddish-brown tomato sauce. The plate is covered with fine couscous and whole wheat cracker crumbs, sculpted into undulating 3D desert dunes. Atop the dunes stands a 3D red-robed traveler formed by folding and curling salmon sashimi, with thin red chili threads serving as a billowing scarf. At the far end of the plate is a tall mountain carved from 3D cornmeal cake, its peak drizzled with glistening golden mango purée to simulate sacred beams of light. The overall lighting employs a spotlight effect, highlighting the textures, grain, and intricacy of the 3D miniature food models, with rich tones and high-definition macro photography.",
    "prompt_zh": "<instructions>\n输入：电影、电视剧、游戏\n分析每个方面、主要角色、最具标志性的场景\n找出4个同类型的\"隐藏佳作\"或较不知名的作品（例如：游戏 -> 游戏，电视剧 -> 电视剧）\n\n对所有4个作品以2x2网格形式执行以下操作：{\n输入 A：电影、电视剧或故事\n分析每个角色、故事线，交互并从输入 A 中提取标志性场景\n挑选合适的食材、酱料和香料来绘制3D标志性场景。\n容器：长形餐盘，以3D形式描绘涉及主要角色的最具标志性场景。\n绘制：一张图片，包含名称\n</instructions>"
}, {
