    "revised_prompt": "微距摄影视角的微缩模型场景，呈现16:9宽屏构图。画面中央的一张深色木质书桌上平铺着一本巨大的复古皮革精装书，书本从中间翻开。翻开的书页中心物理突变为一片汹涌的微缩海洋，海浪由半透明、闪烁着光泽的树脂材质构成，带有白色的水沫。在海浪的正中央，矗立着巨大的3D立体英文字母，拼写出完整的标题 'MOBY DICK'。这些字母呈现风化的灰色浮木纹理，底部被树脂海浪环绕和拍打。在字母后方，一头巨大的微缩模型白色抹香鲸破浪而出，身躯高耸。在字母前方的前景波浪上，一艘精细的木制微缩捕鲸帆船模型正倾斜着迎击巨浪。画面左上角边缘可见一盏复古黄铜台灯，投射出温暖的黄色定向光束，照亮整个立体书场景。海面上缭绕着微缩的雾气。画面采用浅景深效果，书桌边缘及背景处于模糊虚化状态，视觉焦点完全集中在立体的海洋模型和文字上。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/item_3419_1.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "A macro photography perspective of a miniature model scene, presented in a 16:9 widescreen composition. At the center of the frame, a large vintage leather hardcover book lies open on a dark wooden desk. From the center of the opened pages, the book physically transforms into a surging miniature ocean, with waves made of translucent, shimmering resin material complete with white foam. In the very center of the waves, massive 3D three-dimensional English letters stand upright, spelling out the complete title 'MOBY DICK'. These letters feature a weathered gray driftwood texture, with their bases surrounded and lapped by resin waves. Behind the letters, a huge miniature model white sperm whale breaches through the waves, its body towering high. In the foreground waves in front of the letters, an intricately detailed wooden miniature whaling sailboat model tilts as it confronts the giant waves. At the upper-left edge of the frame, a vintage brass desk lamp is visible, casting a warm yellow directional beam of light that illuminates the entire pop-up book scene. Wisps of miniature mist linger over the sea surface. The image employs a shallow depth-of-field effect, with the desk edges and background in a blurred bokeh state, with the visual focus entirely concentrated on the three-dimensional ocean model and text.",
    "prompt_zh": "语义分解：\n分析食物：将其分解为加工阶段（例如：豆子 -> 粉末 -> 固体）。\n分析质感：识别物理属性（例如：光泽、哑光、酥脆、液态）。"
