    "revised_prompt": "这是一张超写实的产品摄影照片，展示了一个关于巧克力制作工艺的复古微缩教育道具透视模型。画面采用纯白色背景和柔和的摄影棚照明，整体色调以复古的奶油色和棕色为主，并呈现出极为严格的居中对称构图。由于是宽屏画幅，展示柜向两侧横向延伸。画面的视角为正视图并带有极其轻微的高俯角，使模型清晰平展地呈现。\n\n模型的容器是一个垂直的影子盒展示柜，背板与水平的地板成90度直角相连，形似一个打开的高端复古科学教学套件。整个背板的外围被一圈厚重的深色复古实木边框包裹。\n\n奶油色的背板信息密度极高，像元素周期表一样排布。顶排水平排列着一系列透明的圆形培养皿，从左到右依次盛装着巧克力加工各个阶段的真实原料：未经处理的生可可豆、烘焙过的棕色可可豆、粗糙的碎可可粒、深褐色的可可液块、淡黄色的可可脂块以及细腻的可可粉。每个培养皿正下方的背板上直接印有微小的黑色科学字体标签，文字依次为：'THEOBROMA CACAO'、'FERMENTED BEANS'、'ROASTED NIBS'、'COCOA MASS'、'COCOA BUTTER'、'COCOA POWDER'。中排水平排列着一系列方形的巧克力样本块，展示了质地和颜色的渐变，从左至右依次为：发白且具有光泽的白巧克力、浅棕色的牛奶巧克力、表面带有哑光质感的半甜巧克力、色泽深邃的黑巧克力以及表面带有干燥易碎纹理的无糖纯巧克力。每个方块下方同样印有标签，文字依次为：'WHITE CHOCOLATE'、'MILK CHOCOLATE'、'SEMI-SWEET'、'BITTERSWEET'、'UNSWEETENED'。\n\n模型底部相连的地板上是一个微缩实验室场景。地板的中央摆放着一张宽大的木制实验台，两侧紧挨着两个较小的木制多层侧柜和置物架，这组家具横向排列，填满了微缩地板的整个宽度。实验台后面站着一个微缩比例的人物——一名穿着白色实验室大褂的科学家，他正低头用玻璃棒混合烧杯中的成分。置物架和实验台上密密麻麻地摆满了微缩道具，包括不同尺寸的透明玻璃烧杯、装满粉末和液体的玻璃罐、试管架以及精密的复古金属天平。\n\n在透视模型地板的最前端边缘，横跨整个模型宽度放置着一行巨大且厚重的3D立体块状字母。这些字母的材质完全由逼真的黑巧克力构成，表面呈现出诱人的丝绒光泽和锋利的模具边缘。这排3D字母拼出清晰的文字：'THE CHEMISTRY OF CHOCOLATE'。整体画面质感极为逼真，像一件陈列在博物馆里的精美藏品。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/item_3483_2.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "This is a hyper-realistic product photography shot showcasing a vintage miniature educational prop cutaway model about chocolate-making craftsmanship. The image uses a pure white background with soft studio lighting, with the overall color palette dominated by vintage cream and brown tones, and presents an extremely strict centered symmetrical composition. Due to the widescreen aspect ratio, the display case extends horizontally to both sides. The viewing angle is a front elevation with an extremely slight high-angle tilt, allowing the model to be presented clearly and flat.\n\nThe model's container is a vertical shadow box display case, with the backboard connected at a 90-degree right angle to the horizontal floor, resembling an opened high-end vintage scientific teaching kit. The entire perimeter of the backboard is framed by a thick, dark vintage solid wood border.\n\nThe cream-colored backboard is extremely information-dense, arranged like a periodic table. The top row features a horizontal series of transparent circular petri dishes, containing real raw materials from various stages of chocolate processing from left to right: unprocessed raw cacao beans, roasted brown cacao beans, coarse cacao nibs, dark brown cacao liquor blocks, pale yellow cocoa butter blocks, and fine cocoa powder. Directly beneath each petri dish, tiny black scientific-font labels are printed on the backboard, reading sequentially: 'THEOBROMA CACAO', 'FERMENTED BEANS', 'ROASTED NIBS', 'COCOA MASS', 'COCOA BUTTER', 'COCOA POWDER'. The middle row features a horizontal series of square chocolate sample blocks, displaying a gradation in texture and color, from left to right: whitish and glossy white chocolate, light brown milk chocolate, semi-sweet chocolate with a matte surface texture, deep-hued dark chocolate, and unsweetened pure chocolate with a dry and crumbly surface texture. Each square block likewise has a label printed beneath it, reading sequentially: 'WHITE CHOCOLATE', 'MILK CHOCOLATE', 'SEMI-SWEET', 'BITTERSWEET', 'UNSWEETENED'.\n\nThe floor connected at the base of the model houses a miniature laboratory scene. At the center of the floor sits a wide wooden laboratory bench, flanked closely on both sides by two smaller wooden multi-tiered side cabinets and shelving units, this furniture arrangement spanning horizontally to fill the entire width of the miniature floor. Behind the laboratory bench stands a miniature-scale figure—a scientist wearing a white laboratory coat, who is leaning down—",
    "prompt_zh": "容器（铰链式工具箱）：\n结构：一个带有连接底板的垂直阴影箱展示架。"
