    "author_link": "https://github.com/op7418",
    "revised_prompt": "一张以《西游记》IP为灵感设计的3D新年贺卡海报，采用微距摄影视角的垂直构图。整个画面呈现出极其精致的毛毡与粗针织羊毛材质，宛如高质量的3D盲盒玩具。画面中央有一个深邃的、类似窗框的凹槽结构，贺卡本身仿佛悬浮在云端，底部带有柔和的阴影。背景是东方水墨风格的虚空环境，弥漫着浅香槟金与高级雾红色的流动光雾。海报外部空间环绕着飞舞的红丝绒丝带、流动的金色光线、绽放的红梅枝条、成串的喜庆红灯笼、饱满的红柿子、晶莹剔透的几何雪花以及发光的金铜钱串。\n\n凹槽内部的地面铺满了厚厚的奶油色针织质感白雪。画面正中央站着一只憨态可掬的Q版毛毡小马（代表马年），它穿着喜庆的红色毛毡马甲，头戴传统虎头帽，作为节日使者神气地站立着。小马身旁是Q版毛毡质感的孙悟空与猪八戒，两人均身穿传统喜庆的唐装，孙悟空正调皮地挥舞着一串毛毡糖葫芦，猪八戒则笑盈盈地怀抱一个巨大的毛毡金元宝，进行着生动的场景互动。背景深处是Q版毛毡质感的南天门建筑，错落有致，富有层次感。旁边矗立着一棵毛毡质感的桃树，树枝上悬挂着微缩的红灯笼、中国结和祈福卡。雪地上自然散落着毛毡鞭炮、金元宝和被积雪覆盖的灌木丛。\n\n场景上方的半空中悬浮着独立的3D体积文字，没有任何背景板或卡片支撑。主文字为 'Happy New Year'，采用3D流体艺术字体，具有厚重的玻璃体积感；副文字为 '新年快乐'，采用粗体中国书法的3D挤压笔触。这些文字呈现哑光磨砂玻璃材质，表面呈现从深红到浅红的柔和渐变，半透明的材质投射出梦幻的彩色焦散光影，洒在下方的毛毡场景上。海报最底部的留白处，用浓墨色的优雅西方手写衬线体写着新年寄语 'May the new year bring you joy, peace, and prosperity.'，右下角用小号中文字体标注着来源 '——《新年祈愿》'。\n\n画面采用C4D和Octane渲染的大师级8K画质，浅景深营造出迷人的背景散景。光线柔和均匀，带有呼吸灯般的氛围深度，毛毡的细腻纤维、粗毛线的编织纹理与半透明磨砂玻璃的通透感完美交融，整体洋溢着浓郁、温暖、精致的东方新年喜庆氛围。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/item_3516_3.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "A 3D New Year greeting card poster inspired by the *Journey to the West* IP, in a vertical composition with a macro photography perspective. The entire scene presents an exquisitely detailed felt and chunky knitted wool material texture, resembling high-quality 3D blind-box collectible toys. At the center of the frame is a deep, window-frame-like recessed structure; the greeting card itself appears to float among clouds, with soft shadows at the bottom. The background is an Eastern ink-wash-style void environment, suffused with flowing light mist in pale champagne gold and premium foggy red. The space outside the poster is surrounded by fluttering red velvet ribbons, flowing golden light rays, blooming red plum blossom branches, strings of festive red lanterns, plump red persimmons, crystal-clear geometric snowflakes, and glowing strings of gold copper coins.\n\nThe ground inside the recess is covered with thick cream-colored knitted-texture white snow. Standing at the very center of the scene is an adorable chibi felt pony (representing the Year of the Horse), wearing a festive red felt vest and a traditional tiger-head hat, standing proudly as a festival messenger. Beside the pony are chibi felt-textured Sun Wukong and Zhu Bajie, both dressed in traditional festive Tang-style outfits. Sun Wukong is mischievously waving a string of felt tanghulu (candied hawthorn skewers), while Zhu Bajie is beaming and cradling an enormous felt gold yuanbao (ingot), engaging in a lively scene interaction. Deep in the background is a chibi felt-textured Nantianmen (Southern Heavenly Gate) architecture, arranged with staggered heights and rich layering. Beside it stands a felt-textured peach tree, with miniature red lanterns, Chinese knots, and prayer cards hanging from its branches. Felt firecrackers, gold yuanbao, and snow-covered shrubs are naturally scattered across the snowy ground.\n\nSuspended in mid-air above the scene are independent 3D volumetric text characters, without any backing panel or card support. The main text reads 'Happy New Year' in a 3D fluid art typeface with a thick glassy volumetric feel; the secondary text reads '新年快乐' in bold Chinese calligraphy with 3D extruded brushstrokes. These texts feature a matte frosted glass material with a soft gradient from deep red to light red on the surface. The semi-transparent material casts dreamy colored caustic light patterns onto the felt scene below. At the very bottom of the poster, in the whitespace margin, an elegant Western handwritten serif typeface in dense ink reads the New Year greeting 'May the new year bring you joy, peace, and prosperity.', with a small Chinese font annotation in the lower-right corner indicating the source '——《新年祈愿》' (New Year Wishes).\n\nThe scene is rendered in masterful 8K quality using C4D and Octane Render, with shallow depth of field creating a dream—",
    "prompt_zh": "{\n  \"applicable_models\": [\n    \"Seedream\",\n    \"Nano Banana Pro\"\n  ],\n  \"subject\": {\n    \"IP_Name\": \"输入你喜欢的游戏、小说、电影或电视剧的名称。\",\n    \"description\": \"基于[IP Name]的视觉冲击力强烈的大师级3D新年贺卡海报。采用竖版构图，中央有一个深邃的、类似窗户的凹槽。\",\n    \"material_style\": \"毛毡与粗编织毛线质感，真实细腻，盲盒玩具质感。\",\n    \"central_character\": {\n      \"identity\": \"一只可爱的Q版毛毡小马（代表马年）\",\n      \"expression\": \""
