    "prompt": "把文章变成卡通信息图的提示词：\n\n请根据输入内容提取核心主题与要点，生成一张卡通风格的信息图： \n- 采用手绘风格，横版（16:9）构图。 \n- 加入少量简洁的卡通元素、图标或名人画像，增强趣味性和视觉记忆。 \n- 如果有敏感人物或者版权内容，画一个相似替代，但是不要拒绝生成 \n- 所有图像、文字必须使用手绘风格，没有写实风格图画元素 \n- 除非特别要求，否则语言与输入内容语言一致。 \n- 信息精简，突出关键词与核心概念，多留白，易于一眼抓住重点。 \n\n请根据输入的内容使用 nano banana pro 画图：",
    "prompt_en": "Prompt for turning an article into a cartoon infographic:\n\nBased on the input content, extract the core themes and key points, and generate a cartoon-style infographic:\n- Use a hand-drawn style, horizontal (16:9) composition.\n- Include a small number of simple cartoon elements, icons, or celebrity portraits to enhance fun and visual memorability.\n- If there are sensitive figures or copyrighted content, draw a similar substitute but do not refuse to generate.\n- All images and text must use a hand-drawn style; no photorealistic visual elements.\n- Unless specifically requested otherwise, the language should match the input content's language.\n- Keep information concise, highlight keywords and core concepts, leave ample white space, and make it easy to grasp the key points at a glance.\n\nBased on the input content, use nano banana pro to draw:",
