    "revised_prompt": "奇幻风格的数字插画，展现了一个充满魔法气息的塔罗牌占卜场景。画面采用宽屏构图，视角为正面的俯视微倾斜角度，展示了一张铺着深紫色天鹅绒桌布的占卜桌面，桌布上隐约可见复杂的金色星象图和占星法阵刺绣。\n\n画面中央横向并排摆放着三张边缘镶有复古金箔的经典塔罗牌，卡牌表面微微散发出金色的魔法光芒。左侧的塔罗牌画面描绘了一轮巨大的满月、双塔以及仰望月亮的狼和狗，牌底部用英文大写衬线体清晰地写着 'THE MOON'。中间的塔罗牌画面是一位在星空下倾倒河水的女子，天空有八角星，牌底部的文字是 'THE STAR'。右侧的塔罗牌画面是一个巨大的命运轮盘以及角落里的四只神兽，牌底部写着 'WHEEL OF FORTUNE'。\n\n桌面的四周散落着各种魔法道具以丰富画面：左侧边缘放置着一个复古黄铜烛台，上面插着一根正在燃烧的白色粗蜡烛，橘黄色的烛光照亮了左侧区域并产生长长的阴影；右侧放置着一块不规则的紫水晶簇和一个底部带有繁复金属雕花的透明水晶球，水晶球内部闪烁着神秘的蓝色微光。空气中漂浮着点点发光的金色魔法光尘。\n\n画面中融合了具体的占卜信息文字：在画面顶部正中央，悬浮着华丽的、发着耀眼金光的哥特式英文字母 'Mystic Tarot Reading'。在画面的左上角，平铺着一张边缘带有轻微烧焦痕迹的羊皮纸条，上面用黑色的复古羽毛笔手写体清晰地写着求问者的生日信息 'Seeker Born: October 31, 1995'。在右上角，有一张对称放置的羊皮纸标签，上面用同样的字体写着今日的占卜日期 'Reading Date: May 15, 2024'。在三张塔罗牌的正下方，有一段优雅的金色发光衬线体英文作为占卜解读，居中横向排版，文字内容为 'The stars align for you. Embrace intuition, for fortune turns in your favor.'。\n\n整体色调以深沉的午夜蓝、神秘的暗紫色和闪耀的暖金色为主，运用了高质量的全局光照和体积光效果，光影对比强烈，营造出静谧、神秘且具有仪式感的魔法氛围。画面细节极其丰富，材质质感写实且逼真。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/item_3533_3.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "A fantasy-style digital illustration depicting a tarot card divination scene imbued with magical atmosphere. The composition adopts a widescreen format with a frontal, slightly tilted top-down perspective, showcasing a divination tabletop draped in deep purple velvet cloth, upon which intricate golden astrological charts and astrology magic circle embroidery are faintly visible.\n\nAt the center of the image, three classic tarot cards with vintage gold-leaf edges are arranged horizontally side by side, their surfaces emanating a faint golden magical glow. The left tarot card depicts a giant full moon, twin towers, and a wolf and dog gazing up at the moon, with 'THE MOON' clearly written at the bottom of the card in uppercase English serif typeface. The middle tarot card shows a woman pouring river water beneath a starry sky with an eight-pointed star above, and the text at the bottom reads 'THE STAR'. The right tarot card features a great Wheel of Fortune with four mythical beasts in the corners, with 'WHEEL OF FORTUNE' written at the bottom.\n\nScattered around the edges of the tabletop are various magical props to enrich the scene: on the left edge sits a vintage brass candlestick holding a burning thick white candle, its warm orange-yellow candlelight illuminating the left area and casting long shadows; on the right side lies an irregular amethyst cluster and a clear crystal ball with elaborate metalwork filigree at its base, the crystal ball flickering with a mysterious blue glow inside. Glowing golden magical light dust floats in the air.\n\nSpecific divination information text is incorporated into the scene: at the top center of the image, ornate Gothic English letters spelling 'Mystic Tarot Reading' hover, radiating dazzling golden light. In the upper left corner, a parchment strip with slightly scorched edges lies flat, bearing the seeker's birth information clearly written in black vintage quill-pen calligraphy: 'Seeker Born: October 31, 1995'. In the upper right corner, a symmetrically placed parchment label displays the divination date in the same script: 'Reading Date: May 15, 2024'. Directly below the three tarot cards, an elegant line of golden glowing serif English text serves as the divination interpretation, centered in horizontal layout, reading 'The stars align for you. Embrace intuition, for fortune turns in your fav",
    "prompt_zh": "请按照以下规则生成一张魔法塔罗牌占卜图像：\n\n【输入】\n\n- 用户生日：{user_birthday}\n- 今日日期：从系统自动获取（{today_date}）\n- 语言：{language, 默认为用户的首选语言}"
}, {
    "filename": "f975cd3e97d14e57be4d2e60deae1de6.png",
    "index": 3534,
    "title": "视觉笔记风格演示幻灯片",
    "title_en": "Presentation Slide Generation Prompt",
    "prompt": "创建一套演示文稿,采用白板、涂鸦的风格,注重分步说明，具有一致的彩色粗铅笔手绘风格，信息丰富，包含中文文字，使用 nano_banana 工具生成图片，提取核心的信息",
    "prompt_en": "Create a set of presentation slides in a whiteboard/doodle style, emphasizing step-by-step instructions with a consistent colorful thick pencil hand-drawn style, information-rich with Chinese text, extracting core information.",
    "source": "https://x.com/yanhua1010/status/1998983914208244097",
    "type": "t2i",
    "author": "@Yanhua",
    "author_link": "https://x.com/yanhua1010/status/1998983914208244097",
    "revised_prompt": "一张视觉笔记风格的宽屏演示幻灯片设计图。背景为带有淡灰色细线的网格纸，整体呈现出轻松、创意且具启发性的彩色马克笔和水彩手绘涂鸦风格。画面顶部中央使用蓝色马克笔质感的中文手写体书写着主标题：'2024产品创新战略'，标题下方垫有黄色水彩笔触的波浪形粗下划线。画面左侧区域展示了一个手绘思维导图，中心是一个带有黄色高亮底色的红色手绘圆圈，内部写着'核心目标'。从中心向外延伸出三条绿色的手绘弧线分支：左上角分支连接着写有'用户体验'的文本框，旁边画有一个黄色的微笑气泡图标，并继续分出'简化流程'和'界面优化'两个子节点；右侧分支写着'技术升级'，配有手绘的蓝色小齿轮图标，分出'AI赋能'和'云端同步'；左下方分支写着'市场拓展'，带有手绘的小火箭图标，分出'海外增长'和'下沉市场'。画面右侧区域展示业务流程图，用四个橙色手绘方框从上到下呈阶梯状排列，方框之间由带有黑色箭头的虚线连接。四个方框内分别写有：'1. 需求洞察'、'2. 敏捷开发'、'3. 灰度测试'、'4. 全量发布'。在'需求洞察'旁画有一个发光的灯泡图标，在'全量发布'旁画着一面飘扬的红旗。画面右下角有一块仿便利贴的淡黄色手绘方块区域，用于核心数据说明，顶部写有'核心增长指标'，下方画有一个绿色的上升趋势折线图，折线最高点用红色粗笔标注着'+45%'，旁边配有手写的关键数据：'月活增长预期'以及'留存率目标: 60%'。画面四周空白处随机点缀着几颗随性的黄色小星星涂鸦、蓝色的墨水飞溅点和红色的感叹号，排版清晰，图文结构紧凑。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/f975cd3e97d14e57be4d2e60deae1de6.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "A widescreen presentation slide design in a visual note-taking style. The background is grid paper with light gray fine lines, creating a relaxed, creative, and inspiring aesthetic with colorful marker and watercolor hand-drawn doodle elements. At the top center of the image, a blue marker-textured Chinese handwritten title reads: '2024 Product Innovation Strategy', underlined with a wavy yellow watercolor brushstroke. The left area features a hand-drawn mind map with a central red circle on a yellow highlight reading 'Core Goals', branching into three green hand-drawn curved lines: the upper-left branch connects to 'User Experience' with a yellow smiley icon, further dividing into 'Simplify Processes' and 'Interface Optimization'; the right branch reads 'Technology Upgrade' with a blue gear icon, splitting into 'AI Empowerment' and 'Cloud Sync'; the lower-left branch reads 'Market Expansion' with a rocket icon, dividing into 'Overseas Growth' and 'Tier-down Markets'. The right area shows a business flowchart with four orange hand-drawn boxes arranged in a staircase pattern, connected by dashed arrows: '1. Demand Insight', '2. Agile Development', '3. Gray-Scale Testing', '4. Full Release'. A lightbulb icon appears beside 'Demand Insight' and a waving red flag beside 'Full Release'. The lower-right corner features a sticky-note style area labeled 'Core Growth Metrics' with a green upward trend chart, the peak marked '+45%' in red, alongside 'Monthly Active User Growth Forecast' and 'Retention Target: 60%'. Decorative yellow stars, blue ink splashes, and red exclamation marks are scattered throughout.",
    "prompt_zh": "创建一套演示文稿，采用白板、涂鸦的风格，注重分步说明，具有一致的彩色粗铅笔手绘风格，信息丰富，包含中文文字，提取核心信息。"
