    "filename": "c00e081d367644c7aeeb90c1c6807f8a.png",
    "index": 3535,
    "title": "笔记本涂鸦朋克女孩素描",
    "title_en": "Chaotic Student Doodle Sketch Prompt",
    "prompt": "{\n  \"image_generation_task\": {\n    \"task_type\": \"text2img\",\n    \"subject\": \"portrait of a young man\",\n    \"constraint\": \"highly detailed notebook sketch\",\n    \n    \"artistic_direction\": {\n      \"medium\": {\n        \"substrate\": \"lined notebook paper\",\n        \"tools\": [\"blue ballpoint pen\", \"red gel pen\", \"black ink\"],\n        \"texture_quality\": \"raw, tactile, paper wrinkles, ink smudges\"\n      },\n      \"style_preset\": {\n        \"name\": \"chaotic_student_doodle\",\n        \"vibes\": [\"energetic\", \"messy\", \"horror vacui\", \"dense\"],\n        \"line_quality\": \"cross-hatching, scribbled shading, varying pressure\"\n      }\n    },\n\n    \"composition_details\": {\n      \"surrounding_elements\": [\n        \"handwritten notes\",\n        \"random arrows\",\n        \"musical notes\",\n        \"speech bubbles with '{argument name=\"speech bubble 1\" default=\"ZAP!\"}' and '{argument name=\"speech bubble 2\" default=\"WHOOSH!\"}'\",\n        \"doodled stars\"\n      ],\n      \"lighting_effect\": {\n        \"type\": \"vibrant outer glow\",\n        \"colors\": [\"neon blue\", \"electric red\"]\n      }\n    },\n\n    \"technical_specs\": {\n      \"aspect_ratio\": \"9:16\",\n      \"resolution\": \"4K\",\n      \"focus\": \"sharp center with artistic scribbles on edges\"\n    }\n  }\n}",
    "prompt_en": "Chaotic notebook doodle sketch of a mischievous punk girl with goggles. Drawn on crinkled lined paper with black ballpoint pen, neon green, and purple highlighter. Energetic cross-hatching, raw ink smudges, and dense scribbles. Surrounded by crossed-out math equations, tiny skulls, lightning bolts, and a speech bubble reading 'ERROR!'. The girl features a vibrant toxic green and ultraviolet outer glow. Sharp central focus.",
    "source": "https://x.com/Strength04_X/status/1999510253155799114",
    "type": "t2i",
    "author": "@𝐌𝐢𝐧𝐝𝐒𝐩𝐚𝐫𝐤",
    "author_link": "https://x.com/Strength04_X/status/1999510253155799114",
    "revised_prompt": "一幅横版的手绘涂鸦插画，绘制在带有明显褶皱痕迹的横线笔记本纸张上。画面中心是一个使用黑色圆珠笔快速勾勒出的调皮朋克女孩半身像。女孩留着凌乱的短发，额头上推着一副厚重的护目镜，嘴角扬起一抹恶作剧般的坏笑，脖子上戴着简单的铆钉项圈。她的绘制技法充满狂野的能量感，使用了密集的交叉排线、粗糙的涂鸦线条以及多处真实的墨水晕染污迹。女孩的轮廓外围包裹着一层醒目的荧光笔涂抹效果，呈现出强烈的霓虹有毒绿色与紫外线紫色交织的外部光晕，与黑色的圆珠笔线条形成强烈对比。\n\n在女孩头部上方偏右的位置，画着一个边缘不规则的黑色圆珠笔对话框，里面清晰地写着大写英文字母 'ERROR!'。在女孩周围宽阔的横线纸背景上，散布着大量随手涂鸦的元素。其中包括被凌乱的粗线条和巨大的叉号粗暴划掉的数学方程式，如 'x = (-b ± √(b² - 4ac)) / 2a'、'∫ e^x dx' 以及 'y = mx + b'。在这些破败的方程式之间，还穿插点缀着几个简笔画风格的小骷髅头图案和曲折的闪电符号，部分闪电和骷髅也被霓虹绿色和紫色的荧光笔随意涂抹高亮。画面呈现出强烈的中心对焦效果，女孩面部和核心涂鸦细节清晰锐利，而四周边缘的纸张纹理和零散符号则自然融入随性的氛围中，整体散发着叛逆、混乱且充满活力的风格。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/c00e081d367644c7aeeb90c1c6807f8a.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "A horizontal hand-drawn doodle illustration on visibly creased lined notebook paper. At the center is a mischievous punk girl bust portrait, rapidly sketched with a black ballpoint pen. She has messy short hair with heavy goggles pushed up on her forehead, a mischievous smirk, and a simple studded choker. The drawing technique is full of wild energy, using dense cross-hatching, rough scribbled lines, and multiple real ink smudges. A striking highlighter glow effect wraps around her outline in intense neon toxic green and ultraviolet purple, contrasting sharply with the black pen lines. Above and to the right of her head is an irregular black ballpoint pen speech bubble clearly reading 'ERROR!' in capital letters. Scattered across the lined paper background are numerous casual doodle elements, including math equations aggressively crossed out with thick lines and large X marks: 'x = (-b ± √(b² - 4ac)) / 2a', '∫ e^x dx', and 'y = mx + b'. Interspersed among these ruined equations are small skull doodles and zigzag lightning symbols, some highlighted with neon green and purple marker. The image features a strong center-focus effect with sharp details at the girl's face and core doodles, while the surrounding paper texture and scattered symbols blend into the casual atmosphere, radiating a rebellious, chaotic, and energetic style.",
    "prompt_zh": "笔记本涂鸦风格的朋克女孩素描，画在有褶皱的横线纸上，使用黑色圆珠笔、荧光绿和紫色荧光笔。密集的交叉排线、墨水污渍和涂鸦。周围是被划掉的数学公式、骷髅头、闪电和写着 'ERROR!' 的对话框。女孩有鲜明的荧光绿和紫外线紫色外部光晕。"
