    "prompt": "Stylebook,コラージュ,ステッカー強め,ポラロイド,いろんな表情で同一人物の写真いっぱい",
    "prompt_en": "Stylebook, collage, heavy stickers, Polaroid, lots of photos of the same person with various expressions.",
    "source": "https://x.com/SDT_side/status/1998402212935119068",
    "type": "t2i",
