    "revised_prompt": "这是一张手工剪贴簿风格的拼贴画，以白色纸张为背景，采用多格拼贴布局。画面中央及四周分布着多个拍立得风格的照片框，每个框内展示同一位粉色头发、黑色短发、粉色双马尾的动漫风格女孩，她身穿白色短袖上衣，背景为纯白色。照片中女孩展现出多种表情：左上角照片中她闭眼大笑，双颊泛红；中上方照片中她眨眼微笑；右上角照片中她表情惊讶，嘴巴微张；左下角照片中她双手托腮，嘴角上扬；中下方照片中她做出嘟嘴表情；右下角照片中她闭眼微笑，手指轻触脸颊。画面四周装饰有粉色和蓝色的波浪形和条纹和纸胶带，以及多个彩虹色、全息光泽的心形贴纸和闪光星星贴纸。背景中散布着手绘风格的动物涂鸦，包括左上角的兔子、左侧的猫咪、左下角的猫咪和兔子、中间的兔子、右侧的猫咪、右下角的猫咪和兔子，以及多个彩色的心形图案。整体色调明亮柔和，充满可爱和活泼的氛围，具有典型的日系卡通插画风格。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/57a216877afa4b26a2c375e5c19505cf.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "A handmade scrapbook-style collage on a white paper background with a multi-frame collage layout. Multiple Polaroid-style photo frames are distributed across the center and around the edges, each containing the same anime-style girl with pink hair and black short hair with pink twin-tails, wearing a white short-sleeve top against a pure white background. The girl displays various expressions across the photos: laughing with closed eyes and rosy cheeks in the upper left; winking and smiling in the upper center; surprised with a slightly open mouth in the upper right; resting her chin on both hands with upturned lips in the lower left; making a pouty face in the lower center; and closing her eyes with a gentle smile while touching her cheek in the lower right. The edges are decorated with pink and blue wavy and striped washi tape, along with multiple rainbow-colored holographic heart stickers and sparkling star stickers. The background is scattered with hand-drawn animal doodles including bunnies and cats, as well as colorful heart patterns. The overall tone is bright and soft, full of cute and lively atmosphere, with a typical Japanese cartoon illustration style.",
    "prompt_zh": "风格手册，拼贴画，贴纸感强，拍立得风格，同一人物不同表情的照片拼合。"
