    "author_link": "https://x.com/saniaspeaks_/status/2020827385030181360",
    "revised_prompt": "这是一张高角度俯拍的手机自拍照，画面主体为一名年轻亚裔女性，她正对着镜头开怀大笑，眼神直视镜头。她留着栗色长卷发，扎成一条松散的低马尾，几缕发丝在微风中飘动，额前留有空气刘海。她身穿一件白色的镂空钩针编织挂脖上衣，佩戴着一副时尚的墨镜，墨镜架在头顶，耳朵上戴着金色的小圆环耳饰。她的妆容自然，涂着桃色的唇膏，脸颊上有淡淡的腮红。\n\n拍摄场景位于户外，背景是一处海边的露台或咖啡馆露台。背景中可以看到白色的石质栏杆，栏杆外是波光粼粼的深蓝色大海，海面上有白色的浪花，远处隐约可见海岸线和山峦。光线柔和温暖，呈现出夕阳或日落时分的金色调，阳光洒在人物的头发和肩膀上，形成逆光效果，使发丝边缘带有光晕。画面左侧有一张木质桌子的一角，桌上放着一个白色的杯子，杯口似乎有蒸汽升起，暗示着饮品的温度。整体构图以人物为中心，背景虚化处理突出了主体，色彩饱和度适中，画面清晰锐利，具有典型的社交媒体生活照风格。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/59368ac95ac34ee58010f4c352df1c1a.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "A high-angle overhead smartphone selfie with a young Asian woman as the main subject, laughing joyfully toward the camera with direct eye contact. She has long wavy chestnut hair tied in a loose low ponytail, with a few strands blowing in the breeze and airy bangs on her forehead. She wears a white crochet halter top with open-knit patterns, a pair of fashionable sunglasses perched on top of her head, and small gold hoop earrings. Her makeup is natural with a peach lip tint and subtle blush. The shooting location is outdoors, with a seaside terrace or café patio in the background. White stone balustrades are visible in the background, beyond which lies a sparkling deep blue sea with white wave crests, and a distant coastline and mountains are faintly visible. The light is warm and soft, presenting a golden tone of sunset, with sunlight falling on the subject's hair and shoulders creating a backlighting effect with a luminous halo around the hair edges. The left side of the frame shows a corner of a wooden table with a white cup, seemingly with steam rising from it. The overall composition is centered on the subject with background bokeh highlighting the main figure, moderate color saturation, sharp and clear image quality, in a typical social media lifestyle photo style.",
    "prompt_zh": "一名年轻亚裔女性在海边阳台上高角度手机自拍，开怀大笑，直视镜头。栗色长卷发扎成松散低马尾，刘海在海风中飘动。穿着白色镂空钩针挂脖上衣，墨镜架在头顶，戴金色小圆环耳饰。背景是海边咖啡馆露台，日落金色光线，社交媒体生活照风格。"
