    "title_en": "Futuristic Fluffy Glass Typography Art",
    "prompt": "{\n  \"model\": \"Nano Banana Pro \",\n  \"aspect_ratio\": \"16:9\",\n  \"style\": \"futuristic fluffy glass typography\",\n  \"prompt\": {\n    \"subject\": \"Futuristic AI name art\",\n    \"text\": \"{argument name=\"text to render\" default=\"Future AI\"}\",\n    \"text_position\": \"center\",\n    \"text_design\": {\n      \"font_style\": \"stylish futuristic custom typography\",\n      \"texture\": \"soft fluffy fibers blended with transparent glass effect\",\n      \"material\": \"frosted glass + plush fluffy surface\",\n      \"shape\": \"bold, smooth, slightly curved futuristic letters\",\n      \"depth\": \"high 3D depth with glass-like thickness\",\n      \"edges\": \"rounded glass edges with soft fluffy diffusion\",\n      \"finish\": \"premium, glossy, futuristic aesthetic\"\n    },\n    \"color_palette\": {\n      \"text_colors\": [\n        \"cyan\",\n        \"electric purple\",\n        \"neon pink\",\n        \"aqua blue\"\n      ],\n      \"gradient\": \"multi-color futuristic gradient flowing through glass text\"\n    },\n    \"lighting\": {\n      \"type\": \"soft futuristic studio lighting\",\n      \"highlights\": \"glass reflections with subtle glow\",\n      \"shadows\": \"soft ambient shadow beneath text\"\n    },\n    \"background\": {\n      \"type\": \"plain attractive futuristic canvas\",\n      \"color\": \"smooth gradient background ({argument name=\"background color\" default=\"deep blue to purple\"})\",\n      \"texture\": \"clean matte with soft light falloff\",\n      \"match_with_text\": \"harmonized futuristic color tones\"\n    },\n    \"composition\": {\n      \"focus\": \"hero glass-fluffy name typography\",\n      \"style\": \"clean, modern, high-end\",\n      \"balance\": \"perfectly centered\"\n    },\n    \"quality\": {\n      \"resolution\": \"ultra HD\",\n      \"detail\": \"high-detail glass refraction and fluffy fibers\",\n      \"sharpness\": \"crisp edges with soft diffusion\"\n    }\n  },\n  \"negative_prompt\": [\n    \"simple flat font\",\n    \"opaque solid text\",\n    \"rough glass\",\n    \"dirty texture\",\n    \"busy background\",\n    \"extra objects\",\n    \"logo\",\n    \"watermark\",\n    \"grain\",\n    \"blur\"\n  ]\n}",
    "prompt_en": "A futuristic fluffy glass typography artwork using Nano Banana Pro model, 16:9 aspect ratio, featuring soft glowing text with plush fuzzy textures and translucent glass materials.",
    "source": "https://x.com/mahivisuals/status/2019798931866321254",
    "type": "t2i",
    "author": "@Manish Bhati",
    "author_link": "https://x.com/mahivisuals/status/2019798931866321254",
    "revised_prompt": "高端商业3D网页UI头图素材，采用16:9宽幅横向构图。画面视觉中心完美居中排列着大写英文字母 'NEXUS'，字体采用流畅倾斜的科幻风格排版。字母的形体由一种超现实的混合材质构成：内部核心为厚实且具有虹彩效果的透明亚克力玻璃，玻璃通体折射出由鲜艳的珊瑚色、发光的青绿色与流动的银色交织而成的流体渐变光影；外部则紧密包裹着一层发光的超柔软细密绒毛。毛茸茸的外层将玻璃内部透出的光线进行漫反射，在字母周围形成一圈生物发光般的霓虹光晕。画面布光采用戏剧性的底部光源与字母内部照明相结合，精准勾勒出亚克力玻璃表面锐利且高光泽的反射，同时突显了外部绒毛极致细腻、蓬松的物理纹理质感。背景为极简的深石板灰色，在居中文本的正后方带有一层微妙的青绿色径向渐变光晕，使主体字母在暗色背景中脱颖而出。整体画面呈现出8K分辨率级别的超高清晰度，材质纹理逼真，构图干净现代，充满前卫的数字艺术氛围。",
    "image": "https://eb118-file.cdn.bcebos.com/ernie-image/e3e23764f76e4444a6613a14a9419c84.png",
    "revised_prompt_en": "A widescreen digital artwork in 16:9 format featuring the word 'ERNIE' rendered in bold, rounded 3D letters with a futuristic aesthetic. Each letter has a soft, plush exterior surface reminiscent of stuffed toy textures, covered in fine peach-pink fuzz with warm fuzzy fibers visible at the edges. Beneath the fuzzy outer layer, the inner structure is transparent glass-like material with visible luminous veins. The background is a deep gradient from midnight blue to dark purple-black, with glowing particles and soft holographic light halos floating around the letters.",
    "prompt_zh": "使用 Nano Banana Pro 模型创建未来感毛绒玻璃字体艺术作品，16:9 比例，具有柔和发光文字、毛绒触感纹理和半透明玻璃材质效果。"
